The Romans enlist the Franks and the Alemanni to defend the Rhine border. The Huns occupy the Romanian plains of Pannonia. The Eleusinian Mysteries come to an end, as Alaric I destroys the ancient sites in Greece. Emperor An succeeds Emperor Xiaowu as ruler of the Chinese Jin Dynasty.

397

397

柏柏尔王子吉尔多煽动叛乱，反对罗马皇帝霍诺留斯。

The Berber prince, Gildo, foments a rebellion against the Roman Emperor Honorius

399

399

雅兹德格尔德一世成为波斯国王。中国佛教史学家法显开始了他的印度和斯里兰卡之旅，这段旅程被记录在他的著作《佛教王国记》中。

Yazdegerd I becomes king of Persia. Chinese Buddhist historian, Fa-Hien, begins his journey through India and Sri Lanka, written about in his work, A Record of Buddhistic Kingdoms, Being an Account by the Chinese Monk Fa-Hien of his Travels in India and Ceylon in Search of the Buddhist Books of Discipline.

400

400

世界人口达到2.06亿。阿拉里克首次入侵意大利。大约在同一时期：法兰克人在荷兰北部定居；汪达尔人开始从达契亚和匈牙利向西迁徙；铁器在东非传播；南非古城大津巴布韦开始建造；笈多王朝扩张，最终控制了整个印度；佛教经典被翻译成中文；以蒙特阿尔班为都城的萨波特克王国在墨西哥南部繁荣发展；菊花传入日本。波斯天文学家发明了星盘。

The population of the world reaches 206 million. The first invasion of Italy by Alaric. Around this date: The Franks establish themselves in northern Holland; the Vandals start to move westward from Dacia and Hungary; the use of iron spreads through eastern Africa; construction begins at Great Zimbabwe, an ancient South African city; the Gupta empire grows until it controls all of India; Buddhist scriptures are translated into Chinese; the Zapotec state with its capital at Monte Alban flourishes in southern Mexico; chrysanthemums are introduced to Japan. Persian astronomers invent the astrolabe.

401

401

西哥特人进攻意大利北部。《摩诃婆罗多》 ——古印度两大梵文史诗之一——完成。西哥特人在波伦提亚战役中战败。

The Visigoths attack northern Italy. The Mahabharata, one of the two major Sanskrit epics of ancient India, is completed. The Visigoths are defeated at the Battle of Pollentia.

402

402

阿瓦尔人在舍伦的领导下建立了一个游牧帝国，疆域从蒙古延伸到额尔齐斯河。

The Avars, led by Shelun, establish a nomadic empire that ranges from Mongolia to the Irtysh.

404

404

最后一场角斗士比赛在罗马举行。

The last gladiatorial competition takes place in Rome.

405

405

亚美尼亚字母是由亚美尼亚僧侣梅斯罗布·马什多茨发明的。

The Armenian alphabet is invented by Mesrob Mashdots, an Armenian monk.

406

406

驻扎在不列颠的罗马军团发动叛乱，推举马库斯为新皇帝；马库斯遇刺身亡，格拉提安继位。罗马教堂首次使用彩色玻璃。

Roman legions in Britain mutiny against Honorius and select Marcus as their new Emperor; he is assassinated and replaced by Gratianus. Stained glass is used for the first time in churches in Rome.

407

407

格拉提亚努斯遇刺身亡，君士坦丁三世接管了罗马在不列颠的驻军；他率领罗马军队从不列颠撤往高卢，占领了阿尔勒，这通常被视为罗马从不列颠撤军的标志。汪达尔人入侵高卢。

Gratianus is assassinated, and Constantine III takes over the Roman garrison in Britain; he leads the Roman military units from Britain to Gaul, occupying Arles, generally seen as Rome’s withdrawal from Britain. The Vandals invade Gaul.

408

408

君士坦丁三世攻占西班牙。狄奥多西二世继承其父阿卡狄乌斯的皇位，成为东罗马帝国皇帝；匈奴人进攻东罗马帝国，但被击退。

Constantine III captures Hispania. Theodosius II succeeds his father, Arcadius, as Emperor of the Eastern Roman Empire; the Huns attack the Eastern Empire, but are repulsed.

409

409

汪达尔人、阿兰人和苏维汇人突破君士坦丁三世的防线，占领了西班牙。西哥特国王阿拉里克一世第二次围攻罗马，并拥立普里斯库斯·阿塔罗斯为西罗马皇帝。西班牙、高卢和意大利半岛爆发饥荒。

The Vandals, Alans and Suevi break through Constantine III’s garrisons and take Hispania. The Visigothic king, Alaric I, lays siege to Rome for a second time; he sets up Priscus Attalus as Western Emperor. There is famine in Hispania, Gaul and the Italian Peninsula.

410

410

西哥特人洗劫了罗马。

The Visigoths sack Rome.

412

412

西哥特人在阿拉里克的继任者阿陶尔夫的带领下，进军高卢南部。

The Visigoths move into the south of Gaul, led by Ataulf, successor to Alaric.

413

413

库玛拉·笈多一世继承其父旃陀罗笈多成为笈多王朝的统治者。

Kumara Gupta I succeeds his father Chandragupta as ruler of the Gupta Empire.

415

415

西哥特人离开高卢纳博讷，入侵西班牙。犹太人被逐出亚历山大港。喀拉喀托火山爆发。

The Visigoths leave Gallia Narbonensis and invade Hispania. The Jews are expelled from Alexandria. Krakatoa erupts.

419

419

恭帝继承安帝之位，成为中国晋朝的统治者。

Emperor Gong succeeds Emperor An as ruler of the Chinese Jin dynasty.

420

420

巴赫拉姆五世继承亚兹德格尔德成为波斯国王。金朝在中国灭亡；刘瑜（刘宋武帝）是宋朝的开国君主。

Bahram V succeeds Yazdegerd as king of Persia. The Jin Dynasty ends in China; Liu Yu (Emperor Wu of Liu Song) is the first ruler of the Song Dynasty.

421

421

君士坦提乌斯三世成为西罗马帝国的共同皇帝。

Constantius III becomes joint-emperor of the Western Empire.

423

423

霍诺留去世后，高级官员约翰内斯夺取了西罗马帝国的皇位，并被宣布为皇帝。

On the death of Honorius, Joannes, a senior civil servant, seizes the throne of the Western Roman Empire, and is declared Emperor.

424

424

宋文帝继承宋绍帝成为中国宋朝的统治者。

Song Wen Di succeeds Song Shao Di as ruler of the Chinese Song Dynasty.

425

425

瓦伦提尼安三世成为西罗马皇帝。

Valentinian III becomes Western Roman Emperor.

426

426

汪达尔人的国王冈德里克也成为了阿兰人的国王。

King Gunderic of the Vandals also becomes king of the Alans.

428

428

盖塞里克成为汪达尔人和阿兰人的国王。

Geiseric becomes king of the Vandals and Alans.

430

430

圣帕特里克在传教之旅中抵达爱尔兰。冯霸之后，冯弘继位成为北燕皇帝，北燕是当时争夺中国统治权的诸侯国之一。

St Patrick reaches Ireland on his missionary expedition. Feng Ba is succeeded by Feng Hong as emperor of the Northern Yan, one of the states vying for control of China.

434

434

效力于皇帝瓦伦提尼安三世的将军埃提乌斯夺取了罗马政权，统治了20年。匈奴王阿提拉与其兄弟布莱达一起控制了匈奴各部。

Aëtius, a general in the service of Emperor Valentinian III, takes power in Rome, holding it for 20 years. Attila the Hun, with his brother Bleda, gains control over the Hun tribes.

436

436

匈奴王阿提拉进攻勃艮第，屠杀了王室。

Attila the Hun attacks Burgundy, wiping out the royal family.

438

438

亚兹德格尔德二世成为波斯国王。

Yazdegerd II becomes king of Persia.

439

439

迦太基被汪达尔人攻陷。中国北方在北魏王朝的统治下统一，北朝时代开始。

Carthage falls to the Vandals. North China is united under the Northern Wei Dynasty; the era of the Northern Dynasties begins.

440

440

汪达尔国王盖塞里克攻占西西里岛。禅宗创始人菩提达摩出生。

Geiseric, king of the Vandals, captures Sicily. Bodhidharma, the founder of Zen Buddhism, is born.

443

443

勃艮第人在罗讷河畔建立了一个王国。

The Burgundians create a kingdom on the banks of the Rhône.

445

445

匈奴王阿提拉进攻西欧。

Attila the Hun attacks Western Europe.

447

447

第一个英格兰王国诞生于不列颠统治者沃提根将萨尼特赐予撒克逊领袖亨吉斯特之时。匈奴王阿提拉与罗马人在乌图斯河战役中交锋，双方战成平局。匈奴人入侵巴尔干半岛，最远到达温泉关。

The first English kingdom is created when Thanet is granted by Vortigern, the ruler of the Britons, to the Saxon leader Hengist. Attila the Hun meets the Romans in the indecisive Battle of the Utus. The Huns invade the Balkans as far as Thermopylae.

450

450

撒克逊人、盎格鲁人和朱特人入侵不列颠。阿斯帕尔和普尔凯莉娅拥立马尔西安为东罗马皇帝。大约在同一时期，美洲最大的土坯建筑——太阳神庙（Huaca del Sol）建成。

Saxons, Angles and Jutes invade Britain. Marcian is proclaimed Eastern Emperor by Aspar and Pulcheria. Around this date, the Huaca del Sol, the largest adobe structure in the Americas, is built.

451

451

阿提拉在沙隆战役中被西罗马将军埃提乌斯击败。迦克墩公会议正式确立了基督教正统教义。在瓦尔塔南茨战役中，亚美尼亚军队被波斯军队击败。

Attila is defeated at Chalons by Western Roman general, Aëtius. The Council of Chalcedon formalizes Christian orthodoxy. At the Battle of Vartanantz, the Armenian army is defeated by the Persians.

452

452

阿提拉入侵意大利后去世。太武帝之后，南安王继位，文成帝继位，成为中国北魏王朝的统治者。

Attila invades Italy but dies. Tai Wu Di is succeeded by Nan An Wang, and then by Wen Cheng Di as ruler of the Northern Wei Dynasty in China.

453

453

狄奥多里克二世继承其兄托里斯蒙德的王位，成为西哥特国王。

Theodoric II succeeds his brother, Thorismund, as king of the Visigoths.

454

454

瓦伦丁尼安三世皇帝在拉文纳刺杀了埃提乌斯。

Emperor Valentinian III assassinates Aëtius in Ravenna.

455

455

瓦伦提尼安三世被埃提乌斯的前士兵谋杀，以报复瓦伦提尼安在前一年杀死埃提乌斯。佩特罗尼乌斯·马克西姆斯继位为帝，但后来被愤怒的暴民杀害；罗马军事统帅阿维图斯被拥立为帝。罗马遭到汪达尔人的洗劫。东哥特人征服了潘诺尼亚和达尔马提亚。斯坎达笈多继承鸠摩罗笈多成为笈多王朝的统治者。

Valentinian III is murdered by former soldiers of Aëtius, in revenge for Valentinian’s killing of Aëtius the previous year. Petronius Maximus becomes Emperor but is later killed by an angry mob; Roman military commander Avitus is proclaimed Emperor. Rome is plundered by the Vandals. The Ostrogoths conquer Pannonia and Dalmatia. Skandagupta succeeds Kumaragupta as ruler of the Gupta Empire.

456

456

圣帕特里克以传教主教的身份重返爱尔兰。

St Patrick returns to Ireland as a missionary bishop.

457

457

在克雷福德战役中，四千名不列颠人在与亨吉斯特及其子奥伊斯克的战斗中阵亡。马约里安被拥立为西罗马皇帝，而利奥一世则成为东罗马皇帝。希尔德里克一世继承墨洛维奇成为法兰克国王。霍尔米兹德三世成为波斯国王。

Four thousand Britons are slain at Crayford in battle against Hengist and his son Oisc. Majorian is declared Western Roman Emperor, while Leo I becomes emperor in the east. Childeric I succeeds Merovech as king of the Franks. Hormizd III becomes king of Persia.

460

460

马约里安皇帝被西哥特人击败。科普特教会脱离亚历山大东正教会。亥姆霍兹人征服贵霜人并进入印度。

Emperor Majorian is defeated by the Visigoths. The Coptic Church splits from the Orthodox Church of Alexandria. The Hepthalites conquer the Kushans and enter India.

461

461

马约里安辞职，利比乌斯·塞维鲁成为皇帝。

Majorian resigns and Libius Severus becomes Emperor.

462

462

古代世界七大奇迹之一的宙斯神像在被移至君士坦丁堡后毁于火灾。

The Statue of Zeus, one of the Seven Wonders of the Ancient World, is destroyed by fire after being moved to Constantinople.

465

465

宋谦飞帝和宋明帝先后成为中国宋朝的统治者。

Song Qian Fei Di and then Song Ming Di become rulers of the Song Dynasty in China.

466

466

利奥一世皇帝击退了匈奴人对达契亚的入侵。欧里克继承其兄狄奥多里克二世的王位，成为西哥特国王。

Emperor Leo I repels the Hun invasion of Dacia. Euric succeeds his brother Theodoric II as king of the Visigoths.

467

467

安提米乌斯成为西罗马皇帝。

Anthemius becomes Western Roman Emperor.

471

471

萧文帝继承先文帝成为北魏王朝的统治者。

Xiao Wen Di succeeds Xian Wen Di as ruler of the Chinese Northern Wei Dynasty.

472

472

里西默将军宣布奥利布里乌斯为皇帝，并围攻了西罗马皇帝安提米乌斯所在的罗马城；安提米乌斯在逃离该城时被杀。

General Ricimer proclaims Olybrius Emperor, and places Rome, where Western Emperor Anthemius is located, under siege; Anthemius is slain fleeing the city.

473

473

格利塞里乌斯被尊为西罗马皇帝。贡多巴德成为勃艮第国王。

Glycerius is named Western Emperor. Gundobad becomes king of the Burgundians.

474

474

尤利乌斯·尼波斯成为西罗马皇帝，废黜了格利塞里乌斯。利奥二世短暂成为东罗马皇帝，他去世后，芝诺继位，与汪达尔人缔结条约，结束了长达45年的战争。

Julius Nepos becomes Western Roman Emperor, deposing Glycerius. Leo II briefly becomes Eastern Emperor and on his death Zeno takes over, concluding a treaty with the Vandals that ends 45 years of war.

475

475

芝诺皇帝被迫逃离君士坦丁堡。巴西利斯库斯在君士坦丁堡被拥立为东罗马皇帝。《塔木德》（犹太教律法的主要来源）完成。菩提达摩前往中国。

Emperor Zeno is forced to flee Constantinople. Basiliscus is acclaimed Eastern Emperor in Constantinople. The Talmud, the source of the majority of Jewish religious law, is completed. Bodhidharma travels to China.

476

476

这一日期被认为是罗马帝国灭亡的标志；末代西罗马皇帝罗慕路斯·奥古斯都被日耳曼入侵者奥多亚克驱逐，奥多亚克占领了这座城市。芝诺被拥立为东罗马皇帝。

The date regarded as representing the fall of the Roman Empire; the last Western Emperor, Romulus Augustus, is expelled by the Germanic invader Odoacer who occupies the city. Zeno is restored as the Eastern Roman Emperor.

477

477

胡内里克成为汪达尔人的国王。宋顺帝继承宋侯飞帝，成为中国宋朝的统治者。

Huneric becomes king of the Vandals. Song Shun Di succeeds Song Hou Fei Di as ruler of the Chinese Song Dynasty.

478

478

第一批神社建于日本。

The first Shinto shrines are built in Japan.

479

479

宋朝结束，南齐王朝建立；齐高帝是南齐王朝的第一位统治者。

The end of the Song Dynasty and beginning of the Southern Qi Dynasty in southern China; Qi Gao Di is the first ruler of the Qi Dynasty.

480

480

奥多亚克挫败了尤利乌斯·尼波斯夺回意大利的企图；尤利乌斯战死。纳拉辛哈笈多·巴拉迪蒂亚继承其父斯坎达笈多，成为笈多王朝的统治者。

Odoacer defeats an attempt by Julius Nepos to recapture Italy; Julius is killed. Narasimhagupta Baladitya succeeds his father Skandagupta as ruler of the Gupta Empire.

481

481

克洛维一世在希尔德里克一世去世后成为法兰克国王。

Clovis I becomes king of the Franks upon the death of Childeric I.

482

482

齐高帝成为中国南齐王朝的统治者。

Qi Gao Di becomes ruler of the Chinese Southern Qi Dynasty.

484

484

阿拉里克二世继承欧里克成为西哥特国王。贡萨蒙德成为汪达尔国王。

Alaric II succeeds Euric as king of the Visigoths. Gunthamund becomes king of the Vandals.

486

486

罗马在高卢的统治随着罗马总督西阿格里乌斯在苏瓦松被克洛维一世率领的法兰克人击败而结束。

Roman rule in Gaul ends with the defeat at Soissons of the Roman governor Syagrius by the Franks under Clovis I.

488

488

亨吉斯特去世，其子奥伊斯克继位，成为肯特国王。狄奥多里克大帝成为东哥特国王，入侵意大利。哥特人吉皮德人攻占贝尔格莱德。卡瓦德一世继承巴拉什的王位，成为波斯国王。

Hengist dies and is succeeded by his son Oisc as king of Kent. Theodoric the Great becomes king of the Ostrogoths and invades Italy. The Gothic tribe, the Gepids, capture Belgrade. Kavadh I succeeds Balash in Persia.

489

489

狄奥多里克在伊松佐河和维罗纳战役中击败奥多亚克，强行进入意大利。中国兴建了大型佛教寺庙；中国北方建成了第一座孔庙。

Theodoric defeats Odoacer at the battles of Isonzo and Verona, forcing his way into Italy. Large Buddhist temples are built in China; the first Confucian temple is constructed in northern China.

490

490

奥多亚克的军队在米兰向狄奥多里克大帝投降。

Odoacer’s army surrenders to Theodoric the Great in Milan.

491

491

南撒克逊人的第一位国王埃勒围攻并征服了不列颠南部的设防城镇安德里图姆。阿纳斯塔修斯一世成为拜占庭帝国的统治者。

Ælle, the first king of the south Saxons, besieges and conquers the fortified town of Anderitum in southern Britain. Anastasius I becomes ruler of the Byzantine Empire.

493

493

圣帕特里克去世；争夺圣帕特里克遗体的战役爆发。奥多亚克与狄奥多里克大帝媾和，但后来被狄奥多里克大帝所杀。

St Patrick dies; the Battle for the Body of St. Patrick is fought. Odoacer makes peace with Theodoric the Great, but is later killed by him.

494

494

教宗格拉修斯册封圣乔治为圣人。叙利亚拉塔基亚发生地震，造成严重破坏。

Pope Gelasius canonizes St George. An earthquake devastates Latakia in Syria.

495

495

威塞克斯的塞尔迪克袭击了汉普郡。

Cerdic of Wessex raids Hampshire.

496

496

克洛维一世在托尔比亚克战役中击败阿拉曼尼人，并在兰斯接受天主教洗礼。特拉萨蒙德成为汪达尔国王。波斯国王卡瓦德一世被其兄贾马斯普废黜并流放。中国北魏统治家族拓跋家族改姓元。

Clovis I defeats the Alamanni in the Battle of Tolbiac and accepts Catholic baptism at Rheims. Thrasamund becomes king of the Vandals. Kavadh I of Persia is deposed and exiled by his brother Djamasp. The ruling Tuoba family in the Chinese Northern Wei Dynasty change their family name to Yuan.

497

497

阿勒曼尼人在波恩附近被克洛维一世率领的法兰克人击败。印度天文学家和数学家阿耶波多计算出圆周率 (π) 为：62832/20000 = 3.1416，精确到小数点后四位。

The Alemanni are defeated by the Franks under Clovis I near Bonn. Aryabhata, an Indian astronomer and mathematician, calculates pi (π) to be: 62832/20000 = 3.1416, correct to four rounded-off decimal places.

499

499

波斯国王卡瓦德一世废黜其兄贾马斯普，重登波斯王位。印度天文学家阿耶波多发明了数字零。

Kavadh I of Persia deposes his brother Djamasp and regains the throne of Persia. Indian astronomer, Aryabhatra, invents the number zero.

500

500

东哥特人狄奥多里克成为罗马帝国在意大利残余领土的统治者。西哥特人统治西班牙。中国北魏宣武帝成为北魏王朝的君主。大约在同一时期：蒙斯巴多尼库斯战役，罗马-不列颠人和凯尔特人击败盎格鲁-撒克逊军队；英格兰七国时代开始；威塞克斯王国建立；传奇的达尔里阿达国王弗格斯·莫尔在苏格兰开始统治；瑞典建造了艾尔石纪念碑；加纳帝国成为西非最重要的强权；中亚游牧民族匈奴摧毁了强大的印度笈多王朝；中国局势动荡；图勒人迁徙到阿拉斯加；北美霍普韦尔文化建造了精美的墓葬，制作陶器，并使用铁制武器。起源于东南亚的波利尼西亚人定居在夏威夷群岛和复活节岛，并继续向东迁徙。

Ostrogoth Theodoric becomes ruler of what remains of the Roman Empire in Italy. The Visigoths rule Spain. Emperor Xuanwu of Northern Wei China becomes sovereign of the Northern Wei Dynasty. Around this date: The Battle of Mons Badonicus in which Romano-British and Celts defeat an Anglo-Saxon army; the beginning of the Heptarchy (seven kingdoms) period in England; the Kingdom of Wessex is founded; the legendary king of Dál Riata, Fergus Mór, begins his reign in Scotland; the monument of Ale’s Stones is built in Sweden; the Ghanaian Empire becomes the most important power in West Africa; the Huns, a nomadic Central Asian people, destroy the powerful Gupta Empire of India; instability in China; the Thule people move into Alaska; Hopewell culture in northern America builds elaborate burial mounds, makes pottery, and uses iron weapons; Polynesians, originating in South-East Asia, settle in the Hawaiian Islands and on Easter Island, and continue to travel eastwards.

501

501

齐和帝继承齐东训侯成为中国南齐王朝的统治者。

Qi He Di succeeds Qi Dong Hun Hou as the ruler of the Chinese Southern Qi Dynasty.

502

502

中国南方的南齐王朝灭亡，梁王朝建立；梁武帝继齐和帝之后建立梁王朝。

The Southern Qi Dynasty in southern China ends and the Liang Dynasty is founded; Liang Wu Di succeeds Qi He Di.

503

503

拜占庭帝国与波斯之间爆发战争，战争持续到公元557年。

War breaks out between the Byzantine Empire and Persia, lasting until 557.

504

504

狄奥多里克大帝击败了吉皮德人。

Theodoric the Great defeats the Gepids.

506

506

《阿拉里克法典》是一部罗马法律汇编，由西哥特国王阿拉里克二世下令编纂。

The Breviary of Alaric, a collection of Roman law, is compiled by order of Alaric II, king of the Visigoths.

507

507

西撒克逊人入侵英格兰西南部的布立吞王国杜姆诺尼亚，并在隆博斯战役中击败西威尔士人。他们还在内特利战役中杀死了强大的不列颠国王纳坦利奥德。克洛维一世在普瓦捷附近击败西哥特人，结束了西哥特人在高卢的统治。格萨莱克继承其父阿拉里克二世的王位，成为西哥特国王。

The West Saxons invade Dumnonia, a Brythonic kingdom in south-west England and defeat the West Welsh at Llongborth. They also slay a powerful British king named Natanleod at the Battle of Netley. Clovis I defeats the Visigoths near Poitiers, ending Visigothic power in Gaul. Gesalec succeeds his father Alaric II as king of the Visigoths.

508

508

克洛维一世将巴黎（当时称为卢泰西亚）定为首都。

Clovis I establishes Paris, known as Lutetia, as his capital

511

511

克洛维一世去世后，法兰克王国分裂为四。希尔德贝尔特一世成为巴黎国王；克洛泰尔一世成为苏瓦松国王；克洛多梅尔成为奥尔良国王；泰德里克一世成为兰斯和奥斯特拉西亚国王。

The Frankish kingdom is split in four after the death of Clovis I. Childebert I becomes king of Paris; Clotaire I king of Soissons; Chlodomer king of Orléans, and Theuderic I king of Rheims and Austrasia.

512

512

威尔士守护圣人圣大卫诞辰。已知最早的阿拉伯字母文字，写于叙利亚的泽贝德。岛国鱼山国被朝鲜新罗王朝将军李司甫征服。

The birth of St David, patron saint of Wales. The earliest known dated text in the Arabic alphabet, is written at Zebed in Syria. The island nation of Usan-guk is conquered by the Korean Silla Dynasty general, Lee Sabu.

516

516

西吉斯蒙德成为勃艮第国王。

Sigismund becomes king of Burgundy.

518

518

查士丁成为拜占庭皇帝。

Justin becomes Byzantine Emperor.

519

519

塞迪克成为威塞克斯国王。

Cerdic becomes king of Wessex.

520

520

东盎格利亚王国建立。菩提达摩抵达中国。

The kingdom of East Anglia is created. Bodhidharma arrives in China.

522

522

阿马拉里克成为西哥特国王。优素福·杜·努瓦斯夺取也门政权。

Amalaric becomes king of the Visigoths. Yusuf dhu-Nuwas captures power in Yemen.

523

523

希尔德里克成为汪达尔人的国王。爱尔兰圣布里吉德逝世。

Hilderic becomes king of the Vandals. The death of St Brigid of Ireland.

524

524

法兰克人在韦泽朗斯战役中击败勃艮第人。法兰克国王克洛多梅尔去世后，希尔德贝尔特一世吞并了奥尔良和沙特尔。罗马基督教哲学家波伊提乌出版了《哲学的慰藉》 。

The Franks defeat the Burgundians in the Battle of Vézeronce. Childebert I annexes Orléans and Chartres after the death of Chlodomer, king of the Franks. Roman Christian philosopher, Boethius, publishes the Consolations of Philosophy.

525

525

英格兰东北部的伯尼西亚由盎格鲁人定居。阿拉伯南部的也门被阿克苏姆国王卡莱布征服；他在那里修建了教堂。

Bernicia in north-east England is settled by the Angles. The southern Arabian country of Yemen is conquered by King Kaleb of Axum; he builds churches.

526

526

阿塔拉里克继承狄奥多里克成为东哥特国王。叙利亚和安条克发生地震，造成约30万人死亡。

Athalaric succeeds Theodoric as king of the Ostrogoths. An earthquake in Syria and Antioch kills approximately 300,000.

527

527

威塞克斯的塞尔迪克和他的儿子辛里克在切尔斯利击败了不列颠人。撒克逊人在泰晤士河北岸登陆，控制了如今伦敦和圣奥尔本斯之间的土地，埃塞克斯王国由此建立。查士丁尼成为拜占庭皇帝，他试图重新统一基督教教会的东正教和西正教。狄奥尼修斯·埃克西古斯错误地计算了耶稣的诞辰；日期开始以公元纪年（Anno Domini）而非建城纪年（Ab Urbe Condita）计算。

Cerdic of Wessex and his son Cynric defeat the Britons at Chearsley. The Kingdom of Essex is founded when the Saxons land north of the Thames and take control of the land between what is now London and St Albans. Justinian becomes Emperor of Byzantium; he tries to reunite the Eastern and Western branches of the Christian church. Dionysius Exiguus calculates the date of the birth of Jesus, incorrectly; dates start to be calculated Anno Domini instead of Ab Urbe Condita.

中世纪和文艺复兴世界

The Medieval and Renaissance World

528 – 1599

528 – 1599

 

 

528

528

查士丁尼任命一个委员会编纂所有帝国法律，即《民法大全》（Corpus Juris Civilis）。安条克发生地震，造成数千人死亡。萧庄帝继承萧明帝，成为中国北魏的统治者。摩腊婆王耶输陀罗门击败了入侵印度的匈奴人。百济成王将佛教定为国教。

Justinian appoints a commission to codify all imperial laws, the Corpus Juris Civilis. An earthquake in Antioch kills thousands. Xiao Zhuang Di succeeds Xiao Ming Di as ruler of the Chinese Northern Wei Dynasty. Yasodharman of Malwa defeats the Hun invaders in India. King Seong of Baekje adopts Buddhism as the state religion.

529

529

圣本笃在罗马以南的蒙特卡西诺创建了一座修道院。柏拉图于公元387年在雅典创立的学院被查士丁尼关闭。伯利恒的圣诞教堂在撒玛利亚人的叛乱中被焚毁。奥兰治会议颁布了教规，认可了奥古斯丁的教义。

St. Benedict founds a monastery at Monte Cassino, south of Rome. The Academy at Athens, founded by Plato in 387, is closed by Justinian. The Church of the Nativity in Bethlehem is burnt down during a revolt by the Samaritans. The Canons of the Council of Orange are established, approving Augustinian doctrine.

530

530

拜占庭将领贝利萨留和赫尔莫根尼在达拉斯战役中击败波斯人，阻止了他们入侵罗马美索不达米亚。汪达尔人和阿兰人的国王希尔德里克被他的堂兄盖利默废黜。魏长光王继承萧庄帝，成为中国北魏的统治者。

Byzantine generals Belisarius and Hermogenes defeat the Persians in the Battle of Daras, halting their incursion into Roman Mesopotamia. Hilderic, king of Vandals and Alans is deposed by his cousin Gelimer. Wei Chang Guang Wang succeeds Xiao Zhuang Di as ruler of the Chinese Northern Wei Dynasty

531

531

狄乌迪斯继承阿马拉里克成为西哥特国王。霍斯劳一世继承卡瓦德一世成为波斯国王。

Theudis succeeds Amalaric as king of the Visigoths. Khosrau I succeeds Kavadh I as king of Persia.

532

532

法兰克人入侵勃艮第王国。君士坦丁堡爆发尼卡暴动，大教堂被毁，三万人丧生；查士丁尼一世下令建造新大教堂，即圣索菲亚大教堂。萧武帝继安定王之后统治中国北方。新罗征服朝鲜半岛的金官伽倻。这一年，公元纪年法（Anno Domini）开始被使用，该历法由斯基泰僧侣狄奥尼修斯·埃克西古斯（Dionysius Exiguus）发明。

Franks invade the kingdom of Burgundy. The Nika riots in Constantinople; the cathedral is destroyed and 30,000 die; Justinian I orders the building of a new cathedral, the Hagia Sophia. Xiao Wu Di succeeds An Ding Wang in Northern China. Silla conquers Geumgwan Gaya on the Korean peninsula. This is the first year in which the Anno Domini calendar is used for numbering the years, a system invented by the Scythian monk, Dionysius Exiguus.

533

533

拜占庭将军贝利萨留登陆北非，进攻汪达尔人。狄奥德贝尔特一世成为奥斯特拉西亚国王，奥斯特拉西亚包括今天法国东部、德国西部、比利时、卢森堡和荷兰的部分地区。

The Byzantine general, Belisarius, lands in North Africa and attacks the Vandals. Theodebert I becomes king of Austrasia, comprising parts of the territory of present-day eastern France, western Germany, Belgium, Luxembourg and the Netherlands.

534

534

法兰克国王科塔尔一世和希尔德贝尔特一世推翻了勃艮第国王戈多马尔，终结了勃艮第王国。贝利萨留终结了北非汪达尔王国，其领土回归拜占庭帝国。辛里克成为威塞克斯国王。狄奥达哈德成为东哥特国王。

The Frankish kings, Cothar I and Childebert I, overthrow Godomar, king of the Burgundians, and end the kingdom of Burgundy. Belisarius brings the Vandal kingdom of North Africa to an end and the provinces return to the Byzantine Empire. Cynric becomes king of Wessex. Theodahad becomes king of the Ostrogoths.

535

535

查士丁尼一世命令贝利萨留开始收复意大利。印度笈多王朝崩溃。中国西魏王朝建立。据记载，这一年及次年天气异常寒冷黑暗，可能是由于喀拉喀托火山爆发所致。

Justinian I orders Belisarius to start the reconquest of Italy. India’s Gupta Empire collapses. The beginning of the Western Wei dynasty in China. In this and the following year, the weather is reported to be unusually cold and dark, possibly due to an eruption of Krakatoa.

536

536

贝利萨留攻占那不勒斯，进入罗马。法兰克人入侵普罗旺斯。在君士坦丁堡宗教会议上，主教们承认拜占庭皇帝在教会事务中的至高无上地位。

Belisarius takes Naples and enters Rome. The Franks invade Provence. At the Synod of Constantinople, bishops acknowledge the supremacy of the Byzantine Emperor in Church matters.

537

537

君士坦丁堡的圣索菲亚大教堂已经竣工。

Hagia Sophia in Constantinople is completed.

538

538

加布兰·麦克·多曼盖尔特成为达尔里阿达国王。东哥特国王维蒂格斯结束了对罗马的围攻，撤退到拉文纳，将罗马城留给了贝利萨留。教皇成为西方世界最高统治者，统治长达1260年。日本古墳时代结束，大和时代后半段——飞鸟时代开始。大约在同一时期，佛教传入日本，并迅速传播到全国各地。

Gabrán mac Domangairt becomes king of Dál Riata. Witiges, king of the Ostrogoths, ends his siege of Rome and retreats to Ravenna, leaving the city in the hands of Belisarius. The Pope becomes the leading ruler in the West for the next 1,260 years. The Kofun era in Japan ends and the Asuka period, the second part of the Yamato period, begins. Around this date, Buddhism arrives in Japan, spreading throughout the country.

539

539

敬明天皇即位。

Emperor Kimmei ascends the throne of Japan.

540

540

不列颠至高王库斯滕宁·阿普·卡多被废黜，返回杜姆诺尼亚。贝利萨留将军攻占米兰和东哥特首都拉文纳。东哥特国王维蒂格斯之后由伊尔迪巴德继位。波斯萨珊王朝进攻叙利亚西南部的德拉，并攻占了今土耳其境内的安条克。

High King Custennin ap Cado of Britain is deposed and returns to Dumnonia. General Belisarius conquers Milan and the Ostrogoth capital Ravenna. Ostrogoth King Witiges is succeeded by Ildibad. The Persian Sassanids attack Daraa in south-western Syria and capture Antioch in modern-day Turkey.

541

541

瘟疫出现在埃及，次年蔓延至君士坦丁堡。君士坦丁堡有超过10万人死亡，帝国其他地区则有数百万人丧生。托提拉成为东哥特国王；他重新征服了那不勒斯、贝内文托和意大利的其他地区。

Plague appears in Egypt, spreading the following year to Constantinople. More than 100,000 die in Constantinople and several million in the rest of the Empire. Totila becomes king of the Ostrogoths; he reconquers Naples, Benevento and other parts of Italy.

542

542

希尔德贝尔特一世攻占潘普洛纳，围攻西班牙的萨拉戈萨。

Childebert I captures Pamplona and besieges Zaragoza in Spain.

543

543

圣本笃·努尔西亚逝世，他是本笃会修士的创始人。北非的努比亚王国皈依基督教。

The death of St Benedict of Nursia, founder of the Benedictine Order of monks. The Nubian kingdoms in North Africa adopt Christianity.

544

544

贝利萨留返回意大利与东哥特人作战。

Belisarius returns to Italy to fight the Ostrogoths.

545

545

托提拉率领东哥特人围攻罗马。

The Ostrogoths under Totila besiege Rome.

546

546

东哥特人重新夺回罗马。

The Ostrogoths retake Rome.

547

547

艾达在英格兰东北部的班堡建立了伯尼西亚王国。西奥德巴尔德成为奥斯特拉西亚国王。

Ida founds the kingdom of Bernicia at Bamburgh, in north-east England. Theodebald becomes king of Austrasia.

548

548

贝利萨留被解除拜占庭在意大利军队的指挥权，由纳尔塞斯接任。图迪吉塞尔继承图迪斯成为西哥特国王。

Belisarius is relieved of command of the Byzantine forces in Italy and is replaced by Narses. Theudigisel succeeds Theudis as king of the Visigoths.

549

549

托提拉重新夺回罗马。阿吉拉继承狄奥迪吉塞尔成为西哥特国王。金文帝继承武帝成为中国梁朝的统治者。

Totila recaptures Rome. Agila succeeds Theudigisel as king of the Visigoths. Emperor Jinwen succeeds Emperor Wu as ruler of the Liang Dynasty in China.

550

550

法兰克人征服了图林根人。东魏王朝被北齐王朝取代，北齐王朝建立；齐文宣帝是北齐王朝的开国君主。大约在同一时期：玛雅人建造了基里瓜卫城；非洲东北部苏丹的努比亚人皈依基督教；拜占庭丝绸业由僧侣从中国走私蚕到君士坦丁堡而兴起。印度数学家在位值制中赋予零一个数字表示。

The Franks conquer the Thuringii. The Eastern Wei Dynasty is succeeded by the Northern Qi Dynasty in northern China; Qi Wen Xuan Di is the first ruler of the Northern Qi Dynasty. Around this date: The construction of the Mayan acropolis of Quiriguá; the Nubians in Sudan, north-eastern Africa, become Christian; the Byzantine silk industry is started by monks who smuggle silkworms to Constantinople from China. Hindu mathematicians give zero a numeral representation in a positional notation system.

551

551

拜占庭帝国从西哥特人手中夺取了西班牙南部部分地区。贝鲁特被地震和海啸摧毁。梁宇张王继承梁建文帝，成为中国梁朝的统治者。

The Byzantine Empire captures part of southern Spain from the Visigoths. Beirut is destroyed by an earthquake and a tsunami. Liang Yu Zhang Wang succeeds Liang Jian Wen Di as ruler of the Chinese Liang dynasty.

552

552

威塞克斯国王辛里克攻占了萨鲁姆古堡。在塔吉纳战役中，纳尔塞斯将军击败并杀死了东哥特国王托提拉；泰亚继位，但纳尔塞斯在年底前重新夺回了罗马。突厥人在布明汗的领导下建立了已知最早的突厥国家。亚美尼亚历元年。梁元帝继承梁宇章王，成为中国梁朝的统治者。

Cynric, king of Wessex, captures the fort at Old Sarum. In the Battle of Taginae, General Narses defeats and kills Totila, king of the Ostrogoths; Teia succeeds him but Narses recaptures Rome by the end of the year. Göktürks establish the first known Turkic state under the leadership of Bumin Khan. Year One in the Armenian calendar. Liang Yuan Di succeeds Liang Yu Zhang Wang as ruler of the Chinese Liang dynasty.

553

553

第五次大公会议召开。蒙斯拉克塔里乌斯战役后，东哥特王国被拜占庭帝国征服。

The Fifth Ecumenical Council is held. The Ostrogoth kingdom is conquered by the Byzantines after the Battle of Mons Lactarius.

554

554

纳尔塞斯将军收复意大利。拜占庭军队从西哥特人手中夺取格拉纳达和安达卢西亚。阿塔纳吉尔德继承阿吉拉成为西哥特国王。魏公帝继承西魏飞帝成为中国西魏王朝的统治者。百济和伽倻结盟，向朝鲜半岛的新罗发动战争，但最终战败。

General Narses reconquers Italy. Byzantine forces seize Granada and Andalusia from the Visigoths. Athanagild succeeds Agila as king of the Visigoths. Wei Gong Di succeeds Western Wei Fei Di as ruler of the Chinese Western Wei Dynasty. Baekje and Gaya ally and wage war upon Silla in the Korean peninsula, but are defeated.

555

555

南凉初年；第一位统治者是南梁宣帝。在中国梁朝，梁元帝的继任者是梁正阳侯，然后是梁景帝。

The beginning of the Nan Liang Dynasty; the first ruler is Nan Liang Xuan Di. In the Chinese Liang Dynasty, Liang Yuan Di is succeeded by Liang Zheng Yang Hou and then Liang Jing Di.

556

556

威塞克斯的辛里克和塞奥林在贝兰堡与不列颠人作战。西魏王朝在中国灭亡。

Cynric and Ceawlin of Wessex fight against the Britons at Beranburh. The Western Wei Dynasty ends in China.

557

557

北方，北周王朝建立；第一位统治者是萧敏帝。南方，梁朝结束，陈朝建立；第一位统治者是陈武帝。

The beginning of the Northern Zhou Dynasty in northern China; the first ruler is Xiao Min Di. In southern China, the end of the Liang Dynasty and the beginning of the Chen Dynasty; the first ruler is Chen Wu Di.

558

558

康纳尔·麦克·科姆盖尔成为达尔里阿达国王。在君士坦丁堡，圣索菲亚大教堂的穹顶坍塌。克洛泰尔一世重新统一了法兰克王国。光华寺建成。

Conall mac Comgaill becomes king of Dál Riata. In Constantinople, the dome of the Hagia Sophia collapses. Clotaire I reunites the Frankish kingdom. The Guanghua Temple is built.

559

559

格拉帕继承其父伊达的王位，成为伯尼西亚国王。保加尔人入侵拜占庭领土，但在君士坦丁堡附近被贝利萨留击退。伽倻联盟成员阿拉伽倻向朝鲜半岛的新罗投降。

Glappa succeeds his father Ida as king of Bernicia. The Bulgars raid Byzantine territory, but are driven back near Constantinople by Belisarius. Ara Gaya, a member of the Gaya confederacy, surrenders to Silla in the Korean peninsula.

560

560

塞奥林成为威塞克斯国王。埃塞尔伯特继承其父厄门里克，成为肯特国王。阿达继承其兄格拉帕，成为伯尼西亚国王。埃拉成为英格兰北部德伊拉国王。圣科伦巴与圣芬尼安因诗篇的作者身份发生争执，导致次年爆发激烈战斗。

Ceawlin becomes king of Wessex. Æthelbert succeeds his father Eormenric as king of Kent. Adda succeeds his brother Glappa as king of Bernicia. Aella becomes king of Deira in northern England. St Columba quarrels with St Finnian over authorship of a psalter, leading to a pitched battle the next year.

561

561

法国墨洛温王朝爆发内战。吴承帝继承萧昭帝，成为中国北齐王朝的统治者。

Civil war breaks out among the Merovingians in France. Wu Cheng Di succeeds Xiao Zhao Di as ruler of the Chinese Northern Qi Dynasty

562

562

贝利萨留因贪污罪在君士坦丁堡受审。拜占庭帝国与波斯帝国签订和平条约。玛雅城邦蒂卡尔被卡拉克穆尔击败。南孝明帝继南梁宣帝之后，成为中国南朝的统治者。

Belisarius stands trial in Constantinople for corruption. A peace treaty is signed between the Byzantine and the Persian empires. Tikal, a Mayan city state, is defeated by Kalakmul. Nan Xiao Ming Di succeeds Nan Liang Xuan Di as ruler of the Chinese Nan dynasty.

563

563

圣科伦巴从爱尔兰来到苏格兰传播基督教，并声称在尼斯湖看到了水怪。

St Columba arrives in Scotland from Ireland to spread Christianity and reports seeing a monster in Loch Ness.

565

565

查士丁二世继承查士丁尼一世成为拜占庭帝国的统治者。侯柱继承武成帝成为中国北齐王朝的统治者。在中国，回鹘人被突厥人征服。

Justin II succeeds Justinian I as ruler of the Byzantine Empire. Hou Zhu succeeds Wu Cheng Di as ruler of the Chinese Northern Qi Dynasty. In China, the Uyghurs are conquered by the Göktürks.

567

567

柳瓦一世继承阿塔纳吉尔德成为西哥特国王。东日耳曼哥特部落吉皮德人被阿瓦尔人征服。

Liuva I succeeds Athanagild as king of the Visigoths. The East Germanic Gothic tribe, the Gepids, are conquered by the Avars.

568

568

威塞克斯的塞奥林在维班顿战役中击败了肯特的埃塞尔伯特。埃塞尔里克继承其兄阿达的王位，成为伯尼西亚国王。阿尔博因国王率领伦巴第人入侵意大利；逃离伦巴第人的难民建立了威尼斯。利奥维吉尔德继承其兄柳瓦一世的王位，成为西哥特国王。土耳其人和萨珊王朝摧毁了七国帝国。

Ceawlin of Wessex defeats Æthelbert of Kent at the Battle of Wibbandun. Æthelric succeeds his brother Adda as king of Bernicia. King Alboin leads the Lombards into Italy; refugees fleeing them go on to found Venice. Leovigild succeeds his brother Liuva I as king of the Visigoths. The Turks and Sassanids destroy the Hepthalite Empire.

570

570

萨珊王朝首都泰西封成为当时世界上最大的城市。拜占庭和波斯开始为期50年的休战。伊斯兰教创始人穆罕默德诞生。

Ctesiphon, capital of the Sassanid Empire, becomes the largest city in the world. Byzantium and Persia start a 50-year truce. The birth of Muhammad, founder of Islam.

572

572

拜占庭帝国与波斯开战，同时西哥特人在西班牙也发动进攻。日本天皇毗达津即位。

The Byzantine Empire begins a war with Persia and is also attacked by the Visigoths in Spain. Emperor Bidatsu takes the throne of Japan.

574

574

Áedán mac Gabráin 成为达尔里亚塔国王。拜占庭皇帝查士丁二世退休，任命提比略二世君士坦丁为继承人。西哥特国王柳维吉尔德征服了西班牙北部的坎塔布里亚。

Áedán mac Gabráin becomes king of Dál Riata. Byzantine Emperor Justin II retires, naming Tiberius II Constantine as his heir. Visigothic king, Liuvigild conquers Cantabria in northern Spain.

575

575

东盎格利亚王国由盎格鲁人中的“北方人”和“南方人”两派建立，分别以诺福克和萨福克命名。

The Kingdom of East Anglia is founded by the Angle groups ‘North Folk’ and ‘South Folk’, naming Norfolk and Suffolk, respectively.

577

577

在威塞克斯国王西奥林的率领下，盎格鲁-撒克逊人在迪奥勒姆战役中击败了不列颠凯尔特人。

The Anglo-Saxons under Ceawlin of Wessex defeat the British Celts at the Battle of Deorham.

578

578

金刚组是世界上历史最悠久的持续运营公司，成立于日本大阪；该公司于 2006 年关闭。

Kongo Gumi, the world’s oldest continuously operating company, is founded in Osaka, Japan; it closed in 2006.

579

579

斯拉夫人开始迁徙到巴尔干半岛和希腊。中国的北齐王朝灭亡。

The Slavs begin to migrate into the Balkans and Greece. The Northern Qi Dynasty comes to an end in China.

580

580

埃塞尔伯特成为肯特国王。罗马元老院向君士坦丁堡派遣使节，这是其有记载的最后一次行动。

Ethelbert becomes king of Kent. The Roman Senate sends an embassy to Constantinople, its last recorded act.

581

581

隋朝取代了北周朝，北周朝是中国北方最后一个王朝；隋朝的第一位统治者是隋文帝。

The Sui Dynasty replaces the Northern Zhou Dynasty, the last of the Northern Dynasties in China; its first ruler is Sui Wen Di.

582

582

莫里斯继承提比略二世·君士坦丁成为拜占庭皇帝。君士坦丁堡遭受火灾和地震的蹂躏。

Maurice succeeds Tiberius II Constantine as Emperor of Byzantium. Fire and earthquake ravage Constantinople.

584

584

伦巴第人洗劫了蒙特卡西诺。西哥特人从拜占庭手中夺取了科尔多瓦。

The Lombards sack Monte Cassino. The Visigoths take Cordoba from Byzantium.

585

585

克里奥达成为麦西亚国王。高卢发生饥荒。日本天皇佑明登基。在中国，孝靖帝继承孝明帝的王位，成为南梁王朝的统治者。伊比利亚半岛上的苏维汇王国被西哥特国王柳维吉尔德征服。

Creoda becomes king of Mercia. There is famine in Gaul. Emperor Yõmei ascends to the throne of Japan. In China, Emperor Xiaojing succeeds Emperor Xiaoming as ruler of the Nan Liang Dynasty. The Suebi kingdom on the Iberian Peninsula is conquered by the Visigoths under King Liuvigild.

586

586

拜占庭人在德拉附近的索拉洪战役中击败了波斯人。雷卡雷德继承其父柳维吉尔德的王位，成为西哥特国王。

The Byzantines defeat the Persians at the Battle of Solachon, near Daraa. Reccared succeeds his father Liuvigild as king of the Visigoths.

587

587

威尔士守护圣人圣大卫逝世。斯莱达成为埃塞克斯国王。中国南梁王朝灭亡。日本肃顺天皇即位。

The death of St David, patron saint of Wales. Sledda becomes king of Essex. The Nan Liang Dynasty in China comes to an end. Emperor Sushun ascends to the throne of Japan.

588

588

埃塞尔里克成为诺森布里亚王国的第一位国王，该王国由盎格鲁-撒克逊人的两个部落——伯尼西亚和德伊拉——联合而成。一颗大型陨石撞击中国农村，造成十人死亡。

Æthelric becomes the first king of Northumbria, after the kingdom is formed from the union of the two Anglian tribes of Bernicia and Deira. Ten people are killed in rural China by a large meteorite impact.

589

589

罗马爆发瘟疫。西哥特王国放弃阿里乌教派，皈依天主教。

Plague in Rome. The Visigoth kingdom renounces Arianism and embraces Catholicism.

591

591

蝗灾摧毁了意大利的庄稼。吉那笈多将《维摩诘经》翻译成中文。

A locust swarm destroys the harvest in Italy. Jnanagupta translates the Vimalakirti Sutra into Chinese.

592

592

Ceawlin 被废黜了威塞克斯国王和不列颠王位。

Ceawlin is deposed as both king of Wessex and as Bretwalda.

593

593

埃塞尔弗里思继承胡萨成为伯尼西亚国王。皮巴成为麦西亚国王。推古天皇登基成为日本皇位。

Æthelfrith succeeds Hussa as king of Bernicia. Pybba becomes king of Mercia. Empress Suiko ascends to the throne of Japan.

594

594

推古天皇颁布《兴盛三宝诏》，正式承认佛教在日本的合法地位。

Empress Suiko issues the Flourishing Three Treasures Edict, officially recognizing the practice of Buddhism in Japan

595

595

坎特伯雷的奥古斯丁奉教皇格里高利一世之命前往肯特郡。穆罕默德与赫蒂彻结婚。印度数学家开始使用十进制。位于中国河北省的赵州桥开始动工，它是世界上最古老的敞肩石拱桥。

Augustine of Canterbury is sent on a mission to Kent by Pope Gregory I. Muhammad marries Khadija. The decimal system is being used by Indian mathematicians. Construction begins on the Zhaozhou Bridge in Hebei Province, China, the world’s oldest open-spandrel stone segmental arch bridge.

597

597

圣奥古斯丁成为坎特伯雷大主教。孝德宗成为日本天皇。

St Augustine becomes Archbishop of Canterbury. Kõtoku becomes Emperor of Japan.

599

599

也门被萨珊王朝征服。玛雅城市帕伦克被另一个玛雅城市卡拉克穆尔击败。

Yemen is conquered by the Sassanid Empire. The Maya–city of Palenque is defeated by another Maya–city, Kalakmul.

600

600

世界人口增长至约2.08亿。天花首次袭击欧洲。教皇格里高利一世编纂了后来被称为格里高利圣咏的曲调。波斯人开始使用风车灌溉。大约在同一时期：印度和波斯文学中最早出现关于象棋的记载；爱尔兰艺术和文学进入一个重要时期；北美霍普韦尔文化不再占据主导地位；玻利维亚的蒂亚瓦纳科文明兴起；玛雅文明达到鼎盛时期；秘鲁瓦里文明兴起。

The population of the world rises to about 208 million. Smallpox hits Europe for the first time. Pope Gregory I codifies what comes to be known as Gregorian chant. The Persians begin to use windmills for irrigation. Around this date: The earliest references to chess in Indian and Persian literature; the beginning of an important period of art and literature in Ireland; the Hopewell culture of North America ceases to be dominant; Tiahuanaco civilization begins in Bolivia; Mayan civilization is at its high point; the rise of Huari in Peru.

601

601

已知最早的英语单词——“城镇”和“牧师”——都记录在埃塞尔伯特的法律中。

The earliest dated English words – ‘Town’ and ‘Priest’ – are both recorded in the Laws of Æthelbert.

602

602

福卡斯杀死莫里斯，自立为拜占庭皇帝。拜占庭帝国与萨珊帝国之间爆发了一系列战争。斯拉夫部落开始在巴尔干半岛定居。维京人入侵爱尔兰。

Phocas kills Maurice and declares himself Byzantine Emperor. A series of wars begins between the Byzantine Empire and the Sassanid Empire. Slavic tribes start to settle the Balkans. The Vikings invade Ireland.

603

603

日本圣德太子建立了十二级等级制度，据说他还撰写了一部十七条宪法。

Japan’s Prince Shotoku establishes the Twelve Level Cap and Rank system and is said to have authored a 17-article constitution.

604

604

萨伯特继承斯莱达成为埃塞克斯国王。诺森布里亚的埃塞尔弗里思统一了德伊勒和伯尼西亚。西哥特人将最后的拜占庭人逐出西班牙。

Saebert succeeds Sledda as king of Essex. Æthelfrith of Northumbria unites Deira and Bernicia. The Visigoths drive the last Byzantines from Spain.

605

605

大约在同一时期，中国修建了京杭大运河。

Around this time, the Grand Canal is built in China.

606

606

沙尚卡是孟加拉有记载的第一位独立君主。

Shashanka is the first recorded independent king of Bengal.

607

607

威塞克斯的切奥伍夫与南撒克逊人作战。松斯坦王统一西藏。

Ceolwulf of Wessex fights the South Saxons. King Songstan unifies Tibet.

609

609

罗马万神殿是供奉圣母玛利亚和所有圣人的。

The Pantheon in Rome is consecrated to the Virgin Mary and all saints.

610

610

希拉克略推翻了东罗马皇帝福卡斯，成为皇帝；他将东罗马帝国的官方语言从拉丁语改为希腊语。根据伊斯兰教的信仰，大天使加百列首次显现给穆罕默德，向他诵读了《古兰经》第97章（血块章）的首节经文，并开始启示《古兰经》。

Heraclius overthrows the East Roman Emperor Phocas and becomes Emperor; he changes the official language of the East Roman Empire from Latin to Greek. According to Islamic belief, the archangel Gabriel first appears to Muhammad, reciting to him the first verses of the Surat al-Alaq and beginning the revelation of the Qur’an.

613

613

波斯帝国将军沙赫尔巴拉兹攻占大马士革。

Shahrbaraz, a general of the Persian Empire, captures Damascus.

614

614

沙赫巴拉兹攻占并洗劫了耶路撒冷；圣墓教堂被大火烧毁，真十字架被夺取。

Shahrbaraz captures and sacks Jerusalem; the Church of the Holy Sepulchre is damaged by fire and the True Cross is captured.

615

615

土耳其人入侵中国。

The Turks invade China.

616

616

埃德巴尔德继承埃塞尔伯特成为肯特国王。诺森布里亚的埃塞尔弗里思击败了波伊斯军队；在艾德尔河战役中，他被东盎格利亚的雷德瓦尔德杀死，这场战役确立了雷德瓦尔德的不列颠王位。埃德温成为诺森布里亚国王。亚历山大被波斯国王霍斯劳二世攻占。在未来威斯敏斯特教堂的所在地建立了一座圣殿。

Eadbald succeeds Ethelbert as king of Kent. Æthelfrith of Northumbria defeats the army of Powys; he is slain by Rædwald of East Anglia in the Battle of the River Idle, which establishes Rædwald’s claim as Bretwalda. Edwin becomes king of Northumbria. Alexandria is captured by Khosrau II of Persia. A shrine is founded on the site of the future Westminster Abbey.

617

617

隋公帝继承隋炀帝，成为中国皇帝。

Sui Gong Di succeeds Sui Yang Di as Emperor of China.

618

618

中国唐朝的开端。

The beginning of the Tang dynasty in China.

619

619

阿瓦尔人攻打君士坦丁堡。中国历法的计算开始采用太阳和月亮的真实运动轨迹，并用两条错位且方向相反的抛物线来模拟。

The Avars attack Constantinople. The calculation of the Chinese calendar begins to use the true motions of the sun and moon modelled using two offset, opposing parabolas.

621

621

拜占庭皇帝希拉克略入侵波斯。伊斯兰历元年，即伊斯兰教创立之年。

The Byzantine Emperor, Heraclius, invades Persia. Year One of the Islamic calendar, the year that Islam began.

622

622

穆罕默德和他的追随者从麦加迁徙到麦地那。

Muhammad and his followers emigrate from Mecca to Medina.

622

622

中国第一部百科全书《物文类集》编纂完成。

The first Chinese Encyclopedia, Yiwen Leiju (Collection of Literature Arranged by Categories), is completed.

624

624

爱丁堡由诺森布里亚国王埃德温建立。拜占庭人在西哥特人统治70年后收复安达卢西亚；他们还击败了围攻君士坦丁堡的阿瓦尔人和斯拉夫人。唐朝廷皈依佛教。唐高祖退位，将王位传给其子李世民。

Edinburgh is founded by King Edwin of Northumbria. The Byzantines recapture Andalusia after 70 years of Visigoth rule; they also defeat the Avars and Slavs besieging Constantinople. The Tang court adopts Buddhism. Emperor Gaozu of Tang China abdicates in favour of his son, Li Shimin.

627

627

希拉克略皇帝在尼尼微战役中击败波斯人，结束了罗马-波斯战争。

Emperor Heraclius defeats the Persians in the Battle of Nineveh, ending the Roman–Persian Wars.

628

628

婆罗摩笈多撰写了《婆罗摩笈多历算书》，这是一部早期的数学著作。

Brahmagupta writes the Brahmasphutasiddhanta, an early book on mathematics.

629

629

拜占庭帝国从波斯帝国手中夺回耶路撒冷。

Jerusalem is retaken by the Byzantine Empire from the Persian Empire.

630

630

拜占庭-阿拉伯战争爆发。库布拉特汗建立大保加利亚。穆罕默德不流血征服麦加。

The start of the Byzantine–Arab Wars. Khan Kubrat establishes Great Bulgaria. Muhammad conquers Mecca bloodlessly.

632

632

穆罕默德去世后，阿布·伯克尔继位。

The death of Muhammad; he is succeeded by Abu Bakr.

633

633

在英格兰，麦西亚人击败了诺森布里亚人。李仲峰建造了一座天球仪。

In England, the Mercians defeat the Northumbrians. Li Chung Feng builds a celestial globe.

634

634

阿拉伯人入侵巴勒斯坦。

The Arabs invade Palestine.

635

635

圣艾丹在英格兰诺森伯兰郡创建了林迪斯法恩岛。

St Aidan founds Lindisfarne in Northumbria, England.

636

636

在雅穆克战役中，拜占庭帝国将叙利亚割让给了阿拉伯人。阿拉伯人随后入侵波斯。伊拉克的巴士拉城由哈里发奥马尔建立。

In the Battle of Yarmuk, the Byzantine Empire loses Syria to the Arabs. The Arabs invade Persia. The city of Basra in Iraq is founded by Caliph Omar.

637

637

阿拉伯人击败波斯军队，攻占波斯首都泰西封、耶路撒冷和阿勒颇。中国首都长安成为当时世界上最大的城市。

The Arabs defeat the Persian army, taking the Persian capital of Ctesiphon, Jerusalem and Aleppo. Chang’an, the capital of China, becomes the largest city in the world.

638

638

穆斯林攻占耶路撒冷、安条克、凯撒利亚和阿克。伊斯兰历法开始实施。

The Muslims capture Jerusalem, Antioch, Caesarea Maritima and Akko. The Islamic calendar is introduced.

640

640

阿拉伯人开始在北非传播伊斯兰教。

Arabs begin to spread the Muslim faith across northern Africa.

640

640

伊斯兰教领袖哈里发奥马尔开始征服埃及

The Islamic leader, Caliph Omar, begins the conquest of Egypt

641

641

拜占庭皇帝希拉克洛纳斯被废黜，他的兄弟君士坦斯二世成为唯一的皇帝。

The Byzantine Emperor Heraclonas is deposed and his brother Constans II becomes sole emperor.

642

642

建立修道院定居点，后来发展成为温彻斯特大教堂。阿拉伯人在尼哈万德战役中征服波斯。光玉皇后登基成为日本皇位。现存最早的有纪年的阿拉伯纸莎草纸文献的日期。

A monastic settlement is established which later becomes Winchester Cathedral. The Arabs conquer Persia at the Battle of Nehawand. Empress Kogyoku ascends to the throne of Japan. The date of the earliest surviving dated Arabic papyrus.

643

643

阿拉伯军队在的黎波里取得北非首胜。波斯萨珊王朝末代君主逃往中国。

Arab armies win their first North African victory at Tripoli. The last Sassanid king of Persia flees to China.

644

644

中国唐朝开始入侵朝鲜半岛高句丽王国。

The Tang dynasty of China begins invasion of the kingdom of Goguryo in Korea.

645

645

日本朝廷开始效仿中国的政府模式。

The Japanese court begins to copy the Chinese style of government.

拜占庭人从阿拉伯人手中夺回亚历山大港。孝德天皇即位日本皇位。

The Byzantines recapture Alexandria from the Arabs. Emperor Kotoku ascends the Japanese throne.

646

646

拜占庭帝国收复埃及的尝试失败后，阿拉伯人重新夺回了亚历山大，结束了埃及近十个世纪的希腊罗马文明。孝德天皇在日本推行大化改革，这是一系列政治和社会改革措施。

Alexandria is recaptured by the Arabs after a Byzantine attempt to retake Egypt fails, ending nearly 10 centuries of Graeco-Roman civilization in Egypt. Emperor Kotoku introduces the Taika reforms, a series of political and social doctrines, in Japan.

649

649

阿拉伯人征服了塞浦路斯。

The Arabs conquer Cyprus.

650

650

克罗地亚人和塞尔维亚人占领了如今的波斯尼亚地区。阿拉伯人完成了对波斯的征服。伊斯兰教成为伊朗的国教。外科手术的初步发展出现在印度。大约在同一时期：穆罕默德的启示被记录下来，成为《古兰经》；美洲原住民霍普韦尔人在密西西比河上游定居；墨西哥的特奥蒂瓦坎城成为重要的贸易中心。

Croats and Serbs occupy the area that is now Bosnia. The Arabs complete the conquest of Persia. Islam becomes the state religion in Iran. The first surgical developments take place in India. Around this time: The revelations of Muhammad are written down, becoming the Qur’an; the Native American Hopewell people establish themselves along the upper Mississippi River; the city of Teotihuacan in Mexico becomes an important trade centre.

651

651

埃及与马库里亚签订了长达700年的《巴克特条约》，这是历史上持续时间最长的条约。雅兹德格尔德三世被杀，波斯人对阿拉伯征服的抵抗结束，萨珊王朝也随之灭亡；穆斯林征服了波斯。穆罕默德的女婿阿里遇刺身亡；穆阿维叶成为哈里发，建立了倭马亚王朝。

The bakt between Egypt and Makuria, the longest-lasting treaty in history, at 700 years, is signed. Yazdegard III is killed, ending both Persian resistance to Arab conquest, as well as the Sassanid dynasty; the Muslims conquer Persia. Ali, Muhammad’s son-in-law is assassinated; Muuawiyah becomes caliph and establishes the Umayyad dynasty.

652

652

信奉基督教的努比亚人和埃及的阿拉伯人一致认为，尼罗河畔的阿斯旺是阿拉伯扩张的最南端。

Christian Nubians and Arabs in Egypt agree on Aswan on the River Nile being the southernmost limit of Arab expansion.

654

654

阿拉伯人入侵罗德岛；罗德岛巨像的残骸被变卖。

The Arabs invade Rhodes; the remains of the Colossus of Rhodes are sold off.

655

655

诺森布里亚人在温瓦德战役中击败了麦西亚人。

The Northumbrians defeat the Mercians in the Battle of Winwaed.

656

656

诺森布里亚吞并了麦西亚。

Northumbria annexes Mercia.

657

657

威尔士军队在卡德瓦拉德的率领下，对撒克逊人发动了最后一次进攻。唐朝击败了土耳其人。圣希尔达在约克郡海岸的惠特比建立了一座修道院。

The last Welsh offensive, led by Cadwaladr, is mounted against the Saxons. The Tang Dynasty defeats the Turks. St Hilda founds an abbey on the Yorkshire coast at Whitby.

659

659

麦西亚人反抗诺森布里亚，拥立伍尔夫赫尔为王。

Mercians rebel against Northumbria and proclaim Wulfhere king.

663

663

英国爆发了一场短暂的瘟疫。拜占庭皇帝君士坦斯二世入侵意大利南部。一位不知名的僧侣登上了富士山之巅。

A brief outbreak of plague hits Britain. Byzantine Emperor Constans II invades southern Italy. An anonymous monk reaches the summit of Mount Fuji.

664

664

在惠特比宗教会议上，罗马基督教被选为首选，而非凯尔特基督教。

At the Synod of Whitby, Roman Christianity is chosen in preference to Celtic.

665

665

第二次巴顿河战役后，盎格鲁-撒克逊人皈依基督教。东罗马皇帝君士坦斯二世在浴池中遇刺身亡。

The Anglo-Saxons convert to Christianity after the Second Battle of Badon. The Eastern Roman Emperor Constans II is assassinated in his bath.

668

668

高句丽位于满洲南部和朝鲜北部，被唐朝和新罗的联军推翻，导致朝鲜半岛统一。

Goguryeo in southern Manchuria and northern Korea, is overthrown by the alliance of Tang China and Silla, leading to the unification of Korea.

670

670

位于今突尼斯境内的凯鲁万城建立。大约在同一时期，叙利亚化学家卡利尼库斯发明了希腊火，这是一种高度易燃的液体，被拜占庭军队用于战斗。

The city of Kairouan in what is now Tunisia is founded. Around this date, the Syrian chemist, Callinicus, invents Greek Fire, a highly inflammable liquid used by the Byzantine army in battle.

671

671

诺森布里亚国王埃格弗里思在两河之战中击败了皮克特人。天智天皇驾崩后，因继承权之争而爆发的真信之乱在日本发生。

King Ecgfrith of Northumbria defeats the Picts at the Battle of Two Rivers. The Jinshin War, a succession dispute following the death of Emperor Tenji, is fought in Japan.

674

674

阿拉伯人第一次围攻君士坦丁堡。英国教堂里出现了第一批玻璃窗。

The first Arab siege of Constantinople begins. The first glass windows appear in English churches.

675

675

保加尔人是来自俄罗斯草原的游牧民族，他们定居在多瑙河南岸的土地上。

The Bulgars, a nomadic people from the Russian steppes are, settling the lands south of the Danube.

677

677

在锡莱姆海战中，阿拉伯舰队被拜占庭军队摧毁。

In the Battle of Syllaeum the Arab fleet is destroyed by Byzantines.

680

680

伊拉克卡尔巴拉战役是穆罕默德的孙子侯赛因·伊本·阿里及其亲属的支持者与倭马亚王朝哈里发叶齐德一世的军队之间的战斗。

The Battle of Karbala in Iraq is fought between supporters and relatives of Muhammad’s grandson Husayn ibn Ali and forces of Yazid I, the Umayyad caliph.

681

681

保加尔人击败拜占庭帝国；这被认为是保加利亚的诞生日。

The Bulgars defeat the Byzantine Empire; this is considered to be the birth date of Bulgaria.

683

683

玛雅帕伦克城邦统治者帕卡尔大帝的统治结束。

The end of the reign of Pacal the Great, ruler of the Mayan state of Palenque.

685

685

瘟疫夺去了诺森布里亚一座修道院所有僧侣的生命，只有院长和一个小男孩幸存——他就是后来的学者比德。阿拉伯人抵达了今天的摩洛哥境内。

Plague kills all the monks in a Northumbrian monastery apart from the abbot and one small boy – the future scholar, Bede. The Arabs reach present-day Morocco.

686

686

肯特王国被凯德瓦拉率领的西撒克逊人征服。怀特岛成为英国最后一个皈依基督教的地方。

The kingdom of Kent is conquered by the West Saxons under Caedwalla. The Isle of Wight becomes the last place in the United Kingdom to convert to Christianity.

687

687

耶路撒冷圆顶清真寺开始动工。

Construction work begins on the Dome of the Rock in Jerusalem.

688

688

拜占庭帝国皇帝查士丁尼二世击败了保加利亚人。

Emperor Justinian II of the Byzantine Empire defeats the Bulgarians.

690

690

武则天在中国掌权，成为中国历史上唯一一位女统治者；她建立了周朝。

Wu Ze Tian comes to power in China, the only woman in history to rule China; she founds the Zhou dynasty.

691

691

圆顶清真寺已竣工。

The Dome of the Rock is completed.

692

692

阿拉伯人征服了亚美尼亚。

The Arabs conquer Armenia.

693

693

葡萄牙城市维塞乌被摩尔人从拜占庭帝国手中夺取。

The Portuguese city of Viseu is taken from the Byzantine Empire by the Moors.

694

694

武则天征服了中国西部的和田王国。科潘的第十三位玛雅统治者十八兔开始了长达44年的统治。

Empress Wu conquers the kingdom of Khotan in Western China. The 13th Mayan ruler of Copán, 18-Rabbit begins a 44-year reign.

695

695

拜占庭人起义反抗查士丁尼二世；利昂提乌斯被拥立为皇帝，查士丁尼二世被流放。

The Byzantines revolt against Justinian II; Leontius is made emperor and Justinian II is banished.

697

697

保罗·卢西奥·阿纳费斯托当选为威尼斯第一任总督。

Paolo Lucio Anafesto is elected the first Doge of Venice.

 

 

阿拉伯人摧毁了位于北非的拜占庭城市迦太基。

Arabs destroy the Byzantine city of Carthage in North Africa.

700

700

大约在这一时期：维京人开始入侵不列颠群岛；班图人开采并交易了南加丹加的铜矿；密西西比河流域出现了筑墩的密西西比文化；在亚利桑那州东部，普韦布洛人开始居住在地面以上的房屋中并开始耕作；莫切文明和纳斯卡文明衰落。

Around this date: Vikings start to invade the British Isles; the copper deposits of south Katanga are mined and traded by the Bantu; the mound-building Mississippi culture emerges in the Mississippi river basin; in eastern Arizona, the Pueblo people start to live in houses above ground and begin farming; the Moche and Nazca civilizations collapse.

702

702

拜占庭皇帝查士丁尼二世复辟。倭马亚清真寺，又称大清真寺，在大马士革竣工。

The Byzantine Emperor Justinian II regains his throne. The Umayyad Mosque, also known as the Grand Mosque, is completed in Damascus.

705

705

穆斯林军队开始扩张，征服了土库曼斯坦和信德，并一路推进到中国边境。中国丞相张建之杀害了张氏兄弟，拥立中宗皇帝，标志着短暂的周朝的终结。

Muslim armies begin a period of expansion, conquering Turkmenistan and Sind and pushing as far as the borders of China. Chinese Chancellor, Zhang Jianzhi, murders the Zhang brothers and restores Emperor Zhongzong, marking the end of the short-lived Zhou Dynasty.

707

707

拜占庭帝国将巴利阿里群岛拱手让给了摩尔人。

The Byzantines lose the Balearic Islands to the Moors.

708

708

在法国，据称大天使米迦勒显灵后，蒙托姆贝岛被献给他，并更名为圣米歇尔山。日本首次铸造铜币。

In France, after a reported appearance of the archangel Michael, the island of Mont Tombe is dedicated to him and renamed Mont Saint-Michel. Copper coins are minted in Japan for the first time.

709

709

一场猛烈的风暴将杰图岛和赫姆岛隔开。

A violent storm separates the Channel Islands of Jethou and Herm.

710

710

穆斯林王国尼科尔在摩洛哥建立。位于关西地区、今京都以南的奈良成为日本首都。耶路撒冷第一座阿克萨清真寺竣工。

The Muslim Kingdom of Nekor is founded in Morocco. Nara, in the Kansai region, south of modern-day Kyoto, becomes the capital of Japan. The first Al-Aqsa Mosque in Jerusalem is finished.

711

711

腓力比库斯煽动叛乱反对查士丁尼二世，并在后者死后自立为拜占庭皇帝。倭马亚摩尔人在瓜达莱特战役后征服了伊比利亚半岛。倭马亚王朝在印度建立了第一个穆斯林国家。

Philippicus incites a revolt against Justinian II, and upon the latter’s death declares himself Byzantine Emperor. Umayyad Moors conquer the Iberian Peninsula after the Battle of Guadalete. Umayyads found the first Muslim state in India.

712

712

《古事记》是日本从诞生至今的历史著作，它是日本现存最古老的书籍。

The Kojiki, a history of Japan from its birth, is completed; it is the oldest surviving book in Japan.

713

713

腓力比克皇帝被废黜；阿纳斯塔修斯二世被拥立为皇帝。

Emperor Philippicus is deposed; Anastasius II is proclaimed emperor.

716

716

狄奥多西三世领导了反对阿纳斯塔修斯二世的起义，并被拥立为拜占庭皇帝。

Theodosius III leads a revolt against Anastasius II and is proclaimed Byzantine Emperor.

717

717

皮克特国王内赫坦（德里勒之子）将僧侣驱逐出苏格兰爱奥那岛。利奥三世篡夺拜占庭王位。阿拉伯人围攻君士坦丁堡近一年。

The Pictish king, Nechtan, son of Derile, expels the monks from the Scottish island of Iona. Leo III usurps the throne of Byzantium. Arabs besiege Constantinople for almost a year.

718

718

佩拉约在科瓦东加击败阿拉伯人，并在伊比利亚半岛建立了阿斯图里亚斯王国。利奥三世皇帝和特维尔汗击败了围攻君士坦丁堡的阿拉伯军队，阻止了阿拉伯人入侵欧洲。世界上最古老的酒店——宝志温泉酒店在日本石川县开业。

Pelayo defeats the Arabs at Covadonga and establishes the Kingdom of Asturias in the Iberian Peninsula. Emperor Leo III and Khan Tervel defeat the Arab forces besieging Constantinople, stopping an Arab invasion of Europe. The world’s oldest hotel, Houshi Onsen, opens in Ishikawa-ken, Japan.

719

719

努比亚教会从东正教改信科普特教会。

The church of Nubia changes its allegiance from the Eastern Orthodox Church to the Coptic Church.

720

720

日本最古老的历史书籍之一《日本书纪》已经完成。

The Nihon Shoki (The Chronicles of Japan), one of the oldest Japanese history books, is completed.

721

721

在图卢兹战役中，穆斯林西班牙总督阿尔-萨姆赫·伊本·马利克·阿尔-哈乌拉尼被阿基坦公爵奥多击败；阿拉伯人入侵高卢的企图被阻止。

In the Battle of Toulouse, Al-Samh ibn Malik al-Khawlani, the governor of Muslim Spain is defeated by Duke Odo of Aquitaine; an Arab invasion of Gaul is prevented.

722

722

威塞克斯和苏塞克斯之间爆发战争。

War breaks out between Wessex and Sussex.

723

723

据称世界上第一座机械钟是在中国制造的。

The world’s first mechanical clock is allegedly built in China.

725

725

比德出版了《论时间的规律》，计算了从基督诞生开始的日期。

Bede publishes De Ratione Temporum, calculating dates from the birth of Christ.

726

726

首届相扑锦标赛由西武天皇在日本举办。

The first annual Sumo tournament is staged in Japan by Emperor Seibu.

730

730

拜占庭帝国皇帝利奥三世下令摧毁所有圣像；第一次圣像破坏运动开始。

Emperor Leo III of the Byzantine Empire orders the destruction of all icons; the beginning of the First Iconoclastic Period.

731

731

教宗格里高利二世谴责破坏圣像运动，导致拜占庭意大利与帝国决裂。比德完成了他的《英格兰教会史》。

Pope Gregory II condemns iconoclasm, causing Byzantine Italy to break with the Empire. Bede completes his Historia Ecclesiastica Gentis Anglorum.

732

732

法兰克国王查理·马特在普瓦捷击败穆斯林，阻止了穆斯林北上的扩张，并在西欧、伊斯兰世界和拜占庭帝国之间建立了力量平衡。埃格伯特成为约克主教，他创建了一座图书馆，使约克成为著名的学术中心。

Charles Martel, King of the Franks, defeats the Muslims at Poitiers, bringing to a halt the Muslim advance northwards and establishing a balance of power between Western Europe, Islam and the Byzantine Empire. Egbert becomes Bishop of York; he founds a library and makes the city a renowned centre of learning.

735

735

圣比德之死。

Death of the Venerable Bede.

736

736

有记载的最早的啤酒花种植记录出现在今天的德国哈勒陶地区。华严宗佛教从朝鲜半岛传入日本。

The first documented instance of hop cultivation in the Hallertau region of present-day Germany. The Kegon school of Buddhism arrives in Japan from Korea.

739

739

查理·马特尔将摩尔人逐出法国。

Charles Martel drives the Moors out of France.

741

741

日本当局颁布法令，要求在全国各地建立佛教寺庙。

Japanese authorities decree that Buddhist temples should be established throughout the country.

742

742

唐玄宗开始偏爱道教而非佛教。

Emperor Xuanzong of Tang begins to favour Taoism over Buddhism.

745

745

鼠疫开始席卷欧洲。

Bubonic plague begins to sweep through Europe.

748

748

中东发生地震，摧毁了许多拜占庭文化遗迹。

An earthquake strikes the Middle East, destroying many remnants of Byzantine culture.

750

750

倭马亚王朝末代哈里发被阿拔斯王朝首任哈里发推翻；哈里发国迁至巴格达，巴格达发展成为世界贸易和文化中心。特奥蒂瓦坎被托尔特克人洗劫一空。萨波特克人的城市蒙特阿尔班被废弃。

The last Umayyad caliph is overthrown by the first Abbasid caliph; the caliphate is moved to Baghdad, which develops into a centre of world trade and culture. Teotihuacan is sacked by the Toltec. The Zapotec city of Monte Alban is abandoned.

751

751

矮子丕平当选法兰克国王，标志着墨洛温王朝的终结和加洛林王朝的开始。阿拉伯军队在撒马尔罕附近的怛罗斯战役中击败了唐朝军队。现存最古老的印刷文献——一部佛教经典——在朝鲜印刷完成。

Pepin the Short is elected king of the Franks, marking the end of the Merovingian and beginning of the Carolingian dynasty. Arabian armies defeat Chinese Tang troops at the Battle of Talas near Samarkand. The oldest surviving printed document, a Buddhist scripture, is printed in Korea.

753

753

乌兹别克斯坦的撒马尔罕被阿拉伯人征服。

Samarkand in Uzbekistan is conquered by the Arabs.

755

755

安史之乱在中国爆发，导致唐玄宗退位。

The An Lushan rebellion begins in China, resulting in the abdication of Emperor Xuanzong.

756

756

矮子丕平击败了威胁教皇斯蒂芬三世的意大利北部伦巴第人。阿卜杜勒·拉赫曼一世征服了伊比利亚半岛，并在今西班牙科尔多瓦重建了倭马亚王朝。

Pepin the Short defeats the Lombards of northern Italy who have threatened Pope Stephen III. Abd-ar-rahman I conquers Iberia and re-establishes the Umayyad dynasty at Cordoba in modern Spain.

757

757

奥法因修建奥法堤而闻名，成为麦西亚国王。巴勒斯坦和叙利亚发生大地震。

Offa, noted for Offa’s Dyke, becomes king of Mercia. A major earthquake strikes Palestine and Syria.

758

758

中国城市广州遭到阿拉伯和波斯劫掠者的洗劫。

The Chinese city of Guangzhou is sacked by Arab and Persian raiders.

759

759

法兰克人攻占纳博讷；撒拉逊人被逐出法国。日本诗人大友屋持编纂了日本第一部诗歌集《万叶集》。

The Franks capture Narbonne; the Saracens are driven out of France. Japanese poet Otomo no Yakamochi compiles the first Japanese poetry anthology, Man’yoshu.

760

760

玛雅城市多斯皮拉斯被遗弃。

The Mayan city of Dos Pilas is abandoned.

762

762

统治伊拉克的阿拔斯王朝将巴格达定为首都。

The Abbasid dynasty, rulers of Iraq, names Baghdad as its capital.

763

763

藏军占领中国首都长安。

Tibetan forces occupy the Chinese capital Chang’an.

764

764

麦西亚国王奥法征服肯特，拥立埃格伯特二世为王。据历史学家狄奥法内斯记载，同年黑海冰层融化，冰山漂过君士坦丁堡。

Offa of Mercia conquers Kent, and installs Egbert II on the throne. According to the historian Theophanes in this year, the Black Sea melts and icebergs float past Constantinople.

768

768

查理曼大帝在其父矮子丕平去世后加冕为法兰克国王。重要的定居点海德比在维京时代的丹麦建立。

Charlemagne is crowned king of the Franks on the death of his father, Pepin the Short. The important settlement of Hedeby is founded in Viking Denmark.

772

772

麦西亚的奥法征服了苏塞克斯。查理曼大帝开始与撒克逊人和弗里西亚人作战；撒克逊被征服并皈依基督教。

Offa of Mercia conquers Sussex. Charlemagne starts fighting the Saxons and the Frisians; Saxony is subdued and converts to Christianity.

773

773

数字零的概念被引入巴格达市。

The concept of the number zero is introduced to the city of Baghdad.

774

774

查理曼征服了伦巴第王国。

Charlemagne conquers the kingdom of the Lombards.

775

775

三佛逝王国疆域从苏门答腊和爪哇延伸至马来西亚。

The Srivijaya kingdom extends from Sumatra and Java to Malaysia.

777

777

查理曼大帝击败了撒克逊人。

Charlemagne defeats the Saxons.

778

778

查理曼的军队在巴斯克人手中惨败；11 世纪的《罗兰之歌》大致取材于这场战役。

Charlemagne’s army suffers a terrible defeat at the hands of the Basques; the 11th-century Song of Roland is loosely based on the events of this battle.

781

781

查理曼大帝划定了教皇的疆域。

Charlemagne defines the papal territory.

784

784

奥法堤道开始动工，这是一座位于英格兰和威尔士之间的巨大防御土方工程，由麦西亚国王奥法建造。

Construction starts on Offa’s Dyke, a massive, defensive earthwork between England and Wales, built by Offa, king of Mercia.

786

786

哈伦·拉希德的统治时期与伊拉克统治者阿拔斯王朝的“黄金时代”重合。

Harun-al-Rashid’s reign coincides with the ‘Golden Age’ of the Abbasids, rulers of Iraq.

787

787

前三艘维京船在威塞克斯登陆，北欧人开始劫掠城镇和沿海修道院。

The first three Viking ships land in Wessex and the Norsemen start to plunder towns and coastal monasteries.

788

788

查理曼大帝征服巴伐利亚。摩洛哥在阿拉伯首领伊德里斯的统治下成为独立国家。

Charlemagne conquers Bavaria. Morocco becomes an independent state under Idris, an Arab chief.

790

790

一场反对女皇伊琳娜的叛乱导致她的儿子君士坦丁六世被宣布为拜占庭帝国的唯一统治者。

A revolt against Empress Irene leads to her son, Constantine VI, being declared sole ruler of the Byzantine Empire.

793

793

维京人洗劫了林迪斯法恩修道院，这是维京人对英格兰的第一次重大袭击。

Vikings sack the monastery of Lindisfarne in the first major Viking raid in England.

794

794

平安京（京都）成为日本首都。

Heian-kyo (Kyoto) becomes the Japanese capital.

796

796

查理曼大帝击败了阿瓦尔人。

Charlemagne defeats the Avars.

797

797

伊琳娜女皇下令逮捕并废黜君士坦丁六世。

Empress Irene orders Constantine VI captured and deposed.

800

800

查理大帝（查理曼大帝）在罗马圣彼得大教堂由教皇利奥三世加冕为皇帝，标志着神圣罗马帝国的开端。凯尔特僧侣在爱奥那岛开始编纂《凯尔经》。大约在同一时期：西欧建造了第一批城堡；阿格拉布王朝的埃米尔统治着北非的突尼斯；阿拉伯人和波斯人在东非沿岸的马林迪、蒙巴萨、基尔瓦和摩加迪沙建立了贸易站；霍霍坎人在亚利桑那州南部扩展了他们的定居点；毛利人开始从波利尼西亚迁徙到新西兰；北美中部进入密西西比纪。

The coronation of Charles the Great (Charlemagne) as Emperor in St Peter’s Church, Rome, by Pope Leo III, marks the beginning of the Holy Roman Empire. Celtic monks begin work on the Book of Kells on the island of Iona. Around this date: The first castles are built in Western Europe; the Aghlabid dynasty of emirs rules in Tunis in North Africa; Arabs and Persians set up trading posts at Malindi, Mombasa, Kilwa, and Mogadishu on the East African coast; the Hohokam people expand their settlements in southern Arizona; the Maori start migrating to New Zealand from Polynesia; the beginning of the Mississippian Period in the Central North American continent.

801

801

伊琳娜女皇被废黜，尼基弗鲁斯一世继位。

Empress Irene is deposed and replaced by Nicephorus I.

802

802

埃格伯特成为威塞克斯国王。克鲁姆成为保加利亚可汗。吴哥王朝由阇耶跋摩二世国王在柬埔寨建立。

Egbert becomes king of Wessex. Krum becomes Khan of Bulgaria. The Angkorian dynasty is founded in Cambodia by King Jayavarman II.

803

803

威尼斯脱离拜占庭帝国获得独立。

Venice gains independence from the Byzantine Empire.

805

805

玛雅城市科潘已被废弃。

The Mayan city of Copán is abandoned.

806

806

维京人屠杀了爱奥那岛上所有宗教社区的居民。

Vikings slaughter all the inhabitants of the religious community on the island of Iona.

807

807

基督教化的维京人在康沃尔海岸登陆，并与康沃尔人结盟，共同对抗西撒克逊人。

Christianized Vikings land on the Cornish coast and form an alliance with the Cornish to fight against the West Saxons.

809

809

拜占庭帝国和保加尔人之间的战争一直持续到公元 817 年。

The Byzantine Empire and the Bulgars are at war until 817.

810

810

《凯尔经》由凯尔特人完成。保加尔人在克鲁姆汗的领导下消灭了阿瓦尔人。中国要求西藏归还占领的领土。

The Book of Kells is completed by the Celts. Bulgars, under Khan Krum, destroy the Avars. China demands the return of territory captured by Tibet.

811

811

保加利亚汗王克鲁姆击败拜占庭人并杀死了皇帝。

Khan Krum of Bulgaria defeats the Byzantines and kills the emperor.

813

813

虔诚者路易与他的父亲查理曼大帝共同加冕为法兰克帝国皇帝。在第三次图尔宗教会议上，神父们被命令用当地语言（通俗拉丁语或德语）布道。马蒙成为阿拔斯王朝的哈里发；他在巴格达创建的智慧宫——一座图书馆和翻译学院——成为阿拉伯世界最重要的学府。

Louis the Pious is crowned co-emperor of the Franks with his father Charlemagne. At the Third Council of Tours priests are ordered to preach in the vernacular (either Vulgar Latin or German). Al-Mamun rules as Abbasid caliph; the House of Wisdom – a library and translation institute – he founds in Baghdad becomes the most important school in the Arab world.

814

814

查理曼大帝驾崩，虔诚者路易继位。保加利亚人围攻君士坦丁堡。塞尔维亚建国。

The death of Charlemagne; Louis the Pious succeeds him. The Bulgarians lay siege to Constantinople. Serbia is founded.

820

820

波斯数学家穆萨·花剌子模发展了一套代数体系。

Musa al-Chwarazmi, a Persian mathematician, develops a system of algebra.

823

823

克里特岛被萨拉森人从拜占庭人手中夺取。

Crete is conquered from the Byzantines by the Saracens.

824

824

《罗马宪章》确立了神圣罗马帝国皇帝凌驾于教皇之上的权威。伊尼戈·阿里斯塔反抗法兰克人，建立了纳瓦拉王国。

The Constitutio Romana establishes the authority of the Holy Roman Emperors over the pope. Iñigo Arista revolts against the Franks and establishes the kingdom of Navarre.

825

825

肯特郡、萨里郡、苏塞克斯郡、东安格利亚郡和埃塞克斯郡都隶属于威塞克斯郡。

Kent, Surrey, Sussex, East Anglia and Essex submit to Wessex.

827

827

瓦伦丁教皇成为第100任教皇。阿拉伯人入侵西西里岛。哈立德·本·阿卜杜勒梅利克和阿里·本·伊萨测量了地球的周长，结果为40248公里。

Pope Valentine becomes the 100th pope. Arabs invade Sicily. Chalid Ben Abdulmelik and Ali Ben Isa measure the circumference of the Earth, getting a result of 40,248 km.

828

828

威塞克斯的埃格伯特成为英格兰第一位国王。

Egbert of Wessex becomes the first king of England.

829

829

威塞克斯的埃格伯特征服了麦西亚，并被尊称为不列颠瓦尔达。

Egbert of Wessex conquers Mercia and is recognized as Bretwalda.

830

830

威塞克斯的埃格伯特击败了威尔士人。《不列颠史》（Historia Brittonum）成书，该书被认为是内尼乌斯所著，以列举亚瑟王的十二场战役而闻名。印度尼西亚的佛教圣地婆罗浮屠历经五十年建成。

Egbert of Wessex defeats the Welsh. The Historia Brittonum, attributed to Nennius, and known for its list of the twelve battles of King Arthur, is written. The Buddhist monument of Borobodur, in Indonesia, is completed after 50 years of work.

831

831

苏格兰国旗诞生的传说日期；据说它在国王昂古斯二世与盎格鲁人交战的前夜显现。拜占庭皇帝狄奥斐罗禁止使用圣像。虔诚者路易在其统治时期第一次内战结束后，重新登基成为法兰克皇帝。萨拉森人攻占巴勒莫。圣安斯加尔在瑞典比尔卡创建了第一座教堂。第二座圣马可大教堂在威尼斯建成。

The legendary date of the genesis of the Flag of Scotland; it is said to have appeared to King Óengus II the night before a battle against the Angles. Byzantine Emperor, Theophilus, forbids the usage of icons. Louis the Pious is reinstated as Emperor of the Franks following the end of the first civil war of his reign. The Saracens capture Palermo. St Ansgar founds the first church in Sweden, at Birka. The second St Mark’s Basilica is built in Venice.

836

836

威塞克斯的埃格伯特被丹麦人击败。

Egbert of Wessex is defeated by the Danes.

837

837

哈雷彗星从距离地球约 500 万公里处掠过——这是它有史以来最接近地球的一次。

Halley’s Comet passes within approximately 5 million kilometres of the Earth – its closest ever approach.

838

838

在欣斯顿丘陵，威塞克斯的埃格伯特击败了丹麦人和西威尔士人。命运之石被安放在苏格兰的斯昆宫。费德利米德成为爱尔兰至高王。

At Hingston Down, Egbert of Wessex beats the Danish and the West Welsh. The Stone of Destiny is placed at Scone Palace, Scotland. Feidlimid becomes High-King of Ireland.

840

840

洛泰尔继承虔诚者路易的皇位。

Lothar succeeds Louis the Pious as Emperor.

841

841

挪威人建立的城镇迪夫林（Dyflinn）或都柏林位于爱尔兰。

The Norse town of Dyflinn or Dublin is founded in Ireland.

842

842

德国人路易和秃头查理宣誓效忠斯特拉斯堡，结成联盟对抗神圣罗马帝国皇帝洛泰尔。

Louis the German and Charles the Bald swear the Oaths of Strasbourg, an alliance against Holy Roman Emperor, Lothar.

843

843

肯尼斯·麦克阿尔平统一了苏格兰王国，成为苏格兰（阿尔巴）的第一位国王，同时也是皮克特人的国王。凡尔登条约将加洛林帝国瓜分给虔诚者路易的三个儿子；法兰西王国首次成为一个独立的国家。

Kenneth MacAlpin unites the kingdom of Scotia, becoming the first king of Scotland (Alba) as well as king of the Picts. The Treaty of Verdun divides the Carolingian Empire between the three sons of Louis the Pious; the kingdom of France becomes a distinct state for the first time.

844

844

罗德里·莫尔成为威尔士第一亲王。路易二世加冕为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。

Rhodri Mawr rules as the first prince of all Wales. Louis II is crowned Holy Roman Emperor.

845

845

佛教在中国是被禁止的。

Buddhism is banned in China.

846

846

阿拉伯海盗洗劫了梵蒂冈。

Arab pirates sack the Vatican.

850

850

阿拉伯人完善了星盘，这种导航仪器一直沿用到18世纪六分仪发明为止。大约在同一时期，墨西哥南部低地的玛雅文明开始衰落，其城市也被废弃。爱尔兰哲学家约翰·埃里根纳提出水星、金星、火星和木星都围绕太阳运行。

The Arabs perfect the astrolabe, the navigation instrument used until the invention of the sextant in the 18th century. Around this time, Mayan civilization in the southern lowlands of Mexico goes into decline and its cities are abandoned. Irish philosopher John Eriugena posits that Mercury, Venus, Mars and Jupiter circle the Sun.

855

855

路易二世继承洛泰尔成为西罗马皇帝。

Louis II succeeds Lothar as Western Emperor.

856

856

希腊科林斯地震造成约 45,000 人死亡；伊朗地震造成 200,000 人死亡。

An earthquake in Corinth in Greece, kills an estimated 45,000; in Iran an earthquake kills 200,000.

858

858

藤原氏家族，一个强大的摄政家族，开始控制日本天皇。

The beginning of the control of Japanese emperors by the Fujiwara clan, a powerful family of regents.

859

859

世界上最古老的大学——卡鲁因大学，位于摩洛哥的非斯市。

The University of Al Karaouine, the oldest university in the world, is founded in Fes in Morocco.

860

860

维京人控制了俄罗斯的诺夫哥罗德，并进攻君士坦丁堡。

The Vikings control Novgorod in Russia and attack Constantinople.

862

862

俄罗斯北部的东斯拉夫和芬兰部落邀请以瓦良格酋长留里克为首的维京人统治他们。

The East Slavic and Finnish tribes of northern Russia invite the Vikings, led by Varangian chieftain Rurik, to rule them.

865

865

俄国远征军威胁君士坦丁堡。保加利亚在鲍里斯一世统治下皈依东正教。

A Russian expedition threatens Constantinople. Bulgaria, under Boris I, converts to Orthodox Christianity.

866

866

维京军队攻占约克。路易二世在意大利击败了撒拉逊入侵者。教皇尼古拉一世禁止在巫术审判中使用酷刑。

A Viking army captures York. Louis II beats the Saracen invaders in Italy. Pope Nicholas I forbids the use of torture in prosecutions for witchcraft.

867

867

巴西尔一世成为拜占庭帝国的唯一统治者。

Basil I becomes sole ruler of the Byzantine Empire.

868

868

葡萄牙第一伯爵领由维马拉·佩雷斯建立，此前他从摩尔人手中收复了杜罗河北岸的地区。艾哈迈德·伊本·图伦脱离阿拔斯王朝，在埃及建立了图伦王朝。现存最古老的印刷书籍《金刚经》在中国印刷出版。

The First County of Portugal is established by Vímara Peres, after the reconquest of the region north of the Douro river from the Moors. Ahmad ibn-Tulun breaks away from the Abbasid caliphate, establishing the Tulunid dynasty in Egypt. The Diamond Sutra, the oldest printed book still in existence, is printed in China.

869

869

西罗马皇帝路易二世与东罗马皇帝巴西尔一世结盟，共同对抗撒拉逊人。

The Western Emperor Louis II allies with Eastern Emperor Basil I against the Saracens.

870

870

维京大军入侵英格兰，征服东盎格利亚。布拉格城堡建成。马耳他被来自西西里的阿拉伯人征服。

The Viking Great Summer Army invades England and conquers East Anglia. Prague Castle is founded. Malta is conquered by Arabs from Sicily.

871

871

阿尔弗雷德大帝成为英格兰国王。

Alfred the Great becomes king of England.

874

874

英戈尔弗·阿纳森 (Ingólfur Arnarson) 抵达冰岛，成为第一位永久维京定居者。

Ingólfur Arnarson arrives in Iceland as the first permanent Viking settler.

875

875

维京国王哈拉尔·金发征服了奥克尼和设得兰群岛，并将它们并入自己的王国。西法兰克国王秃头查理加冕为皇帝。

Harald Fairhair, Viking king, subdues Orkney and Shetland and adds them to his kingdom. Charles the Bald, king of West Francia, is crowned Emperor.

877

877

口吃者路易成为西法兰克国王。柬埔寨高棉国王因陀罗跋摩一世统一了他的王国。

Louis the Stammerer becomes king of the West Franks. Indravarman I of the Khmer in Cambodia unites his kingdom.

878

878

阿尔弗雷德在埃坦顿击败了古斯鲁姆率领的维京人；韦德莫尔条约将英格兰瓜分为盎格鲁-撒克逊人和丹麦人。

Alfred defeats the Vikings under Guthrum at Ethandune; the Treaty of Wedmore divides England between the Anglo-Saxons and the Danes.

879

879

尼泊尔从西藏获得独立。

Nepal gains independence from Tibet.

881

881

胖子查理加冕为西罗马皇帝。

Charles the Fat is crowned Western Emperor.

882

882

俄罗斯的奥列格将基辅定为首都。

Oleg of Russia makes Kiev his capital.

884

884

黄潮起义被唐朝在沙陀突厥的帮助下镇压了。

The Huang Chao rebellion is suppressed by the Tang Dynasty of China with the help of the Shatuo Turks.

885

885

维京人围攻法国巴黎，当时巴黎是西法兰克王国的首都。

The Vikings besiege Paris in France, at the time capital of the kingdom of the West Franks.

886

886

阿尔弗雷德大帝攻占伦敦，并将其更名为伦登堡。泰米尔朱罗王朝以坦焦尔为都城，统治南印度直至1267年。阿尔弗雷德大帝铸造了第一枚半便士；此前的半便士是由一便士切成两半制成的。

Alfred the Great captures London and renames it Lundenburgh. The Tamil Chola dynasty rules south India from its capital at Tanjore, until 1267. Alfred the Great mints the first halfpenny; previous halfpennies had been pennies cut in half.

887

887

藤原元经被任命为日本天皇的首席顾问。

Fujiwara Mototsune is installed as chief adviser to the Japanese emperor.

889

889

在朝鲜半岛，统一的新罗王国强征赋税，引发农民起义。高棉人在柬埔寨的吴哥开始建造一系列都城中的第一座。

In Korea, the unified Silla kingdom collects taxes by force, setting off peasant rebellions. The Khmers start to build the first of a series of capital cities at Angkor in Cambodia.

890

890

大约在同一时期，秘鲁的瓦里帝国开始衰落。

Around this time, the Huari Empire goes into decline in Peru.

891

891

《盎格鲁-撒克逊编年史》是一部编年史集，记载了盎格鲁-撒克逊人的历史，由僧侣撰写。

The collection of annals known as the Anglo-Saxon Chronicle, the history of the Anglo-Saxons, is written by monks.

894

894

诺森布里亚人和东盎格鲁人向阿尔弗雷德大帝宣誓效忠，但随即撕毁停战协定，进攻英格兰西南部。日本停止与中国的商业往来。

Northumbrians and East Angles swear allegiance to Alfred the Great, but promptly break their truce by attacking the south-west of England. Japan ceases commercial relations with China.

895

895

《音乐手册》的创作日期大致为[日期] ，标志着西方复调音乐的开端。

The approximate date of the composition of the Musica Enchiriadis, marking the beginnings of Western polyphonic music.

896

896

在卡林西亚的阿努尔夫的领导下，东法兰克人入侵并征服了意大利。保加利亚人在西蒙一世的率领下，在保加利亚菲贡战役中击败了拜占庭帝国。

The Eastern Franks invade and conquer Italy under the leadership of Arnulf of Carinthia. The Bulgarians, under Simeon I, defeat the Byzantine Empire at Bulgarophygon.

899

899

阿尔弗雷德大帝去世；爱德华二世继位。

The death of Alfred the Great; he is succeeded by Edward the Elder.

900

900

世界人口约为2.4亿。波斯科学家拉齐斯在他的著作中区分了天花和麻疹。大约在同一时期：来自中亚的游牧民族马扎尔人入侵欧洲，定居匈牙利；托尔特克人征服了墨西哥中央谷地，并在图拉建立了首都。

The world population is approximately 240 million. The Persian scientist Rhazes distinguishes smallpox from measles in the course of his writings. Around this date: Magyars, nomadic people from central Asia, invade Europe, settling Hungary; the Toltec conquer the Central Valley in Mexico and build their capital at Tula.

901

901

穆斯林征服西西里岛。军事长官朱文攻占唐朝都城。

Muslims conquer Sicily. Military governor, Zhu Wen, seizes the imperial Tang dynasty capital.

902

902

吴国由杨兴密在今中国南方的扬州建立。

The Wu State is founded in present-day Yangzhou in southern China by Yang Xingmi.

904

904

教宗塞尔吉乌斯三世继任教宗利奥五世，成为第119任教宗，开启了长达30年的“色情统治”时期。塞萨洛尼卡被撒拉逊人攻陷。阿拔斯王朝入侵并控制了埃及的图伦王朝埃米尔国。唐朝都城长安，古代世界最大的城市，被朱文摧毁。英国皇家铸币局成立。

Pope Sergius III succeeds Pope Leo V as the 119th pope, beginning the 30-year era of the Pornocracy. Thessalonica is captured by the Saracens. Abbasids invade and take control of the Tulunid emirate of Egypt. Chang’an, the capital of the Tang dynasty and the largest city in the ancient world, is destroyed by Zhu Wen. The Royal Mint is founded in England.

906

906

在斯昆举行的宗教会议团结了苏格兰基督教牧师，旨在进行福音改革，而不受罗马教皇塞尔吉乌斯三世的干预或权威。

A Synod at Scone unites Scottish Christian pastors for gospel reformation without the interference or authority of Pope Sergius III in Rome.

907

907

唐朝统治三百年后灭亡，朱文建立后梁朝，这是中国北方五朝中的第一个王朝；此后五十年间，中国处于战国纷争的局面。立轴画和手卷画在中国兴起。

The Tang dynasty falls after 300 years, and Zhu Wen establishes the Later Liang dynasty, the first of northern China’s Five Dynasties; for the next 50 years, China is divided into many warring states. Paintings on hanging scrolls and handscrolls are established in China.

908

908

在叶鲁阿宝赤的领导下，契丹蒙古人开始征服内蒙古和中国北方的几个地区。

Khitan Mongols under Ye-lu a-pao-chi begin the conquest of Inner Mongolia and several districts of northern China.

909

909

本笃会克吕尼修道院由奥弗涅伯爵威廉一世在勃艮第创建。

The Benedictine Cluny Abbey is founded in Burgundy by William I, Count of Auvergne.

911

911

维京首领罗洛定居在法国诺曼底。

Rollo, the Viking chief, settles in Normandy, France.

912

912

阿卜杜勒·拉赫曼三世成为西班牙科尔多瓦的倭马亚王朝哈里发；在他和平的统治时期，他发展了艺术和工业，例如造纸业。

Abd-al-Rahman III becomes Umayyad caliph of Cordoba, Spain; during his peaceful reign he develops arts and industry, such as paper-making.

914

914

维京人征服了爱尔兰的大部分地区。

Vikings conquer much of Ireland.

916

916

麦西亚女王埃塞尔弗莱德征服了威尔士。

The Mercian warrior queen Æthelflaed conquers Wales.

920

920

撒克逊人从丹麦人手中夺回东盎格利亚。加纳帝国的黄金时代在非洲拉开帷幕。

The Saxons retake East Anglia from the Danes. The golden age of the Ghana empire begins in Africa.

921

921

据报道，中国后梁朝时期，所有“蛮夷”部落都被契丹人平定。

In the Later Liang dynasty in China all ‘barbarian’ tribes are reported to have been pacified by the Khitan.

923

923

后梁王朝被李存许建立的后唐王朝所灭。

The Later Liang dynasty falls to the Later Tang dynasty, founded by Li Cunxu.

924

924

中国西北部的齐国被后唐朝征服。

Qi State in north-west China falls to the Later Tang dynasty.

925

925

蜀国，十国之一，在后唐入侵时投降。

Former Shu, one of the Ten Kingdoms, surrenders when invaded by the Later Tang.

927

927

如今英格兰境内的各个小王国被埃塞尔斯坦国王统一，建立了英格兰王国。位于意大利南部的古城塔兰托被撒拉逊人摧毁。楚国，即十国之一，由马阴建立。

The various small kingdoms within what is now England are unified by King Æthelstan, creating the kingdom of England. The ancient city of Taranto, in southern Italy, is destroyed by the Saracens. Chu State, one of the Ten Kingdoms, is founded by Ma Yin.

930

930

随着冰岛议会（现为世界上历史最悠久的议会）的成立，冰岛联邦正式成立。

With the establishment of the Alþing, now the world’s oldest parliament, the Icelandic Commonwealth is founded.

931

931

埃里克·布拉德阿克斯成为挪威第二任国王。

Eric Bloodaxe becomes second king of Norway.

934

934

德国国王亨利一世（绰号“捕鸟者”）率领基督教军队在国王格努帕的指挥下击败异教徒军队，征服了海德比。冰岛的埃尔德吉亚火山喷发是迄今为止记录到的最大规模的玄武岩洪流（玄武岩熔岩覆盖一片区域的喷发）。

The German king, Henry I, the Fowler, and his Christian forces under king Gnupa defeat the Heathen army and conquer Hedeby. The Eldgjá volcanic eruption in Iceland is the largest basalt flood (an eruption covering an area in basalt lava) ever recorded.

935

935

哈康一世（哈拉尔·哈拉尔之子）统一了挪威。安达卢斯首都科尔多瓦成为当时世界上最大的城市。后来，孟之祥建立了十国之一的蜀国。高丽王朝在朝鲜半岛中西部建立。

Haakon the Good, son of Harald Fairhair, reunites Norway. Córdoba, capital of Al-Andalus, becomes the largest city in the world. Later Shu, one of the Ten Kingdoms, is founded by Meng Zhixiang. Koryo state is founded in west-central Korea.

936

936

奥托大帝成为德国国王；962年，他加冕为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。在中国，后唐被后金灭亡，后金由石敬堂建立，石敬堂死后被称为后金高祖。十六州，包括今北京周边地区，被契丹帝国吞并。

Otto the Great becomes king of Germany; he is crowned Holy Roman Emperor in 962. In China, the Later Tang Dynasty falls to the Later Jin Dynasty founded by Shi Jingtang, posthumously known as Gaozu of Later Jin. Sixteen Prefectures, which includes the area around modern-day Beijing, is absorbed by the Khitan Empire.

937

937

英格兰国王埃塞尔斯坦在英格兰北部布鲁南堡战役中击败了一支由苏格兰人、爱尔兰人和丹麦人组成的大军。十国之一的吴国被李檗攻占，李檗随后建立了南唐。

Æthelstan of England defeats a large army of Scots, Irish and Danes at the Battle of Brunanburh, northern England. The Wu State, one of the Ten Kingdoms, is taken by Li Bian, who then founds the Southern Tang.

938

938

越南脱离中国获得独立。

Vietnam gains independence from China.

939

939

阿拉伯人将马德里割让给了莱昂王国。

The Arabs lose Madrid to the kingdom of Leon.

941

941

罗斯-拜占庭战争爆发。藤原忠平成为日本的独裁统治者。

The Rus’–Byzantine War is fought. Fujiwara Tadahira becomes civil dictator in Japan.

942

942

德赫巴斯国王海威尔·达 (Hywel Dda) 吞并格温内斯 (Gwynedd)，成为威尔士大部分地区的统治者。中国南汉王朝结束。

Hywel Dda, king of Deheubarth, annexes Gwynedd to become ruler of most of Wales. The Southern Han Dynasty ends in China.

945

945

英格兰国王埃德蒙一世征服了斯特拉斯克莱德，但坎伯兰和威斯特摩兰被苏格兰吞并。意大利国王洛泰尔二世控制了意大利，统治至950年。闽国被南唐攻占。

Edmund I of England conquers Strathclyde but Cumberland and Westmorland are annexed by the Scots. Lothair II of Italy takes control of Italy and rules until 950. The kingdom of Min is taken by the Southern Tang.

947

947

契丹帝国采用王朝名称“大辽”。在中国，后金王朝被后汉高祖建立的后汉王朝所取代。

The Khitan empire adopts the dynastic name ‘Great Liao’. In China, the Later Jin dynasty falls to the Later Han dynasty founded by Gaozu of Later Han.

949

949

据信，在这一天，太阳系所有行星的轨道都位于太阳系的同一 90% 弧度内；这种情况要到 2492 年 5 月 6 日才会再次发生。

The orbits of all the planets of the solar system are thought to have been within the same 90% arc of the solar system on this date; it will not occur again until 6 May 2492.

950

950

伊博-乌库文化在尼日利亚东部开始繁荣发展。后汉王朝灭亡。

Igbo-Ukwu culture begins to flourish in eastern Nigeria. The fall of the Later Han dynasty.

951

951

在中国，楚国被南唐吞并，郭维建立了后周王朝。刘民在中国北方建立了北汉王朝。

In China, the Chu State is absorbed by the Southern Tang, and the Later Zhou dynasty is founded by Guo Wei. The Northern Han dynasty is founded by Liu Min in northern China.

954

954

埃里克·血斧死后，埃德雷德成为英格兰国王。

On the death of Eric Bloodaxe, Edred becomes king of England.

955

955

埃德维成为英格兰国王。德意志国王奥托大帝在奥格斯堡附近的莱希费尔德战役中击败马扎尔人，并在赖希尼茨战役中击败斯拉夫人。

Edwy becomes king of England. Otto the Great, king of the Germans, defeats the Magyars at the Battle of Lechfeld, near Augsburg, and defeats the Slavs at Reichnitz.

957

957

昌德拉印度教王朝结束，现代蒙古地区由此进入混乱时期。

The Chandra Hindu dynasty ends, thus beginning a time of chaos in the area of modern-day Mongolia.

958

958

丹麦国王哈拉尔皈依基督教。

King Harald of Denmark accepts Christianity.

959

959

英格兰国王埃德威去世，他的弟弟“和平者”埃德加继位，巩固了英格兰王国。

Edwy, king of England dies and is succeeded by his brother Edgar the Peaceable who consolidates the English kingdom.

960

960

邓斯坦成为坎特伯雷大主教和埃德加的首席顾问；他改革了修道院，并推行圣本笃会规。米奇斯瓦夫一世是波兰的第一位统治者。宋朝统一了中国。

Dunstan becomes Archbishop of Canterbury and Edgar’s chief adviser; he reforms monasteries and enforces the rule of St Benedict. Mieczyslaw I is the first ruler of Poland. The Song dynasty reunifies China.

961

961

拜占庭帝国从穆斯林手中夺回了克里特岛。

The Byzantine Empire recaptures Crete from Muslim control.

962

962

奥托大帝加冕为神圣罗马帝国皇帝；他与教皇约翰十二世签署了《奥托法令》，其中一项内容是将教皇国的控制权授予教皇。土耳其奴隶战士阿尔普提金攻占了阿富汗的加兹尼要塞，建立了加兹尼王朝。

Otto the Great is crowned Holy Roman Emperor; he signs the Diploma Ottonarium with Pope John XII, among other things, granting control of the Papal States to the Pope. Alptigin, a Turkish warrior slave, captures the Afghan fortress of Ghazni and founds the Ghaznavid dynasty.

963

963

卢森堡建城。梅什科一世建立波兰王国；他之后由博莱斯拉夫一世继位，博莱斯拉夫一世极大地扩张了波兰的领土。

Luxemburg is founded. Mieszko I founds the kingdom of Poland; he is succeeded by Boleslav I, who greatly expands its territory.

964

964

苏菲的图文天文著作《恒星之书》出版。

Al-Sufi’s illustrated astronomical text the Book of Fixed Stars is published.

965

965

北宋军队入侵后蜀，迫使后蜀投降。

Northern Song armies invade Later Shu and force them to surrender.

968

968

拜占庭历史学家利奥·迪亚科努斯首次有记载地提到了太阳的日冕。

Byzantine historian Leo Diaconus makes the first recorded reference to the Sun’s corona.

969

969

约翰一世成为东罗马帝国皇帝。法蒂玛王朝从突尼斯扩张，从图伦王朝手中征服埃及；他们建造了开罗，并将其定为埃及首都。

John I becomes Emperor of the Eastern Roman Empire. The Fatimid dynasty expands from Tunis and conquers Egypt from the Tulunid dynasty; they build Cairo and make it the Egyptian capital.

970

970

法国爆发长达十年的饥荒。拜占庭皇帝约翰一世成功抵御了蛮族入侵，保卫了东罗马帝国。法蒂玛王朝在开罗建立了爱资哈尔大学，这是世界上最早的大学之一。中国政府开始发行纸币。

A decade-long famine begins in France. The Byzantine Emperor John I successfully defends the Eastern Roman Empire from a barbarian invasion. The Fatimids build the al-Azhar University in Cairo, one of the world’s first universities. Paper money is introduced by the Chinese government.

971

971

中国南汉被宋朝灭亡。

The Southern Han falls to the Song Dynasty in China.

974

974

拜占庭帝国从阿拔斯王朝手中夺回叙利亚。

The Byzantine Empire retakes Syria from the Abbasids.

975

975

英格兰国王爱德华殉道者加冕。宋太祖征服南唐和湖南。

King Edward the Martyr is crowned in England. Emperor Taizu of the Song Dynasty conquers the Southern Tang and Hunan Province.

976

976

布莱恩·博鲁成为明斯特国王。巴本堡的利奥波德被任命为奥地利藩侯；巴本堡家族统治奥地利直至1246年。岳麓书院在中国湖南省成立。

Brian Boru becomes king of Munster. Leopold of Babenberg is appointed Margrave of Austria; the Babenberg family rules Austria until 1246. The Yuelu Academy, in Hunan Province, China, is founded.

978

978

埃塞尔雷德二世十岁时，因其同父异母的兄长殉道者爱德华被刺杀而成为英格兰国王。弗拉基米尔成为基辅大公。托尔特克人与尤卡坦半岛的玛雅人融合。吴越国向宋朝投降。

Æthelred II becomes king of England at the age of ten, following the assassination of his half-brother, Edward the Martyr. Vladimir becomes Grand Prince of Kiev. The Toltec merge with the Maya on the Yucután Peninsula. The Wu-Yue State surrenders to the Song Dynasty.

979

979

马恩岛议会廷沃尔德成立。宋朝灭亡北汉。

The Tynwald, the parliament of the Isle of Man, is founded. The Song Dynasty destroys the Northern Han State.

980

980

在东非，阿里·伊本·哈桑建立了赞吉帝国，继承了基尔瓦帝国。

In East Africa, The Zanj Empire is founded by Ali ibn Hasan, succeeding the Kilwa Empire.

981

981

维京探险家红胡子埃里克发现了格陵兰岛。成百上千渴望土地的维京人涌向那里。阿拉伯人生产出了第一款商业化销售的剃须专用皂。

Viking explorer Eric the Red discovers Greenland. Hundreds of land-starved Vikings flood to it. The Arabs produce the first commercially sold special soap for shaving.

983

983

中国出版了一部共1000章的百科全书《太平御兰》。

A 1,000-chapter encyclopaedia, the Taiping Yulan, is produced in China.

985

985

朱罗王朝国王罗茶罗茶一世征服了印度南部的喀拉拉邦。

Chola King Rajaraja I conquers Kerala in south India.

987

987

雨果·卡佩成为法国第一位卡佩王朝国王。

Hugh Capet becomes the first Capetian king of France.

988

988

艾资哈尔大学位于埃及开罗，是世界上第二古老的大学。

Al-Azhar University is founded in Cairo, Egypt, the second oldest university in the world.

989

989

基辅的弗拉基米尔选择东正教作为其国民的国教。桑科雷大学在廷巴克图成立。

Vladimir of Kiev chooses Orthodox Christianity as the official religion for his people. Sankore University is founded in Timbuktu.

990

990

开罗的哈基姆清真寺开始动工。托尔特克人占领了玛雅古城奇琴伊察。

Construction work begins on the Al-Hakim Mosque in Cairo. The Toltec people take over the Mayan city of Chichen Itza.

997

997

加兹尼的穆罕默德在阿富汗帝国掌权；在他的统治期间，他入侵印度 17 次。
