Mohammed of Ghazni comes to power in the Afghan empire; he invades India 17 times during his reign.

998

998

奥托三世夺回罗马城，并恢复了其表兄教皇格里高利五世的职位，此前他残害并弄瞎了其对手——对立教皇约翰十六世。

Otto III retakes the city of Rome and reinstates his cousin Pope Gregory V after mutilating and blinding his rival, the Antipope John XVI.

1000

1000

世界人口为3.1亿。斯沃尔德海战（或称斯沃尔德海战）在波罗的海西部爆发，交战双方为挪威国王奥拉夫·特里格瓦松及其敌对联盟。匈牙利由伊什特万一世建立。大约在同一时期：莱夫·埃里克森登陆北美，并将其命名为文兰；胡图族抵达今天的卢旺达和布隆迪，人口很快超过了当地的特瓦族；班图语族在南部非洲建立王国；由于黄金贸易，西非的塔克鲁尔王国和高王国蓬勃发展；中国发明了火药；毛利人在新西兰定居；波利尼西亚人开始建造石庙；日本宫廷女官紫式部创作了小说《源氏物语》；秘鲁农民开始种植红薯和玉米。

The population of the world is 310 million. The Battle of Svolder or Svold, a naval battle, is fought in the western Baltic between King Olaf Tryggvason of Norway and an alliance of his enemies. The Hungarian state is founded by Stephen I. Around this date: Leif Ericson lands in North America, calling it Vinland; the Hutu arrive in present-day Rwanda and Burundi, soon outnumbering the native Twa; Bantu-speaking peoples set up kingdoms in southern Africa; the kingdoms of Takrur and Gao flourish in West Africa due to the gold trade; gunpowder is invented in China; Maori people settle in New Zealand; Polynesians begin to build stone temples; the Japanese court lady, Murasaki Shikibu, writes the novel Tale of Genji; farmers in Peru grow sweet potatoes and corn.

1002

1002

英格兰国王埃塞尔雷德下令屠杀所有在英格兰的丹麦人，导致圣布莱斯日大屠杀。布莱恩·博鲁成为爱尔兰最高国王。拜占庭皇帝巴西尔二世与保加利亚沙皇萨穆伊尔之间爆发全面战争。

The English king, Æthelred, orders all Danes in England to be killed, leading to the St Brice’s Day Massacre. Brian Boru becomes High King of Ireland. All-out war breaks out between Byzantine Emperor Basil II and Bulgarian Tsar Samuil.

1006

1006

有记录以来最亮的超新星 SN 1006 位于天狼座。

The brightest supernova ever recorded, SN 1006, is observed in the constellation of Lupus.

1009

1009

圣墓教堂被哈里发哈基姆·比·阿姆尔·阿拉摧毁。越南第一个独立王朝——李朝宣告建立。

The Church of the Holy Sepulchre is destroyed by Caliph al-Hakim bi-Amr Allah. The Ly dynasty, Vietnam’s first independent dynasty, is proclaimed.

1010

1010

维京探险家托尔芬·卡尔塞夫尼试图在北美建立定居点。波斯诗人菲尔多西完成了他的诗集《列王纪》。越南北部建立了李朝。马姆斯伯里的艾尔默尝试驾驶他自己制造的滑翔机飞行。

Viking explorer Thorfinn Karlsefni attempts to found a settlement in North America. Persian poet Ferdowsi finishes writing his poetic opus, The Shahnameh. The Native Ly dynasty is founded in northern Vietnam. Eilmer of Malmesbury attempts flight in a glider of his own construction.

1013

1013

丹麦国王斯韦恩一世入侵英格兰；埃塞尔雷德二世逃往诺曼底，斯韦恩成为英格兰国王。中国首都开封成为当时世界上最大的城市。

The Danes invade England under King Sweyn I; Æthelred II flees to Normandy, and Sweyn becomes king of England. Kaifeng, capital of China, becomes the largest city in the world.

1014

1014

埃塞尔雷德返回英格兰，重夺英格兰王位。爱尔兰至高王布莱恩·博鲁在克朗塔夫战役中击败维京人，但自己也战死沙场。在克莱迪翁战役中，巴西尔二世击败保加利亚军队，屠杀了15000名战俘。德国国王亨利二世加冕为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。拉金德拉一世成为朱罗王朝的统治者，朱罗王朝统治着印度的大部分地区。

Æthelred returns to England and retakes the English crown. Brian Boru, High King of all Ireland, defeats the Vikings at the Battle of Clontarf, but loses his life. In the Battle of Kleidion, Basil II defeats the Bulgarian army and massacres 15,000 prisoners. Henry II of Germany is crowned Henry II, Holy Roman Emperor. Rajendra I becomes ruler of the Cholas, who dominate much of India.

1015

1015

维京国王克努特大帝入侵英格兰。

Canute the Great, a Viking king, invades England.

1016

1016

克努特成为英格兰、丹麦、挪威和瑞典部分地区的国王，直到 1035 年。可萨汗国的统治者乔治·楚尔被拜占庭-罗斯联军俘虏，可萨汗国就此灭亡。

Canute becomes king of England, Denmark, Norway and part of Sweden, until 1035. George Tsul, ruler of Khazaria, is captured by a combined Byzantine–Rus’ force, effectively ending Khazaria’s existence.

地震部分摧毁了圆顶清真寺。

Earthquakes partly destroy the Dome of the Rock.

1017

1017

英格兰分为威塞克斯伯爵领、麦西亚伯爵领、东盎格利亚伯爵领和诺森布里亚伯爵领。哈姆扎·伊本·阿里·伊本·艾哈迈德宣称法蒂玛王朝的哈里发哈基姆·比·阿姆尔·阿拉是真主，并创立了德鲁兹教。

England is divided into the earldoms of Wessex, Mercia, East Anglia and Northumbria. Hamza ibn-’Ali ibn-Ahmad declares that the Fatimid Caliph Al-Hakim bi-Amr Allah is God, founding the Druze religion.

1018

1018

保加利亚并入拜占庭帝国。巴克法斯特修道院在英格兰建立。

Bulgaria becomes part of the Byzantine Empire. Buckfast Abbey is founded in England.

1019

1019

瑞典和挪威在孔艾尔夫签署条约。来自阿富汗地区的加兹尼军队占领了印度北部的大部分地区。俄罗斯基辅的统治者智者雅罗斯拉夫开始统一俄罗斯众多公国。

Sweden and Norway sign a treaty at Kungälv. Ghazni armies from the area of Afghanistan occupy most of northern India. Yaroslav the Wise, ruler of Kiev in Russia, begins the unification of many Russian principalities.

1020

1020

克努特大帝编纂了英格兰的法律。大约在同一时期，波兰国王博莱斯拉夫一世建立了一个强大的国家。包括罗马、佛罗伦萨和威尼斯在内的意大利城镇成为城邦。圣约翰骑士团在耶路撒冷建造了一座收容所。

Canute the Great codifies the laws of England. Around this time, Boleslav I of Poland creates a powerful state. Italian towns, including Rome, Florence and Venice, become city states. A hospice is built in Jerusalem by the Knights Hospitaller.

1021

1021

阿尔-扎希尔成为法蒂玛王朝哈里发；法蒂玛王朝的势力衰落。

Al-Zahir becomes Fatimid Caliph; Fatimid power declines.

1023

1023

塞维利亚的法官兼总督夺取政权，称阿巴德一世，从而建立了阿巴德王朝。

The Judge-Governor of Sevilla seizes power as Abbad I, thus founding the Abbadid dynasty.

1024

1024

神圣罗马帝国萨利安王朝由康拉德二世创立。

The Salian Dynasty of the Holy Roman Empire is founded by Conrad II.

1030

1030

法国国王亨利一世起兵反抗其父罗伯特。在阿富汗，马苏德夺取了伽色尼王朝的王位；他的帝国疆域从波斯一直延伸到恒河。意大利僧侣圭多·阿雷佐创立了视唱练耳法，用于通过听觉学习音乐。

Henry I of France revolts against his father Robert. In Afghanistan, Masud seizes the Ghaznavid throne; his empire stretches from Persia to the Ganges. An Italian monk, Guido of Arezzo, develops the solfège system, for learning music by ear.

1031

1031

亨利一世成为法国国王。科尔多瓦的摩尔人哈里发国崩溃。

Henry I becomes king of France. The Moorish caliphate of Córdoba collapses.

1034

1034

拜占庭皇后佐伊嫁给了她的侍从，并拥立他为东罗马帝国皇帝，即米海尔四世。

Empress Zoe of Byzantium marries her chamberlain and elevates him to the throne of the Eastern Roman Empire as Michael IV.

1035

1035

哈罗德一世代替他的同父异母兄弟担任摄政王。法国北部的诺曼底势力日益强大。

Harold I becomes regent in place of his half brother. Normandy in the north of France grows powerful.

1037

1037

哈罗德一世从他的同父异母兄弟哈斯卡努特手中夺取了英格兰王位。西班牙的卡斯蒂利亚王国和莱昂王国合并。

Harold I takes the crown of England from his half-brother Harthcanut. The Spanish kingdoms of Castile and Leon unite.

1038

1038

中国西北部的西夏宣布独立。

Western Xia in north-western China declares independence.

1040

1040

哈斯卡努特在桑威治登陆，重夺英格兰王位。邓肯一世国王在与他的堂兄兼对手麦克白的战斗中阵亡，麦克白继承了他的王位。塞尔柱突厥人在波斯击败加兹尼王朝，并向巴格达进军。现存最古老的酿酒厂在德国魏恩施蒂芬成立。

Harthcanut lands at Sandwich and reclaims the English throne. King Duncan I is killed in battle against his first cousin and rival Macbeth, who succeeds him. The Seljuk Turks defeat the Ghaznavids in Persia and advance on Baghdad. The oldest brewery still active is founded at Weihenstephan in Germany.

1041

1041

忏悔者爱德华结束流放生涯，返回哈特卡努特王位，成为王位继承人。

Edward the Confessor returns from exile to become the heir to Harthcanut’s throne.

1042

1042

忏悔者爱德华成为英格兰国王。拜占庭国王米海尔五世被民众起义废黜；拜占庭帝国皇后佐伊与她的妹妹狄奥多拉一起成为皇后；她第三次结婚，并拥立她的丈夫为君士坦丁九世。

Edward the Confessor becomes king of England. Michael V of Byzantium is deposed by popular revolt; Zoe, Empress of the Byzantine Empire becomes Empress with her sister Theodora; she marries for the third time and elevates her husband to the throne as Constantine IX.

1043

1043

齐亚里德王朝在波斯终结。

The Ziyarids dynasty ends in Persia.

1044

1044

阿奴律陀在缅甸掌权；他建立了一个庞大的帝国，壮大了军队，并建立了王朝。中国各地建立了学校，为科举考试培训学生。阿奴律陀国王夺取了缅甸蒲甘王朝的王位。

Anawrahta takes power in Burma; he builds a large empire, strengthens his army, and founds a dynasty. Schools are established throughout China to train students for the civil service exams. King Anawrahta seizes the throne of Pagan, Myanmar.

1045

1045

忏悔者爱德华开始建造威斯敏斯特教堂。熙德在西班牙被尊为民族英雄。毕昇在中国发明了活字印刷术。

Edward the Confessor begins the construction of Westminster Abbey. El Cid is proclaimed a national hero in Spain. Movable-type printing is invented by Bi Sheng in China.

1047

1047

征服者威廉巩固了对诺曼底的控制。

William the Conqueror secures control of Normandy.

1050

1050

瑞典军队进攻芬兰。约鲁巴人的文化在西非尼日利亚的伊费蓬勃发展。阿纳萨齐人定居在如今新墨西哥州的查科峡谷。日本雕塑家丈昭创立了他的学校。

Swedish forces attack Finland. The culture of the Yoruba people of Ife flourishes in Nigeria in West Africa. Anasazi settlers inhabit the Chaco canyon in modern-day New Mexico. The Japanese sculptor, Jocho, founds his school.

1051

1051

俄罗斯的伊拉里翁成为东斯拉夫国家基辅罗斯的第一位本土东正教大主教。

Ilarion of Russia becomes the first native Metropolitan of the Eastern Orthodox Church in the East Slavic state of Kievan Rus.

1053

1053

在奇维塔特战役中，诺曼底伯爵汉弗莱的 3000 名骑兵击溃了教皇利奥九世的军队。

In the Battle of Civitate, 3,000 horsemen of Norman Count Humphrey rout the troops of Pope Leo IX.

1054

1054

罗马天主教会与拜占庭东正教会之间发生了永久性分裂。

A permanent split occurs between the Catholic Church of Rome and the Orthodox Christian Church of Byzantium.

1057

1057

苏格兰国王麦克白在与苏格兰国王马尔科姆三世的战斗中阵亡。缅甸国王阿瑙拉塔攻占泰国北部丹东，巩固了该国的上座部佛教。

King Macbeth of Scotland is killed in battle against Malcolm III of Scotland. King Anawrahta of Myanmar captures Thanton in northern Thailand, strengthening Theravada Buddhism in the country.

1059

1059

阿尔摩拉维王朝征服了摩洛哥柏柏尔人，即贝尔格瓦塔人。

The Almoravids conquer the Moroccan Berbers, the Berghouata.

1061

1061

诺曼人征服了西西里岛的墨西拿。西弗里西亚（荷兰）的大部分地区被德意志帝国军队征服，并割让给了乌得勒支主教。

The Normans conquer Messina in Sicily. Most of West Frisia (Holland) is conquered by imperial German armies and given to the Bishop of Utrecht.

1062

1062

阿尔摩拉维王朝征服了摩洛哥，建立了一个以马拉喀什为首都的王国，其疆域从西班牙延伸到塞内加尔。

The Almoravids overrun Morocco and establish a kingdom with its capital at Marrakech, stretching from Spain to Senegal.

1064

1064

亚利桑那州的日落火山口火山首次喷发。

The Sunset Crater Volcano in Arizona erupts for the first time.

1065

1065

威斯敏斯特教堂举行祝圣仪式。加利西亚王国和葡萄牙王国在加西亚的统治下获得独立。穆斯林塞尔柱突厥人入侵小亚细亚。

Westminster Abbey is consecrated. The kingdoms of Galicia and Portugal become independent under the rule of Garcia. Muslim Seljuk Turks invade Asia Minor.

1066

1066

在斯坦福桥战役中，英格兰国王哈罗德·戈德温森击败了挪威国王哈拉尔，标志着英格兰维京时代的结束。诺曼底公爵威廉在黑斯廷斯战役中击败哈罗德，加冕为英格兰国王。哈雷彗星出现，并被记录在贝叶挂毯上。

At the Battle of Stamford Bridge, King Harold Godwinson of England defeats Harald of Norway marking the end of the Viking era in England. William, Duke of Normandy, defeats Harold at the Battle of Hastings and is crowned king of England. Halley’s Comet appears and is recorded in the Bayeux Tapestry.

1067

1067

伦敦塔开始动工。特朗卡韦尔家族接管了法国卡尔卡松的产业。

Work begins on the building of the Tower of London. The Trencavel family takes over in Carcassonne in France.

1069

1069

征服者威廉骑马穿过英格兰北部，烧毁房屋、庄稼、牲畜和土地，导致超过 10 万人死于饥饿和严寒。

William the Conqueror rides through the north of England, burning houses, crops, cattle and land, resulting in the deaths of over 100,000 people from starvation and winter cold.

1070

1070

赫里沃德·韦克在英格兰东部的沼泽地带发动了一场撒克逊人的叛乱。

Hereward the Wake begins a Saxon revolt in the Fens of eastern England.

1071

1071

意大利南部最后一个拜占庭控制的城市巴里被罗伯特·吉斯卡尔攻占。土耳其塞尔柱人占领耶路撒冷；他们在曼齐克特战役中击败拜占庭军队，并控制了小亚细亚的大部分地区。非洲人君士坦丁将希腊医学带到了西方。

The last Byzantine-controlled city in southern Italy, Bari, is captured by Robert Guiscard. Turkish Seljuks take Jerusalem; they defeat the Byzantine army at the Battle of Manzikert and take control of much of Asia Minor. Constantine the African brings Greek medicine to the West.

1072

1072

英格兰国王威廉一世入侵苏格兰，在芬兰地区击败了赫里沃德·韦克。诺曼军队开始征服西西里岛。

William I of England invades Scotland; he defeats Hereward the Wake in the Fens. Norman armies begin the conquest of Sicily.

1073

1073

拉比·伊查基·阿尔法西 (Rabbi Yitchaki Alfassi) 完成了犹太法律的重要著作《 Rif》的撰写。

Rabbi Yitchaki Alfassi finishes writing the Rif, an important work of Jewish law.

1075

1075

三位伯爵反抗征服者威廉的叛乱是诺曼征服中最后一次重要的抵抗行动。神圣罗马帝国皇帝亨利四世征服了萨克森。辽代编纂完成佛教大藏经。

The rebellion of three earls against William the Conqueror is the last serious act of resistance in the Norman Conquest. Henry IV, Holy Roman Emperor, subjugates Saxony. The Liao Dynasty version of the Buddhist Tripitaka is completed.

1076

1076

德克五世伯爵从乌得勒支主教手中夺回了西弗里西亚（荷兰）的大部分地区。阿尔摩拉维王朝攻占了加纳首都昆比。

Count Dirk V reconquers most of West Frisia (Holland) from the Bishop of Utrecht. The Almoravids capture the Ghanaian capital of Kumbi.

1077

1077

罗伯特·库尔特霍斯发动了第一次反抗其父征服者威廉的起义。有记载的第一次决斗审判在英格兰举行。教皇格里高利将神圣罗马帝国皇帝亨利四世逐出天主教会；亨利请求宽恕，但帝国与教皇之间的冲突一直持续到12世纪。杜克利亚王国在塞尔维亚建立。阿尔摩拉维王朝入侵非洲的加纳。贝叶挂毯完成。

Robert Curthose instigates his first insurrection against his father, William the Conqueror. The first recorded trial by combat is staged in England. Pope Gregory expels the Holy Roman Emperor Henry IV from the Catholic Church; Henry pleads forgiveness, but conflict between the Empire and the Papacy continues into the 12th century. The kingdom of Duklja is founded in Serbia. The Almoravids invade Ghana in Africa. The Bayeux Tapestry is completed.

1078

1078

圣地亚哥-德孔波斯特拉大教堂始建于西班牙加利西亚地区。

The cathedral of Santiago de Compostela is begun in Galicia, Spain.

1079

1079

英格兰国王威廉一世建立了新森林。圣鲁普雷希茨贝格修道院院长希尔德加德首次提及啤酒花在酿酒中的应用。波斯天文学家奥马尔·海亚姆计算出一年的长度为365.24219858156天，精确到秒。

William I of England establishes the New Forest. Abbess Hildegarde of St Ruprechtsberg makes the first surviving reference to the use of hops in brewing. The Persian astronomer Omar Khayyám computes the length of the year as 365.24219858156 days; he is accurate to within one second.

1080

1080

英格兰国王威廉一世致信教皇，提醒他英格兰国王不欠教皇任何效忠。

William I of England writes to the pope to remind him that the king of England owes him no allegiance.

1081

1081

拜占庭皇帝尼基弗鲁斯三世被阿莱克修斯一世·科穆宁推翻，中拜占庭时期结束，科穆宁王朝开始。科孚岛被意大利南部诺曼国王罗伯特·吉斯卡尔从拜占庭帝国手中夺取。

Byzantine Emperor Nicephorus III is overthrown by Alexius I Comnenus, ending the Middle Byzantine period and beginning the Comnenan dynasty. Corfu is taken from the Byzantine Empire by Robert Guiscard, Norman king of southern Italy.

1082

1082

神圣罗马帝国皇帝亨利四世围攻罗马并攻入城内；罗马人同意召开宗教会议，以裁决亨利与教皇格里高利七世之间的争端。整部佛教三藏经的韩文印刷工作完成。

Henry IV, Holy Roman Emperor, besieges Rome and gains entry; a synod is agreed upon by the Romans to rule on the dispute between Henry and Pope Gregory VII. The Korean printing of the entire Buddhist Tripitaka is completed.

1083

1083

教皇格里高利七世被神圣罗马帝国皇帝亨利四世围困在圣天使堡。波斯尼亚被杜克利亚征服。

Pope Gregory VII is besieged in Castel Sant’Angelo by Henry IV, the Holy Roman Emperor. Bosnia is conquered by Duklja.

1085

1085

大约在这一时期，图勒爱斯基摩文化传播到格陵兰岛和西伯利亚。

Around this date, Thule Eskimo culture spreads to Greenland and Siberia.

1086

1086

《末日审判书》是英格兰国王威廉一世为了确保税收和征费的合理性而委托编纂的。随着日本天皇闭关锁国制度的推行，藤原家族的势力开始衰落。

The Domesday survey is commissioned by William I of England to ensure proper taxation and levies. The power of the Fujiwara family declines in Japan with the introduction of the cloistered emperor system.

1090

1090

大约在同一时期，中国开封建造了一座水力驱动的机械钟。

Around this date, a mechanical clock, driven by water, is built in Kaifeng in China.

1091

1091

缅甸蒲甘正在兴建约15000座寺庙和宫殿。

The construction of around 15,000 temples and palaces is under way in Pagan, Myanmar.

1092

1092

伊斯兰教派刺客杀死了塞尔柱维齐尔。

The Islamic sect, the Assassins, kill the Seljuk vizier.

1096

1096

第一次十字军东征是为了从塞尔柱人手中夺回巴勒斯坦而发起的。

The First Crusade is launched to retake Palestine from the Seljuks.

1098

1098

西多修道院在法国建立，标志着熙笃会修士的开端。

The monastery of Citeaux is founded in France marking the start of the Cistercian Order of monks.

1099

1099

十字军攻占耶路撒冷。

The Crusaders capture Jerusalem.

1100

1100

贾亚德瓦创作了印度爱情诗《吉塔戈文达》。大约在同一时期：中古英语取代了古英语；北美亚利桑那州的霍霍坎人建造了平台土墩；复活节岛上竖立了第一批雕像；夏威夷群岛出现了有组织的社会；波利尼西亚人在皮特凯恩岛建立了最早的定居点；秘鲁的印加帝国崛起；西非的加纳帝国衰落；中非扎伊尔的加丹加建立；秘鲁西北海岸的昌昌遗址是奇穆文明的鼎盛时期；北美的阿纳萨齐人在梅萨维德、查科峡谷和切利峡谷建造了崖居；跳棋游戏被发明。

Jayadeva writes the Indian love poem, Gitagovinda. Around this date: Middle English replaces Old English; the Hohokam people of Arizona, North America, are building platform mounds; the first statues are erected on Easter Island; the beginnings of organized societies in the Hawaiian Islands; the earliest settlements by Polynesians in Pitcairn Island; the rise of the Incas in Peru; the Ghana empire in West Africa declines; Katanga in Zaire, Central Africa, is founded; the height of the Chimu civilization at Chan Chan, on the north-west coast of Peru; the Anasazi people in North America build cliff dwellings at Mesa Verde, Chaco Canyon and the Canyon de Chelly; the game of checkers is invented.

1101

1101

罗伯特·库尔特霍斯放弃了对盎格鲁-诺曼王位的继承权，亨利一世由此成为英格兰国王。第二波十字军抵达了新建立的耶路撒冷王国。

Robert Curthose gives up his claim to the Anglo-Norman throne, thus establishing Henry I as king of England. A second wave of Crusaders arrives in the newly established kingdom of Jerusalem.

1102

1102

图卢兹的雷蒙四世围攻的黎波里，但被安条克公国的摄政王坦克雷德囚禁。

Raymond IV of Toulouse besieges Tripoli but is imprisoned by Tancred, regent of the principality of Antioch.

1104

1104

威尼斯军械库建立。阿拉贡国王阿方索一世成为阿拉贡和纳瓦拉国王。耶路撒冷伯爵鲍德温一世攻占阿克。埃德萨伯爵鲍德温二世在哈兰战役中被塞尔柱突厥人俘虏；坦克雷德成为摄政王。冰岛赫克拉火山爆发，摧毁了多个定居点。

The Venetian Arsenal is founded. Alfonso I of Aragon becomes king of Aragon and Navarre. Baldwin I of Jerusalem captures Acre. Baldwin II, Count of Edessa, is taken prisoner by the Seljuk Turks at the Battle of Harran; Tancred becomes regent. The volcano Hekla erupts in Iceland, destroying settlements.

1105

1105

神圣罗马帝国皇帝亨利四世被其子亨利五世废黜。

Henry IV, the Holy Roman Emperor, is deposed by his son, Henry V.

1106

1106

英格兰国王亨利一世在坦什布雷战役中击败了他的哥哥，诺曼底公爵罗伯特·库尔特霍斯。1106年的大彗星在威尔士、日本、韩国、中国和欧洲均有观测到。

Henry I of England defeats his older brother Robert Curthose, Duke of Normandy, at the Battle of Tinchebrai. The Great Comet of 1106 is seen in Wales, Japan, Korea, China and Europe.

1107

1107

中国货币采用三种颜色印刷，以防止伪造。

Chinese money is printed in three colours to prevent counterfeiting.

1108

1108

圣马格努斯成为第一位奥克尼伯爵。

St Magnus becomes the first Earl of Orkney.

1109

1109

十字军攻占了的黎波里。

The Crusaders capture Tripoli.

1110

1110

亨利五世入侵意大利。十字军攻占西顿和贝鲁特。

Henry V invades Italy. The Crusaders conquer Sidon and Beirut.

1112

1112

德国巴登邦成立。阿方索一世成为葡萄牙伯爵。

The German state of Baden is founded. Alfonso I becomes Count of Portugal.

1113

1113

柬埔寨苏利耶跋摩二世统治时期开始；他开始建造吴哥窟寺庙群。

The start of the reign of Suryavarman II of Cambodia; he begins construction of the temple complex of Angkor Wat.

1114

1114

巴塞罗那的拉蒙·贝伦格尔三世征服了伊维萨岛和马略卡岛。

Ramon Berenguer III of Barcelona conquers Ibiza and Mallorca.

1115

1115

女真人建立了中国的金朝。巴黎成为宗教学习中心。克莱尔沃的伯纳德开始了他的事业，他所建立的修道院后来成为欧洲最重要的修道院。皮埃尔·阿伯拉尔成为巴黎圣母院的教士。

The Jurchen establish the Jin Dynasty of China. Paris becomes a centre of religious learning. The beginning of the career of Bernard of Clairvaux, whose abbey becomes the most important monastery in Europe. Pierre Abélard becomes canon of Notre Dame de Paris.

1116

1116

耶路撒冷国王鲍德温一世入侵埃及。现代书籍装帧形式（即用独立页面装订在一起）在中国发明。

Baldwin I of Jerusalem invades Egypt. The modern book format of separate pages stitched together is invented in China.

1117

1117

有记载的最早使用指南针进行导航的案例。

The earliest recorded use of a compass for navigational purposes.

1118

1118

诺曼底爆发了反对英格兰国王亨利一世的叛乱。拉蒙·贝伦格尔三世从摩尔人手中夺取了塔拉戈纳。阿方索一世将摩尔人逐出萨拉戈萨。圣殿骑士团成立，旨在保护通往耶路撒冷的道路。

A rebellion against Henry I of England breaks out in Normandy. Ramon Berenguer III captures Tarragona from the Moors. Alfonso the Battler expels the Moors from Zaragoza. The Knights Templar are founded, to protect the road to Jerusalem.

1119

1119

博洛尼亚大学成立于意大利。

Bologna University is founded in Italy.

1120

1120

马尔文的韦尔彻创建了一套地球测量系统，使用经纬度的度、分、秒。中国人玩彩绘扑克牌。

Welcher of Malvern creates a system of measurement for the Earth using the degrees, minutes and seconds of latitude and longitude. The Chinese play with painted playing cards.

1121

1121

《沃尔姆斯协约》谴责皮埃尔·阿伯拉尔关于圣三位一体的著作；同年晚些时候，与阿伯拉尔有染的埃洛伊丝的叔叔沙特尔的富尔伯特下令阉割了阿伯拉尔。格鲁吉亚国王率领55000人的军队在格鲁吉亚东部的迪戈里击败了20万穆斯林联军。

The Concordat of Worms condemns Pierre Abélard’s writings on the Holy Trinity; later in the year, Fulbert of Chartres, uncle of Heloïse, with whom Abélard has had an affair, has Abélard castrated. The king of Georgia with an army of 55,000 defeats the 200,000-strong Muslim coalition troops at Didgori, Eastern Georgia.

1123

1123

圣巴塞洛缪医院在伦敦成立。威尼斯共和国和耶路撒冷王国签署了《世界和平条约》。

St Bartholomew’s Hospital is founded in London. The Republic of Venice and the Kingdom of Jerusalem sign the Pactum Warmundi treaty.

1124

1124

大卫一世杀死亚历山大一世，成为苏格兰国王。泰尔城陷落于十字军之手。

David I kills Alexander I and becomes king of Scotland. Tyre falls to the Crusaders.

1125

1125

萨克森的洛泰尔在亨利五世去世后成为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。游吟诗人和游吟音乐在法国流行起来。

Lothair of Saxony becomes Holy Roman Emperor on the death of Henry V. Troubadour and trouvère music becomes popular in France.

1126

1126

阿方索七世加冕为西班牙卡斯蒂利亚-莱昂国王。宋朝在黄河流域战役中战败，晋朝在中国北方建立。

Alfonso VII is crowned king of Castile and León in Spain. The Jin Dynasty is established in the north of China with the Sung Dynasty’s loss in battle at the Huang He river valley.

1127

1127

拜占庭帝国的首都君士坦丁堡成为当时世界上最大的城市。女真军队攻陷了宋朝都城开封，中国南北长达一个多世纪的政治分裂就此开始。

Constantinople, capital of the Byzantine Empire, becomes the largest city in the world. Jurchen forces sack the Song Chinese capital, Kaifeng, and more than a century of political division begins between north and south in China.

1128

1128

苏格兰国王大卫一世在爱丁堡创建了荷里路德修道院。葡萄牙王子阿方索在战场上击败了他的母亲莱昂的特蕾莎，并控制了国家。

Holyrood Abbey is founded in Edinburgh by David I, King of Scotland. Prince Alfonso of Portugal defeats his mother, Teresa of León, in battle and gains control of the country.

1130

1130

盲人马格努斯和哈拉尔·吉尔共同成为挪威国王，挪威的内战时期开始了。

Magnus the Blind and Harald Gille become joint kings of Norway and the country’s civil war era begins.

1131

1131

安茹的富尔克和梅利桑德成为耶路撒冷的国王和王后。

Fulk of Anjou and Melisende become king and queen of Jerusalem.

1132

1132

圣丹尼斯修道院是世界上第一座哥特式教堂，由苏格修道院长在巴黎建造。

St Denis Abbey, the first Gothic church, is built by Abbot Suger in Paris.

1133

1133

达勒姆大教堂已竣工。

Durham Cathedral is completed.

1134

1134

纳博讷被图卢兹的阿方斯一世攻占。泽兰群岛由北海的一场巨大风暴形成。挪威国王马格努斯四世在法尔勒夫战役中击败了挪威国王哈拉尔四世。

Narbonne is seized by Alphonse I of Toulouse. The Zeeland archipelago is created by a massive storm in the North Sea. Magnus IV of Norway defeats Harald IV of Norway at the battle at Färlev.

1135

1135

塞尔柱突厥人对巴格达的统治结束了。

The domination of Baghdad by the Seljuk Turks ends.

1136

1136

威尔士的欧文·格温内德在克鲁格·莫尔击败了诺曼人。皮埃尔·阿伯拉尔撰写了《灾难史》，详细记述了他与埃洛伊丝的关系。

Owain Gwynedd of Wales defeats the Normans at Crug Mawr. Pierre Abélard writes the Historia Calamitatum, detailing his relationship with Héloïse.

1138

1138

英格兰人在旗帜之战中击败了苏格兰国王大卫一世。叙利亚阿勒颇发生致命地震，造成约23万人死亡。

The English defeat David I of Scotland in the Battle of the Standard. A deadly earthquake in Aleppo, Syria kills around 230,000 people.

1139

1139

奥里克战役之后，阿尔方索王子成为独立葡萄牙的国王阿尔方索一世。

Following the Battle of Ourique, Prince Alfnso becomes King Alfonso I of an independent Portugal.

1141

1141

金朝与南宋签订《绍兴条约》，两国享有20年的和平。意大利葡萄酒酿造公司里卡索利成立。

The Jin dynasty and the Southern Song dynasty sign the Treaty of Shaoxing and enjoy peace for the next 20 years. The Italian winemaking company Ricasoli is founded.

1143

1143

凯顿的罗伯特完成了欧洲第一部《古兰经》拉丁文译本。

Robert of Ketton makes the first European translation of the Qur’an, into Latin.

1144

1144

诺曼底在安茹的杰弗里统治下落入安茹王朝之手。乔尔达诺·皮耶尔莱奥尼创立了革命性的罗马公社。

Normandy comes under Angevin control under Geoffrey of Anjou. Giordano Pierleoni founds the revolutionary Commune of Rome.

1145

1145

教皇尤金三世颁布《量子先驱》（Quantum Praedecessores），号召发动第二次十字军东征。塞尔柱帝国的梅尔夫成为当时世界上最大的城市。

Pope Eugene III issues Quantum Praedecessores, calling for the Second Crusade. Merv in the Seljuk Empire becomes the largest city in the world.

1146

1146

圣伯纳德·克莱尔沃在勃艮第宣讲第二次十字军东征。

St Bernard of Clairvaux preaches the Second Crusade in Burgundy.

1147

1147

葡萄牙国王阿方索一世和十字军从摩尔人手中夺取了里斯本。与阿尔摩拉维王朝敌对的柏柏尔穆斯林阿尔摩哈德王朝攻占了马拉喀什，并继续征服了阿尔摩拉维王朝统治下的西班牙、阿尔及利亚和的黎波里。

King Alfonso I of Portugal and the Crusaders capture Lisbon from the Moors. The Almohads, Berber Muslims opposed to the Almoravids, seize Marrakech and go on to conquer Almoravid Spain, Algeria and Tripoli.

1148

1148

葡萄牙国王阿方索一世从摩尔人手中夺取了阿布兰特斯。

King Alfonso I of Portugal takes Abrantes from the Moors.

1149

1149

努尔丁在伊纳布战役中击败了安条克公国。第二次十字军东征的基督教军队在小亚细亚败给了土耳其人；他们放弃了对大马士革的围攻。

Nur ad-Din defeats the principality of Antioch at the Battle of Inab. The Christian armies of the Second Crusade lose to the Turks in Asia Minor; they abandon the siege of Damascus.

1150

1150

默西河上的渡轮开始在利物浦和伯肯黑德之间运营。巴黎大学（现称索邦大学）成立。扎格维王朝统治埃塞俄比亚高原。大约在同一时期：北美霍普韦尔文化终结；秘鲁沿海的奇穆文明蓬勃发展；毛利人开始在新西兰南岛北部的河口地区定居。

The ferry across the Mersey begins running between Liverpool and Birkenhead. The University of Paris, now known as the Sorbonne, is founded. The Zagwe dynasty rules in the Ethiopian highlands. Around this time: The end of Hopewell culture in North America; the Chimu civilization flourishes on the coast of Peru; Maoris begin to settle in the river mouth areas in the north of the South Island in New Zealand.

1151

1151

阿富汗的加兹尼被古尔王朝的王子们焚毁。墨西哥的托尔特克帝国灭亡。中国人首次在战争中使用炸药。

Ghazni in Afghanistan is burned by the princes of Ghur. The Toltec Empire in Mexico comes to an end. Explosives are used in battle for the first time, by the Chinese.

1152

1152

爱尔兰教会承认教皇的权威。腓特烈一世·巴巴罗萨当选为德意志国王。阿尔摩哈德王朝征服阿尔及利亚。

The Church of Ireland acknowledges the pope’s authority. Frederick I Barbarossa is elected king of the Germans. The Almohad dynasty conquers Algeria.

1153

1153

马尔科姆四世成为苏格兰国王。《温彻斯特条约》使玛蒂尔达皇后的儿子安茹的亨利成为英格兰国王。安茹王朝控制了加斯科涅和吉耶讷。拜占庭帝国的首都君士坦丁堡再次成为世界上最大的城市。耶路撒冷的鲍德温三世从其母梅利桑德手中夺取了耶路撒冷王国的统治权，并攻占了阿什凯隆。伊斯兰教传入马尔代夫。

Malcolm IV becomes king of Scotland. The Treaty of Winchester allows Empress Matilda’s son, Henry of Anjou, to become king of England. The Angevin dynasty takes control of Gascony and Guyenne. Constantinople, capital of the Byzantine Empire, again becomes the largest city in the world. Baldwin III of Jerusalem takes control of the Kingdom of Jerusalem from his mother Melisende, and also captures Ascalon. Islam is introduced to the Maldives.

1154

1154

亨利·金雀花成为英格兰国王亨利二世。瑞典国王埃里克将基督教传入芬兰。努尔丁控制了大马士革，统一了叙利亚。穆罕默德·伊德里西完成了他的世界地图集，这幅地图集直到15世纪仍是最精确的地图之一。英格兰的伯明翰和伯明翰斗牛场建成。

Henry Plantagenet becomes King Henry II of England. Sweden’s King Eric introduces Christianity to Finland. Nur ad-Din gains control of Damascus, uniting Syria under one ruler. Muhammad al-Idrisi completes his atlas of the world, which will remain one of the most accurate maps until the 15th century. Birmingham in England and the Birmingham Bull Ring are founded.

1155

1155

腓特烈一世·巴巴罗萨成为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。

Frederick I Barbarossa becomes Holy Roman Emperor.

1156

1156

尤里·多尔戈鲁基王子加固莫斯科城，这被认为是莫斯科建城之日。加尔默罗会成立。默兹河谷的艺术家创作了斯塔沃洛特三联画，这是一个用来存放据称是真十字架碎片的圣物匣。日本爆发了保元动乱，一场关于继承权的内战。

Prince Yuriy Dolgorukiy fortifies Moscow, regarded as the date of the founding of the city. The Carmelite Order is established. Mosan artists create the Stavelot Triptych, a reliquary to house what were purported to be pieces of the True Cross. The Hogen disturbance, a civil war about succession, takes place in Japan.

1158

1158

英镑正式推出。

The British Pound Sterling is introduced.

1159

1159

罗马天主教枢机主教被赋予选举教皇的权力。突尼斯被阿尔摩哈德王朝征服。平治之乱在日本爆发。

Roman Catholic cardinals are given the right to elect the Pope. Tunis is conquered by the Almohad caliphs. The Heiji Rebellion occurs in Japan.

1160

1160

耶输跋摩二世继承其叔父达拉宁陀罗跋摩成为高棉帝国的统治者。

Yasovarman II succeeds his uncle Dharanindravarman as ruler of the Khmer Empire.

1162

1162

托马斯·贝克特被祝圣为坎特伯雷大主教。

Thomas Becket is consecrated as Archbishop of Canterbury.

1163

1163

欧文·格温内斯被公认为威尔士统治者。图尔会议谴责阿尔比派。教皇亚历山大三世为巴黎圣母院奠基。蒙古帝国缔造者成吉思汗诞辰。

Owain Gwynedd is recognized as ruler of Wales. The Council of Tours names and condemns the Albigensians. The first stone of Paris’s Notre Dame Cathedral is laid by Pope Alexander III. The birth of Genghis Khan, creator of the Mongol Empire.

1164

1164

托马斯·贝克特与亨利二世发生争执，离开英国去寻求教皇和法国国王的支持。

Thomas Becket argues with Henry II and leaves England to solicit support from the pope and the king of France.

1165

1165

穆斯林从十字军手中夺取了凯撒利亚腓立比。

The Muslims take Caesarea Philippi from the Crusaders.

1167

1167

威廉·马歇尔，据说是史上最伟大的骑士，被册封为骑士。葡萄牙国王阿方索一世被莱昂王国击败。伦巴第联盟在莱尼亚诺战役中击败腓特烈一世。平清盛成为首位被任命为日本政府大臣（大上大人）的武士。

William Marshal, said to be the greatest knight that ever lived, is knighted. Alfonso I of Portugal is defeated by the kingdom of Léon. The Lombard League defeats Frederick I in the Battle of Legnano. Taira no Kiyomori becomes the first samurai to be appointed Daijo Daijin, chief minister of the government of Japan.

1168

1168

英格兰王子理查德成为阿基坦公爵，后来成为英格兰国王理查一世。为了防止老开罗被十字军攻占，哈里发下令焚毁这座城市；大火燃烧了54天。

Prince Richard of England becomes Duke of Aquitaine and later becomes King Richard I of England. To prevent Old Cairo being captured by the Crusaders, its caliph orders the city to be set on fire; it burns for 54 days.

1169

1169

征服爱尔兰的开端。理查德·菲茨·吉尔伯特·德·克莱尔（绰号“强弓”）与流亡的爱尔兰酋长德莫特·麦克默罗结盟，帮助他收复伦斯特王国。阿基坦的埃莉诺离开英格兰，在普瓦捷建立起她的大宫廷。努尔丁入侵埃及，他的侄子萨拉丁成为被征服地区的苏丹。

The start of the conquest of Ireland. Richard Fitz Gilbert de Clare (‘Strongbow’) makes an alliance with the exiled Irish chief, Dermot MacMurrough, to help him recover the kingdom of Leinster. Eleanor of Aquitaine leaves England to establish her great court in Poitiers. Nur ad-Din invades Egypt, and his nephew Saladin becomes sultan of the conquered territory.

1170

1170

坎特伯雷大主教托马斯·贝克特在坎特伯雷大教堂遇刺身亡。英格兰国王亨利二世支持诺曼人入侵爱尔兰，由此引发了爱尔兰与英格兰之间长达八个世纪的冲突和战争；都柏林被诺曼人攻占。阿尔摩哈德王朝统治下的非斯成为当时世界上最大的城市。

Thomas Beckett, Archbishop of Canterbury, is assassinated in Canterbury cathedral. Henry II of England sponsors the Norman invasion of Ireland, sparking eight centuries of conflict and war between Ireland and England; Dublin is captured by the Normans. Fes in the Almohad Empire becomes the largest city in the world.

1171

1171

威尔士的里斯·阿普·格鲁菲德同意与英格兰的亨利二世进行谈判。穆斯林战士、埃及军队指挥官萨拉丁推翻了法蒂玛王朝，恢复了逊尼派的统治。

Rhys ap Gruffydd of Wales agrees to negotiate with Henry II of England. Saladin, Muslim warrior and commander in the Egyptian army, overthrows the Fatimid dynasty, restoring Sunni rule.

1172

1172

亨利二世征服爱尔兰。阿夫朗什宗教会议赦免了亨利二世刺杀托马斯·贝克特的罪行。卡舍尔宗教会议终结了凯尔特基督教体系，并将其置于罗马的统治之下。

Henry II conquers Ireland. The Council of Avranches absolves Henry of the assassination of Thomas Becket. The Synod of Cashel ends the Celtic Christian system and brings it under the authority of Rome.

1173

1173

比萨斜塔开始建造。阿基坦的埃莉诺和她的儿子们在1173-1174年的起义中反抗她的丈夫英格兰国王亨利二世，但最终失败。萨拉丁宣布自己为埃及苏丹。代数国际象棋记谱法首次被记录使用。

Construction starts on the Tower of Pisa. Eleanor of Aquitaine and her sons rebel unsuccessfully against her husband Henry II of England in the revolt of 1173–4. Saladin declares himself sultan of Egypt. The first recorded use of algebraic chess notation.

1174

1174

苏格兰国王威廉一世被英格兰国王亨利二世俘虏；亨利二世占领苏格兰。萨拉丁攻占大马士革。中国正式将越南命名为安南。后古典时代已知的第一个赛马场在英格兰纽马克特开业。意大利帕多瓦城大部分被大火烧毁。

William I of Scotland is captured by Henry II of England; Henry occupies Scotland. Saladin captures Damascus. Vietnam is given the official name of Annam by China. The first known racetrack of the post-classical era opens at Newmarket in England. Fire destroys most of Padua in Italy.

1175

1175

爱尔兰末代至高王鲁艾德里·乌阿·康乔拜尔（罗里·奥康纳）通过《温莎条约》向亨利二世臣服。

Ruaidri Ua Conchobair (Rory O’Conner), the last High King of Ireland, submits to Henry II with the Treaty of Windsor.

1176

1176

伦敦桥开始动工。有记载的第一次威尔士诗歌节（Eisteddfod）由里斯·阿普·格鲁菲德在卡迪根举办。森斯大教堂安装了第一台“钟表”。

Construction begins on the first London Bridge. The first recorded Welsh Eisteddfod is held by Rhys ap Gruffydd at Cardigan. The Cathedral of Sens installs the first ‘horologe’.

1177

1177

耶路撒冷的鲍德温四世和沙蒂永的雷纳德在蒙吉萨尔战役中击败了萨拉丁。一场大火摧毁了京都。占婆人洗劫了高棉首都吴哥窟。

Baldwin IV of Jerusalem and Raynald of Chatillon defeat Saladin at the Battle of Montgisard. A fire devastates Kyoto. The Cham sack the Khmer capital of Angkor Wat.

1178

1178

比萨斜塔在第三层完工后开始倾斜。

The Leaning Tower of Pisa begins to lean as the third level is completed.

1179

1179

挪威卡尔夫斯金内特战役扭转了内战的局势。第三次拉特兰公会议谴责瓦勒度派和卡特里派为异端，并设立了第一批犹太人隔离区。威斯敏斯特学校由威斯敏斯特教堂的僧侣创办。噶举派佛教的直贡噶举派创立。

The Norwegian Battle of Kalvskinnet changes the tide of the civil wars. The Third Council of the Lateran condemns Waldensians and Cathars as heretics, and creates the first ghettos for Jews. Westminster School is founded by the monks of Westminster Abbey. The Drigung Kagyu school of Kagyu Buddhism is founded.

1180

1180

腓力二世·奥古斯都成为法国统治者，征服了西部的安茹王国领土。葡萄牙国王阿方索一世被莱昂的费尔南多二世俘虏。印度南部的朱罗王国走向衰落。美国亚利桑那州的日落火山口发生了最后一次大规模火山喷发。在日本，持仁亲王挑起了平氏和源氏之间的源平合战。中国南宋的都城杭州成为当时世界上最大的城市。

Philip II Augustus becomes ruler of France, conquering Angevin lands in the west. Alfonso I of Portugal is taken prisoner by Ferdinand II of Léon. The Chola kingdom in southern India goes into decline. The last major volcanic eruption of Sunset Crater, in Arizona. In Japan, Prince Mochihito instigates the Genpei War between the Taira and Minamoto clans. Hangzhou, capital of Southern Song China, becomes the largest city in the world.

1181

1181

中国和日本的天文学家观测到一颗超新星，这是有记录以来观测到的八颗超新星之一。阇耶跋摩七世击败占婆，统治高棉王国。

Chinese and Japanese astronomers observe a supernova, one of only eight observed in recorded history. Jayavarman VII defeats the Cham and assumes control of the Khmer kingdom.

1182

1182

法国国王腓力二世将犹太人驱逐出巴黎。

The Jews are expelled from Paris by Philip II of France.

1183

1183

克拉克之围是阿尤布王朝与十字军之间的一场战役。平宗盛和平氏家族带着年仅三岁的安德天皇和三件神器逃往日本西部，以躲避源氏的追击。

The Siege of Kerak is waged between the Ayyubids and the Crusaders. Taira no Munemori and the Taira clan flee with the three-year-old Emperor Antoku and the three sacred treasures to western Japan to escape pursuit by the Minamoto clan.

1184

1184

巴黎的街道是根据腓力·奥古斯都的命令铺设的。教皇诏书《废除法令》（Ad Aboldendam）颁布，旨在反对几个欧洲异端团体：卡特里派、瓦勒度派、帕塔林派和谦卑派。

The streets of Paris are paved by order of Philip Augustus. The papal bull, Ad Aboldendam, is issued against several European heretical groups: the Cathars, the Waldensians, the Patarines and the Humiliati.

1185

1185

圣殿骑士团在伦敦定居，并开始建造新圣殿教堂。彼得和阿森建立了第二保加利亚王国。在拜占庭帝国，伊萨克二世·安杰卢斯废黜了安德罗尼库斯一世·科穆宁，登上了拜占庭帝国的皇位。在日本源平合战中，坛之浦海战以源氏的胜利告终。

Knights Templar settle in London and begin the building of New Temple Church. Peter and Asen establish the Second Bulgarian Kingdom. In the Byzantine Empire, Isaac II Angelus deposes Andronicus I Comnenus and takes the throne of the Byzantine Empire. In the Genpei War in Japan, the naval battle of Dan-no-ura leads to a Minamoto victory.

1186

1186

居伊·德·卢西尼昂成为耶路撒冷国王。加兹尼王朝的末代统治者被北印度穆斯林帝国的建立者古尔的穆罕默德废黜。

Guy of Lusignan becomes king of Jerusalem. The last Ghaznavid ruler is deposed by Mohammed of Ghur, the Muslim founder of an empire in North India.

1187

1187

教皇格里高利八世提议发动第三次十字军东征。萨拉丁击败十字军并攻占耶路撒冷。古林·穆罕默德征服旁遮普。托尔特克人在奇琴伊察被废黜。禅宗传入日本。吴哥窟国王阇耶跋摩七世击败占婆征服者。

Pope Gregory VIII proposes the Third Crusade. Saladin defeats the Crusaders and takes Jerusalem. Ghorin Muhammed conquers the Punjab. The Toltecs are deposed at Chichen Itza. Zen Buddhism arrives in Japan. King of Angkor Wat, Jayavarman VII, defeats the Cham conquerors.

1188

1188

伦敦建成纽盖特监狱。狮心王理查与法国国王腓力二世结盟，对抗其父英格兰国王亨利二世。威尔士开始招募人员参加第三次十字军东征，英格兰和法国开始征收“萨拉丁什一税”。

Newgate Prison is built in London. Richard the Lionheart allies with Philip II of France against his father, Henry II of England. Recruitment is undertaken in Wales for the Third Crusade and the ‘Saladin Tithe’, a tax, is levied in England and France.

1189

1189

军队集结，准备参加第三次十字军东征。狮心王理查加冕为英格兰国王。阿克城围城战开始。萨拉丁攻占了十字军的蒙特利尔城堡和克拉克城堡。1276年，英国法律将1189年定为“远古时期”的终结。

Troops assemble for the Third Crusade. Richard the Lionheart is crowned as king of England. The Siege of Acre begins. The Crusader castles of Montreal and Kerak are captured by Saladin. The year 1189 is fixed in 1276 as the end of ‘time immemorial’ in English law.

1190

1190

第三次十字军东征开始。约克郡发生犹太人大屠杀和集体自杀事件。条顿骑士团，一个军事组织，在德国成立，旨在保卫巴勒斯坦和叙利亚的基督教领土。英格兰国王理查一世威胁要向西西里国王坦克雷德开战，并攻占了墨西拿。腓特烈一世·巴巴罗萨在率军进军耶路撒冷途中溺亡于萨莱夫河。日本封建时代开始。

The Third Crusade begins. There is a massacre and mass-suicide of the Jews of York. The Teutonic Order of knights, a military society, is set up in Germany to defend Christian lands in Palestine and Syria. Richard I of England threatens war against Tancred of Sicily, and captures Messina. Frederick I Barbarossa drowns in the Saleph River while leading an army to Jerusalem. The Japanese Feudal Era begins.

1191

1191

萨拉丁的守军投降，结束了对阿克长达两年的围攻；英格兰国王理查一世在阿尔苏夫击败萨拉丁。茶叶从中国传入日本。

Saladin’s garrison surrenders, ending the two-year siege of Acre; Richard I of England defeats Saladin at Arsuf. Tea comes to Japan from China.

1192

1192

英格兰国王理查一世与萨拉丁达成停战协议，结束了第三次十字军东征。理查一世被奥地利国王利奥波德五世俘虏。耶路撒冷国王康拉德一世遇刺身亡。在日本，源赖朝被授予幕府将军的称号，建立了日本历史上第一个幕府政权。

A truce between Richard I of England and Saladin ends the Third Crusade. Richard is taken hostage by Leopold V of Austria. Conrad I, king of Jerusalem, is assassinated. In Japan, Minamoto no Yoritomo is granted the title of shogun, establishing the first shogunate in Japan’s history.

1193

1193

萨拉丁去世后，埃及和叙利亚的库尔德阿尤布王朝的领土被他的后裔瓜分。古尔王朝的奴隶将领、奴隶王朝的创始人库特布丁攻占了德里。

Saladin dies, and the lands of the Kurdish Ayyubid dynasty of Egypt and Syria are split among his descendants. Qutb-ud-Din, a Ghurid slave commander and founder of the Slave dynasty, captures Delhi.

1194

1194

英格兰国王理查一世从神圣罗马帝国皇帝亨利六世手中被赎回。在中国，黄河改道，并在接下来的700年里取代淮河流域。北欧神话集《老埃达》成书。

Richard I of England is ransomed from Henry VI, Emperor of the Holy Roman Empire. In China, the Yellow River experiences a major change in course and takes over the Huai River drainage system for the next 700 years. The Elder Edda, a collection of Scandinavian mythology, is written.

1196

1196

在伦敦，穷人发动了反对富人的民众起义。在如今荷兰的地区，水务委员会成立，由此诞生了世界上现存最古老的民主政体之一。

In London, there is a popular uprising of the poor against the rich. Water boards are established in the region of present-day Netherlands, creating one of the oldest democratic entities still in existence in the world today.

1199

1199

英格兰国王理查一世在沙吕斯围城战中阵亡，无地王约翰继位成为英格兰国王。

King Richard I of England is killed at the siege of Châlus and John ‘Lackland’ becomes king of England.

1200

1200

蒙古人征服了中国北方。大约在同一时期：英国早期哥特时期开始；埃塞俄比亚国王拉利贝拉建造了岩石教堂；卡内姆-博尔努帝国在北非建立；在北美，拥有众多神庙土墩的城市卡霍基亚达到鼎盛时期；科罗拉多州的克利夫峡谷和菲尤克斯峡谷建造了公寓楼群和圆形基瓦；秘鲁的印加人向日益壮大的库斯科定居点迁移；南太平洋汤加岛上的图伊汤加王国建造了一个珊瑚平台用于举行祭祀仪式。

The Mongols defeat Northern China. Around this date: The Early Gothic period begins in England; King Lalibela of Ethiopia builds churches cut from rock; the Kanem-Bornu Empire is established in northern Africa; in North America, Cahokia, a city of temple mounds, is at its height; complexes of apartment blocks and circular kivas are built at Cliff Canyon and Fewkes Canyon, Colorado; the Incas in Peru gravitate to the growing settlement of Cuzco; the Tui Tonga monarchy builds a coral platform for ceremonial worship on the island of Tonga in the South Pacific.

1201

1201

第四次十字军东征开始了。

The Fourth Crusade is launched.

1202

1202

利沃尼亚剑士兄弟会成立。莱昂纳多·斐波那契出版《计算之书》，将阿拉伯零引入欧洲。第一批弄臣出现在欧洲宫廷。

The military order, the Livonian Brothers of the Sword, is founded. Leonardo Fibonacci publishes Liber Abaci, introducing the Arabian zero to Europe. The first jesters appear in European courts.

1203

1203

法国国王腓力二世进入鲁昂，最终促成了诺曼底与法国的统一。第四次十字军东征舰队进入博斯普鲁斯海峡，攻占君士坦丁堡；阿莱克修斯四世被拥立为拜占庭皇帝。第四次十字军东征的领袖之一，蒙费拉特的博尼法斯建立了塞萨洛尼卡王国。

Philip II of France enters Rouen, leading to the eventual unification of Normandy and France. The Fleet of the Fourth Crusade enters the Bosphorus and Constantinople is captured; Alexius IV is named Byzantine Emperor. Boniface of Montferrat, a leader of the Fourth Crusade, founds the kingdom of Thessalonica.

1204

1204

由于诺曼底公国的分裂，泽西岛享有自治权。佛兰德斯伯爵鲍德温加冕为拉丁帝国皇帝。丹麦国王瓦尔德马二世被挪威承认为国王。拜占庭皇帝阿莱克修斯四世在革命中被推翻；阿莱克修斯五世被拥立为皇帝。

Jersey enjoys self-government thanks to the division of the Duchy of Normandy. Baldwin, Count of Flanders is crowned Emperor of the Latin Empire. Valdemar II, king of Denmark, is recognized as king in Norway. Byzantine Emperor Alexius IV is overthrown in a revolution; Alexius V is proclaimed Emperor.

1205

1205

弗兰德斯的亨利加冕为拉丁帝国皇帝。

Henry of Flanders is crowned Emperor of the Latin Empire.

1206

1206

曾是突厥斯坦奴隶的艾巴克在印度北部建立了新的德里苏丹国。库特布丁在印度建立了马穆鲁克王朝，这是德里苏丹国的第一个王朝。成吉思汗建立了蒙古帝国。

The former Turkestan slave Aibak founds the new sultanate of Delhi in north India. Qutb ud-Din proclaims the Mameluk dynasty in India, the first dynasty of the Delhi Sultanate. The Mongol Empire is founded by Genghis Khan.

1207

1207

约翰国王颁布特许状，创建了利物浦自治市镇。

King John issues letters patent, creating the new Borough of Liverpool.

1208

1208

兵力较弱的瑞典军队在勒拿河战役中击败了入侵的丹麦军队。

An inferior Swedish force defeats the invading Danes in the Battle of Lena.

1209

1209

伦敦桥竣工。剑桥大学成立。阿尔比十字军东征对抗卡特里派，阿尔比十字军领袖西蒙·德·蒙福尔攻占卡尔卡松。圣方济各创立方济各会。成吉思汗征服突厥斯坦。

London Bridge is completed. Cambridge University is founded. The Albigensian Crusade against the Cathars begins; Simon de Montfort, leader of the Albigensian Crusade, takes Carcassonne. St Francis of Assisi founds the Franciscan religious order. Genghis Khan conquers Turkestan.

1211

1211

成吉思汗入侵金朝。兰斯圣母院开始建造。有记载的最早的复式记账法也出现于此时。

Genghis Khan invades Jin China. Construction begins on Notre Dame de Reims. The oldest recorded example of double-entry bookkeeping dates from this time.

1212

1212

伦敦大部分地区被夷为平地。十字军将穆斯林逐出西班牙北部。鸭长明创作了《方丈记》，这是日本古典散文的伟大作品之一。

Most of London is burned to the ground. Crusaders push the Muslims out of northern Spain. Kamo no Chomei writes the Hojoki, one of the great works of classical Japanese prose.

1213

1213

在达姆海战中，英国舰队摧毁了法国舰队，这是新成立的英国皇家海军取得的首场重大胜利。教皇英诺森三世号召发起第五次十字军东征，以夺回耶路撒冷。

In the Battle of Damme, the English fleet destroys a French fleet in the first major victory for the fledgling Royal Navy. Pope Innocent III calls for the Fifth Crusade to recapture Jerusalem.

1214

1214

在法国，腓力二世击败了英格兰的约翰。

In France, Philip II defeats John of England.

1215

1215

英国国王约翰签署《大宪章》，赋予贵族更多权力。第四次拉特兰公会议召开，通过了圣餐变体论。多明我会成立。

English King John seals the Magna Carta, giving more power to the barons. The Fourth Lateran Council meets, adopting the doctrine of transubstantiation. The Dominican Order is founded.

1216

1216

亨利三世成为英格兰国王。法国王子路易在第一次男爵战争中入侵英格兰。

Henry III becomes king of England. Prince Louis of France invades England in the First Barons’ War.

1217

1217

《兰贝斯条约》结束了第一次男爵战争。塞尔维亚王国建立。第五次十字军东征以基督教军队对埃及的进攻失败而拉开序幕。

The Treaty of Lambeth ends the First Barons’ War. The kingdom of Serbia is founded. The Fifth Crusade begins with a failed Christian attack on Egypt.

1218

1218

利沃尼亚剑士兄弟开始征服爱沙尼亚。成吉思汗摧毁了西辽帝国。阿尤布王朝瓦解，但阿尤布王朝统治埃及直至1250年。

The Livonian Brothers of the Sword begin the conquest of Estonia. Genghis Khan destroys the Kara-Khitai Empire. The Ayyubid Empire breaks up but Ayyubids rule Egypt until 1250.

1220

1220

英国废除了神判。索尔兹伯里大教堂开始动工。成吉思汗攻占布哈拉和撒马尔罕。

Trial by ordeal is abolished in England. Building work begins on Salisbury Cathedral. Genghis Khan takes Bukhara and Samarkand.

1221

1221

梅尔夫城被成吉思汗的军队洗劫一空，城内居民惨遭屠杀。尤卡坦半岛的玛雅人起义反抗奇琴伊察的统治者。

Merv is sacked and its people massacred by Genghis Khan’s forces. The Maya of the Yucatán revolt against the rulers of Chichen Itza.

1222

1222

帕多瓦大学成立。《曼登宪章》在马里颁布，确立人权并废除奴隶制。

The University of Padua is founded. The Manden Charter establishing human rights and abolishing slavery is proclaimed in Mali.

1224

1224

那不勒斯大学成立。

The University of Naples is founded.

1227

1227

爱沙尼亚人的独立战争结束了；此后七个世纪，该国一直处于外国统治之下。僧侣道元将禅宗佛教从中国带到了日本。

The Estonians’ fight for independence ends; there is foreign rule in the country for the next seven centuries. The monk, Dogen, brings Zen Buddhism to Japan from China.

1228

1228

第六次十字军东征爆发。德国国王康拉德四世成为耶路撒冷名义上的国王，腓特烈二世担任摄政。阿霍姆王朝首位国王苏卡法在阿萨姆建立统治；阿霍姆王朝统治长达600年。

The Sixth Crusade is launched. Conrad IV of Germany becomes titular king of Jerusalem, with Frederick II as regent. Sukaphaa, the first Ahom king, establishes his rule in Assam; Ahom kings reign for 600 years.

1229

1229

基督徒收复耶路撒冷。加泰罗尼亚人从穆斯林手中夺取了马略卡岛。巴黎大学爆发学生骚乱和长达两年的罢课。

The Christians regain Jerusalem. The island of Majorca is captured by the Catalans from the Muslims. There are student riots and a two-year strike at the University of Paris.

1230

1230

莱昂王国与卡斯蒂利亚王国合并。归来的十字军将麻风病带入欧洲。《布兰诗歌》编纂完成。大约在同一时期，哈夫斯王朝取代阿尔摩哈德王朝统治突尼斯。

The kingdom of Léon unites with the kingdom of Castile. The returning Crusaders introduce leprosy to Europe. The Carmina Burana poetry and song collection is compiled. Around this time, the Hafsid monarchy takes over from the Almohads in Tunisia.

1232

1232

佛教经典《高丽大藏经》第一版被蒙古入侵者摧毁。

The first edition of Tripitaka Koreana, Buddhist scriptures, is destroyed by Mongol invaders.

1233

1233

宗教裁判所成立。穆斯坦西里亚大学在巴格达成立。

The Inquisition is established. Mustansiriya University is founded in Baghdad.

1234

1234

蒙古人终结了金朝。

The Mongols bring the Jin dynasty to an end.

1235

1235

阿卜杜勒·瓦迪德的柏柏尔王国在非洲马格里布地区建立。大约在同一时期，伟大的战士领袖孙迪亚塔在西非建立了马里帝国。

The Berber kingdom of Abd al-Wadids is founded in the Maghreb in Africa. Around this time, the great warrior leader Sun Diata, founds the Mali Empire in West Africa.

1236

1236

科尔多瓦被基督教军队重新夺回。立陶宛人和塞米加利亚人在绍列战役中击败了利沃尼亚的宝剑兄弟会。伏尔加保加利亚被蒙古汗王拔都征服。

Córdoba is retaken for Christianity. Lithuanians and Semigallians defeat the Livonian Brothers of the Sword in the Battle of Saule. Volga Bulgaria is conquered by the Mongol khan, Batu.

1237

1237

蒙古人入侵俄罗斯。

The Mongols invade Russia.

1238

1238

瓦伦西亚从摩尔人手中被夺取。高棉人被逐出老挝琅勃拉邦。素可泰王国在泰国建立。

Valencia is captured from the Moors. The Khmers are expelled from Luang Phrabang in Laos. The Sukhothai Kingdom is founded in Thailand.

1240

1240

俄国将领亚历山大·涅夫斯基在涅瓦河击败瑞典军队，阻止了瑞典军队从北方全面入侵。挪威内战时期结束。

The Russian Alexander Nevsky defeats the Swedes at the Neva River, preventing a full-scale invasion from the north. The civil war era in Norway comes to an end.

1241

1241

吕贝克和汉堡结成汉萨同盟（汉萨联盟），进行贸易和相互保护，标志着汉萨同盟的开始。

Lübeck and Hamburg form a Hansa (association) for trade and mutual protection, marking the beginning of the Hanseatic League.

1242

1242

蒙古人入侵塞尔柱苏丹国。阿拉伯医生伊本·纳菲斯提出心脏的左右心室是分开的，并描述了血液循环过程。

The Mongols invade the Seljuk sultanate. Arab physician Ibn Nafis suggests that the right and left ventricles of the heart are separate and describes the circulation of blood.

1244

1244

蒙塞居尔的卡特里派教徒在被围困九个月后投降；他们遭到屠杀。

The Cathars of Montségur surrender after a nine-month siege; they are massacred.

1245

1245

威斯敏斯特教堂的重建工程开始了。在葡萄牙，爆发了反对葡萄牙国王桑乔二世、拥立其弟阿方索的叛乱。教皇英诺森四世派遣使节前往蒙古宫廷，建议蒙古人皈依基督教。

The rebuilding of Westminster Abbey begins. In Portugal, there is a rebellion against King Sancho II of Portugal in favour of his brother Alphonso. Pope Innocent IV sends an envoy to the Mongol court, suggesting that the Mongols convert to Christianity.

1246

1246

贵由汗登基成为蒙古帝国第三位大汗。

Güyük Khan is enthroned as the 3rd Great Khan of the Mongol Empire.

1247

1247

图林根王位继承战争爆发。埃及从花剌子模人手中夺取耶路撒冷。秦秋绍发表了中国剩余定理的原始形式。

The Thuringian War of Succession begins. Egypt takes control of Jerusalem from the Kharezmians. Ch’in Chiu-Shao publishes the original form of the Chinese remainder theorem.

1248

1248

第七次十字军东征开始。塞维利亚从摩尔人手中夺回。摩尔人开始在格拉纳达建造阿尔罕布拉宫。法国巴黎的圣礼拜堂举行了祝圣仪式。科隆大教堂奠基。罗杰·培根发表了一部重要的科学著作，其中包括关于用凸透镜眼镜治疗远视的论述，以及西方世界首次发表的火药配方。

The Seventh Crusade begins. Seville is taken from the Moors. The Moors begin construction of the Alhambra palace in Granada. The Gothic chapel of Sainte-Chapelle is consecrated in Paris, France. The foundation stone of Cologne Cathedral is laid. Roger Bacon publishes a major scientific work, including writings about convex lens spectacles for treating long-sightedness and the first publication in the Western world of the formula for gunpowder.

1249

1249

英国牛津大学第一所学院——大学学院成立。葡萄牙从摩尔人手中夺回了阿尔加维的法鲁，标志着葡萄牙收复失地运动的结束。

University College, the first college of Oxford University, England, is founded. Faro in the Algarve is recaptured from the Moors, ending the Portuguese Reconquista.

1250

1250

神圣罗马帝国的“大空位期”持续了23年；帝国的统治权从霍亨斯陶芬王朝转移到了哈布斯堡王朝。伦巴第同盟解散。马穆鲁克王朝在埃及夺取政权。乍得湖地区的卡内姆王国开始分裂成敌对派系。韦莱塔王国在今天的埃塞俄比亚建立。奇穆人沿着秘鲁北部沿海扩张其帝国版图。阿兹特克人抵达墨西哥中部。玛雅文明复兴；在玛雅潘建立了一座新都城。威尼斯的里亚托桥由浮桥改建为永久性的架空木桥。阿尔伯特·马格努斯分离出了砷元素。巴黎圣母院竣工。

The Great Interregnum in the Holy Roman Empire lasts 23 years; the Empire passes from the Hohenstaufen dynasty to the Habsburgs. The Lombard League is dissolved. The Bahri dynasty of Mamelukes seize power in Egypt. The Kanem kingdom in Lake Chad region begins to break up into rival factions. The Welayta state is founded in present-day Ethiopia. Chimu people are expanding their empire along the northern coast of Peru. The Aztecs arrive in central Mexico. There is a Maya revival; a new capital is built at Mayapan. The Rialto Bridge in Venice is converted from a pontoon bridge to a permanent, raised wooden structure. Albertus Magnus isolates the element arsenic. Notre Dame Cathedral in Paris is completed.

1251

1251

第一次牧羊人十字军东征爆发，这是一场由法国农民发起的十字军东征，旨在将路易九世从埃及的囚禁中解救出来。亚历山大·涅夫斯基签署了基辅罗斯与挪威之间的第一份和平条约。蒙哥汗当选为蒙古帝国可汗。《高丽大藏经》——一部佛教经典集——被刻在81000块木版上。

The First Shepherds’ Crusade is launched, a French peasants’ crusade to rescue Louis IX from captivity in Egypt. Alexander Nevsky signs the first peace treaty between Kievan Rus’ and Norway. Möngke Khan is elected as Khan of the Mongol Empire. The Tripitaka Koreana, a collection of Buddhist scriptures, is carved on 81,000 wooden blocks.

1252

1252

教皇英诺森四世授权中世纪宗教裁判所对异端分子施以酷刑。瑞典城市斯德哥尔摩建立。天文学方面，人们开始记录阿尔方索历，该历法将一年分为365天5小时49分16秒。欧洲第一批金币在意大利佛罗伦萨铸造，被称为弗罗林。

Pope Innocent IV authorizes the torture of heretics in the medieval Inquisition. The Swedish city of Stockholm is founded. In astronomy, work begins on the recording of the Alfonsine tables dividing the year into 365 days, 5 hours, 49 minutes, 16 seconds. The first European gold coins are minted in the Italian city of Florence, and are known as florins.

1253

1253

热那亚和威尼斯之间爆发了一系列海战，断断续续地持续到1371年。蒙古帝国攻陷巴格达和开罗，并摧毁了老挝的大理（云南）王国，将该地区并入帝国版图。日莲宗创立。

A series of naval wars begins between Genoa and Venice, continuing sporadically until 1371. The Mongol Empire attacks Baghdad and Cairo; it also destroys the kingdom of Dali (Yunnan) in Laos, incorporating the region into the empire. Nichiren Buddhism is founded.

1254

1254

在英国，国王枢密院中的低级男爵被来自郡和城市的民选代表取代。第七次十字军东征被取消。法国国王路易九世将所有犹太人驱逐出法国。在葡萄牙，议会（葡萄牙的国民议会）召开第一次会议。据称曾装饰古罗马图拉真凯旋门的圣马可骏马被安放在威尼斯的圣马可大教堂。哥本哈根获得城市宪章。马尔默建城。

In England, lesser barons are replaced on the King’s Council by elected representatives from the shires and cities. The Seventh Crusade is abandoned. King Louis IX of France expels all Jews from France. In Portugal, the first session of the Cortes (Portugal’s general assembly) is held. The Horses of St Mark, once supposed to have adorned the Arch of Trajan in ancient Rome, are installed at St Mark’s Basilica in Venice. Copenhagen receives its city charter. Malmö is founded.

1255

1255

英国人口普查“百人名册”编制完成。法国南部最后一个卡特里派据点陷落。里斯本成为葡萄牙首都。成吉思汗之孙旭烈兀奉其兄蒙哥汗之命，前往西南亚消灭剩余的穆斯林国家。法国布尔日哥特式大教堂竣工。

The Hundred Rolls, an English census, is conducted. The final Cathar stronghold in southern France falls. Lisbon becomes capital of Portugal. Hulagu Khan, grandson of Genghis Khan, is dispatched by his brother Möngke Khan to destroy the remaining Muslim states in south-western Asia. The Gothic cathedral at Bourges, France, is completed.

1256

1256

旭烈兀汗建立了蒙古波斯王国；它将成为蒙古帝国的四大组成部分之一。

Hulagu Khan founds the Mongol kingdom of Persia; it will become one of the four main divisions of the Mongol Empire.

1257

1257

第一枚高面值金币在英国铸造。

The first high-denomination gold coin is minted in England.

1258

1258

英格兰国王亨利三世被迫接受《牛津条款》，该条款要求召开议会，结束英格兰的君主专制。威尔士末代君主卢埃林是威尔士独立后的最后一位统治者。旭烈兀汗的蒙古军队将巴格达夷为平地，屠杀了100万市民。

King Henry III of England is forced to accept the Provisions of Oxford, requiring the calling of a parliament and ending absolute monarchy in England. Llywelyn the Last is the final ruler of an independent Wales. Hulagu Khan’s Mongol forces burn Baghdad to the ground, killing 1,000,000 citizens.

1259

1259

英国国王亨利三世和法国国王路易九世签署了《巴黎条约》。蒙古金帐汗国入侵立陶宛和波兰。

The Treaty of Paris is signed between kings Henry III of England and Louis IX of France. The Mongol Golden Horde attacks Lithuania and Poland.

1260

1260

蒙古人占领巴勒斯坦。成吉思汗之孙忽必烈成为大汗。马穆鲁克统帅拜巴尔斯继位为埃及苏丹。孟加拉的塞纳王朝灭亡。统治孟买周边地区的印度教锡尔哈里亚王朝灭亡。德国音乐理论家科隆的弗朗哥发表了新的音乐记谱法理论，该体系至今仍在使用。尼古拉·皮萨诺雕刻了比萨洗礼堂的讲坛。

The Mongols take Palestine. Kublai, grandson of Genghis, becomes Great Khan. Mameluke commander Baybars takes over as sultan of Egypt. The Sena Dynasty of Bengal falls. The Hindu Silharya Dynasty, which ruled an area around Mumbai, comes to an end. The German musical theorist, Franco of Cologne, publishes a new theory of musical notation, a system still in use today. Nicola Pisano sculpts the pulpit of the Pisa Baptistery.

1261

1261

君士坦丁堡被尼西亚军队重新夺回，拜占庭帝国得以重建。

Constantinople is recaptured by Nicaean forces, re-establishing the Byzantine Empire.

1262

1262

英格兰国王亨利三世获得教皇诏书，解除其在《牛津条例》下的统治，引发第二次男爵战争。冰岛和格陵兰岛被挪威征服。兰纳泰王国（今泰国境内）国王孟莱建立清莱城，作为王国的首个首都。亚当·德·拉·哈勒创作了第一部轻歌剧《树叶游戏》。

King Henry III of England obtains a papal bull releasing him from the Provisions of Oxford, leading to the Second Barons’ War. Iceland and Greenland come under Norwegian rule. King Mengrai of the Lannathai kingdom in present-day Thailand, founds the city of Chiang Rai as the kingdom’s first capital. Adam de la Halle writes the first operetta, Le Jeu de la feullée.

1263

1263

苏格兰国王亚历山大三世在拉格斯战役中击败维京人。威尼斯人在塞特波齐战役中击败热那亚人。

Alexander III of Scotland defeats the Vikings in the Battle of Largs. The Venetians defeat the Genoese at the Battle of Settepozzi.

1264

1264

第二次男爵战争，一场英格兰内战爆发。爱尔兰议会首次有确切记载的会议在基尔代尔郡的卡斯尔德莫特举行。图林根王位继承战争结束。忽必烈汗将帝国首都从蒙古的哈拉和林迁至中国汗八里（今北京）。英格兰现存最古老的贵族爵位——罗斯男爵爵位设立。托马斯·阿奎那完成其神学著作《驳异教徒大全》。

The Second Barons’ War, a civil war in England, begins. The first definitively known meeting of the Irish legislature takes place at Castledermot in County Kildare. The Thuringian War of Succession ends. Kublai Khan moves the empire’s capital from Karakorum in Mongolia to the Chinese city of Khanbaliq (now Beijing). The title, Baron de Ros, the oldest continuously held peerage title in England, is created. Thomas Aquinas completes his theological work, Summa contra Gentiles.

1265

1265

在威斯敏斯特，英国第一届民选议会（德·蒙福特议会）召开。第二次男爵战争期间，伊夫舍姆战役爆发，爱德华的军队击败西蒙·德·蒙福特并将其杀死。威尔士诗集《阿内林之书》成书。百威啤酒在波西米亚开始酿造。

In Westminster, the first elected English parliament (De Montfort’s Parliament) takes place. The Battle of Evesham is fought in the Second Barons’ War, with Edward’s army defeating Simon de Montfort and killing him. The Book of Aneirin, a Welsh manuscript of poetry, is written. The brewing of Budweiser Budvar beer begins in Bohemia.

1266

1266

苏格兰与挪威之间的战争以挪威将西部群岛和马恩岛割让给苏格兰，换取一大笔钱而告终。马可·波罗的兄弟尼科洛·波罗和叔叔马费奥·波罗抵达中国忽必烈汗的都城汗八里（今北京）。

The war between Scotland and Norway ends with Norway ceding the Western Isles and the Isle of Man to Scotland in exchange for a large monetary payment. Niccolo and Maffeo Polo, brother and uncle of Marco Polo, reach Kublai Khan’s capital Khanbaliq (now Beijing) in China.

1267

1267

英格兰国王亨利三世在《蒙哥马利条约》中承认了格鲁菲德王子的威尔士亲王头衔。西班牙入侵摩洛哥的行动被击退。维也纳强迫犹太人佩戴圆锥形头饰“角状头巾”（Pileum cornutum） ，此前他们已被迫佩戴黄色徽章。马利克·乌尔·萨利赫建立了萨穆德拉·帕赛，这是印度尼西亚的第一个穆斯林国家。罗杰·培根完成了他的巨著《大著作》 （Opus Majus），其中包含对数学、光学、炼金术、天文学、占星术等诸多领域的广泛探讨，包括对放大镜的首次描述。

Henry III of England acknowledges Llywelyn ap Gruffydd’s title of Prince of Wales in the Treaty of Montgomery. A Spanish invasion of Morocco is repelled. Vienna forces Jews to wear the Pileum cornutum, a cone-shaped headdress, in addition to the yellow badges they were already forced to wear. Malik ul Salih establishes Samudra Pasai, the first Muslim state in Indonesia. Roger Bacon completes his work Opus Majus which contains wide-ranging discussion of mathematics, optics, alchemy, astronomy, astrology, and other topics, including the first description of a magnifying glass.

1268

1268

康拉丁，霍亨斯陶芬王朝（德国国王和神圣罗马帝国皇帝）最后一位合法男性继承人，被西西里国王查理一世取代。查理一世是康拉丁的政治对手，也是敌对的罗马天主教会的盟友。匈牙利国王伊什特万五世向保加利亚发动战争。波旁王朝首次崛起。安条克公国被马穆鲁克苏丹拜巴尔斯攻陷。襄阳战役爆发，这场持续六年的战役在宋朝和忽必烈汗的蒙古军队之间展开。威尼斯狂欢节首次被记录在案。西里西亚（今土耳其）发生地震，估计造成6万人死亡。

Conradin, the last legitimate male heir of the Hohenstaufen dynasty of the kings of Germany and Holy Roman Emperors, is replaced by Charles I of Sicily, a political rival and ally to the hostile Roman Catholic Church. King Stephen V of Hungary launches a war against Bulgaria. The House of Bourbon first rises to prominence. The principality of Antioch falls to the Mameluke Sultan Baibars. The Battle of Xiangyang is fought, a six-year battle between the Chinese Song Dynasty and the Mongol forces of Kublai Khan. The carnival in Venice is first recorded. An earthquake in Cilicia (modern Turkey) kills an estimated 60,000 people.

1269

1269

波西米亚国王奥托卡二世继承了卡林西亚和卡尼奥拉的部分地区，成为神圣罗马帝国最有权势的君主。柏柏尔人马里尼德王朝完成了对摩洛哥的征服，取代了阿尔摩哈德王朝。佩勒兰·德·马里库尔首次描述了磁极。

King Otakar II of Bohemia inherits Carinthia and part of Carniola, making him the most powerful prince in the Holy Roman Empire. The Berber Marinid completes the conquest of Morocco, replacing the Almohad dynasty. Pélerin de Maricourt first describes magnetic poles.

1270

1270

第八次十字军东征爆发；法国国王路易九世在围攻突尼斯期间去世。托马斯·阿奎那的《神学大全》（Summa Theologiae）大约在这一时期完成，该书被罗马天主教会视为其神学的最高代表作。阿什凯隆被马穆鲁克苏丹拜巴尔斯从十字军手中夺取并摧毁。耶库诺·阿姆拉克推翻了埃塞俄比亚的扎格维王朝，夺取王位，建立了所罗门王朝。维特洛将阿尔哈曾两百年前的光学著作《光之书》（Kitab al-Manazir）从阿拉伯语翻译成拉丁语。梵文寓言集《五卷书》（Panchatantra）——其历史可追溯至公元前200年——被翻译成拉丁语。中国杭州成为世界上人口最多的城市。

The Eighth Crusade is launched; Louis IX of France dies while besieging Tunis. The Summa Theologiae, by Thomas Aquinas, considered within the Roman Catholic Church to be the paramount expression of its theology, is completed around this time. Ashkelon is captured from the Crusader states and destroyed by the Mameluke sultan Baibars. Yekuno Amlak overthrows the Ethiopian Zagwe dynasty, claims the throne and establishes the Solomonic dynasty. Witelo translates Alhazen’s 200-year-old treatise on optics, Kitab al-Manazir, from Arabic into Latin. The Sanskrit fables known as the Panchatantra, dating from as early as 200 bc, are translated into Latin. Hangzhou, in China, is the most populous city in the world.

1271

1271

英格兰国王爱德华一世和安茹的查理抵达阿克，开始了以失败告终的第九次十字军东征。马穆鲁克苏丹拜巴尔斯从圣约翰骑士团手中夺取了位于今叙利亚境内的克拉克骑士堡。威尔士最大的城堡——卡菲利城堡竣工。威尼斯探险家马可·波罗启程前往中国。

Edward I of England and Charles of Anjou arrive in Acre, starting the unsuccessful Ninth Crusade. Mameluke sultan Baibars captures the Krak des Chevaliers castle from the Knights Hospitaller in present-day Syria. Caerphilly Castle, the largest in Wales, is completed. Venetian explorer Marco Polo sets out for China.

1272

1272

安茹的查理一世占领了阿尔巴尼亚的都拉斯，建立了阿尔巴尼亚王国。最早的文字记载提到了板球。在伦敦，制鞋匠公会获得了管理皮革贸易的权利。

Charles I of Anjou occupies Durres in Albania and establishes an Albanian kingdom. The first recorded reference is made to cricket. In London, the Worshipful Company of Cordwainers acquires the right to regulate the leather trade.

1273

1273

鲁道夫一世成为奥地利第一位哈布斯堡王朝统治者。已故的贾拉勒丁·穆罕默德·鲁米的追随者在科尼亚城建立了旋转苦行僧苏菲教团。在长达六年的襄阳战役中，火器首次被用于战争，宋朝军队最终向忽必烈汗投降。

Rudolph I becomes first Habsburg ruler of Austria. Followers of the recently deceased Jalal al-Din Muhammad Rumi establish the Sufi order of the Whirling Dervishes in the city of Konya. Firearms are used in warfare for the first time in the six-year battle of Xiangyang in which the Song Dynasty’s forces surrender to Kublai Khan.

1274

1274

英格兰国王爱德华一世从第九次十字军东征归来，加冕为王。他下令所有英国犹太人佩戴黄色徽章。

King Edward I of England returns from the Ninth Crusade to be crowned king. He orders all English Jews to wear yellow badges.

1275

1275

英国议会通过了第一部《威斯敏斯特法令》，其中包括贫富平等以及自由公正的选举。一种用于钟表的简易擒纵机构——擒纵机构——也大约在同一时期被发明出来。据记载，马可·波罗曾到访忽必烈汗的蒙古帝国夏都上都。让·德·梅恩创作了法国寓言小说《玫瑰传奇》。

The first of the Statutes of Westminster are passed by the English Parliament; they include equal treatment of rich and poor, and free and fair elections. The verge escapement, a simple type of escapement used in clocks, is invented around this time. Marco Polo reportedly visits Xanadu, Kublai Khan’s summer capital of the Mongol Empire. Jean de Meun writes the French allegorical work of fiction, Roman de la Rose.

1276

1276

大峡谷地区遭遇长达23年的干旱；以农业为生的阿纳萨齐人被迫迁徙。中国南宋朝廷在蒙古帝国的入侵下逃离。

A 23-year drought begins in the Grand Canyon area; the agriculture-dependent people of the Anasazi culture are forced to migrate. The court of the Southern Song dynasty of China flees in the face of an invasion by the Mongol Empire.

1277

1277

拜巴尔斯入侵安纳托利亚，占领了曾经组成鲁姆苏丹国的各个酋长国。缅甸的婆罗门帝国在被忽必烈汗击败后开始瓦解。中国南宋的统治者和百姓为了躲避蒙古人的入侵，成为澳门最早有记载的居民。圣乔治十字首次被用作英格兰国旗。

Baibars invades Anatolia and captures the emirates which once composed the Sultanate of Rüm. Burma’s Pagan Empire begins to disintegrate after being defeated by Kublai Khan. The leaders and citizens of the Southern Song dynasty of China become the first recorded inhabitants of Macau, as they flee the invading Mongols. The St George’s cross is first used as the flag of England.

1278

1278

德国国王鲁道夫一世和匈牙利国王拉迪斯劳斯四世在马奇菲尔德战役中击败波西米亚国王奥托卡二世，这是中世纪规模最大的骑士战役；哈布斯堡王朝将继续统治奥地利和其他占领区，直到1918年第一次世界大战结束。已知最早的《阿维斯塔》手稿完成，这是一部古代波斯琐罗亚斯德教圣典的合集。

Rudolph I of Germany and Ladislaus IV of Hungary defeat Otakar II of Bohemia in the Battle of Marchfield, the largest battle of knights of the Middle Ages; the Habsburgs will continue to rule Austria and other captured territories until the end of the First World War in 1918. The earliest known written copy of the Avesta, a collection of ancient sacred Persian Zoroastrian texts, is completed.

1279

1279

南印度朱罗王朝遭受霍伊萨拉王朝和潘地亚王国的攻击。忽必烈汗完成蒙古对中国的征服，并灭亡了宋朝。日莲正宗佛教的最高圣物——大御本尊由日莲亲笔题写。在英国，第二次百卷调查展开，持续到1280年。

The Chola dynasty of South India falls under attacks by the Hoysala Empire and Pandyan kingdom. Kublai Khan completes the Mongol conquest of China and exterminates the Song dynasty. The Dai-Gohonzon, the supreme object of veneration of Nichiren Shoshu Buddhism, is inscribed by Nichiren. In England, the second of the Hundred Rolls surveys is undertaken; it lasts until 1280.

1280

1280

英格兰国王爱德华一世成立了国王法庭。保加利亚阿森王朝灭亡。中国大运河北段开始修建。

King Edward I of England forms the Court of the King’s Bench. The Asen dynasty of tsars of Bulgaria ends. Construction is begun on the northern section of the Grand Canal of China.

1281

1281

法国和威尼斯对君士坦丁堡的十字军东征被迫撤退。奥斯曼帝国的缔造者奥斯曼一世成为安纳托利亚中部索古特部落的贝伊。蒙古人因一场风暴放弃了入侵日本的计划，据说这场风暴是神风或神风。忽必烈汗下令焚烧道教圣典。

A French and Venetian crusade against Constantinople is forced to turn back. Osman I, founder of the Ottoman Empire, becomes bey of the Sögüt tribe in central Anatolia. The Mongols abandon an invasion of Japan because of a storm, said to be the kamikaze or divine wind. Kublai Khan orders the burning of sacred Taoist texts.

1282

1282

西西里起义，又称西西里晚祷，爆发，反对安茹王朝西西里国王查理一世的统治。水印技术由博洛尼亚的造纸商引入。

The Sicilian rebellion known as the Sicilian Vespers begins against the rule of Angevin King Charles I of Sicily. The technology of watermarks is introduced by paper-manufacturers in Bologna.

1283

1283

坎特伯雷大主教下令关闭伦敦所有犹太教堂。英格兰国王爱德华一世首次使用分尸死刑处死威尔士最后一位独立统治者达菲德·阿普·格鲁菲德。忽必烈汗入侵高棉帝国；阇耶跋摩八世选择进贡而非抵抗入侵。英格兰国王爱德华一世在威尔士开始建造卡那封城堡、康威城堡和哈莱克城堡。

The Archbishop of Canterbury orders the closure of all London synagogues. Death by drawing and quartering is first used as a form of execution by King Edward I of England in his execution of Dafydd ap Gruffydd, the last ruler of an independent Wales. Kublai Khan invades the Khmer empire; Jayavarman VIII pays tribute rather than fight the invasion. The construction of Caernarfon Castle, Conwy Castle and Harlech Castle is begun in Wales by King Edward I of England.

1284

1284

《鲁德兰法令》的颁布，正式将威尔士并入英格兰，组成英格兰和威尔士王国。意大利城邦热那亚在梅洛里亚海战中击败其宿敌比萨，加速了比萨的衰落。蒙古金帐汗国入侵匈牙利。剑桥大学第一所学院——彼得学院成立。威尼斯开始铸造杜卡特金币，这种金币在接下来的600年里成为欧洲货币的标准。亮片最早在威尼斯生产。

The creation of the Statute of Rhuddlan, formally incorporating Wales into England in the entity England and Wales. The Italian city state of Genoa defeats its rival Pisa in the naval Battle of Meloria, hastening Pisa’s decline in power. The Mongol Golden Horde attacks Hungary. Peterhouse, the first college of Cambridge University, is founded. Venice begins coining the ducat, a gold coin that is to become the standard of European coinage for the following 600 years. Sequins are first made in Venice.

1285

1285

马穆鲁克苏丹卡拉温攻占了位于今叙利亚境内的十字军要塞马尔加特，该要塞是圣约翰骑士团的重要据点，此前被认为固若金汤。越南军队击败了入侵的元朝蒙古军队。

Mameluke sultan Qalawun captures the Crusader fortress of Margat in present-day Syria, a major stronghold of the Knights Hospitaller thought to be impregnable. Vietnamese forces defeat an invading Yuan dynasty Mongol army.

1286

1286

苏格兰国王亚历山大三世去世，引发第一次苏格兰独立战争。德国国王鲁道夫一世剥夺了犹太人的所有政治自由。

Alexander III of Scotland dies, initiating the first war of Scottish Independence. Rudolph I of Germany withdraws all political freedoms from the Jews.

1287

1287

阿拉贡国王阿方索三世从摩尔人手中征服了梅诺卡岛。北海与荷兰一浅湖之间的屏障坍塌，引发了有史以来第五大洪水，并形成了须德海海湾；五万人丧生，阿姆斯特丹获得了出海口，得以发展成为港口城市。

King Alfonso III of Aragon conquers the island of Minorca from the Moors. A barrier between the North Sea and a shallow lake in Holland collapses; it causes the fifth largest flood in recorded history and creats the Zuider Zee inlet; 50,000 people die and Amsterdam gains sea access, allowing its development as a port.

1288

1288

教皇尼古拉四世宣布对匈牙利国王拉迪斯劳斯四世发动十字军东征。苏格兰议会通过一项法律，允许女性在闰年向男性求婚。

Pope Nicholas IV proclaims a crusade against King Ladislaus IV of Hungary. The Scottish Parliament creates a law allowing women to propose marriage to men during leap years.

1289

1289

苏丹卡拉温攻占的黎波里伯国，十字军国家就此灭亡。海拔17887英尺的波波卡特佩特火山首次被位于今墨西哥境内的特库阿尼帕斯部落成员登顶。方济各会修士开始在中国传教。

Sultan Qalawun captures the County of Tripoli, thus extinguishing the Crusader state. The 17,887 feet-high volcano Popocatépetl is first ascended by members of the Tecuanipas tribe in present-day Mexico. Franciscan friars begin missionary work in China.

1290

1290

英格兰国王爱德华一世将所有犹太人驱逐出英格兰。蒙古帝国入侵摩尔达维亚的比萨拉比亚地区。德里苏丹国的马穆鲁克王朝被卡尔吉王朝的贾拉鲁丁·费罗兹·卡尔吉推翻。中国发生地震，估计造成10万人死亡。大约在同一时期，眼镜在意大利被发明出来。

Edward I of England banishes all Jews from England. The Mongol Empire invades the Bessarabia region of Moldavia. The Mameluke dynasty of the Sultanate of Delhi is overthrown by Jalal-ud-din Feroz Khalji of the Khalji dynasty. An earthquake in China kills an estimated 100,000. Around this time, spectacles are invented in Italy.

1291

1291

苏格兰贵族承认英格兰国王爱德华一世在调解因亚历山大三世国王驾崩而引发的继承危机方面的权威。瑞士三个州联合起来，开始争取摆脱哈布斯堡王朝的统治。圣马力诺的独立得到教皇诏书的确认。埃及马穆鲁克苏丹哈利勒攻占阿克城，消灭了十字军耶路撒冷王国——最后一个基督教领地，并结束了第九次也是最后一次十字军东征。威尼斯所有玻璃工匠被迫迁往穆拉诺岛，以控制火灾风险，玻璃工业由此在穆拉诺岛建立起来。工程师兼天文学家郭守敬建造了昆明湖，作为北京的水库。

Scottish nobles recognize the authority of King Edward I of England in mediating a resolution of the succession crisis created by the death of King Alexander III. Three Swiss cantons join together to begin a struggle for independence from the Habsburgs. The independence of San Marino is confirmed by a papal bull. Mameluke Sultan of Egypt Khalil captures Acre, exterminating the Crusader Kingdom of Jerusalem, the final Christian landholding, and ending the Ninth and final Crusade. All glassmakers in Venice are forced to move to the island of Murano in order to contain the risk of fire, thus establishing the glass industry there. Engineer and astronomer Guo Shoujing creates the artificial Kunming Lake as a reservoir for Beijing.

1292

1292

约翰·巴利奥尔被选为苏格兰国王。泰国北部的兰纳王国征服了孟族的哈里蓬猜王国。古吉拉特邦的瓦格拉王朝被德干雅达瓦王朝征服。

John Balliol is selected as king of Scotland. The Lanna kingdom of northern Thailand conquers the Mon kingdom of Haripunchai. The Vaghela dynasty in Gujarat is subjugated by the Deccan Yadava dynasty of Daulatabad.

1293

1293

马来群岛的印度教满者伯夷帝国由克尔塔拉贾萨建立。爪哇人击败了蒙古远征军。但丁·阿利吉耶里完成了他的诗集《新生》。

The Hindu Majapahit Empire of the Malay Archipelago is founded by Kertarajasa. The Javanese defeat a Mongol expeditionary force. Dante Alighieri completes his book of verse, La Vita Nuova.

1294

1294

苏格兰国王约翰·巴利奥尔与法国和挪威缔结了古老同盟。忽必烈汗去世后，蒙古帝国的四个汗国得以独立。

John Balliol, king of Scotland negotiates the Auld Alliance with France and Norway. The death of Kublai Khan allows the four khanates of the Mongol Empire to become independent.

1295

1295

爱德华一世召集模范议会。马可·波罗结束中国之旅返回意大利。

Edward I summons the Model Parliament. Marco Polo returns to Italy from his travels to China.

1296

1296

爱德华一世攻占贝里克，屠杀了当地居民；他在邓巴战役中击败了苏格兰人。

Edward I storms Berwick-upon-Tweed, slaughtering the inhabitants; he defeats the Scots at the Battle of Dunbar.

1297

1297

威廉·华莱士发动反抗英国的起义，并在斯特灵桥战役中击败了英国军队。摩纳哥脱离热那亚独立，此后一直由格里马尔迪家族统治。

William Wallace begins his revolt against the English, defeating them at the Battle of Stirling Bridge. Monaco gains independence from Genoa; it has been ruled by the Grimaldi family ever since.

1298

1298

英格兰国王爱德华一世在福尔柯克战役中击败威廉·华莱士，重新征服苏格兰。马可·波罗被囚禁在热那亚期间，口述他的游记给一位当地作家。

King Edward I of England defeats William Wallace in the Battle of Falkirk, reconquering Scotland. While in prison in Genoa, Marco Polo dictates his travels to a local writer.

1299

1299

奥斯曼一世宣布脱离塞尔柱突厥人的统治，奥斯曼帝国由此诞生。墨西哥人定居于查普尔特佩克，这里曾是托​​尔特克人的据点。

Osman I declares independence from the Seljuk Turks, marking the birth of the Ottoman Empire. The Mexicans settle Chapultepec, a former Toltec stronghold.

1300

1300

大约在这一时期：布鲁日、安特卫普、里昂和日内瓦举办了贸易博览会。纺车被发明；清朝人口约有6000万；西非的伊费文化生产出著名的黄铜制品；图阿雷格人建立了以阿加德兹为中心的国家；夏威夷人随着农业经济增长开始形成阶级结构；印加帝国开始向安第斯山脉中部扩张；库克群岛的拉罗汤加岛和社会群岛的莫雷阿岛上建造了石质神庙群；复活节岛上竖立了巨大的石像。

Around this date: Trade fairs take place in Bruges, Antwerp, Lyons and Geneva. The spinning wheel is invented; Imperial China has roughly 60 million inhabitants; Ife culture in West Africa produces famous brasses; the Tuareg establish a state centred on Agadez; Hawaiian peoples start to develop a class structure as a result of economic growth through agriculture; the Incas begin to expand their empire throughout the central Andes; stone temple complexes are erected on Rarotonga on the Cook Islands, and on Moorea Island in the Society Islands; huge stone statues are erected on Easter Island.

1301

1301

卡那封的爱德华（后来的英格兰国王爱德华二世）成为第一位威尔士亲王。苏格兰国王罗伯特一世与英格兰国王爱德华一世媾和。奥斯曼在巴菲翁击败拜占庭军队。但丁被逐出佛罗伦萨，流放至外地。

Edward of Caernarvon (later King Edward II of England) becomes the first Prince of Wales. Robert I of Scotland makes peace with Edward I of England. Osman defeats the Byzantines at Baphaion. Dante is sent into exile from Florence.

1302

1302

在金马刺之战中，弗兰德斯击败了法国人。围绕安茹国王查理一世统治权的西西里晚祷战争结束。

In the Battle of the Golden Spurs, Flanders defeats the French. The War of the Sicilian Vespers over the rule of the Angevin king Charles I ends.

1303

1303

罗马大学成立。

The University of Rome is founded.

1304

1304

英格兰国王爱德华一世攻占斯特灵城堡，这是苏格兰独立战争中叛军的最后一个据点。

Edward I of England takes Stirling Castle, the last rebel stronghold in the Wars of Scottish Independence.

1305

1305

码和英亩这两种计量单位是由英格兰国王爱德华一世制定的。伟大的哥特式艺术家乔托在帕多瓦的圣玛利亚德尔阿雷纳教堂绘制壁画。

The measurements, the yard and the acre, are standardized by Edward I of England. The great Gothic artist Giotto paints frescoes in Sta Maria dell’ Arena in Padua.

1306

1306

罗伯特·布鲁斯成为苏格兰国王。彭布罗克伯爵在梅斯文战役中击败了布鲁斯的苏格兰叛军。法国国王腓力四世将所有犹太人驱逐出法国，并没收了他们的财产。

Robert the Bruce becomes king of Scotland. The Earl of Pembroke defeats Bruce’s Scottish rebels at the Battle of Methven. Philip IV of France exiles all Jews from France and confiscates their property.

1307

1307

爱德华二世成为英格兰国王。但丁·阿利吉耶里开始创作《神曲》。

Edward II becomes king of England. Dante Alighieri begins to write The Divine Comedy.

1308

1308

教廷迁至阿维尼翁；随后爆发教会大分裂。卡佩-安茹家族开始统治匈牙利。

The papal court moves to Avignon; the Great Schism follows. The beginning of the reign of the Capet-Anjou family in Hungary.

1309

1309

教皇克莱孟五世将教廷所在地定在阿维尼翁。

Pope Clement V settles the papal seat in Avignon.

1310

1310

英国牛津大学默顿学院首个专为学生建造的宿舍楼 Mob Quad 竣工。

The first purpose-built accommodation for students, Mob Quad, is completed at Merton College, Oxford, England.

1311

1311

由 21 位英国男爵组成的委员会制定了一系列法令，以法令制定者取代国王，成为国家的实际政府。

A committee of 21 English barons draws up a series of ordinances, which replace the king with ordainers as the effective government of the country.

1312

1312

圣殿骑士团被强行解散。曼萨·曼萨成为马里国王。

The Knights Templar are forcibly disbanded. Mansa Mansa becomes king of Mali.

1313

1313

玫瑰十字会（又称玫瑰十字会）成立。

The Order of the Rose Cross, the Rosicrucian Order, is founded.

1314

1314

罗伯特·布鲁斯在班诺克本战役中击败英​​格兰军队，苏格兰重获独立。《世界地图》（Mappa Mundi）由此绘制完成。

Robert the Bruce defeats the English at the Battle of Bannockburn and Scotland regains its independence. The Mappa Mundi (Map of the World) is made.

1315

1315

瑞士人在莫尔加滕战役中击败奥地利的利奥波德，确保了瑞士联邦的独立。一位拥有努比亚王室血统的穆斯林王子登上了今苏丹栋古拉的王位。欧洲大饥荒导致数百万人死亡（直至1317年）。马穆鲁克王朝的埃及首都开罗成为当时世界上最大的城市。

The Swiss defeat Leopold of Austria at the Battle of Morgarten, ensuring independence for the Swiss Confederation. A Muslim prince of Nubian royal blood ascends the throne of Dongola in present-day Sudan. The Great Famine in Europe kills millions (until 1317). Cairo, capital of Mameluke Egypt becomes the largest city in the world.

1316

1316

第二次阿森里战役以 5000 多人死亡告终，结束了奥康纳家族（Ua Conchobair）作为康诺特国王的统治。

The Second Battle of Athenry ends with over 5,000 dead and ends the power of the Ua Conchobair (O’Connors) as kings of Connacht.

1318

1318

苏格兰人从英格兰人手中夺取了贝里克-阿彭-特威德。马哈拉施特拉王国被德里苏丹国征服。

The Scots capture Berwick-upon-Tweed from the English. The kingdom of Maharashtra is conquered by the Sultanate of Delhi.

1319

1319

马格努斯七世统一了挪威和瑞典。

Magnus VII unites Norway and Sweden.

1320

1320

苏格兰人签署《阿布罗斯宣言》重申其独立地位。吉亚斯·丁·图格拉克建立了德里苏丹国的图格拉克王朝。大约在同一时期，曼萨·曼萨下令在廷巴克图建造宏伟的星期五清真寺。

The Scots reaffirm their independence by signing the Declaration of Arbroath. Ghiyas al-Din Tughlaq founds the Tughlaq dynasty of the Delhi Sultanate. Around this time, Mansa Mansa commissions the building of the great Friday Mosque in Timbuktu.

1322

1322

安普芬战役（常被称为骑士的最后一战）爆发；神圣罗马帝国皇帝路易四世击败了奥地利国王腓特烈一世。

The Battle of Ampfing, often called the last battle of knights, takes place; Louis IV, Holy Roman Emperor, defeats Frederick I of Austria.

1323

1323

《诺特堡条约》规定了瑞典和俄罗斯的边界。亚历山大灯塔，世界七大奇迹之一，毁于一系列地震。

The Treaty of Nöteborg regulates the Swedish–Russian border. The Pharos Lighthouse of Alexandria, one of the Seven Wonders of the World, is destroyed by a series of earthquakes.

1324

1324

帕多瓦的马西利乌斯出版了《和平捍卫者》，奠定了现代主权理论的基础。马里皇帝曼萨·穆萨率领数千人的随从和数百磅黄金，进行了一次传奇的麦加朝圣之旅。

The publication of Defensor Pacis, laying the foundations of modern doctrines of sovereignty, by Marsilius of Padua. Malian Emperor Mansa Musa makes a legendary pilgrimage to Mecca, taking an entourage numbering in the thousands as well as hundreds of pounds of gold.

1325

1325

阿兹特克人在特斯科科湖的一个岛屿上建立了特诺奇蒂特兰城（今墨西哥城）。霍霍坎人开始建造卡萨格兰德，这是希拉河以南最大的建筑，位于今天的美国西南部。日本将军足利尊氏反叛天皇，成为足利幕府的第一位将军。

The Aztecs found the city of Tenochtitlan (now Mexico City) on an island in Lake Texcoco. The Hohokam people begin building Casa Grande, the largest structure south of the Gila River in modern-day south-western United States. Ashikaga Takauji, a Japanese general, rebels against the emperor and becomes the first of the Ashikaga shoguns.

1326

1326

爱德华二世的妻子伊莎贝拉与情人罗杰·莫蒂默入侵英格兰，俘虏了国王。《诺夫哥罗德条约》划定了芬马克地区俄罗斯和挪威的边界。奥斯曼帝国的奥尔汗从拜占庭帝国手中夺取了土耳其西北部的布鲁萨，并将其定为首都。

Isabella, Edward II’s wife, invades England with her lover Roger Mortimer, capturing the king. The Treaty of Novgorod delineates the border between Russia and Norway in Finnmark. The Ottoman Orhan takes Brusa in north-western Turkey from the Byzantines and makes it his capital.

1327

1327

爱德华三世成为英格兰国王。

Edward III becomes king of England.

1328

1328

英格兰承认苏格兰为独立国家。锯木厂被发明出来。

England recognizes Scotland as an independent nation. The sawmill is invented.

1330

1330

在韦尔布日德战役中，米哈伊尔三世率领的保加尔人被塞尔维亚人击败；保加利亚的大片领土落入塞尔维亚之手。

The Bulgars under Michael III are beaten by the Serbs at Velbuzhd; large parts of Bulgaria fall to Serbia.

1332

1332

英国议会首次分裂为两院的记录。卢塞恩与乌里、施维茨和下瓦尔登组成瑞士联邦。伟大的非洲哲学家和历史学家伊本·赫勒敦出生。

The first record of the division of the English Parliament into two Houses. Lucerne forms the Swiss Confederation with Uri, Schwyz, and Unterwalden. The great African philosopher and historian, Ibn Khaldun is born.

1333

1333

在日本，后醍醐天皇推翻了北条氏，攻占了镰仓。

In Japan, Emperor Godaigo overthrows the Hojo clan and captures Kamakura.

1334

1334

乔托开始在佛罗伦萨建造钟楼。格拉纳达的阿尔罕布拉宫竣工。有记载的第一次黑死病爆发发生在中国的湖北省。

Giotto begins the building of the campanile in Florence. The Alhambra palace in Granada is completed. The first recorded outbreak of the Black Death occurrs in Hubei, in China.

1335

1335

阿布·赛义德去世，蒙古帝国的伊尔汗国分崩离析。

Abu Said dies and the Ilkhanate division of the Mongol Empire disintegrates.

1336

1336

印度的毗奢耶那伽罗王朝由卞原一世建立，成为抵抗伊斯兰教的中心。日本足利幕府建立。

The Hindu Empire of Vijayanagar in India, founded by Harihara I, becomes a centre of resistance to Islam. The Ashikaga shogunate is established in Japan.

1337

1337

英格兰国王爱德华三世觊觎法国王位，百年战争（1337-1453）爆发。爱德华，即黑太子，成为第一位英格兰公爵。牛津的威廉·默利首次做出天气预报。

Edward III of England claims the French throne and the Hundred Years’ War (1337–1453) begins. Edward, the Black Prince, becomes the first English Duke. William Merlee of Oxford makes the first weather forecasts.

1338

1338

奥斯曼帝国抵达博斯普鲁斯海峡。

The Ottomans reach the Bosphorus.

1339

1339

莫斯科克里姆林宫开始动工。克什米尔被穆斯林征服。

Construction starts on the Kremlin in Moscow. Kashmir is conquered by the Muslims.

1340

1340

英格兰国王爱德华三世被拥立为法国国王。

Edward III of England is declared king of France.

1341

1341

彼特拉克在罗马被加冕为桂冠诗人，成为自古代以来第一位获此殊荣的人。

Petrarch is crowned poet laureate in Rome, the first man since antiquity to be given this honour.

1344

1344

爱德华三世发行了三种新的金币：弗罗林、豹纹和头盔。佛罗伦萨两大银行——巴尔迪银行和佩鲁齐银行——宣布破产。

Edward III introduces three new gold coins, the florin, the leopard and the helm. The Bardi and the Peruzzi, two great Florentine banking houses, are declared bankrupt.

1345

1345

约克大教堂竣工。塞尔维亚帝国宣告成立。

York Minster is completed. The Serbian Empire is proclaimed.

1346

1346

英军在克雷西战役中击败法军。君士坦丁堡发生地震，圣索菲亚大教堂东侧拱门受损。

The English defeat the French at the Battle of Crécy. An earthquake in Constantinople damages the eastern arch of Hagia Sophia.

1347

1347

英格兰人在克罗伊托伊战役中击败了法国人。巴赫曼·沙阿在印度南部德干地区建立了一个独立的苏丹国。鼠疫（黑死病）蔓延至欧洲。

The English defeat the French at the Battle of Croytoye. Bahman Shah establishes an independent sultanate in the Deccan, in southern India. Bubonic plague or Black Death reaches Europe.

1348

1348

英法两国签署停战协定，该协定持续至1352年。乔万尼·薄伽丘创作了《十日谈》。埃及遭受黑死病肆虐，三分之一的人口丧生。位于中国蒙古的杭州成为当时世界上最大的城市。嘉德勋章创立。

A truce is signed between England and France; it lasts until 1352. Giovanni Boccaccio writes The Decameron. Egypt is devastated by the Black Death; one third of the population dies. Hangzhou in Mongolian China becomes the largest city in the world. The Order of the Garter is created.

1349

1349

瑞士巴塞尔的犹太人被集中起来焚烧，因为有人声称他们是瘟疫的罪魁祸首。

The Jewish population of Basel in Switzerland is rounded up and incinerated because it is claimed that they are the cause of the plague.

1350

1350

由英国国王爱德华三世亲自指挥的英国舰队在西班牙人海战中击败了西班牙舰队。最后一个印度教爪哇王国满者伯夷开始在东南亚扩张。如今亚利桑那州境内的霍霍坎村落开始被废弃。爱德华三世开始重建温莎城堡。李星道创作了戏剧《灰阑记》，探讨了正义与报应。日本能剧诞生。毛利人在新西兰北岛开始繁荣发展。大约在同一时期：纳瓦特尔语成为墨西哥谷地的主要语言；四里湾建筑风格被引入中东的清真寺和学校建筑中。

An English fleet personally commanded by King Edward III defeats a Spanish fleet in the Battle of Les Espagnols sur Mer. The last Hindu Javanese kingdom of Majapahit begins to spread in south-east Asia. Hohokam villages in what is now Arizona begin to be abandoned. Edward III begins the rebuilding of Windsor Castle. Li Xingdao writes The Chalk Circle, a play about justice and retribution. The beginning of Noh Theatre in Japan. Maoris begin to flourish in North Island, New Zealand. Around this time: Nahuatl becomes the predominant language of the Valley of Mexico; the four-liwan architectural style is introduced into the building of mosques and schools in the Middle East.

1351

1351

苏黎世加入瑞士联邦。土耳其人首次渡过达达尼尔海峡进入欧洲。一场起义削弱了中国元朝的统治。过去四年里，7500万欧洲人死于黑死病。在英国，网球运动开始在户外进行。

Zürich joins the Swiss Confederation. The Turks cross the Dardanelles into Europe for the first time. An uprising weakens the Mongolian Yuan dynasty of China. In the past four years, 75 million Europeans have died of Black Death. In England, tennis begins to be played in the open air.

1352

1352

柏柏尔学者伊本·白图泰游历非洲，并写下了他的旅程记述。

Ibn Battuta, a Berber scholar, travels across Africa and writes an account of his journey.

1353

1353

乔凡尼·薄伽丘完成了《十日谈》。

Giovanni Boccaccio finishes the Decameron.

1354

1354

奥斯曼帝国占领加里波利。老挝澜沧王国建立。

The Ottomans occupy Gallipoli. The Lao kingdom of Lan Xang is established.

1355

1355

葡萄牙爆发内战。

Civil war breaks out in Portugal.

1356

1356

爱德华·巴利奥尔将苏格兰国王的头衔让给了英格兰国王爱德华三世。在普瓦捷战役中，由黑太子指挥的英军击败了法军，并俘虏了法国国王约翰二世。北欧众多城市组成的贸易联盟——汉萨同盟正式成立。塞尔维亚拉什卡国王斯特凡·杜尚被拥立为塞尔维亚人、阿尔巴尼亚人和希腊人的沙皇。巴赫里苏丹纳西尔·纳西尔丁·哈桑拆除了吉萨大金字塔大部分的石灰岩外壳，用于在开罗建造堡垒和清真寺。

Edward Balliol surrenders his title of king of Scotland to Edward III of England. In the Battle of Poitiers the English, commanded by the Black Prince, defeat the French, capturing King John II of France in the process. The Hanseatic League, a trading alliance between many cities in northern Europe, is officially founded. The king of Raška in Serbia, Stefan Dušan, is proclaimed Tsar of all Serbs, Arbanasses and Greeks. The majority of the Great Pyramid of Giza’s limestone casing stones are removed by Bahri Sultan An-Nasir Nasir-ad-Din al-Hasan to build fortresses and mosques in Cairo.

1358

1358

雅克里起义爆发，这是一场发生在巴黎北部的农民起义。穆罕默德二世成为梅里尼德王朝的统治者，该王朝统治着今天的摩洛哥。位于中国蒙古的南京成为世界上最大的城市。

The Jacquerie Revolt takes place; a peasant uprising north of Paris. Muhammad II becomes ruler of the Merinid dynasty in present-day Morocco. Nanjing in Mongolian China becomes the largest city in the world.

1360

1360

《布雷蒂尼条约》标志着百年战争第一阶段的结束。法国铸造了第一批法郎。

The Treaty of Brétigny marks the end of the first phase of the Hundred Years’ War. The first francs are minted in France.

1361

1361

黑死病在英格兰再次爆发。布达成为匈牙利的首都。蒙古蓝帐汗国陷入无政府状态，17年间更换了20位可汗。
