Black Death reappears in England. Buda becomes capital of Hungary. Anarchy reigns in the Mongol Blue Horde; there are 20 khans in 17 years.

1362

1362

匈牙利国王路易一世征服保加利亚北部。拜占庭帝国仅剩君士坦丁堡城。一场名为“大曼德伦克”（Grote Mandrenke）的西南大西洋强风暴席卷英格兰、荷兰、德国北部和石勒苏益格，造成25000人死亡。自1066年诺曼征服以来，英语首次取代法语成为英格兰的官方语言。

Louis I of Hungary conquers northern Bulgaria. The Byzantine Empire is reduced to the city of Constantinople. The Grote Mandrenke, a massive south-westerly Atlantic gale, kills 25,000 in England, the Netherlands, northern Germany and Schleswig. English replaces French as England’s national language, for the first time since the Norman Conquest of 1066.

1363

1363

Guy de Chauliac 写了一本关于外科手术的书，《Chirugia Magna》。

Guy de Chauliac writes a book on surgery, Chirugia Magna.

1364

1364

查理五世成为法国国王。阿瓦王朝在今天的缅甸北部建立。

Charles V becomes king of France. The Ava dynasty is established in present-day northern Burma.

1365

1365

巴赫曼尼苏丹穆罕默德沙一世入侵印度南部的维查耶那加尔帝国。泰国北部的素可泰王国成为阿瑜陀耶王国的附属国。

Bahmani Sultan Mohammed Shah I invades the Vijayanagara Empire in southern India. The Sukhothai kingdom in northern Thailand becomes a tributary state of the Ayutthaya kingdom.

1366

1366

位于今比利时的时代啤酒厂成立。

The Stella Artois brewery in present-day Belgium is founded.

1367

1367

法国人和英国人帮助佩德罗恢复了卡斯蒂利亚国王的统治。在法国，查理五世创建了第一座皇家图书馆。

The French and English help to restore Pedro as king of Castile. In France, Charles V creates the first royal library.

1368

1368

莫斯科进攻特维尔。特维尔在立陶宛和蓝帐汗国的帮助下进行反击。蒙古领袖帖木儿攻陷德里。蒙古人被逐出中国；朱元璋建立明朝。长城开始修建。

Moscow attacks Tver. Tver makes a counter-attack with the aid of Lithuania and the Blue Horde. The Mongol leader Tamerlane sacks Delhi. The Mongols are driven out of China; Zhu Yuanzhang founds the Ming dynasty. Work begins on the current Great Wall of China.

1369

1369

法国与英国爆发战争；法国重新夺回阿基坦的大部分地区。雨果·奥布里奥在巴黎建立了巴士底狱。

War breaks out between France and England; the French recapture most of Aquitaine. Hugues Aubriot founds the Bastille, in Paris.

泰国阿瑜陀耶王国第二次征服柬埔寨。

The Thai kingdom of Ayutthaya conquers Cambodia for a second time.

1370

1370

帖木儿完成了对中亚和波斯部分地区的征服，建立了帖木儿帝国。杰弗里·乔叟创作了他的第一部作品《公爵夫人之书》。钢制弩首次被用作战争武器。

Tamerlane completes his conquest of Central Asia and parts of Persia, establishing the Tamerlaneid Empire. Geoffrey Chaucer writes his first book, The Book of the Duchess. The steel crossbow is first used as a weapon of war.

1371

1371

罗伯特二世成为苏格兰第一位斯图亚特王朝国王。拜占庭共治皇帝约翰五世·帕列奥洛戈斯向奥斯曼帝国宣誓效忠，以阻止土耳其人入侵君士坦丁堡。奥斯曼帝国控制了除萨洛尼卡以外的整个马其顿地区。

Robert II becomes the first Stuart king of Scotland. The Byzantine co-emperor John V Palaiologos pledges loyalty to the Ottoman Empire to prevent the Turks invading Constantinople. The Ottomans gain control of all of Macedonia, apart from Salonika.

1372

1372

自 1340 年以来，法国首次控制了英吉利海峡。

The French gain control of the English Channel for the first time since 1340.

1373

1373

英葡友好条约签​​署，这是世界上现存最古老的条约。默顿学院图书馆在英国牛津建成。

The treaty of Anglo-Portuguese friendship is signed, the oldest active treaty in the world. Merton College Library is built in Oxford, England.

1374

1374

英格兰国王爱德华三世赐予英国作家杰弗里·乔叟终身每日一加仑葡萄酒。舞蹈狂症起源于亚琛，可能由麦角中毒引起。

Edward III of England grants the English writer Geoffrey Chaucer a gallon of wine a day for the rest of his life. The dancing mania illness begins in Aix-la-Chapelle, possibly caused by ergot poisoning.

1375

1375

英国人签署了《布鲁日条约》，只保留了加莱、波尔多和巴约讷这三个沿海城镇。埃及的马穆鲁克人征服了亚美尼亚的奇里乞亚王国。罗宾汉的故事首次出现在英国文学作品中。

The English sign the Treaty of Bruges, leaving them with only the coastal towns of Calais, Bordeaux and Bayonne. The Mamelukes from Egypt conquer the Armenian kingdom of Cilicia. Robin Hood first appears in English literature.

1376

1376

英格兰召开了良政议会，试图改革腐败的王室议会。黑太子驾崩。阿卡马皮奇利成为阿兹特克-墨西哥王朝的第一位特拉托阿尼。

The Good Parliament is held in England; it attempts to reform the corrupt Royal Council. The Black Prince dies. Acamapitchili becomes the first Tlatoani of the Aztec-Mexican dynasty.

1377

1377

在英国，爱德华三世驾崩，他统治了50年。理查二世继位；坏议会推翻了好议会的政绩。教廷从阿维尼翁迁回罗马。伊本·赫勒敦开始撰写《历史绪论》，这是一部早期穆斯林历史著作。活字印刷术首次被用于印刷一部韩国佛教典籍。

In England, Edward III of England dies; he has reigned for 50 years. Richard II becomes king; the Bad Parliament undoes the work done by the Good Parliament. The Papacy moves back to Rome from Avignon. Ibn Khaldun begins work on the Muqaddimah, an early Muslim view of history. Movable metal type is used for the first time, to print a Korean Buddhist text.

1378

1378

约翰·威克里夫公开了他的论题。教宗格里高利十一世去世后，天主教会分裂为两派，一派在罗马，一派在阿维尼翁。在佛罗伦萨，乔姆皮人起义短暂地建立了欧洲第一个代表所有社会阶层的政府。哈雷彗星出现。

John Wyclif makes his theses public. The Great Schism occurs following the death of Pope Gregory XI – a split in the Catholic Church with one pope in Rome, one in Avignon. In Florence, the Revolt of the Ciompi briefly provides the first European government representing all social classes. Halley’s Comet appears.

1379

1379

黑羊帝国土库曼人的独立公国建立在今天的亚美尼亚境内。

The independent principality of the Turkomans of the Black Sheep Empire is established in present-day Armenia.

1380

1380

俄军抵御了蓝帐汗国、立陶宛和梁赞的大规模入侵。挪威与丹麦结成卡尔马联盟。帖木儿击败了波斯、俄罗斯、格鲁吉亚和埃及。白帐汗国的汗王脱脱铁实革废黜了蓝帐汗国的汗王马迈。两大汗国联合组成了金帐汗国。大约在同一时期，刚果王国在非洲中部扎伊尔（今刚果河口）地区建立。约翰·威克里夫和尼古拉斯·赫里福德完成了圣经的首个英文译本。

Russian forces resist a large invasion by the Blue Horde, Lithuania and Ryazan. Norway enters the Kalmar Union with Denmark. Tamerlane defeats Persia, Russia, Georgia and Egypt. Khan Tokhtamysh of the White Horde dethrones Khan Mamai of the Blue Horde. The two hordes unite to form the Golden Horde. Around this time, the Kongo kingdom is founded in the Congo river-mouth region of Zaire, central Africa. John Wyclif and Nicholas of Hereford complete the first English translation of the Bible.

1381

1381

英格兰农民起义由沃特·泰勒领导。威尼斯在与热那亚的三年基奥贾战争中获胜。帖木儿征服波斯东部，结束了萨巴达尔王朝的统治。

The Peasants’ Revolt in England is led by Wat Tyler. Venice wins the three-year War of Chioggia against Genoa. Tamerlane conquers east Persia, ending the rule of the Sarbadar Dynasty.

1382

1382

奥斯曼帝国从保加利亚人手中夺取索非亚。金帐汗国的脱脱铁汗攻占莫斯科。伦敦宗教会议谴责约翰·威克里夫的教义。英国温彻斯特公学成立。

The Ottomans take Sofia from the Bulgarians. Khan Tokhtamysh of the Golden Horde overruns Moscow. John Wyclif’s teachings are condemned by the Synod of London. Winchester College is founded in England.

1383

1383

葡萄牙爆发内战和无政府状态，史称1383-1385年危机。狮牌啤酒首次酿造。巴黎巴士底狱竣工。

A period of civil war and anarchy, known as the 1383–5 Crisis, begins in Portugal. Löwenbräu beer is first brewed. The construction of the Bastille is completed in Paris.

1385

1385

阿尔巴尼亚被奥斯曼帝国征服，开始了长达80年的抵抗土耳其统治的斗争。金帐汗国征服了波斯西部部分札剌亦儿帝国的领土。

Albania is conquered by the Ottomans, beginning 80 years of resistance to Turkish rule. The Golden Horde conquers parts of the Jalayirid Empire in western Persia.

1386

1386

在马盖特海战中，英国击败了入侵的法国和卡斯蒂利亚海军联军。瑞士在森帕赫海战中获胜，捍卫了其摆脱哈布斯堡王朝统治的独立地位。威尼斯人控制了科孚岛。德国最古老的大学——海德堡鲁普雷希特-卡尔斯大学成立。

The English defeat an invading French and Castilian naval force in the Battle of Margate. Winning the Battle of Sempach, the Swiss safeguard their independence from Habsburg rule. The Venetians take control of the island of Corfu. The Ruprecht-Karls University of Heidelberg, the oldest university in Germany, is founded.

1387

1387

帖木儿征服了波斯中部的穆扎法尔王朝。杰弗里·乔叟开始创作《坎特伯雷故事集》。

Tamerlane conquers the Muzaffarid Empire in central Persia. Geoffrey Chaucer begins writing The Canterbury Tales.

1388

1388

威克里夫圣经编纂完成。米兰大教堂开始动工。

The Wyclif Bible is completed. The construction of Milan Cathedral is begun.

1389

1389

英格兰和法国在百年战争中签署停战协定。挪威和丹麦女王玛格丽特也成为瑞典的统治者。塞尔维亚基督徒在科索沃战役中被奥斯曼土耳其人击败。耶尔德勒姆·巴耶济德成为苏丹，并在尼科波利斯战役中征服了匈牙利国王齐格蒙特的基督教军队。卡内姆-博尔努帝国（今乍得东部和尼日利亚）将其在今乍得境内的领土割让给了比拉拉人。

England and France sign a truce in the Hundred Years’ War. Queen Margaret of Norway and Denmark also becomes ruler of Sweden. Christian Serbs are defeated by Ottoman Turks at Kosovo in Serbia. Yilderim Bayezid becomes sultan and conquers the Christian army of Sigismund of Hungary at Nicopolis. The Kanem-Bornu Empire (now eastern Chad and Nigeria) loses its land in present-day Chad to the Bilala.

1390

1390

罗伯特三世成为苏格兰国王。阿兹特克首都特诺奇蒂特兰的主神庙——大神庙建成。大约在同一时期：中亚的撒马尔罕重建，成为帖木儿的首都；奥斯曼土耳其人完成对小亚细亚的征服；卡法王国在今天的埃塞俄比亚建立；维拉科查成为第八位印加统治者。

Robert III becomes king of Scotland. Templo Mayor, the main temple of the Aztec capital of Tenochtitlan, is built. Around this time: Samarkand in Central Asia is reconstructed and becomes Tamerlane’s capital; Ottoman Turks complete the conquest of Asia Minor; the kingdom of Kaffa is established in present-day Ethiopia; Viracocha becomes the eighth Inca ruler.

1391

1391

中国人发明厕纸是供皇帝使用的。

The Chinese invent toilet paper for use by their emperors.

1392

1392

奥克尼伯爵控制了设得兰群岛和法罗群岛。日本南北朝廷分裂的局面结束；足利氏成为室町幕府将军。在英国，外国人被禁止出售商品。

The Earl of Orkney takes control of the Shetland Islands and the Faeroe Islands. The end of the division of Japan into northern and southern courts; the Ashikagas become shoguns of Muromachi. In England, foreigners are banned from selling goods.

1393

1393

帖木儿终结了波斯的穆扎法尔王朝。波斯尼亚抵抗奥斯曼帝国的入侵，并与匈牙利签订和平条约。奥斯曼土耳其人攻占了东保加利亚的首府。

Tamerlane ends the Muzaffarid dynasty in Persia. Bosnia resists an invasion by the Ottoman Empire and signs a peace treaty with Hungary. Ottoman Turks capture the capital city of East Bulgaria.

1394

1394

法国国王查理六世下令将所有犹太人驱逐出法国。奥斯曼帝国开始围攻君士坦丁堡长达八年。帖木儿攻陷阿斯特拉罕。汉城（今首尔）成为朝鲜王朝的首都。

Charles VI of France orders the expulsion of all Jews from France. The Ottomans begin an eight-year siege of Constantinople. Tamerlane sacks Astrakhan. Hanseong (now Seoul) becomes capital of the Joseon dynasty in present-day Korea.

1396

1396

奥斯曼帝国征服保加利亚。

The Ottomans conquer Bulgaria.

1397

1397

《卡尔马协定》将丹麦、挪威和瑞典联合起来。

The Kalmar Agreement unites Denmark, Norway and Sweden.

1398

1398

帖木儿攻陷德里——十万人惨遭屠杀。波西米亚宗教改革家扬·胡斯在布拉格大学讲授神学。

Tamerlane sacks Delhi – 100,000 are massacred. Jan Hus, the Bohemian religious reformer, lectures on theology at Prague University.

1399

1399

约翰·冈特去世；他的儿子亨利·博林布鲁克废黜了理查二世，并成为英格兰国王亨利四世。

The death of John of Gaunt; his son Henry Bolingbroke deposes Richard II and takes the throne as Henry IV of England.

1400

1400

理查二世遇刺身亡。欧文·格伦道尔自立为威尔士亲王，发动叛乱。神圣罗马帝国皇帝温塞斯拉斯因酗酒被废黜。首次提及扬琴。大约在同一时期：欧洲人口下降至6000万；津巴布韦金矿的黄金经东海岸的索法拉出口到亚洲；易洛魁联盟成立，由五个美洲原住民部落组成——莫霍克族、奥奈达族、奥农达加族、卡尤加族和塞内卡族；阿兹特克帝国在墨西哥扩张；印加帝国也进入扩张期；伊斯兰教传入马六甲；汤加人在穆阿克建造了一座重要的祭祀中心；普韦布洛人放弃了北部地区，聚集到大型城镇；印加人开始使用奇普作为计数工具；阿兹特克祭司每年献祭数万人，以确保太阳每日重生。

Richard II is murdered. Owen Glendower declares himself Prince of Wales and starts a rebellion. Wenceslas, the Holy Roman Emperor, is deposed because of his drunkenness. The first reference to the dulcimer. Around this date: Europe’s population falls to 60 million; gold from mines in Zimbabwe is exported to Asia via Sofala on the east coast; the Iroquois Confederacy is formed, featuring five Native American tribes – the Mohawk, the Oneida, the Onondaga, the Cayuga and the Seneca; the Aztec Empire expands in Mexico; the Inca Empire also enters a period of expansion; Islam reaches Malacca; the Tonga people build a major ceremonial centre at Mu’ac; the Pueblo people abandon northern sites and gather in large towns; the Inca are using the quipu as a numeric device for counting; Aztec priests sacrifice tens of thousands of people each year to ensure the rebirth of the Sun every day.

1401

1401

帖木儿攻占大马士革和巴格达。

Tamerlane takes Damascus and Baghdad.

1402

1402

亨利四世在威尔士与欧文·格伦道尔交战。苏格兰王位继承人，罗撒西公爵大卫·斯图亚特，被其叔父，第一代奥尔巴尼公爵罗伯特·斯图亚特囚禁期间去世。热那亚重新夺回摩纳哥。帖木儿在土耳其安基拉战役中击败奥斯曼帝国，并征服了其帝国。朱棣在中国称帝，成为永乐皇帝，并成为中国历史上最伟大的皇帝之一。塞维利亚大教堂开始建造。

Henry IV fights Owen Glendower in Wales. David Stewart, Duke of Rothesay, the heir to the throne of Scotland, dies while being kept prisoner by his uncle, Robert Stewart, the 1st Duke of Albany. Genoa recaptures Monaco. Tamerlane defeats the Ottomans at the Battle of Ankyra in Turkey and overruns their empire. Zhu Di seizes the throne as the Yongle Emperor in China; he becomes one of China’s greatest emperors. Seville Cathedral is begun.

1403

1403

亨利四世在什鲁斯伯里战役中击败了哈里·“热刺”·珀西。从这一天到1409年，一部超过两万章的百科全书《永乐大典》在中国编纂完成。洛伦佐·吉贝尔蒂为佛罗伦萨洗礼堂的青铜大门创作了写实风格的人体雕塑，标志着文艺复兴的到来。

Henry IV defeats Harry ‘Hotspur’ Percy at the Battle of Shrewsbury. Between this date and 1409, an encyclopaedia of over 20,000 chapters, Yongle Dadian, is compiled in China. Lorenzo Ghiberti sculpts human bodies in realistic style for bronze doors of Florence Baptistery, heralding the Renaissance.

1405

1405

法国人抵达威尔士，支持欧文·格伦道尔对抗亨利。帖木儿去世。中国首次远航印度洋。日本开始与中国进行贸易。

The French arrive in Wales to support Owen Glendower against Henry. Tamerlane dies. The first Chinese maritime expedition is undertaken to the Indian Ocean. Japan begins to trade with China.

1406

1406

詹姆斯一世成为苏格兰国王。威尔士亲王亨利击败威尔士人。北京紫禁城开始建造。

James I becomes king of Scotland. Henry, Prince of Wales defeats the Welsh. The building of the Forbidden City is begun in Beijing.

1407

1407

伦敦的伯利恒医院变成了精神病院。

Bethlehem hospital in London becomes an institution for the insane.

1408

1408

意大利雕塑家多纳泰罗创作了《大卫》和《圣约翰》。

The Italian sculptor Donatello creates David and St John.

1409

1409

比萨宗教会议试图解决长达 30 年的大分裂，罢免了两位教皇，并选举亚历山大五世为教皇。

The Council of Pisa tries to resolve the 30-year Great Schism, deposing both popes and electing Alexander V.

1410

1410

约翰二十二世当选为对立教宗，他得到了美第奇家族的支持。在坦能堡战役中，波兰国王拉迪斯劳斯二世击败了条顿骑士团。

John XXII is elected antipope; he is backed by the Medici family. In the Battle of Tannenberg, Ladislaus II of Poland beats the Teutonic Knights.

1411

1411

匈牙利国王齐格蒙特当选为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。古吉拉特邦国王艾哈迈德·沙阿掌权，并建造了首都艾哈迈达巴德。苏格兰圣安德鲁斯大学成立。

Sigismund of Hungary is elected Holy Roman Emperor. Ahmad Shah of Gujarat comes to power and builds the capital city of Ahmadabad. St Andrews University is founded in Scotland.

1412

1412

圣女贞德的诞生。

The birth of Joan of Arc.

1413

1413

亨利五世成为英格兰国王。

Henry V becomes king of England.

1414

1414

英国国王亨利五世接受了爱德华二世的法国主张。在佛罗伦萨，美第奇家族成为教皇的官方银行家。

The English king, Henry V, adopts the French claims of Edward II. In Florence, the Medicis become official bankers to the papacy.

1415

1415

亨利五世在阿金库尔战役中击败法军，主要归功于长弓。葡萄牙国王若昂二世攻占摩洛哥的休达。宗教改革家扬·胡斯被处以火刑。大约在同一时期，布鲁内莱斯基发展出一套绘画中的线性透视体系。

Henry V defeats the French at Agincourt, mainly thanks to the longbow. King John of Portugal seizes Ceuta in Morocco. The religious reformer, Jan Hus is burnt at the stake. Around this time, Brunelleschi develops a system of linear perspective in painting.

1416

1416

欧文·格伦道尔去世。荷兰渔民首次使用流网捕鱼。大约在同一时期，林堡兄弟创作了《非常富裕的时祷书》，这是一部手稿插图的杰作。

Owen Glendower dies. Drift nets are used for the first time by Dutch fishermen. Around this time, the Limbourg brothers create Les Très Riches Heures, a masterpiece of manuscript illumination.

1417

1417

天主教教会的大分裂终于结束；罗马选举出一位教宗，马丁五世。

The Great Schism in the Catholic Church finally comes to an end; a single pope, Martin V, is elected in Rome.

1418

1418

特斯科坎的诗人国王内萨瓦尔科约特尔登基。

Nezahualcoyotl, poet-king of the Texcocan, takes the throne.

1419

1419

世宗大王统治时期，朝鲜半岛繁荣昌盛；他颁布了官方的朝鲜文字。布鲁内莱斯基设计了佛罗伦萨的弃婴医院，并建造了佛罗伦萨大教堂的穹顶。

Korea prospers under King Sejong; he introduces an official Korean script. Brunelleschi designs the Foundling Hospital in Florence and constructs the dome of Florence Cathedral.

1420

1420

《特鲁瓦条约》承认亨利五世为法国王位继承人。葡萄牙水手开始探索非洲西海岸，并在马德拉岛定居。老科西莫成为佛罗伦萨美第奇银行的经理。西非高地区的桑海人开始袭击马里帝国。明朝的都城从南京迁至北京。

The Treaty of Troyes acknowledges Henry V as heir to the French throne. Portuguese sailors begin to explore the west coast of Africa and settle Madeira. Cosimo (the Elder) becomes manager of the Medici bank in Florence. The Songhai people in the Gao region of West Africa, begin raids on the Mali empire. The Chinese Ming capital moves from Nanjing to Beijing.

1422

1422

亨利六世成为英格兰国王，查理七世成为法国国王。

Henry VI becomes king of England and Charles VII, king of France.

1426

1426

特诺奇蒂特兰的阿兹特克人与邻近的特斯科科和特拉科潘城结成三方联盟；皇帝伊兹科亚特尔重组国家，将所有权力集中在自己手中。

The Aztecs at Tenochtitlan form a Triple Alliance with the neighbouring cities of Texcoco and Tlacopan; Emperor Itzcoatl reorganizes the state to concentrate all power in his hands.

1428

1428

圣女贞德率领法国军队对抗英国；英国军队开始围攻奥尔良。

Joan of Arc leads the French against England; the English begin the siege of Orléans.

1429

1429

圣女贞德解除了奥尔良之围；她在帕泰战役中击败了英国人，迫使他们离开卢瓦尔河谷。

Joan of Arc raises the Siege of Orléans; she beats the English at the Battle of Patay, forcing them to leave the Loire Valley.

1430

1430

圣女贞德被俘。奥斯曼帝国成为制造大炮的大师。东南亚的高棉帝国开始瓦解；吴哥窟被泰国军队洗劫后废弃。东非海岸的基尔瓦苏丹开始实施一项宏伟的建设工程。波尼人开始在内布拉斯加州的主要河流沿岸定居。德国金属工匠古腾堡尝试使用活字印刷术。大约在同一时期，中古英语被现代英语所取代。常被称为“音乐王子”的若斯坎·德普雷是文艺复兴时期的一位杰出作曲家。

Joan of Arc is taken prisoner. The Ottomans become master cannon-makers. The Khmer Empire in south-east Asia begins to collapse; Angkor Wat is abandoned after being sacked by the Thai army. The sultans of Kilwa on the East African coast begin a grand building programme. The Pawnee people begin to settle along the major rivers in Nebraska. Gutenberg, a German metalworker, experiments with printing, using movable type. Around this time, Middle English is replaced by Modern English. Josquin Desprez, often called the ‘Prince of Music’, is a leading composer of the Renaissance.

1431

1431

圣女贞德被英国人处以火刑，年仅19岁。英格兰国王亨利六世在巴黎加冕为法国国王。中国航海家郑和进行了他的第七次也是最后一次航行，他远航至非洲东海岸。玛格丽·肯普撰写了第一部英文自传《玛格丽·肯普传》。

Joan of Arc is burnt at the stake by the English; she is 19. Henry VI of England is crowned king of France in Paris. Chinese mariner Zheng He makes his seventh and final voyage; he sails as far as the east coast of Africa. Margery Kempe writes the first English autobiography, The Book of Margery Kempe.

1433

1433

双头鹰成为神圣罗马帝国的象征。图阿雷格游牧民族占领了廷巴克图。

The double eagle becomes the symbol of the Holy Roman Empire.Tuareg nomads occupy Timbuktu.

1434

1434

科西莫·德·美第奇成为佛罗伦萨的统治者。基督教皇帝泽拉·雅各布在埃塞俄比亚开始统治；他扩张了教会，并兴建了宏伟的修道院。高棉首都从吴哥窟迁至金边。荷兰成为欧洲音乐中心。荷兰画家扬·凡·艾克创作了描绘资产阶级生活的画作，例如《阿尔诺芬尼夫妇像》。

Cosimo de Medici becomes ruler of Florence. The reign of Christian emperor, Zera Yacub, begins in Ethiopia; he expands the Church and promotes great monasteries. The Khmer capital moves from Angkor Wat to Phnom Penh. Holland is the centre for European music. Dutch painter Jan van Eyck paints scenes of bourgeois life such as the Arnolfini Marriage Group.

1437

1437

苏格兰国王詹姆斯一世被罗伯特·格雷厄姆爵士等人刺杀。

James I of Scotland is assassinated by Sir Robert Graham and others.

1438

1438

印加皇帝维拉科查去世；他的继任者帕查库蒂将印加帝国向北扩张到厄瓜多尔。

The Inca Emperor Viracocha dies; his successor Pachacuti expands the Inca Empire northwards into Ecuador.

1440

1440

印加人开始在库斯科建造宏伟的堡垒。阿兹特克皇帝蒙特祖玛一世掌权，征服了墨西哥东部的大片地区。柏拉图学院在佛罗伦萨成立。

Incas begin the construction of the great fortress at Cuzco. The Aztec Emperor Moctezuma I gains power; he conquers large areas of eastern Mexico. The Platonic Academy is founded in Florence.

1443

1443

韩语音节文字（韩文）是世宗大王下令创制的。

The Korean syllabary, the Hangul, is created on the orders of King Sejong.

1444

1444

奥斯曼帝国征服了黑海沿岸的匈牙利，打通了通往君士坦丁堡的道路。哥本哈根成为丹麦的首都。

The Ottomans conquer Hungary at the Black Sea, opening their route to Constantinople. Copenhagen becomes the capital of Denmark.

1447

1447

波兰国王卡齐米日四世将波兰王国与立陶宛大公国统一。斯坎德培击败穆拉德二世，使波斯、印度和阿富汗获得独立。

Casimir IV of Poland unites the Polish kingdom with the Grand Duchy of Lithuania. Skanderberg defeats Murad II, gaining independence for Persia, India and Afghanistan.

1448

1448

在特莱洛克国王的统治下，泰国在接下来的40年里不断扩张；他推行了重大的行政和法律改革。

Thailand expands for the next 40 years under King Trailok; he brings about major administrative and legal reforms.

1449

1449

足利义政统治日本直至1474年。

The Ashikaga Yoshimasa rule in Japan until 1474.

1450

1450

在美第奇家族的领导下，佛罗伦萨成为文艺复兴和人文主义的中心。梵蒂冈图书馆建立。位于南部非洲的大津巴布韦遗址的建设达到顶峰。在秘鲁，印加古城马丘比丘在乌鲁班巴河上方的高山脊上建成；大约在同一时期，印加人在安第斯山脉修建了2万英里的道路。

Under the leadership of the Medicis, Florence becomes the centre of the Renaissance and humanism. The Vatican Library is founded. Building at Great Zimbabwe, southern Africa, is at its height. In Peru, the Inca city of Machu Picchu is constructed on a high ridge above the Urubamba River; around this time, the Incas build 20,000 miles of road in the Andes.

1452

1452

德国成立了第一个专业助产士协会。列奥纳多·达·芬奇出生。

The first association of professional midwives is founded in Germany. Leonardo da Vinci is born.

1453

1453

英格兰国王亨利六世精神失常，约克公爵理查德成为摄政。百年战争结束，英军被逐出法国，仅保留加莱。奥斯曼帝国围攻并攻占君士坦丁堡，拜占庭帝国灭亡，中世纪宣告结束。

Henry VI of England becomes insane; Richard, Duke of York becomes regent. The Hundred Years’ War ends; the English are expelled from France, retaining only Calais. The Ottomans besiege and capture Constantinople, ending the Byzantine Empire and the Middle Ages.

1455

1455

约克家族和兰开斯特家族之间的玫瑰战争在英格兰爆发。古腾堡在欧洲印刷了第一部《圣经》。威尼斯宫在罗马建成。威尼斯水手卡达马斯托探索了塞内加尔河和冈比亚河，发现了佛得角群岛。一座巨大的神庙在特诺奇蒂特兰建成，供奉阿兹特克战神惠齐洛波奇特利。

The Wars of the Roses between the houses of York and Lancaster begin in England. The first Bible is printed in Europe by Gutenberg. The Palazzo Venezia is built in Rome. Cadamasto, a Venetian sailor, explores the Senegal and Gambia rivers and discovers the Cape Verde Islands. A huge temple is built in Tenochtitlan to the Aztec war god Huitzilopochtli.

1456

1456

奥斯曼土耳其人攻占雅典。匈牙利贵族约翰·胡尼亚迪率领匈牙利军队攻占贝尔格莱德，驱逐了土耳其人。

The Ottoman Turks capture Athens. The Hungarians, under nobleman John Hunyadi, storm Belgrade and drive out the Turks.

1459

1459

奥斯曼土耳其人占领了塞尔维亚。

The Ottoman Turks capture Serbia.

1460

1460

沃里克伯爵和约克公爵的长子马奇伯爵爱德华攻占伦敦；在北安普顿战役中，他们击败兰开斯特军队并俘虏了亨利国王；约克成为亨利的继承人，但在韦克菲尔德战役中阵亡。詹姆斯二世在罗克斯堡战役中阵亡。中国景德镇的皇家瓷器厂成功出口明代瓷器。

The Earl of Warwick and Edward, Earl of March, eldest son of the Duke of York, seize London; at the Battle of Northampton they defeat a Lancastrian army and capture King Henry; York becomes Henry’s heir, but dies in the Battle of Wakefield. James II is killed at the Battle of Roxburgh. The imperial porcelain works at Jingdezhen in China successfully export Ming pottery.

1461

1461

约克的爱德华成为英格兰国王。土耳其人征服了特拉布宗，这是拜占庭帝国唯一幸存的城邦。

Edward of York becomes king of England. The Turks conquer Trebizond, the only surviving Byzantine state.

1462

1462

卡斯蒂利亚从阿拉伯人手中夺取了直布罗陀。伊凡三世（大帝）成为莫斯科大公，直至1505年。索尼·阿里成为桑海统治者，并最终建立了一个帝国。

Castille takes Gibraltar from the Arabs. Ivan III (the Great) becomes Grand Prince of Muscovy, until 1505. Sonni Ali becomes ruler of the Songhai and goes on to build an empire.

1463

1463

奥斯曼土耳其人和威尼斯人之间的战争（持续到1479年）；土耳其人最终取得胜利。苏丹穆罕默德二世在伊斯坦布尔建造了一座清真寺，周围环绕着八所学院，这是奥斯曼教育体系的巅峰之作。

War (until 1479) between the Ottoman Turks and the Venetians; the Turks are eventually triumphant. Sultan Mehmet II builds a mosque in Istanbul, surrounded by eight colleges, the peak of the Ottoman educational system.

1465

1465

亨利六世被爱德华四世囚禁。第一部印刷乐谱问世。

Henry VI is imprisoned by Edward IV. The first printed music appears.

1466

1466

荷兰学者德西德里乌斯出生；他领导了北欧的学术复兴。

Desiderius, the Dutch scholar, is born; he leads a revival of learning in northern Europe.

1467

1467

日本陷入内战，持续了100多年。瑞士英雄威廉·泰尔的名字首次出现在一首民谣中。

A period of civil war begins in Japan and lasts for more than 100 years. The name of the Swiss hero William Tell appears for the first time, in a ballad.

1468

1468

洛伦佐·美第奇和朱利亚诺·美第奇成为佛罗伦萨的统治者。桑海国王桑尼·阿里将图阿雷格游牧民族赶出廷巴克图。

Lorenzo and Giulliano Medici become rulers of Florence. Songhai King Sonni Ali drives the Tuareg nomads out of Timbuktu.

1470

1470

亨利六世复辟，登上英格兰王位。秘鲁北部的奇穆文化衰落。大约在同一时期，托马斯·马洛里爵士创作了《亚瑟之死》。

Henry VI is restored to the English throne. Chimu culture in northern Peru collapses. Around this time, Sir Thomas Mallory writes Morte d’Arthur.

1471

1471

亨利六世死于伦敦塔，很可能是被谋杀。奥斯曼帝国的统治范围从托罗斯山脉延伸至亚得里亚海。托帕·印加将印加帝国的版图扩张至玻利维亚、智利和阿根廷。德国艺术家阿尔布雷希特·丢勒出生。

Henry VI dies, probably murdered, in the Tower of London. The Ottomans rule from the Taurus Mountains to the Adriatic. Topa Inca expands the Inca Empire into Bolivia, Chile and Argentina. German artist Albrecht Dürer is born.

1473

1473

西斯廷教堂建成。特诺奇蒂特兰吞并了邻近的阿兹特克城市特拉特洛尔科。

The Sistine Chapel is built. Tenochtitlan absorbs the neighbouring Aztec city, Tlatelolco.

1474

1474

法国国王路易十一向勃艮第公爵大胆查理宣战。托帕·印加继帕查库特克之后成为皇帝。威廉·卡克斯顿印刷了第一本英文书籍。德国天文学家雷吉奥蒙塔努斯描述了利用月距确定经度的方法。

Louis XI of France declares war on Charles the Bold, Duke of Burgundy. Topa Inca becomes emperor, succeeding Pachacutec. William Caxton prints the first book in English. The German astronomer Regiomontanus describes the method of finding longitude by using lunar distance.

1475

1475

爱德华四世入侵法国。英法两国签订皮基尼和约。土耳其人征服克里米亚。米开朗基罗出生。

Edward IV invades France. The peace of Piquigny is agreed between England and France. The Turks conquer the Crimea. Michelangelo is born.

1476

1476

威廉·卡克斯顿在威斯敏斯特设立了一家印刷厂。

William Caxton sets up a printing press at Westminster.

1477

1477

查理一世（大胆查理）被瑞士人击败并杀害。奥地利的马克西米利安与勃艮第的玛丽联姻，使哈布斯堡家族继承了欧洲最强大的国家之一。卡克斯顿印制了《坎特伯雷故事集》。威尼斯画家提香出生。

Charles the Bold is defeated and killed by the Swiss. The marriage of Maximillian of Austria to Mary of Burgundy makes the Habsburgs heirs to one of the most powerful European states. Caxton prints The Canterbury Tales. Venetian painter Titian is born.

1478

1478

匈牙利获得了摩拉维亚和西里西亚。土耳其人征服了阿尔巴尼亚。

Hungary gains Moravia and Silesia. The Turks conquer Albania.

1479

1479

西班牙在费迪南德和伊莎贝拉的统治下实现统一。根据《君士坦丁堡条约》，威尼斯同意向奥斯曼帝国缴纳贡赋，以换取在黑海的贸易权。布鲁塞尔成为欧洲挂毯制作中心。

Spain is united under Ferdinand and Isabella. In the Treaty of Constantinople, Venice agrees to pay tribute to the Ottoman Empire for trading rights in the Black Sea. Brussels becomes the centre of European tapestry-making.

1480

1480

西班牙宗教裁判所成立，旨在揭露异端邪说。俄国沙皇伊凡三世停止向蒙古人纳贡。列奥纳多·达·芬奇发明了降落伞。

The Spanish Inquisition is introduced to uncover heresy. Tsar Ivan III of Russia stops paying tribute to the Mongols. Leonardo da Vinci invents the parachute.

1481

1481

奥斯曼帝国创始人穆罕默德二世逝世。

The death of Muhammed II, founder of the Ottoman Empire.

1482

1482

葡萄牙人探索了刚果河河口，并在黄金海岸建立了定居点。

The Portuguese explore the Congo River estuary and establish settlements on the Gold Coast.

1483

1483

英格兰国王爱德华四世驾崩，爱德华五世继位。理查三世废黜爱德华，成为英格兰国王。俄国人开始探索西伯利亚。葡萄牙人在安哥拉登陆；传教士于次年抵达。足利义政在日本京都完成了银阁寺的建造。意大利画家拉斐尔出生。

The death of Edward IV of England; he is succeeded by Edward V. Richard III deposes Edward and becomes king of England. The Russians start exploring Siberia. The Portuguese land in Angola; missionaries arrive the following year. Ashikaga Yoshimasa completes the building of the Silver Pavilion Temple, or Ginkakuji, at Kyoto in Japan. The Italian artist Raphael is born.

1484

1484

波提切利创作了《维纳斯的诞生》。第一部欧洲航海年鉴出版。

Botticelli paints The Birth of Venus. The first European nautical almanac is published.

1485

1485

亨利七世在博斯沃思原野战役中击败了最后一位金雀花王朝国王理查三世，成为英格兰和威尔士的第一位都铎王朝国王；玫瑰战争结束。匈牙利攻占维也纳和下奥地利，成为中欧最强大的国家。

Henry VII becomes the first Tudor king of England and Wales after the defeat of the last Plantagenet king, Richard III, at the Battle of Bosworth Field; the Wars of the Roses end. Hungary captures Vienna and Lower Austria, becoming the most powerful state in central Europe.

1486

1486

阿兹特克皇帝阿维特索特尔统治至 1502 年；阿兹特克帝国在墨西哥达到了鼎盛时期。

The Aztec Emperor Ahuitzotl rules, until 1502; the Aztec Empire is at the height of its power in Mexico.

1488

1488

詹姆斯四世成为苏格兰国王。第一次大规模的一向一揆（或称一向佛教起义）在日本爆发。明朝皇帝下令重建长城，以抵御北方入侵者。崔泓轸将他游历中国的日记呈献给朝鲜国王。葡萄牙探险家巴尔托洛梅乌·迪亚士绕过好望角。

James IV becomes king of Scotland. The first major Ikko-ikki, or Uprising of Ikko Buddhists, occurs in Japan. Ming emperors order the rebuilding of the Great Wall to defend China from northern invaders. Choe Pu presents his diary of travels in China to the Korean king. The Portuguese explorer Bartholomew Diaz rounds the Cape of Good Hope.

1489

1489

加号（+）和减号（-）开始使用；它们最早出现在约翰内斯·维德曼的著作《商业算术》中。

The plus (+) and minus (-) symbols come into use; they are first used in the book Mercantile Arithmetic by Johannes Widmann.

1491

1491

经过六年战争，马穆鲁克王朝和奥斯曼土耳其人缔结了和平。葡萄牙人为刚果王国的统治者施洗，使其皈依基督教。

After six years of war, the Mamelukes and the Ottoman Turks make peace. The Portuguese baptize the ruler of the Congo kingdom as a Christian.

1492

1492

信奉基督教的西班牙人从穆斯林手中夺取了西班牙的格拉纳达，结束了穆斯林在西班牙的统治。德里苏丹锡坎德尔·洛迪吞并了比哈尔邦，并将首都迁至阿格拉，以便征服拉贾斯坦邦。纽伦堡的马丁·贝海姆制作了一个地球仪。克里斯托弗·哥伦布登陆巴哈马群岛、古巴和伊斯帕尼奥拉岛；他是自维京人以来第一个到达美洲的欧洲人。

The Christian Spanish capture Granada in Spain from the Muslims, ending Muslim influence in Spain. Sikander Lodi, sultan of Delhi, annexes Bihar and moves his capital to Agra so that he can conquer Rajasthan. Martin Behaim of Nuremberg constructs a terrestrial globe. Christopher Columbus lands on the Bahama Islands, Cuba and Hispaniola; he is the first European to reach the Americas since the Vikings.

1493

1493

教皇将新发现的新大陆瓜分给了西班牙和葡萄牙。桑海帝国在阿斯基亚·穆罕默德统治时期达到鼎盛，他征服了曼丁哥帝国的大部分领土。

The pope divides the newly discovered lands of the New World between Spain and Portugal. The Songhai Empire reaches its peak under Askia Mohammed, who takes over much of the Mandingo Empire.

1494

1494

查理八世入侵意大利。返回美洲后，哥伦布登陆牙买加。卢卡·迪·帕乔利（Luca di Pacioli）撰写了《算术、几何、比例和比例总结》，这是他那个时代的数学知识的集合。

Charles VIII invades Italy. Returning to the Americas, Columbus lands in Jamaica. Luca di Pacioli writes Summa de arithmetica, geometrica, proportioni et proportionalita, a collection of the mathematical knowledge of his time.

1495

1495

查理八世被神圣同盟击败。约翰·科尔修士首次在文字中提及了一批苏格兰威士忌。

Charles VIII is defeated by the Holy League. Friar John Cor makes the first known written reference to a batch of Scotch whisky.

1497

1497

意大利航海家约翰·卡伯特发现了纽芬兰。瓦斯科·达·伽马绕过好望角，继续航行至印度。

The Italian navigator John Cabot discovers Newfoundland. Vasco da Gama rounds the Cape of Good Hope, sailing on to India.

1498

1498

意大利宗教改革家萨沃纳罗拉被处以火刑。哥伦布发现了特立尼达和南美洲。

The Italian religious reformer Savonarola is burnt at the stake. Columbus discovers Trinidad and South America.

1499

1499

路易十二入侵意大利并征服米兰。意大利航海家亚美利哥·韦斯普奇探索了南美洲东北海岸。克里斯托弗·哥伦布镇压了西班牙殖民者在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛的叛乱。约翰·卡伯特在探索北美海岸时去世。

Louis XII invades Italy and conquers Milan. The Italian navigator, Amerigo Vespucci explores the north-east coastline of South America. Christopher Columbus quashes a revolt in Hispaniola by Spanish settlers. John Cabot dies exploring the North American coast.

1500

1500

佩德罗·卡布拉尔宣布巴西归葡萄牙所有。希罗尼穆斯·博斯创作了《愚人船》。瑞士记录了首例成功的剖腹产。布鲁塞尔和威尼斯之间开通了定期邮政服务，后来扩展到其他城市。大约在同一时期：英国开始使用铅笔；纸牌游戏在欧洲流行；西非的桑海帝国在阿斯基亚·穆罕默德·图雷的统治下进入了其扩张和实力最强的时期；贸易促进了西非豪萨邦的发展；图西族牧民迁入胡图族领地；法国开始在加拿大进行探险活动。

Pedro Cabral claims Brazil for Portugal. Hieronymus Bosch paints the Ship of Fools. The first successful caesarean birth is recorded in Switzerland. A regular postal service starts between Brussels and Venice, later extending to other cities. Around this date: Black-lead pencils are being used in England; card games gain popularity in Europe; the Songhai Empire in West Africa enters its period of greatest expansion and power under Askia Mohammed Turré; trade encourages the growth of the Hausa states in West Africa; Tutsi herders move into Hutu lands; French exploration in Canada begins.

1501

1501

法国和西班牙占领了那不勒斯。俄罗斯和波兰交战。波斯萨法维王朝第一位沙阿伊斯梅尔登基。教皇诏书授权焚书。大约在同一时期，意大利画家安德烈亚·曼特尼亚创作的写实版《死去的基督》引起了轩然大波。

France and Spain occupy Naples. Russia and Poland are at war. The reign of Ismail, first Safavid shah of Persia, begins. Book burning is authorized by papal bull. Around this time, Italian painter Andrea Mantegna creates a scandal when he depicts Christ realistically in The Dead Christ.

1502

1502

法国和西班牙之间爆发战争。蒙特祖玛二世成为阿兹特克帝国的统治者。在德国，彼得·海因莱因制造出了第一枚可正常运转的钟表机芯。哥伦布开始了第四次也是最后一次航行；他到达了洪都拉斯、尼加拉瓜、哥斯达黎加、巴拿马和哥伦比亚。

War breaks out between France and Spain. Moctezuma II becomes ruler of the Aztec dominions. In Germany, Peter Heinlein makes the first working watch movement. Columbus sets out on his fourth and final voyage; he reaches Honduras, Nicaragua, Costa Rica, Panama and Colombia.

1503

1503

苏格兰和英格兰签署《永久和平条约》，该条约有效期为十年。法国在切里尼奥拉战役和加里利亚诺战役中战败。列奥纳多·达·芬奇开始创作《蒙娜丽莎》（又名《乔康达》）。坎特伯雷大教堂竣工，历时433年建成。

Scotland and England sign the Treaty of Everlasting Peace; it lasts ten years. France is defeated in the battles of Cerignola and Garigliano. Leonardo da Vinci begins painting La Gioconda (the Mona Lisa). Canterbury Cathedral is finished; it took 433 years to build.

1505

1505

在《布卢瓦条约》中，法国保留了米兰，但将那不勒斯割让给了西班牙。葡萄牙人发现了莫桑比克，并开始与非洲人进行贸易。正德成为中国皇帝。意大利数学家西庇阿·德尔·费罗正在求解三次方程。

In the Treaty of Blois, France keeps Milan but gives Naples to Spain. The Portuguese found Mozambique and begin to trade with the Africans. Zhengde becomes Emperor of China. Scipione del Ferro, an Italian mathematician, is solving cubic equations.

1506

1506

刚果国王阿方索（位于非洲中西南）引入欧洲习俗。克里斯托弗·哥伦布逝世。罗马圣彼得大教堂开始动工。瑞士卫队成为梵蒂冈和教皇的护卫力量。尼科洛·马基雅维利在佛罗伦萨组建民兵。

King Alfonso of Kongo, in south-western central Africa, introduces European customs. Christopher Columbus dies. Work begins on the construction of the basilica of St Peter’s in Rome. The Swiss Guard becomes the protective force of the Vatican and the pope. Niccolò Machiavelli creates a militia in Florence.

1507

1507

恩津加·姆本巴，基督教徒和葡萄牙盟友，成为中非刚果王国的国王。马丁·瓦尔德泽米勒绘制了一幅世界地图，首次使用了“美洲”这个名称。列奥纳多·达·芬奇完成了《蒙娜丽莎》。

Nzinga Mbemba, Christian and Portuguese ally, becomes king of the Kongo kingdom in central Africa. Martin Waldseemuller creates a map of the world, using the name ‘America’ for the first time. Leonardo da Vinci completes the Mona Lisa.

1508

1508

马克西米利安一世成为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。教皇授予西班牙在新大陆控制传教活动的权利。米开朗基罗开始在梵蒂冈西斯廷教堂绘制天顶画（于1512年完成）。

Maximillian I becomes Holy Roman Emperor. The pope grants Spain the right to control missionary activities in the New World. Michelangelo begins painting the ceiling of the Sistine Chapel in the Vatican (completed in 1512).

1509

1509

亨利八世成为英格兰国王，统治长达38年。第乌海战确立了葡萄牙对印度洋的控制权。一场毁灭性的地震摧毁了君士坦丁堡。西班牙人将第一批奴隶从非洲带到新大陆。

Henry VIII becomes king of England; he will reign for 38 years. The Battle of Diu establishes Potuguese control over the Indian seas. A catastrophic earthquake devastates Constantinople.The first slaves are brought from Africa to the New World by the Spanish.

1511

1511

大约在同一时期，葡萄牙航海家开始探索太平洋；葡萄牙人占领了马来西亚的马六甲。

Around this time, Portuguese navigators begin to explore the Pacific; the Portuguese capture Malacca in Malaysia.

1512

1512

法国人被逐出米兰。哥白尼提出太阳是宇宙的中心。

The French are driven out of Milan. Copernicus suggests that the Sun is the centre of the universe.

1513

1513

苏格兰国王詹姆斯四世在弗洛登战役中被英格兰军队击毙。奥斯曼地理学家皮里·雷斯在他的世界地图上标注了美洲。教皇利奥十世使用凹透镜来改善狩猎时的视力。西班牙探险家瓦斯科·努涅斯·德·巴尔博亚首次发现了太平洋。葡萄牙人抵达中国。

James IV of Scotland is killed by the English at the Battle of Flodden Field. The Ottoman geographer Piri Reis includes the Americas in his map of the world. Pope Leo X uses concave lenses to improve his sight while hunting. Vasco Núñez de Balboa, Spanish explorer, first sights the Pacific Ocean. The Portuguese reach China.

1514

1514

土耳其和波斯交战；波斯人在查尔迪兰战役中战败。

Turkey and Persia are at war; the Persians lose the Battle of Chaldiran.

1515

1515

约克大主教托马斯·沃尔西成为英格兰大法官和枢机主教。弗朗索瓦一世成为法国国王。逊尼派伊斯兰教成为奥斯曼帝国的国教。法国从瑞士手中夺回米兰。法国开设了第一批国家级武器和纺织品制造厂。德国艺术家马蒂亚斯·格吕内瓦尔德创作了伊森海姆祭坛画。

Thomas Wolsey, Archbishop of York, becomes Lord Chancellor of England and a cardinal. Francis I becomes king of France. Sunni Islam becomes the state religion of the Ottomans. The French regain Milan from the Swiss. France opens the first national factories for the manufacture of weapons and textiles. German artist Matthias Grünewald paints the Isenheim altarpiece.

1516

1516

在法国和西班牙签订的《努瓦永条约》中，法国放弃了对那不勒斯的主权要求。桑海帝国鼎盛时期，其首都在廷巴克图。托马斯·莫尔爵士撰写了《乌托邦》。

In the Treaty of Noyon, between France and Spain, France relinquishes its claim to Naples. The Songhai Empire, at its height, has its capital at Timbuktu. Sir Thomas More writes Utopia.

1517

1517

德国学者马丁·路德发表了质疑天主教教义的《九十五条论纲》，由此拉开了宗教改革的序幕。奥斯曼帝国击败马穆鲁克王朝，征服埃及和叙利亚。第一批来自美洲的咖啡抵达欧洲。

Martin Luther, German scholar, publishes his 95 Theses questioning Catholic practices, launching the Reformation. Ottomans defeat the Mamelukes and conquer Egypt and Syria. The first coffee from the Americas arrives in Europe.

1518

1518

眼镜是用磨砂镜片制成的。瑞士医生菲利普·帕拉塞尔苏斯使用鸦片酊作为止痛药。意大利建筑师安德烈奥·帕拉迪奥出生。

Eyeglasses are made using ground lenses. Philippus Paracelsus, a Swiss physician, uses laudanum as a painkiller. Italian architect Andreo Palladio is born.

1519

1519

乌尔里希·茨温利在瑞士宣扬宗教改革。奥地利大公（兼西班牙国王）查理当选为神圣罗马帝国皇帝，并于1556年退位。埃尔南·科尔特斯登陆尤卡坦半岛海岸，进军阿兹特克首都特诺奇蒂特兰，杀死蒙特祖玛一世；马匹首次出现在新大陆。航海家瓦斯科·努涅斯·德·巴尔博亚因逃兵和叛国罪在西班牙被斩首。费迪南德·麦哲伦尝试环球航行，途中去世，他的船员于1522年完成航行。

Ulrich Zwingli preaches reformation in Switzerland. Charles, Archduke of Austria (and king of Spain) is elected Holy Roman Emperor; he retires in 1556. Hernan Cortés lands on the coast of Yucutan, marches on the Aztec capital, Tenochtitlán, and kills Moctezuma; horses appear in the New World for the first time. The navigator Vasco Nunez de Balboa is beheaded in Spain for desertion and treason. Ferdinand Magellan attempts a voyage around the world: he dies en route and his crew complete the voyage in 1522.

1520

1520

法国国王弗朗索瓦一世和英国国王亨利八世在金缕原野会面，但未能结盟。克里斯蒂安二世成为丹麦、挪威和瑞典的国王。苏莱曼大帝统治时期开始，奥斯曼帝国达到鼎盛时期。第一批来自新大陆的巧克力抵达欧洲。

Francois I of France and Henry VIII of England meet on the Field of Cloth of Gold; they fail to form an alliance. Christian II becomes king of Denmark, Norway and Sweden. The reign of Suleyman the Magnificent begins; the Ottoman Empire is at its peak. The first chocolate from the New World arrives in Europe.

1521

1521

沃尔姆斯议会将马丁·路德逐出教会；路德开始将《圣经》翻译成德语，并于1534年完成。法国和西班牙因意大利问题开战。苏莱曼攻占贝尔格莱德和罗德岛。科尔特斯宣布墨西哥归西班牙所有。西班牙在委内瑞拉建立殖民地。

The Diet of Worms excommunicates Martin Luther; Luther begins to translate the Bible into German, completing it in 1534. France and Spain go to war over Italy. Suleyman captures Belgrade and Rhodes. Cortés claims Mexico for Spain. A Spanish colony is established in Venezuela.

1522

1522

查理五世将法国人逐出米兰。阿尔布雷希特·丢勒设计了一架飞行器。帕拉塞尔苏斯撰写了第一部现代外科手术手册。麦哲伦探险队中只有一艘船返回了欧洲。

Charles V drives the French out of Milan. Albrecht Dürer designs a flying machine. Paracelsus writes the first modern surgery manual. Only one ship from Magellan’s expedition makes it back to Europe.

1523

1523

瑞典国王古斯塔夫·瓦萨领导了反对丹麦统治的起义，并被推选为国王古斯塔夫一世。葡萄牙人被逐出中国。

Gustavus Vasa of Sweden leads a revolt against Danish rule and is elected King Gustavus I. The Portuguese are expelled from China.

1524

1524

法国重新夺回米兰。意大利人乔瓦尼·达·韦拉扎诺发现了纽约湾。第一批来自美洲的火鸡抵达欧洲。

France recaptures Milan. The Italian Giovanni da Verrazano discovers New York Bay. The first turkeys from the Americas arrive in Europe.

1525

1525

西班牙官方地图绘制者迭戈·里贝罗绘制了第一张涵盖太平洋的科学海图。

Diego Ribeiro, official mapmaker for Spain, makes the first scientific charts covering the Pacific.

1526

1526

蒙古统治者成吉思汗和莫卧儿王朝第一位皇帝帖木儿的后裔巴布尔入侵印度。葡萄牙人在巴布亚新几内亚登陆。

Babur, a descendant of Mongol ruler Genghis Khan and of Tamerlane, the first Mughal emperor, invades India. The Portuguese land on Papua New Guinea.

1527

1527

查理五世的军队洗劫了罗马，并俘虏了教皇克莱门特七世。印加人开始了一场血腥的内战。

Charles V’s troops sack Rome and capture Pope Clement VII. The Incas begin a bloody civil war.

1529

1529

沃尔西因未能为亨利八世争取到离婚而遭解职；托马斯·莫尔爵士出任大法官；亨利八世开始与罗马教会断绝关系。法国在《康布雷和约》中放弃了对意大利的领土要求。穆斯林在辛布拉库雷战役中击败了埃塞俄比亚基督教军队，并占领了埃塞俄比亚王国，直到1543年葡萄牙军队出兵才将其击败。

Wolsey is dismissed for failing to obtain a divorce for Henry VIII; Sir Thomas More becomes Lord Chancellor; Henry begins to cut ties with the Church of Rome. France renounces its claims to Italy in the Peace of Cambrai. The Muslims defeat Christian Ethiopian forces at the Battle of Shimbra Kure and overrun the kingdom until 1543, when Portuguese troops help to defeat them.

1530

1530

圣约翰骑士团由查理五世在马耳他建立。查理五世加冕为意大利国王。瑞士爆发内战，天主教徒击败新教徒。葡萄牙人开始组织跨大西洋奴隶贸易。西班牙人征服厄瓜多尔、巴拉圭和智利部分地区。

The Knights of St John are established on Malta by Charles V. Charles V is crowned king of Italy. Civil war breaks out in Switzerland; the Catholics defeat the Protestants. The Portuguese begin to organize the transatlantic slave trade. The Spaniards conquer Ecuador, Paraguay, and a part of Chile.

1532

1532

托马斯·莫尔爵士因亨利八世的离婚而辞职。约翰·加尔文在法国发起了一场新教运动。西班牙征服者弗朗西斯科·皮萨罗入侵秘鲁，摧毁了印加帝国，杀死了其统治者阿塔瓦尔帕，尽管阿塔瓦尔帕曾向他献上大量黄金。甘蔗首次在巴西种植。弗朗索瓦·拉伯雷创作了粗俗讽刺剧《巨人传》。

Sir Thomas More resigns over Henry’s divorce. John Calvin starts a Protestant movement in France. Spanish Conquistador Francisco Pizarro invades Peru and destroys the Inca Empire, killing its ruler Atahualpa, even though he gave him a vast amount of gold. Sugar cane is first cultivated in Brazil. François Rabelais writes the bawdy satire Pantagruel.

1533

1533

亨利八世与阿拉贡的凯瑟琳的婚姻被宣布无效；他迎娶安妮·博林，并被教皇克莱门特七世逐出教会；托马斯·克兰麦成为坎特伯雷大主教。巴巴罗萨成为奥斯曼帝国海军总司令。北越分裂为东京王国和安南王国。

Henry VIII’s marriage to Catherine of Aragon is annulled; he marries Anne Boleyn and is excommunicated by Pope Clement VII; Thomas Cranmer becomes Archbishop of Canterbury. Barbarossa becomes Chief Admiral of the Ottoman fleet. North Vietnam splits into the kingdoms of Tonking and Annam.

1534

1534

英国国王亨利八世与罗马教廷决裂，宣布自己为英国教会的最高领袖。土耳其人占领突尼斯、巴格达和美索不达米亚。法国人雅克·卡蒂埃探索拉布拉多和圣劳伦斯河。罗耀拉创立耶稣会。马丁·路德出版了他的新约圣经译本。

Henry VIII of England breaks with Rome; he declares himself head of the English Church. The Turks take Tunis, Baghdad and Mesopotamia. The Frenchman Jacques Cartier explores Labrador and the St Lawrence River. Loyola founds the Jesuits. Martin Luther publishes his translation of the New Testament.

1535

1535

托马斯·莫尔爵士被处决。法国和西班牙交战。曼科·印加在秘鲁高原建立了维尔坎班巴王国，该王国一直延续到1572年。

Sir Thomas More is executed. France and Spain are at war. Manco Inca founds the state of Vilcambamba in the Peruvian highlands, lasting until 1572.

1536

1536

安妮·博林被处决；亨利八世迎娶简·西摩。法国与土耳其结盟，入侵萨伏伊和皮埃蒙特。阿克巴成为印度皇帝。西班牙吞并古巴。

Anne Boleyn is executed; Henry VIII marries Jane Seymour. France allies with Turkey and invades Savoy and Piedmont. Akbar becomes Emperor of India. Spain annexes Cuba.

1537

1537

简·西摩在生下未来的爱德华六世后去世。

Jane Seymour dies after giving birth to the future Edward VI.

1538

1538

法国和西班牙签署了《尼斯停战协定》。

The Truce of Nice is signed between France and Spain.

1540

1540

亨利八世娶了克利夫斯的安妮，后与其离婚，又娶了凯瑟琳·霍华德。西班牙人抵达加利福尼亚。西班牙医生迈克尔·塞尔维特描述了肺循环。

Henry VIII marries Anne of Cleves, divorces her and marries Catherine Howard. The Spanish arrive in California. Spanish physician Michael Servetus describes pulmonary circulation.

1541

1541

约翰·诺克斯将宗教改革带到苏格兰。土耳其人征服匈牙利。埃尔南多·德·索托发现了密西西比河。希腊画家埃尔·格列柯出生。

John Knox brings the Reformation to Scotland. The Turks conquer Hungary. Hernando de Soto discovers the Mississippi. The Greek painter El Greco is born.

1542

1542

凯瑟琳·霍华德被处决。苏格兰国王詹姆斯五世在索尔韦海战中阵亡。玛丽·斯图亚特成为苏格兰女王。

Catherine Howard is executed. James V of Scotland dies at the Battle of Solway. Mary Stuart becomes queen of Scotland.

1543

1543

亨利八世与凯瑟琳·帕尔结婚。神圣罗马帝国和英格兰结盟对抗法国和苏格兰，并入侵法国。葡萄牙人将火器引入日本。尼古拉斯·哥白尼发表了《天体运行论》，书中他指出太阳而非地球才是太阳系的中心。

Henry VIII marries Catherine Parr. The Holy Roman Empire and England form an alliance against France and Scotland and invade France. The Portuguese introduce firearms to Japan. Nicolas Copernicus publishes De revolutionibus orbium coelestium, in which he states that the Sun, not the Earth, is the centre of the solar system.

1544

1544

《继承法》恢复了伊丽莎白一世在英国王位继承序列中的地位。查理五世再次入侵法国。瑞典王位继承与男性继承人挂钩。

The Act of Succession restores Elizabeth to the Line of Succession to the throne of England. Charles V invades France again. Swedish succession is tied to the male line.

1545

1545

特伦托会议试图改革天主教会。英国战舰“玛丽·罗斯”号在索伦特海战中被击沉。

The Council of Trent attempts to reform the Catholic Church. English warship the Mary Rose is sunk at the Battle of the Solent.

1546

1546

桑海军队征服了马里。他宾瑞提称缅甸全境国王。佛兰德地理学家杰拉杜斯·墨卡托描述了地球的磁极。

Songhai forces conquer Mali. Tabinshwehti assumes the title of king of all Burma. The Flemish geographer Gerardus Mercator describes the Earth’s magnetic poles.

1547

1547

亨利八世去世；爱德华六世成为英格兰国王。亨利二世成为法国国王。伊凡雷帝成为俄罗斯沙皇。

Henry VIII dies; Edward VI becomes king of England. Henry II becomes king of France. Ivan the Terrible becomes Tsar of Russia.

1548

1548

神圣罗马帝国吞并荷兰。

The Holy Roman Empire annexes the Netherlands.

1549

1549

伊凡四世创建了俄罗斯第一届国民议会。耶稣会士圣方济·沙勿略将基督教传入日本。《公祷书》在英国出版。

Ivan IV creates Russia’s first national assembly. The Jesuit St Francis Xavier takes Christianity to Japan. The Book of Common Prayer is published in England.

1550

1550

西非的沃洛夫帝国灭亡。图西族人大约在同一时期建立了卢旺达王国。蒙古人围攻北京。西班牙人在智利和哥伦比亚发现了黄金。明代剧作家、代表作《牡丹亭》的唐熙安祖出生。德国数学家格奥尔格·雷蒂库斯出版了三角函数表。

The Wolof Empire in West Africa disappears. The Tutsi establish the kingdom of Rwanda around this time. The Mongols besiege Beijing. The Spanish discover gold in Chile and Colombia. Tang Xi Anzu, Ming playwright and author of The Peony Pavilion, is born. A German mathematician, Georg Rheticus, publishes trigonometric tables.

1551

1551

土耳其和匈牙利一直交战到 1562 年。莽应奴继承缅甸王位并征服泰国。

Turkey and Hungary go to war until 1562. Bayinnaung inherits the Burmese throne and overruns Thailand.

1552

1552

查理五世与法国国王亨利二世之间爆发战争。苏格兰女王玛丽在打高尔夫球。

War breaks out between Charles V and Henry II of France. Mary Queen of Scots plays golf.

1553

1553

爱德华去世后，简·格雷夫人被拥立为英格兰女王；她的统治仅持续了九天，信奉天主教的玛丽一世即位。罗马天主教主教制度在英格兰得以恢复。

Lady Jane Grey is declared queen of England after the death of Edward; her reign lasts nine days and the Catholic Mary I becomes queen. Roman Catholic bishops are restored in England.

1554

1554

简·格雷夫人被处决。玛丽一世嫁给了西班牙王位继承人菲利普。土耳其人征服了北非沿海地区。

Lady Jane Grey is executed. Mary I marries Philip, heir to the Spanish throne. The Turks conquer the coast of North Africa.

1555

1555

英国回归罗马天主教；新教徒遭受迫害。《奥格斯堡宗教和约》赋予新教诸侯宗教信仰自由。大津巴布韦遗址竣工。中国西北部发生地震，造成83.5万人死亡。烟草从新大陆传入西班牙。

England returns to Roman Catholicism; Protestants are persecuted. In the Religious Peace of Augsburg, Protestant princes are granted freedom of worship. Great Zimbabwe is completed. A total of 835,000 people die in an earthquake in north-west China. Tobacco is brought to Spain from the New World.

1556

1556

菲利普二世成为西班牙国王。阿克巴大帝成为印度莫卧儿王朝的统治者；他击败了印度教徒，开始了对整个次大陆的征服，并于1605年完成。

Philip II becomes king of Spain. Akbar the Great becomes Mughal ruler of India; he defeats the Hindus and begins the conquest of the entire subcontinent, completed in 1605.

1557

1557

法国在圣康坦战役中被英国和西班牙击败。葡萄牙在澳门建立殖民地。利沃尼亚战争爆发，波兰、俄罗斯、瑞典和丹麦卷入其中，战争持续到1582年。建筑师锡南完成了苏莱曼一世的清真寺建筑群。

France is defeated by England and Spain at the Battle of St Quentin. The Portuguese establish a colony at Macao. The Livonian War begins, involving Poland, Russia, Sweden and Denmark; it lasts until 1582. The architect Sinan completes Suleyman I’s mosque complex.

1558

1558

伊丽莎白一世成为英格兰女王，统治45年；天主教法律被废除。英格兰失去加莱。苏格兰女王玛丽嫁给了法国王位继承人弗朗索瓦。乔塞福·扎利诺定义了现代音乐中的大调和小调音阶。佛兰德画家彼得·勃鲁盖尔开始了长达十年的创作高峰期。

Elizabeth I becomes queen of England and reigns for 45 years; Catholic legislation is repealed. England loses Calais. Mary, queen of Scots marries François, heir to the French throne. Gioseffo Zarlino creates definitions of the modern major and minor musical scales. The Flemish painter Pieter Breughel begins a prolific ten-year period.

1559

1559

弗朗索瓦二世成为法国国王。西班牙控制了几乎整个意大利。马德里郊外的埃斯科里亚尔宫开始动工。

François II becomes king of France. Spain now controls almost all of Italy. Work starts on the palace of Escorial outside Madrid.

1560

1560

英格兰与苏格兰改革派签署了《贝里克条约》。凯瑟琳·德·美第奇成为法国摄政王，直至1574年。法国宗教战争爆发（持续至16世纪90年代）：新教少数派与天主教多数派发生冲突，贵族们在软弱的瓦卢瓦王朝国王统治下争夺权力。查理九世成为法国国王。大约在同一时期，秘鲁万卡韦利卡发现了水银矿藏。

The Treaty of Berwick is signed between England and the Scottish reformers. Catherine de Medici becomes regent of France until 1574. The French Wars of Religion begin (until the 1590s): the Protestant minority is in conflict with the Catholic majority, as nobles fight for power under the weak Valois kings. Charles IX becomes king of France. Around this time, mercury is discovered at Huancavelica in Peru.

1561

1561

苏格兰女王玛丽寡居后返回苏格兰。莫斯科圣瓦西里大教堂竣工。

Mary, queen of Scots returns, widowed, to Scotland. The Cathedral of St Basil the Blessed in Moscow is completed.

1562

1562

约翰·霍金斯爵士开启了英国的奴隶贸易，将奴隶从西非运往美洲。

Sir John Hawkins starts the English slave trade, transporting slaves from West Africa to the Americas.

1563

1563

《三十九条信纲》颁布，确立了英国国教。伊凡雷帝征服了利沃尼亚的部分地区。

The Thirty-nine Articles establishing the Anglican Church are published. Ivan the Terrible conquers part of Livonia.

1564

1564

英法两国签订《特鲁瓦和约》。俄国开始实行恐怖统治。教皇批准出版《禁书目录》。威廉·莎士比亚、克里斯托弗·马洛和伽利略·伽利莱出生。

The Peace of Troyes is signed between England and France. A reign of terror begins in Russia. The pope gives his approval to the publication of an Index of Prohibited Books. The birth of William Shakespeare, Christopher Marlowe and Galileo Galilei.

1565

1565

葡萄牙人发现了里约热内卢。佛兰德画家老彼得·勃鲁盖尔创作了《猎人归来》。

The Portuguese found Rio de Janeiro. Flemish painter Pieter Breughel the Elder paints The Return of the Hunters.

1567

1567

苏格兰女王玛丽的丈夫达恩利勋爵被谋杀后，玛丽嫁给了博斯韦尔伯爵，随后被囚禁并被迫退位；詹姆斯六世成为苏格兰国王。伤寒在美洲造成两百万人死亡。西班牙水手阿尔瓦罗·德·门达从秘鲁卡亚俄港向西航行，横渡太平洋；他抵达了所罗门群岛。

Following the murder of Lord Darnley, husband of Mary, queen of Scots, Mary marries the Earl of Bothwell, is imprisoned and forced to abdicate; James VI becomes king of Scotland. Typhoid kills two million in the Americas. Alvaro de Menda, a Spanish sailor, sets sail from Callao in Peru westwards to cross the Pacific; he reaches the Solomon Islands.

1568

1568

苏格兰女王玛丽被英国女王伊丽莎白一世囚禁。荷兰开始争取摆脱西班牙统治的独立运动，并最终于1648年取得胜利。瓶装啤酒首次在伦敦生产。

Mary, queen of Scots is imprisoned by Elizabeth I in England. A Dutch campaign for independence from Spanish rule begins; it is finally achieved in 1648. Bottled beer is produced for the first time in London.

1569

1569

波兰和立陶宛合并。

Poland and Lithuania merge.

1570

1570

法国胡格诺派教徒，即改革后的新教徒，被赋予了有条件的宗教信仰自由。大约在同一时期，中非的卡内姆-博尔努王国在伊德里斯三世的统治下达到鼎盛时期。

French Huguenots, reformed Protestants, are given conditional freedom of worship. Around this time, the Kanem-Bornu kingdom in central Africa is at its most powerful under Idris III.

1571

1571

奥地利的唐·胡安在勒班陀海战中击溃了阿里·帕夏率领的奥斯曼舰队。

Don John of Austria routs the Ottoman fleet under Ali Pasha at the Battle of Lepanto.

1572

1572

在巴黎圣巴托罗缪大屠杀中，8000名新教徒被杀害。西班牙人斩首了最后一位印加帝国领袖图帕克·阿马鲁。

In the Massacre of St Bartholomew, in Paris, 8,000 Protestants are killed. The Spanish behead the last Inca leader, Tupac Amaru.

1573

1573

威尼斯放弃塞浦路斯，与土耳其媾和。奥地利的唐·胡安重新夺回突尼斯。万历皇帝在中国即位，开启了绘画和瓷器制作的黄金时代。

Venice abandons Cyprus and makes peace with Turkey. Don John of Austria recaptures Tunis. Emperor Wan Li comes to power in China, ushering in a period of great paintings and porcelain-making.

1574

1574

土耳其重新夺回突尼斯，控制了北非大部分地区。《太平广志》出版，这是第一本用活字印刷的中文书籍。理查德·伯比奇获得在伦敦开设剧院的许可证。

Turkey retakes Tunis and controls most of North Africa. Taiping Guangzhi is published, the first Chinese book printed with movable type. Richard Burbage gains a licence to open a theatre in London.

1575

1575

葡萄牙人开始殖民安哥拉；随后爆发了一个多世纪的战争。罗马尼亚特兰西瓦尼亚王子斯特凡·巴托里当选为波兰国王。

The Portuguese begin to colonize Angola; more than a century of warfare follows. Stephen Batory, prince of Transylvania in Romania, is elected king of Poland.

1576

1576

法国禁止新教。鲁道夫二世成为神圣罗马帝国皇帝，直至1612年。

Protestantism is banned in France. Rudolf II becomes Holy Roman Emperor until 1612.

1577

1577

阿克巴大帝完成了对北印度的吞并。英国航海家弗朗西斯·德雷克开始环球航行，并于1580年完成。拉尔夫·霍林谢德撰写了两卷本的《英格兰、苏格兰和爱尔兰编年史》。埃尔·格列柯正在创作他最伟大的作品。佛兰德斯画家彼得·保罗·鲁本斯出生。

Akbar the Great completes the annexation of northern India. English seaman Francis Drake sets out on a voyage round the world, completed in 1580. Ralph Holinshed writes the two-volume Chronicles of England, Scotland and Ireland. El Greco is painting his greatest works. Flemish artist Peter Paul Rubens is born.

1578

1578

穆斯林在卡斯尔卡比勒战役中击败葡萄牙人。弗朗西斯·德雷克爵士宣布温哥华归英国所有。

The Muslims defeat the Portuguese at the Battle of Al Kasr Al-Kabil. Sir Francis Drake claims Vancouver for England.

1579

1579

英国和荷兰结成联盟对抗西班牙。荷兰北部各省组成乌得勒支联盟。

The English and the Dutch form an alliance against Spain. The Dutch northern provinces form the Union of Utrecht.

1580

1580

西班牙征服了欧洲的葡萄牙和美洲的阿根廷。

Spain conquers Portugal in Europe and Argentina in the Americas.

1581

1581

乌得勒支联盟宣布脱离西班牙独立，自称为荷兰共和国，并选举奥兰治的威廉为统治者。波兰入侵俄罗斯。俄罗斯人完成了对西伯利亚的征服。印度的阿克巴征服了阿富汗。伽利略研究了钟摆。

The Union of Utrecht declares independence from Spain, calls itself the Dutch Republic and elects William of Orange as its ruler. Poland invades Russia. The Russians complete the conquest of Siberia. Akbar of India conquers Afghanistan. Galileo investigates the pendulum.

1582

1582

波兰、俄罗斯和瑞典宣布和平。爱丁堡大学成立。格里历在罗马天主教国家推广，其误差仅为每3300年一天。

Peace is declared between Poland, Russia and Sweden. Edinburgh University is founded. The Gregorian Calendar is introduced in Roman Catholic countries; it is accurate to within one day every 3,300 years.

1583

1583

第一批人寿保险单在伦敦签发。

The first life insurance policies are issued in London.

1584

1584

荷兰共和国国王奥兰治亲王威廉被西班牙的支持者刺杀。沃尔特·雷利爵士派遣探险队前往北美弗吉尼亚，一年后又派遣殖民探险队，但以失败告终。中国平均律被确立。

William of Orange of the Dutch Republic is assassinated by a supporter of the Spanish. Sir Walter Ralegh sends an expedition to Virginia in North America, followed a year later by a colonizing expedition, which fails. The Chinese tempered musical scale is defined.

1585

1585

英国向荷兰共和国派遣军队。

England sends troops to the Dutch Republic.

1586

1586

苏格兰女王玛丽卷入了一场反对伊丽莎白一世的阴谋。日本封建领主织田信长攻占京都，开启了日本的统一时期。弗朗西斯·德雷克远征西印度群岛。

Mary, queen of Scots is involved in a conspiracy against Elizabeth I. A period of national unification in Japan begins when feudal lord Oda Nobunaga captures the capital, Kyoto. Francis Drake makes an expedition to the West Indies.

1587

1587

苏格兰女王玛丽被处决。英格兰与西班牙交战（直至1603年）；德雷克在加的斯摧毁了西班牙舰队。

Mary, queen of Scots is executed. England is at war with Spain (until 1603); Drake destroys the Spanish fleet at Cadiz.

1588

1588

英国舰队在英格兰南部海岸击败了西班牙无敌舰队；西班牙国力衰落。亨利·德·吉斯遇刺身亡。沙阿·阿巴斯成为萨法维王朝的统治者，推行改革并重建了伊斯法罕。在日本重组后的社会中，只有武士才被允许携带武器。

The English fleet defeats the Spanish Armada off the south coast of England; Spanish power declines. Henri of Guise is murdered. Shah Abbas becomes ruler of the Safavid Empire, creating reforms and rebuilding Isfahan. In Japan’s reorganized society, only Samurai are permitted to carry weapons.

1589

1589

英国第一台针织机由威廉·李发明。法国国王亨利三世遇刺身亡，信奉新教的纳瓦拉的亨利继位。法国宫廷开始使用叉子作为餐具。

The first English knitting machinery is invented by William Lee. Henry III of France is murdered and the Protestant Henri of Navarre becomes king. Forks are being used as eating implements at the French court.

1590

1590

缅甸开始分裂成许多小国。莎士比亚开始了他的剧作家生涯；在他1616年去世之前，他创作了大约38部戏剧。伽利略研究了物体下落的现象。大约在同一时期，伊斯法罕皇家清真寺建成。

Burma begins to break up into small states. Shakespeare begins his career as a playwright; he writes around 38 plays before his death in 1616. Galileo studies falling bodies. Around this time, the Royal Mosque is built in Isfahan.

1591

1591

桑海帝国被摩洛哥军队推翻。丰臣秀吉统一日本。

The Songhai Empire is overthrown by the Moroccan army. Hideyoshi unifies Japan.

1592

1592

阿克巴大帝征服信德。葡萄牙商人定居蒙巴萨。朝鲜成功击退了日本的第一次入侵，此后日本又多次入侵。阮氏和郑氏统治越南，直至1788年。庞贝古城遗址在意大利被发现。

Akbar the Great takes Sind. Portuguese traders settle in Mombassa. Korea succeeds in beating off the first of a number of Japanese invasions. The Nguyen and Trinh lords take power in Vietnam; they rule unti 1788. The ruins of Pompei are discovered in Italy.

1593

1593

法国第一位波旁王朝国王亨利四世皈依天主教，结束了法国的宗教战争。奥地利和土耳其之间爆发战争，一直持续到1606年。

Henry IV, the first Bourbon king of France, converts to Catholicism, ending the French religious wars. War breaks out between Austria and Turkey, until 1606.

1595

1595

瑞典在与俄罗斯签订的《特乌西纳条约》中获得爱沙尼亚。墨卡托去世，他自1578年起分册出版了他的地图集。

Sweden gains Estonia in the Treaty of Teusina with Russia. Mercator dies, having published his atlas in parts since 1578.

1597

1597

休·奥尼尔，蒂龙伯爵，领导了爱尔兰反抗英国的起义。

A rebellion in Ireland against the English is led by Hugh O’Neill, Earl of Tyrone.

1598

1598

亨利四世赋予新教胡格诺派教徒平等权利。大约在同一时期，荷兰在西非几内亚海岸建立了第一批贸易站。朝鲜人发明了铁甲舰。

Henry IV grants equal rights to Protestant Huguenots. The first Dutch trading posts are established on the coast of Guinea, West Africa, around this time. The Koreans invent an iron-clad ship.

1599

1599

爱尔兰叛军击败埃塞克斯伯爵；双方达成停战协议。中国入侵缅甸。伦敦环球剧院建成。西班牙画家委拉斯凯兹出生。

Irish rebels defeat the Earl of Essex; a truce is arranged. China invades Burma. The Globe Theatre is built in London. Spanish painter Velázquez is born.

启蒙世界

The Enlightened World

1600 – 1799

1600 – 1799

 

 

1600

1600

伊丽莎白一世授予英国东印度公司特许状。天文学家第谷·布拉赫和约翰内斯·开普勒在布拉格附近合作。在北美，五个阿尔冈昆部落在瓦胡森阿卡瓦的领导下结成联盟。在日本关原之战中，德川家康击败对手，夺取政权，德川幕府或江户时代开始。大约在同一时期：宗教战争在欧洲爆发；赞比西河北岸的卡隆加王国通过象牙贸易致富；大津巴布韦被德兰士瓦、博茨瓦纳和津巴布韦的几个区域首府所取代；图西族控制了乌隆迪（布隆迪）；马赛人从东非大裂谷向南迁徙；复活节岛的雕像建造活动停止；在汤加，政治领导权从图伊·汤加王朝转移到图伊·科诺库波卢王朝。

Elizabeth I grants a charter to the English East India Company. Astronomers Tycho Brahe and Johannes Keppler work together near Prague. In North America, five Algonquin tribes form a confederacy under Wa-hun-sen-acawh. In the Battle of Sekigahara in Japan, Tokugawa Ieyasu defeats his rivals and takes power and the Tokugawa or Edo period begins. Around this time: Religious wars erupt across Europe; the Kalonga kingdom, north of the Zambezi River, becomes rich through trading ivory; Great Zimbabwe is replaced by several regional capitals in the Transvaal, Botswana and Zimbabwe; the Tutsis gain control of Urundi (Burundi); the Masai move south from the Rift Valley; statue-building dies out on Easter Island; in Tonga, political leadership passes from the Tu’i Tonga dynasty to the Tu’i Konokupolu dynasty.

1601

1601

埃塞克斯伯爵试图反抗伊丽莎白一世，最终被处决。伊丽莎白时代的《济贫法》规定各教区有责任救济穷人。

The Earl of Essex attempts rebellion against Elizabeth I and is executed. Elizabethan Poor Law charges the parishes with providing for the poor.

1602

1602

萨伏伊攻打日内瓦。荷兰东印度公司成立。波斯和土耳其之间爆发圣战，持续到1618年。在华传教的意大利耶稣会传教士利玛窦出版了中文世界地图集。

Savoy attacks Geneva. The Dutch East India Company is founded. Holy war breaks out between Persia and Turkey, lasting until 1618. Matteo Ricci, an Italian Jesuit missionary working in China, publishes a Chinese atlas of the world.

1603

1603

英国王室合并；苏格兰国王詹姆斯六世成为英格兰国王詹姆斯一世。詹姆斯一世下令逮捕沃尔特·雷利爵士，罪名是叛国。俄国人定居西伯利亚。日本将军利康被任命为幕府将军，成为无可争议的统治者；江户（东京）成为首都。德国天文学家约翰·拜耳编纂星表，他使用的星表系统至今仍在使用。

The Union of the Crowns in Britain; James VI of Scotland becomes James I of England. James orders the arrest of Sir Walter Ralegh for treason. The Russians settle Siberia. Leyasu is appointed shogun, undisputed ruler, in Japan; Edo (Tokyo) becomes the capital. German astronomer Johann Bayer catalogues the sky, employing a system still used today.

1604

1604

英格兰和西班牙媾和。法国东印度公司成立。哥萨克人在西伯利亚的托木斯克建立定居点。

England and Spain make peace. The French East India Company is founded. A Cossack settlement is founded at Tomsk in Siberia.

1605

1605

英国的火药阴谋失败。鲍里斯·戈杜诺夫的沙皇统治在俄国结束。贾汉吉尔成为印度皇帝；他同时遵循穆斯林圣人和印度教瑜伽士的教义。米格尔·德·塞万提斯的《堂吉诃德》出版。

The Gunpowder Plot fails in England. Boris Godunov’s reign as Tsar ends in Russia. Jahangir becomes Emperor of India; he follows the teachings of both Muslim saints and Hindu yogis. Don Quixote by Miguel de Cervantes is published.

1606

1606

英国通过了针对罗马天主教徒的法律。奥斯曼帝国和哈布斯堡王朝签署《齐特瓦条约》，相互承认对方的主权。俄罗斯爆发哥萨克和农民起义。西班牙航海家路易斯·瓦埃斯·德·托雷斯绕过新几内亚，抵达了如今以他名字命名的海峡。荷兰航海家威廉·扬斯发现了澳大利亚。荷兰画家伦勃朗·范·莱茵出生。

Laws are passed against Roman Catholics in England. The Ottomans and Habsburgs acknowledge each other’s sovereignty by signing the Treaty of Tsitva. Cossack and peasant uprisings occur in Russia. Luis Vaez de Torres from Spain sails around New Guinea and reaches the straits now named after him. Dutch navigator Willem Jansz sights Australia. Dutch painter Rembrandt van Rijn is born.

1607

1607

詹姆斯敦殖民地在弗吉尼亚州建立，这是英国在北美的第一个永久性定居点。儒家思想成为德川幕府政治和日本社会的主要力量。

Jamestown Colony, the first permanent English settlement in North America, is founded in Virginia. Confucianism becomes the main force in Tokugawa politics and Japanese society.

1608

1608

德国新教联盟由腓特烈四世建立。加拿大魁北克城由法国移民建立。伽利略·伽利莱制造了一架望远镜，并于1610年观测到了木星的卫星。

The Protestant Union is formed in Germany by Frederick IV. Quebec in Canada is founded by French settlers. Galileo Galilei builds a telescope and in 1610, observes Jupiter’s satellites.

1609

1609

十二年休战协定实际上确保了荷兰的独立。天主教联盟成立，与新教联盟对立。意大利人伽利略·伽利莱证实太阳是宇宙的中心。约翰内斯·开普勒发表了他的前两条行星运动定律。蓝色清真寺在君士坦丁堡建成。图文并茂的百科全书《三财百科》在中国出版。

The Twelve Years’ Truce virtually ensures independence for the Netherlands. The Catholic League is formed in opposition to the Protestant Union. Italian Galileo Galilei confirms that the Sun is the centre of the universe. Johannes Keppler publishes his first two laws of planetary motion. The Blue Mosque is built in Constantinople. The San-ts’ai t’u-hui, an illustrated encyclopedia, is published in China.

1610

1610

亨利·哈德逊探索了哈德逊湾。茶叶传入欧洲。托马斯·哈里奥特发现了太阳黑子。

The Hudson Bay is explored by Henry Hudson. Tea is introduced to Europe. Thomas Harriot discovers sunspots.

1611

1611

苏格兰和英格兰殖民者在阿尔斯特定居。古斯塔夫·阿道夫大帝成为瑞典国王。詹姆斯一世授权的《圣经》版本完成。

Scottish and English colonists settle in Ulster. Gustavus Adolphus the Great becomes king of Sweden. James I’s authorized version of the Bible is completed.

1612

1612

在英国，异教徒最后一次被处以火刑。在日本，基督徒遭受迫害（直至1639年）。萨法维王朝重新征服了阿塞拜疆。弗吉尼亚殖民者开始种植烟草作为经济作物。

Heretics are burned at the stake for the last time in England. Christians are persecuted in Japan (until 1639). The Safavids reconquer Azerbaijan. Tobacco is grown as a commercial crop by Virginia colonists.

1613

1613

米哈伊尔一世成为俄罗斯沙皇，罗曼诺夫王朝建立。特兰西瓦尼亚王子贝特伦·加博尔在匈牙利掌权。天花和麻疹肆虐美国原住民，从佛罗里达向北蔓延。波瓦坦族酋长的女儿波卡洪塔斯在弗吉尼亚州詹姆斯敦被俘。伦敦环球剧院毁于火灾。

Michael I becomes Tsar of Russia; the Romanov dynasty begins. Transylvanian prince, Bethlen Gabor, comes to power in Hungary. Smallpox and measles ravage Native Americans from Florida northward. Native American Powhatan chief’s daughter, Pocahontas, is captured at Jamestown, Virginia. In London, the Globe theatre is destroyed by fire.

1614

1614

苏格兰数学家约翰·纳皮尔出版了对数表。

The Scottish mathematician John Napier publishes tables of logarithms.

1615

1615

中国北方部落开始组建满族军事组织。明代山水画家董其昌在中国工作。

Northern Chinese tribes begin to form Manchus, military organizations. Ming landscape artist Dong Qichang is working in China.

1616

1616

沃尔特·雷利爵士出狱后，率领探险队寻找黄金国。荷兰水手威廉·舒滕绕过合恩角。威廉·巴芬发现了加拿大的巴芬湾。波卡洪塔斯与她的英国丈夫一起航行到英国。

Sir Walter Ralegh, released from prison, leads an expedition to find El Dorado. Dutch sailor William Schouten rounds Cape Horn. William Baffin discovers Baffin’s Bay in Canada. Pocahontas sails to England with her English husband.

1617

1617

莫卧儿皇帝贾汉吉尔授予托马斯·罗爵士在印度港口城市设立仓库的权利，这标志着英国在印度享有贸易优势的开始。

Sir Thomas Rowe is granted the right by Emperor Jahangir to maintain warehouses in port cities in India, marking the beginning of the trading advantage enjoyed by the English in India.

1618

1618

三十年战争爆发，除英国外，几乎整个欧洲都卷入了战争。法国探险家保罗·伊贝尔抵达廷巴克图。

The thirty Years’ War begins, involving almost all of Europe except Britain. The French explorer Paul Imbert reaches Timbuktu.

1619

1619

美国第一届议会在詹姆斯敦召开。荷兰人几乎垄断了摩鹿加群岛和其他印度尼西亚岛屿的香料贸易。第一批奴隶抵达弗吉尼亚。英国人威廉·哈维发现了血液循环。

The first American parliament meets at Jamestown. The Dutch establish a virtual monopoly of the spice trade in the Moluccas and other Indonesian islands. The first slaves arrive in Virginia. Englishman William Harvey discovers the circulation of the blood.

1620

1620

恩东戈女王恩津加继续在安哥拉与葡萄牙人作战。加勒比海诸岛在1635年之前被英国、荷兰和法国从西班牙手中夺取。日本放松了与外界接触的限制政策。清教徒先驱乘坐“五月花号”前往美洲。荷兰人科尼利厄斯·德雷贝尔发明了人力潜艇。

Queen Nzinga of Ndongo continues the struggle against the Portuguese in Angola. The Caribbean Islands are captured from Spain by the English, the Dutch and the French over a period ending in 1635. The Japanese relax their policy of restricting contact with the outside world. The Pilgrim Fathers sail to America in the Mayflower. The Dutchman Cornelius Drebbel invents a human-powered submarine.

1621

1621

荷属西印度群岛公司成立。里加被瑞典控制。

The Dutch West Indies Company is founded. Riga comes under Swedish control.

1622

1622

詹姆斯一世解散了英国议会。西班牙占领了瓦尔泰利纳山口，随后与法国开战。奥斯曼二世遇刺后，改革派穆拉德四世成为奥斯曼苏丹。美洲原住民开始对弗吉尼亚的定居点进行长达十年的袭击。

James I dissolves the English Parliament. Spain occupies the Valtelline Pass; war follows with France. The reforming Murad IV becomes Ottoman sultan following the assassination of Osman II. Native Americans begin ten years of attacks on the settlements in Virginia.

1624

1624

红衣主教黎塞留成为法国首相。英国殖民者抵达印度东部。弗吉尼亚成为英国的直辖殖民地。教皇公开焚烧马丁·路德翻译的《圣经》。英国数学家威廉·奥特雷德发明了计算尺。

Cardinal Richelieu becomes First Minister in France. English settlers arrive in eastern India. Virginia becomes a crown colony. The pope publically burns Martin Luther’s translation of the Bible. William Oughtred, an English mathematician, invents the slide rule.

1625

1625

查理一世成为英格兰国王并解散议会。丹麦国王克里斯蒂安四世向神圣罗马帝国皇帝斐迪南二世宣战。荷兰人雨果·格劳秀斯出版了《战争与和平法》，该书成为国际法的基础。奥斯曼帝国通货膨胀严重。达荷美王国建立。法国人开始在加勒比地区定居。

Charles I becomes king of England and dissolves Parliament. Christian IV of Denmark enters the war against the Holy Roman Emperor, Ferdinand II. Dutchman Hugo Grotius publishes De Jure Belli ac Pacis, which becomes the basis of international law. There is rampant inflation in the Ottoman Empire. The kingdom of Dahomey is founded. The French begin to settle in the Caribbean.

1626

1626

在德绍战役中，天主教军队击败了新教徒。克里斯蒂安四世在卢特尔战役中战败。荷兰人以价值60荷兰盾的贸易商品（约合24美元）从美洲原住民勒纳佩人手中购买了曼哈顿岛。

In the Battle of Dessau, Catholic forces defeat the Protestants. Christian IV loses the Battle of Lutter. The Dutch buy Manhattan Island from the Native American Lenape for 60 guilders worth of trade goods (about $24).

1627

1627

拉罗谢尔的胡格诺教徒被黎塞留围困。哈布斯堡王朝在波西米亚的世袭统治得到确认。帝国军队征服了德国大部分新教地区。满清军队入侵朝鲜。海因里希·舒茨创作了歌剧《达芙妮》，该剧被认为是第一部歌剧。

The Huguenots in La Rochelle are besieged by Richelieu. The hereditary rule of the Habsburgs is confirmed in Bohemia. Imperial troops subdue much of Protestant Germany. The Manchus overrun Korea. Heinrich Schütz writes Dafne, reckoned to be the first opera.

1628

1628

英国颁布了《权利请愿书》；议会限制了国王的权力。胡格诺派向黎塞留投降，失去了政治权力。英国在孟加拉建立了贸易站。荷兰占领了爪哇岛和摩鹿加群岛。

The Petition of Right is created in England; Parliament curtails the king’s powers. The Huguenots surrender to Richelieu, losing political power. An English trading post is established in Bengal. The Dutch occupy Java and the Moluccan Islands.

1629

1629

查理一世解散议会，亲自统治至1640年。神圣罗马帝国皇帝斐迪南二世与丹麦和挪威国王克里斯蒂安四世签署《吕贝克条约》。斐迪南二世颁布《归还法令》，允许天主教徒收回新教徒的土地。马萨诸塞州成立。意大利建筑师乔瓦尼·布兰卡发明了蒸汽轮机，但并未将其建造出来。

Charles I dissolves Parliament and, until 1640, rules personally. The Treaty of Lübeck is signed between Ferdinand II, Holy Roman Emperor, and Christian IV of Denmark and Norway. Ferdinand II issues the Edict of Restitution, allowing Catholics to reclaim Protestant lands. Massachusetts is founded. Italian architect Giovanni Branca invents a steam turbine, but does not build it.

1630

1630

瑞典国王古斯塔夫·阿道夫加入对抗斐迪南二世的战争。土耳其人攻占哈马丹。英国清教徒在马萨诸塞湾建立殖民地；从英国到马萨诸塞的移民潮由此开始。

Gustavus Adolphus of Sweden enters the war against Ferdinand II. The Turks capture Hamadan. English Puritans set up a colony at Massachusetts Bay; migration begins from England to Massachusetts.

1631

1631

荷兰画家伦勃朗·范·莱茵开始了其创作力最旺盛的时期，在接下来的20年里几乎每年都创作一幅杰作。

The Dutch painter Rembrandt van Rijn begins his most productive period, painting a masterpiece almost annually for the next 20 years.

1632

1632

瑞典国王古斯塔夫·阿道夫取得胜利，但在吕岑战役中阵亡；克里斯蒂娜女王继位。奥斯曼帝国统治者穆拉德四世处决了持有异端观点的文学和文化人士。英国人将葡萄牙人逐出孟加拉。沙贾汗开始在印度建造泰姬陵，并于1653年竣工。

Gustavus Adolphus of Sweden is victorious, but dies in the Battle of Lützen; Queen Christina takes the throne. In the Ottoman Empire, Murad IV executes literary and cultural figures with unorthodox views. The English drive the Portuguese from Bengal. Shah Jahan begins work on the Taj Mahal in India; it is completed in 1653.

1633

1633

伽利略因宣扬哥白尼学说而被定罪。

Galileo is convicted of teaching Copernican doctrine.

1635

1635

斐迪南废除了归还法令，并与萨克森媾和；大多数新教统治者接受了该条约。法国向西班牙宣战。荷兰人在锡兰建立了定居点。伦敦和爱丁堡之间开通了邮政服务。

Ferdinand revokes the Edict of Restitution and makes peace with Saxony; most Protestant rulers accept the treaty. France declares war on Spain. Dutch settlements are established in Ceylon. A postal service is set up between London and Edinburgh.

1636

1636

哈佛大学成立于马萨诸塞州。

Harvard College is founded in Massachusetts.

1637

1637

英国开始限制移民进入美洲殖民地。在日本，岛原之乱导致葡萄牙人被驱逐，基督教被禁止。《中真》 ——一部中国技术百科全书——出版。笛卡尔写下“我思故我在”。

The English begin to restrict immigration to the American colonies. In Japan, the Shimbara Rebellion leads to the expulsion of the Portuguese and the banning of Christianity. Ch’ung-chen, an encyclopedia of Chinese technology, is published. Descartes writes ‘I think, therefore I am’.

1638

1638

苏格兰长老会签署《庄严盟约》。斐迪南三世成为神圣罗马帝国皇帝。土耳其人攻占巴格达。基督教在日本被彻底根除。第一台印刷机传入美洲。俄罗斯探险家穿越西伯利亚抵达太平洋。

Scottish Presbyterians sign the Solemn League and Covenant. Ferdinand III becomes Holy Roman Emperor. The Turks capture Baghdad. Christianity is completely stamped out in Japan. The first printing press reaches America. Russian explorers reach the Pacific Ocean, having crossed Siberia.

1639

1639

第一次主教战争爆发于查理一世与苏格兰教会之间。奎宁首次在欧洲用于治疗发烧。英国人在印度马德拉斯建立殖民地。哥萨克人向太平洋沿岸推进。奥斯曼帝国行政长官埃夫利亚·切莱比开始游历帝国各地，并在《游记》中记录了他的旅程。维吉利奥·马佐基和马可·马拉佐利创作的第一部喜歌剧《谁能承受痛苦，谁就能获得希望》在罗马首演。

The First Bishops’ War occurs between Charles I and the Scottish Church. Quinine is used for the first time in Europe to combat fever. English settlements are set up in Madras in India. The Cossacks advance to the Pacific coast. Ottoman administrator Evliya Chelebi begins to travel throughout the empire, describing his journeys in Travels. The first comic opera, Chi Soffre Speri by Virgilio Mazzocchi and Marco Marazzoli, premieres in Rome.

1640

1640

英国第二次主教战争以《里彭条约》的签订而结束。长期议会召开（直至1660年）。葡萄牙脱离西班牙获得独立。加纳建立凡特王国。焦炭首次从煤炭中提炼出来。奥斯曼苏丹马德·易卜拉欣用毛皮装饰宫殿。《海湾诗篇集》是英国殖民地出版的第一本书。

The Second Bishops’ War in Britain ends with the Treaty of Ripon. The Long Parliament takes place (until 1660). Portugal gains independence from Spain. A Fante state is founded in Ghana. Coke is first produced from coal. The Ottoman Sultan Mad Ibrahim lines his palace with fur. The Bay Psalm Book is the first book published in the English colonies.

1641

1641

在爱尔兰天主教徒起义中，3万名新教徒遭到屠杀。荷兰人占领了马来半岛的马六甲。法国哲学家勒内·笛卡尔撰写了《第一哲学沉思录》。英国开始生产棉布。

In a Catholic revolt in Ireland, 30,000 Protestants are massacred. The Dutch capture Malacca on the Malay Peninsula. The French philospher, René Descartes writes Meditations on First Philosophy. England produces cotton cloth.

1642

1642

1647年，英国爆发保皇党（骑士党）与议会党（圆颅党）之间的内战。朱尔·马扎林枢机主教接替黎塞留成为法国首席大臣。阿巴斯二世统治波斯，直至1666年；他是萨法维王朝最后一位伟大的建筑家和艺术赞助人。加拿大蒙特利尔由法国人建立。伦敦的剧院被清教徒关闭。莫里哀在巴黎创办了一个剧团，后来发展成为法兰西喜剧院。法国哲学家布莱兹·帕斯卡发明了加法器。

Civil war erupts in England between Cavaliers (Royalists) and Roundheads (Paliamentarians), lasting until 1647. Cardinal Jules Mazarin succeeds Richelieu as French Chief Minister. Shah Abbas II comes to power in Persia until 1666; he is the last great Safavid builder and patron of the arts. Montreal, in Canada, is founded by the French. London theatres are closed by the Puritans. Molière starts a theatre group in Paris that evolves into the Comédie Française. The French philosopher Blaise Pascal invents an adding machine.

1643

1643

英国议会签署《庄严盟约》。路易十四成为法国国王。法国在罗克鲁瓦战役中击败西班牙。丹麦和瑞典争夺波罗的海霸权。意大利物理学家托里切利发明了气压计。

The Solemn League and Covenant is signed by the English Parliament. Louis XIV becomes king of France. France defeats Spain in the Battle of Rocroi. Denmark and Sweden fight for Baltic supremacy. Italian physicist Torricelli invents the barometer.

1644

1644

奥利弗·克伦威尔赢得马斯顿荒原战役。满清王朝在中国建立政权，一直持续到1912年。荷兰人在毛里求斯定居。荷兰航海家阿贝尔·塔斯曼抵达塔斯马尼亚和新西兰。

Oliver Cromwell wins the Battle of Marston Moor. The Manchu (Ta Ch’ing) dynasty takes over in China, lasting until 1912. The Dutch settle Mauritius. Dutch navigator Abel Tasman reaches Tasmania and New Zealand.

1645

1645

克伦威尔组建新模范军；议会军赢得纳西比战役。威尼斯与奥斯曼土耳其为争夺克里特岛控制权而爆发坎迪亚战争。巴西人开始将荷兰人逐出巴西殖民地，并于1654年取得胜利。满清军队屠杀了中国扬州城的居民。清政府建立后，汉族人被强制留辫子，即剃光头，后脑勺留一条辫子。

Cromwell forms his New Model Army; Parliamentarians win the Battle of Naseby. The Candian War between Venice and Ottoman Turks for control of Crete begins. The Brazilians begin to force the Dutch from colonial Brazil, succeeding by 1654. The Manchus massacre the population of the Chinese city of Yangzhou. Following the installation of the Qing government, the Han Chinese are forced to wear the queue, a shaved head with a single braid at the back.

1646

1646

查理一世向苏格兰人投降。巴哈马群岛被英国殖民。

Charles I surrenders to the Scots. The Bahamas are colonized by the English.

1647

1647

查理一世被移交给英国议会；他逃脱后与苏格兰人秘密缔结条约。美国第一个公立学校系统在马萨诸塞州建立。

Charles I is handed over to the English Parliament; he escapes and makes a secret treaty with the Scots. The first public school system in America is established in Massachusetts.

1648

1648

苏格兰入侵英格兰，在普雷斯顿潘斯战役中被克伦威尔击败。法国爆发了反对马扎林统治的五年叛乱——弗隆德运动。《威斯特伐利亚和约》结束了三十年战争，荷兰共和国和瑞士共和国获得承认。乔治·福克斯创立了教友会（贵格会）。

Scotland invades England and is defeated by Cromwell at the Battle of Prestonpans. The Frondes, five years of revolts, take place against Mazarin’s rule in France. The Treaty of Westphalia ends the Thirty Years’ War; the Dutch and Swiss republics are recognized. George Fox founds the Society of Friends (Quakers).

1649

1649

英格兰和苏格兰国王查理一世被处决；英联邦成立；英格兰共和国持续到1660年。农奴制在俄罗斯完全确立。

Charles I of England and Scotland is executed; the Commonwealth is founded; England is a republic until 1660. Serfdom is completely established in Russia.

1650

1650

查理二世登陆苏格兰并被拥立为王。葡萄牙人在赞比西地区与穆斯林交战。埃塞俄比亚驱逐了葡萄牙传教士和外交官。第一座罗马天主教堂在北京落成。英国人开始饮用从中国进口的茶叶；咖啡馆风潮在法国、英国和德国兴起。

Charles II lands in Scotland and is proclaimed king. The Portuguese fight with Muslims in the Zambezi region. Ethiopia expels Portuguese missionaries and diplomats. The first Roman Catholic church is opened in Beijing. The English begin to drink tea, imported from China; the coffee house phenomenon begins in France, England and Germany.

1651

1651

查理二世入侵英格兰，但在伍斯特战役中战败，逃往法国。哲学家托马斯·霍布斯撰写了《利维坦》，为君主制辩护。意大利天文学家乔瓦尼·里乔利绘制了月球地图。

Charles II invades England but loses the Battle of Worcester and flees to France. Philosopher Thomas Hobbes writes Leviathon, a defence of monarchy. Italian astronomer Giovanni Riccioli creates a map of the Moon.

1652

1652

英国和荷兰共和国开战。荷兰人在南非建立了开普敦。

England and the Dutch Republic go to war. The Dutch found Cape Town in South Africa.

1653

1653

克伦威尔解散了残余议会；他成为英格兰护国公。

Cromwell dismisses the Rump Parliament; he becomes Lord Protector of England.

1654

1654

英国和荷兰共和国签署了《威斯敏斯特条约》。葡萄牙人从荷兰手中夺取了巴西。布莱兹·帕斯卡和皮埃尔·德·费马创立了概率论。

England and the Dutch Republic sign the Treaty of Westminster. The Portuguese take Brazil from the Dutch. Blaise Pascal and Pierre de Fermat create a theory of probability.

1655

1655

英国从西班牙手中夺取牙买加。瑞典向波兰宣战并占领华沙。

The English capture Jamaica from Spain. Sweden declares war on Poland and occupies Warsaw.

1656

1656

俄罗斯、丹麦和神圣罗马帝国向瑞典宣战。威尼斯人在达达尼尔海峡击溃了土耳其舰队。荷兰人从葡萄牙人手中夺取了锡兰的科伦坡。荷兰科学家克里斯蒂安·惠更斯发现了土星环。

Russia, Denmark and the Holy Roman Empire declare war on Sweden. The Venetians rout the Turkish fleet off the Dardanelles. The Dutch take Colombo in Ceylon from the Portuguese. The rings of Saturn are discovered by Dutch scientist Christian Huygens.

1657

1657

新阿姆斯特丹（后来的纽约）的犹太人被赋予市民的权利，但不得公开进行宗教活动。德川光邦开始编纂他的巨著《大日本史》。

Jews in New Amsterdam (later New York) are granted the rights of burghers, but may not worship in public. Tokugawa Mitsukuni begins the compilation of his huge history of Japan, Dai Nihon shi.

1658

1658

克伦威尔去世，其子理查德继位。在沙丘战役中，英法联军击败西班牙，英军攻占敦刻尔克。莫卧儿王朝最后一位伟大的皇帝奥朗则布登基。

The death of Cromwell; he is succeeded by his son, Richard. In the Battle of the Dunes, England and France defeat Spain; England gains Dunkirk. Emperor Aurangzeb, the last great Mughal emperor, comes to power.

1659

1659

英国军队迫使理查德·克伦威尔辞职，残余议会得以恢复。《比利牛斯条约》确立了法国和西班牙之间的边界。

The English army forces Richard Cromwell to resign and the Rump Parliament is restored. The Treaty of the Pyrenees establishes the border between France and Spain.

1660

1660

查理二世复辟英国王位。莫莱·拉希德恢复摩洛哥苏丹国。波兰将利沃尼亚割让给瑞典。在印度次大陆，莫卧儿帝国鼎盛时期。塞缪尔·佩皮斯开始撰写日记。伦敦皇家学会成立，旨在促进科学发展。英国和德国的舞台上首次出现了女性演员。

Charles II is restored to the English throne. Mawlay-al-Rashid restores the sultanate of Morocco. Poland cedes Livonia to Sweden. In the Indian subcontinent, the Mughal Empire is at its most powerful. Samuel Pepys begins writing his diary. The Royal Society of London is chartered to promote the sciences. The first female players appear on the stage in England and Germany.

1661

1661

马扎林去世；路易十四成为法国的绝对君主。俄罗斯和瑞典媾和，并归还了对方的所有占领地。英国占领了孟买。康熙皇帝扩张了中国疆域，书籍和学术蓬勃发展。

The death of Mazarin; Louis XIV becomes absolute monarch in France. Russia and Sweden make peace and restore all conquests to each other. The English acquire Bombay. Emperor Kangxi extends the Chinese Empire, and books and scholarship flourish.

1662

1662

克里斯托弗·雷恩设计了他的第一座建筑。

Christopher Wren designs his first building.

1663

1663

英国国王查理二世授予北卡罗来纳州土地用于定居。

Charles II of England grants land for settlement in North Carolina.

1664

1664

英国人从荷兰人手中夺取了新阿姆斯特丹，并将其更名为纽约。荷兰人强迫泰国国王授予他们鹿皮出口和与中国进行海上贸易的独家权利。

The English capture New Amsterdam from the Dutch and rename it New York. The Dutch force the king of Thailand to give them sole rights to deerskin exports and seaborne trade with China.

1665

1665

伦敦爆发大瘟疫。第二次英荷战争爆发。牛顿发现万有引力。卡莱布·奇沙特莫克成为第一位获得哈佛大学学位的美洲原住民。扬·维米尔创作了《戴珍珠耳环的少女》。

The Great Plague hits London. The Second Anglo-Dutch War begins. Newton discovers gravity. Caleb Cheeshatemauk is the first Native American to obtain a degree from Harvard. Jan Vermeer paints the Girl with a Pearl Earring.

1666

1666

伦敦大火摧毁了这座城市的许多地区。安东尼奥·斯特拉迪瓦里在意大利克雷莫纳的工作室生产了第一批带有签名的斯特拉迪瓦里小提琴。

The Great Fire of London destroys large parts of the city. Antonio Stradivari’s workshop produces the first signed Stradivarius violins in Cremona in Italy.

1667

1667

荷兰舰队在梅德韦河击败英国舰队。权力继承战争；法国入侵西班牙尼德兰。

The Dutch fleet defeats the English on the Medway. The War of Devolution; France invades the Spanish Netherlands.

1668

1668

英格兰、荷兰和瑞典组成三国同盟对抗法国。西班牙承认葡萄牙独立。继承战争结束；法国保住了在佛兰德斯的占领地。英国东印度公司控制了孟买。

The Triple Alliance of England, the Netherlands and Sweden is created against the French. Spain recognizes Portugal’s independence. The end of the War of Devolution; France retains its conquests in Flanders. The English East India Company controls Bombay.

1669

1669

威尼斯将克里特岛割让给土耳其。印度皇帝奥朗则布禁止印度教。伦勃朗去世。

Venice surrenders Crete to Turkey. Aurangzeb, Emperor of India, bans the Hindu religion. Rembrandt dies.

1670

1670

威廉二世成为荷兰统治者。波兰和土耳其为争夺乌克兰的控制权而开战。俄罗斯爆发农民和哥萨克起义。法国人在塞内加尔定居。阿散蒂各部族在非洲黄金海岸统一；奥塞·图图成为领袖，建立了阿散蒂帝国。哈德逊湾公司成立。克里斯托弗·雷恩进入其创作力最旺盛的时期，设计了超过50座建筑，其中包括圣保罗大教堂。大约在同一时期，剧作家阿芙拉·贝恩成为第一位以写作谋生的英国女性。

William II becomes ruler of the Netherlands. Poland and Turkey go to war for control of the Ukraine. Peasant and Cossack uprisings occur in Russia. The French settle in Senegal. Ashanti clans unify on Africa’s Gold Coast; Osei Tutu becomes leader, founding the Ashanti Empire. The Hudson’s Bay Company is founded. Christopher Wren enters his most prolific period, designing more than 50 buildings, including St Paul’s Cathedral. Around this time, playwright Aphra Behn is the first English woman to make a living as a writer.

1672

1672

《宣誓法案》剥夺了天主教徒和非国教徒在英国担任公职的权利。第三次英荷战争爆发。法国军队入侵尼德兰南部。

The Test Act deprives Catholics and Nonconformists of the right to hold public office in England. The Third Anglo-Dutch War begins. French troops invade southern Netherlands.

1673

1673

为反抗清朝统治，中国南方各省脱离清政府，三藩之战爆发。波士顿邮路连接波士顿和费城之间的各定居点。

In a revolt against the Qing, China’s southern provinces break away and the War of the Three Feudatories begins. The Boston Post Road links settlements between Boston and Philadelphia.

1674

1674

神圣罗马帝国为保卫荷兰而向法国宣战。扬三世击败土耳其人和哥萨克人后成为波兰国王。

The Holy Roman Empire declares war on the French in defence of the Dutch. Jan III becomes king of Poland after defeating the Turks and the Cossacks.

1675

1675

美洲原住民袭击了新英格兰的定居者。戈特弗里德·莱布尼茨阐述了微积分。格林尼治天文台在伦敦建立。马修·洛克创作了歌剧《普赛克》，这是现存第一部英国歌剧。

Native Americans attack settlers in New England. Gottfried Leibniz describes differential and integral calculus. Greenwich Observatory is established in London. Matthew Locke composes Psyche, the first surviving English opera.

1676

1676

根据《祖拉夫诺条约》，土耳其获得乌克兰。印度爆发锡克教叛乱。

In the Treaty of Zuravno, Turkey gains the Ukraine. Sikh rebellions take place in India.

1677

1677

俄罗斯与土耳其开战。本笃·德·斯宾诺莎逝世；这位宗教哲学家在欧洲知识分子中拥有广泛的追随者。

Russia goes to war with Turkey. Benedicte de Spinoza dies; a religious philosopher with a wide following of European intellectuals.

1678

1678

泰特斯·奥茨虚构了​​一个天主教阴谋，意图推翻英格兰国王查理二世。约翰·班扬创作了《天路历程》。

An imaginary Catholic plot to overthrow Charles II of England is invented by Titus Oates. John Bunyan writes The Pilgrim’s Progress.

1679

1679

英国的《人身保护令》确保未经审判不得监禁。越南和柬埔寨开战；越南占领湄公河三角洲。

The Act of Habeas Corpus in England ensures no imprisonment without trial. Vietnam and Cambodia go to war; Vietnam takes the Mekong Delta.

法国探险家路易·亨内平神父抵达加拿大尼亚加拉大瀑布。

Father Louis Hennepin, a French explorer, reaches the Niagara Falls in Canada.

1680

1680

法国占领了斯特拉斯堡、卢森堡和洛林。西非的阿散蒂王国崛起。布图阿王国在津巴布韦平原繁荣发展；葡萄牙人被驱逐到赞比西河谷，并向东撤退。大约在同一时期，马赛人向非洲南部扩张；日本俳句诗人芭蕉正值鼎盛时期。

France occupies Strasbourg, Luxemburg and Lorraine. The Ashanti kingdom in West Africa rises to prominence. The Butua kingdom flourishes on the Zimbabwe plains; the Portuguese are driven into the Zambezi Valley, and eastwards. Around this time, the Masai expand southwards in Africa; Basho, the Japanese haiku poet, is at the height of his popularity.

1681

1681

北美的一块领土，即宾夕法尼亚，被授予英国贵格会教徒威廉·佩恩。

Territory in North America, known as Pennsylvania, is granted to the English Quaker, William Penn.

1682

1682

彼得大帝成为俄罗斯沙皇。土耳其和奥地利开战。井原西鹤创作了《一个风流男人的生活》，这是“浮世绘”文学的代表作之一，“浮世绘”一词用来描述1600年至1867年日本江户时代的文化。

Peter the Great becomes Tsar of Russia. Turkey and Austria go to war. Ihara Saikaku writes The Life of an Amorous Man, an example of the literature of ‘the floating world’, a term used to describe the culture of Edo period Japan which lasts from 1600 to 1867.

1683
