Queen Victoria of Britain is proclaimed empress of India. The Turks put down a Bulgarian uprising with great cruelty. Serbia and Montenegro are defeated by Turkey. Famine in the Deccan, southern India kills more than five million. General George Custer is defeated and killed at the Battle of Little Big Horn. Mark Twain publishes Tom Sawyer. Japan recognizes Korean independence. In the United States, Alexander Graham Bell invents the telephone. Pierre-Auguste Renoir paints Le Bal au Moulin de la Galette. Tchaikovsky writes Swan Lake. Wagner’s The Ring Cycle is performed in full at the Bayreuth Festival. Johannes Brahms writes his First Symphony.

1877

1877

日本萨摩藩叛乱爆发，传统武士阶级的最后抵抗被击败。美国发明家托马斯·爱迪生发明了唱片机。

The Satsuma rebellion in Japan; the last stand of the traditional samurai class is defeated. US inventor Thomas Edison invents the record-player.

1878

1878

柏林会议结束了俄土战争，罗马尼亚、塞尔维亚和黑山获得独立。第二次阿富汗战争：英国入侵阿富汗以对抗俄罗斯的影响力。新喀里多尼亚人反抗法国统治。爱迪生发明了白炽灯泡。伦敦出现了第一盏电灯。

The Congress of Berlin ends the Russo-Turkish War; independence for Romania, Serbia and Montenegro. The Second Afghan War: the British invade Afghanistan to counter Russian influence. The New Caledonians rebel against the French. Edison invents the incandescent lightbulb. The first electric street lighting appears in London.

1879

1879

法国完成了对阿尔及利亚的征服。智利、秘鲁和玻利维亚之间的太平洋战争持续到1894年。祖鲁人与英国开战；英国在伊桑德尔瓦纳战役中战败，但在乌伦迪战役中取得胜利。F·W·伍尔沃斯开设了他的第一家“五分一角”商店。

The French complete the conquest of Algeria. The War of the Pacific between Chile, Peru and Bolivia lasts until 1894. The Zulus go to war with the British; the British are defeated at Isandlwana but victorious at Ulundi. F.W. Woolworth opens his first ‘5 and dime’ store.

1880

1880

欧洲列强瓜分非洲的开端。法国吞并塔希提岛，将其变为殖民地。澳大利亚最著名的丛林大盗内德·凯利被处以绞刑，成为民间英雄。柴可夫斯基创作了《1812序曲》。

The beginning of the European Scramble for Africa. France annexes Tahiti as a colony. Australia’s most famous bushranger, Ned Kelly, is hanged and becomes a folk hero. Tchaikovsky writes the 1812 Overture.

1881

1881

俄国沙皇亚历山大二世遇刺身亡；其子亚历山大三世继位。突尼斯成为法国保护国。犹太人首次迁徙至巴勒斯坦。怀亚特·厄普参与了亚利桑那州OK牧场枪战。西班牙艺术家巴勃罗·毕加索出生。

Tsar Alexander II of Russia is assassinated; his son, Alexander III, takes the throne. Tunisia becomes a French protectorate. The first migration of Jews to Palestine. Wyatt Earp takes part in the gunfight at the OK Corral in Arizona. Spanish artist Pablo Picasso is born.

1882

1882

德国、奥地利和意大利组成三国同盟。英国军队炮轰并占领亚历山大港。比利时吞并刚果。美国不法之徒杰西·詹姆斯被击毙。安东尼·高迪设计的圣家堂开始建造，但至今尚未完工。

The Triple Alliance is formed between Germany, Austria and Italy. British forces bombard and occupy Alexandria. Belgium acquires the Congo. US outlaw Jesse James is killed. Antoni Gaudi’s Church of La Sagrida Familia is begun; it is still unfinished.

1883

1883

在太平洋战争中，玻利维亚失去了海岸线。德国工程师戈特弗里德·戴姆勒发明了一种便携式发动机，这为汽车的诞生奠定了基础。布鲁克林大桥竣工。格拉斯哥成立了男童军旅。东方快车首航。

Bolivia loses its coastline to Chile in the War of the Pacific. German engineer Gottfried Daimler creates a portable engine that leads to the automobile. The Brooklyn Bridge is completed. The Boys Brigade is founded in Glasgow. The Orient Express makes its first journey.

1884

1884

柏林会议将非洲瓜分给欧洲列强。苏丹喀土穆围城战开始。德国占领喀麦隆。慈禧太后解散了中国最高议事会议。牛津英语词典（OED）第一版出版。马克·吐温创作了《哈克贝利·费恩历险记》。穿过伦敦格林威治的本初子午线（0°经度）被确立。

A conference in Berlin divides Africa between the European powers. The siege of Khartoum in the Sudan begins. Germany takes control of Cameroon. Dowager Empress Cixi sacks the grand council of China. The first edition of the Oxford English Dictionary (OED) is published. Mark Twain writes The Adventures of Huckleberry Finn. The prime meridian (0° longitude), running through Greenwich in London, is established.

1885

1885

塞尔维亚与保加利亚开战并战败。在苏丹，穆斯林领袖马赫迪从埃及手中夺取了喀土穆；戈登将军阵亡。印度国大党成立；争取自治的运动开始。在南部非洲的德兰士瓦发现了黄金。巴布亚新几内亚的金矿被开采。第三次缅缅战争爆发；英国吞并缅甸。法国赠送的自由女神像抵达纽约。世界上第一座摩天大楼在芝加哥建成。加拿大太平洋铁路开通。吉尔伯特和沙利文创作了歌剧《米卡多》。

Serbia goes to war with Bulgaria and is defeated. In Sudan, Muslim leader the Mahdi takes Khartoum from Egypt; General Gordon is killed. The foundation of the Indian Congress Party; the campaign for home rule begins. Gold is discovered in the Transvaal in southern Africa. Goldfields are opened up in Papua New Guinea. The Third Burmese War; Britain annexes Burma. The Statue of Liberty, a gift from France, arrives in New York. The world’s first skyscraper is built in Chicago. The Canadian Pacific railway opens. Gilbert and Sullivan write The Mikado.

1886

1886

阿帕奇族酋长杰罗尼莫在逃亡多年后向美军投降。可口可乐由药剂师约翰·斯蒂斯·彭伯顿博士发明。

Apache war chief Geronimo surrenders to the US army after being on the run for years. Coca-Cola is invented by pharmacist Dr John Stith Pemberton.

1887

1887

保加利亚选举科堡的斐迪南为国王，成为巴尔干半岛的领头羊。法国入侵突尼斯。戈特弗里德·戴姆勒发布了他的第一辆汽车。

Bulgaria elects Ferdinand of Coburg as king; it becomes the leading Balkan state. France invades Tunisia. Gottfried Daimler unveils his first automobile.

1888

1888

威廉二世成为德国皇帝。巴西解放了奴隶。苏格兰兽医约翰·博伊德·邓禄普获得了充气轮胎的专利。英格兰成立了足球联赛。开膛手杰克在伦敦杀害了五名女性。文森特·梵高割掉了自己的一块耳朵。埃米尔·贝利纳获得了留声机的专利。施特劳斯创作了交响诗《唐璜》。

William II becomes Kaiser (emperor) of Germany. Slaves are freed in Brazil. Scottish vet John Boyd Dunlop patents the pneumatic tyre. In England, the Football League is formed. Jack the Ripper kills five women in London. Vincent van Gogh cuts off a piece of his ear. The gramophone is patented by Emil Berliner. Strauss writes the symphonic poem, Don Juan.

1889

1889

革命性的青年土耳其党组织在伊斯坦布尔成立；佩德罗二世被军队叛乱推翻；巴西成为共和国。意大利控制了厄立特里亚。马列托亚·劳佩帕成为萨摩亚国王。日本通过了明治宪法；1890年举行了第一次大选。埃菲尔铁塔在巴黎落成。俄罗斯画家马克·夏加尔出生。

The revolutionary Young Turk organization is founded in Istanbul; Pedro II is deposed by army revolt; Brazil becomes a republic. Italy takes control of Eritrea. Malietoa Laupepa becomes king of Samoa. The Meiji constitution is adopted in Japan; the first general election takes place in 1890. The Eiffel Tower opens in Paris. Russian painter Marc Chagall is born.

1890

1890

奥托·冯·俾斯麦被免去德国总理职务。东非的阿拉伯奴隶贸易逐渐消失。美国原住民的抵抗运动在南达科他州伤膝河大屠杀中结束，200名原住民惨遭杀害。美国成为世界领先的工业强国。大约在同一时期，斯特林堡、契诃夫和萧伯纳正在创作现实主义戏剧。福斯桥通车。文森特·梵高开枪自杀，几天后去世。

Otto von Bismarck is dismissed as German chancellor. The Arab slave trade in East Africa is disappearing. Native American resistance in America comes to an end when 200 are massacred at Wounded Knee, South Dakota. The United States becomes the world’s leading industrial power. Around this time, Strindberg, Chechov and Shaw are writing realistic dramas. The Forth Bridge is opened. Vincent van Gogh shoots himself and dies a few days later.

1891

1891

葡萄牙共和革命爆发。在俄罗斯，成千上万的犹太人被迫迁入隔都。智利爆发内战。西伯利亚铁路开始修建。詹姆斯·奈史密斯发明了篮球。托马斯·爱迪生获得了收音机的专利。纽约卡内基音乐厅落成开放。

The Portuguese Republican Revolution breaks out. In Russia, thousands of Jews are forced into ghettos. Civil war breaks out in Chile. Construction begins on the Trans-Siberian railroad. Basketball is invented by James Naismith. The radio is patented by Thomas Edison. Carnegie Hall opens in New York.

1892

1892

阿瑟·柯南·道尔出版了《福尔摩斯探案集》。

Arthur Conan Doyle publishes The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes.

1893

1893

法国征服老挝。新西兰成为第一个赋予女性选举权的国家。巴黎启用了第一批汽车牌照。爱德华·蒙克创作了《呐喊》。德沃夏克创作了《自新世界》。

France conquers Laos. New Zealand becomes the first country to give women the vote. The first car number plates are used in Paris. Edvard Munch paints The Scream. Dvoˇrák composes ‘From the New World’.

1894

1894

俄罗斯末代沙皇尼古拉二世登基。法国在西非达荷美（贝宁）建立保护国。甲午战争爆发，日本获胜并占领朝鲜。德雷福斯事件在法国爆发。伦敦塔桥开放。

Nicholas II, the last Tsar of Russia, takes the throne. The French set up a protectorate in Dahomey (Benin), West Africa. The First Sino-Japanese War; the Japanese win and occupy Korea. The Dreyfus Affair begins in France. London’s Tower Bridge opens.

1895

1895

詹姆逊突袭南非德兰士瓦。在法国，卢米埃尔兄弟发明了电影放映机。约翰·哈维·凯洛格发明了玉米片。古列尔莫·马可尼发明了无线电报。奥斯卡·王尔德的戏剧《不可儿戏》首演；同年晚些时候，王尔德因“鸡奸和严重猥亵罪”被判处两年监禁。威廉·康拉德·伦琴发现了X射线。匈牙利犹太人西奥多·赫茨尔呼吁建立犹太家园，即犹太国。俄罗斯科学家康斯坦丁·齐奥尔科夫斯基提出了太空飞行理论，其中包括多级火箭。

The Jameson Raid into the Transvaal in South Africa is carried out. In France, the Lumière brothers invent the film projector. John Harvey Kellog invents cornflakes. Guglielmo Marconi invents wireless telegraphy. OIscar Wilde’s play, The Importance of Being Earnest, is first performed; later this year, Wilde is sentenced to two years in prison for ‘sodomy and gross indecency’. Wilhelm Conrad Röntgen discovers the x-ray. Hungarian Jew Theodor Herzl calls for a Jewish homeland in The Jewish State. Russian scientist Konstantin Tsiolkovsky develops a theory of space flight, including a multi-stage rocket.

1896

1896

埃塞俄比亚皇帝梅内利克在阿杜瓦战役中击败意大利军队，确保了埃塞俄比亚的独立。英国说服马来各邦组成联邦。历史上最短的战争——英桑战争爆发，仅持续了45分钟。淘金者涌向加拿大育空地区的克朗代克金矿。阿尔弗雷德·诺贝尔的遗嘱设立了诺贝尔和平奖、科学奖和文学奖。第一届现代奥林匹克运动会在雅典举行。

Emperor Menelik of Ethiopia defeats the Italians in the Battle of Adowa, securing an independent Ethiopia. The British persuade the Malay states to form a federation. The shortest war in history takes place, the Anglo-Zanzibar War; it lasts 45 minutes. Miners rush to the gold fields of the Klondike in the Yukon area of Canada. Alfred Nobel’s will establishes the Nobel Prizes for peace, science and literature. The first modern Olympic Games are held in Athens.

1897

1897

穆斯塔法·卡米尔组建埃及民族党，旨在摆脱英国殖民统治。新西兰实行八小时工作制和养老金制度。布拉姆·斯托克出版《德古拉》。维多利亚女王庆祝登基六十周年钻禧。

The Egyptian National Party is formed by Mustafa Kamil to rid the country of the British. New Zealand introduces an eight-hour working day and old age pensions. Bram Stoker publishes Dracula. Queen Victoria celebrates her Diamond Jubilee.

1898

1898

美国吞并夏威夷。美西战争爆发；西班牙给予古巴独立；美国将波多黎各、关岛和菲律宾纳入殖民地。在中国，慈禧太后镇压了改革运动。在法国，玛丽·居里和皮埃尔·居里发现了镭。在英国，亨利·林德菲尔德成为世界上首例车祸死亡事件的受害者。英国雕塑家亨利·摩尔出生。

The United States annexes Hawaii. The Spanish–American War; Spain gives Cuba independence; the United States takes Puerto Rico, Guam and the Philippines as colonies. In China, Dowager Empress Cixi crushes attempts at reform. In France, Marie and Pierre Curie discover radium. In England, Henry Lindfield becomes the world’s first fatality from an automobile accident. English sculptor Henry Moore is born.

1899

1899

寇松勋爵就任印度总督。布尔战争在南非爆发，交战双方为阿非利卡人和英国人；马弗京围城战开始。法国宣布对东南亚老挝实行保护。萨摩亚被美国和德国瓜分。第一部《海牙公约》签署。费利克斯·霍夫曼获得阿司匹林专利。在法国，阿尔弗雷德·德雷福斯获得赦免。

Lord Curzon becomes viceroy of India. The Boer War breaks out between the Afrikaners and the British in southern Africa; the Siege of Mafeking begins. France proclaims a protectorate in Laos, south-east Asia. Samoa is divided between the United States and Germany. The first Hague Convention is signed. Felix Hoffmann patents Aspirin. In France, Alfred Dreyfus is pardoned.

现代世界

The Modern World

1900 – 2007

1900 – 2007

 

 

1900

1900

维多利亚女王在位64年后去世；爱德华七世继位。

Queen Victoria dies after reigning for 64 years; she is succeeded by Edward VII

世界人口超过15亿。英国工党成立；拉姆齐·麦克唐纳被任命为党总书记。德国海军法引入了一项为期20年的远洋舰队建造计划，旨在与英国海军竞争。布尔战争中，马弗京在被围困217天后获救；英国吞并德兰士瓦和奥兰治自由邦，并占领比勒陀利亚和约翰内斯堡。东非布干达王国由卡巴卡（国王）统治，并接受英国的建议。西非爆发阿散蒂起义；英国吞并阿散蒂。俄罗斯吞并满洲。中国义和团运动被镇压。新西兰吞并库克群岛。英国控制汤加的对外关系。国际仲裁法院在海牙成立。西格蒙德·弗洛伊德的《梦的解析》标志着精神分析学的诞生。贾科莫·普契尼的歌剧《托斯卡》首演。在美国，布朗尼相机随处可见。西贝柳斯的《芬兰颂》在赫尔辛基首演。

The population of the world is more than 1½ billion. The Labour Party is founded in Britain; Ramsay MacDonald is appointed secretary. German naval law introduces a 20-year building programme for a high seas fleet to compete with the British Navy. In the Boer War, Mafeking is relieved after 217 days; Britain annexes the Transvaal and the Orange Free State and captures Pretoria and Johannesburg. Buganda, East Africa, is ruled by the Kabaka, or king, with British advice. An Ashanti rising occurs in West Africa; Britain annexes Ashanti. Russia annexes Manchuria. The Boxer Rebellion in China against the Qing emperor is put down. New Zealand annexes the Cook Islands. Britain takes control of Tonga’s external relations. The international court of arbitration is created at The Hague. Sigmund Freud’s Interpretation of Dreams signals the birth of psychoanalysis. Giacomo Puccini’s opera Tosca is performed for the first time. In the United States, the Brownie camera is widely available. Jean Sibelius’s Finlandia premieres in Helsinki.

1901

1901

法国开始实行政教分离。俄国社会革命党（布尔什维克）成立。美国总统威廉·麦金莱遇刺身亡；西奥多·罗斯福继任总统。古巴成为美国保护国。澳大利亚联邦成立。巴黎地铁开通运营。英国下水第一艘潜艇。鲁德亚德·吉卜林出版《吉姆》。巴勃罗·毕加索进入蓝色时期。肾上腺素被分离出来。拉格泰姆爵士乐开始流行。马可尼首次成功发射跨大西洋无线电信号。

Church and State begin to separate in France. The Russian Social Revolutionary Party (Bolsheviks) is founded. US President William Mackinlay is assassinated; Theodore Roosevelt becomes president. Cuba becomes a US protectorate. The Commonwealth of Australia is founded. The Metro subway opens in Paris. Britain launches its first submarine. Rudyard Kipling publishes Kim. Pablo Picasso enters his Blue Period. The adrenalin hormone is isolated. Ragtime jazz gains popularity. Marconi transmits the first transatlantic radio signal.

1902

1902

德国、意大利和奥匈帝国三国同盟续约。埃及阿斯旺大坝建成。伊本·沙特攻占利雅得，沙特阿拉伯王国由此诞生。《韦尔切尼欣条约》结束了第二次布尔战争，英国击败布尔人。澳大利亚妇女获得选举权。英日同盟成立。中国与英国、美国与日本签订了一系列商业条约。

The Triple Alliance between Germany, Italy and Austria-Hungary is renewed. The first Aswan Dam is built in Egypt. Ibn Saud captures Riyadh, beginning the creation of Saudi Arabia. The Treaty of Verceniging ends the second Boer War in South Africa; Britain defeats the Boers. Women are allowed to vote in Australia. The Anglo-Japanese Alliance is formed. A series of commercial treaties are entered into by China and Britain, United States and Japan.

1903

1903

塞尔维亚国王亚历山大遇刺身亡。豪萨兰的索科托哈里发国被英国吞并。巴拿马脱离哥伦比亚。奥维尔·莱特和威尔伯·莱特在北卡罗来纳州基蒂霍克进行动力飞行。在英国，艾米琳·潘克赫斯特创立了全国妇女社会政治联盟。伦敦出现了第一批机动出租车。亨利·詹姆斯出版了《大使》。理查德·史黛夫设计了第一批泰迪熊，并以美国总统西奥多·罗斯福的名字命名。首次跨大西洋无线电广播播出。首届环法自行车赛举行。

Alexander, king of Serbia is assassinated. The Sokoto caliphate in Hausaland is taken over by Britain. Panama secedes from Colombia. Orville and Wilbur Wright make a powered flight at Kitty Hawk, North Carolina. In Britain, Emmeline Pankhurst founds the National Women’s Social and Political Union. The first motor taxis appear in London. Henry James publishes The Ambassadors. Richard Steiff designs the first teddy bears, named for President Teddy Roosevelt. The first transatlantic radio broadcast is made. The first Tour de France cycle race is held.

1904

1904

英国和法国签署了《英法协约》。日俄战争爆发，历史上首次出现堑壕战。法国建立了法属西非联邦。美国结束了对古巴的占领。巴拿马运河开始动工。太平洋战争结束后，玻利维亚和智利达成最终协议。伊斯梅尔·蒙特斯就任玻利维亚总统，推行社会和政治改革。英国探险家弗朗西斯·荣赫鹏爵士探索西藏并攻占拉萨。英国开始实行酒吧和酒馆的许可证制度。劳斯莱斯公司在英国成立。安东·契诃夫创作了《樱桃园》。比阿特丽克斯·波特出版了《彼得兔》。电影《火车大劫案》时长12分钟，是当时最长的电影。詹姆斯·巴里创作的《彼得·潘》在伦敦首演。爱德华·埃尔加创作了《威风堂堂进行曲》。

The Entente Cordiale is signed between Britain and France. The Russo-Japanese War begins and involves trench warfare for the first time. The French create the federation of French West Africa. The United States ends its occupation of Cuba. Work begins on the Panama Canal. A final settlement is agreed between Bolivia and Chile after the War of the Pacific. Ismael Montes becomes president of Bolivia, introducing social and political reforms. The British explorer Sir Francis Younghusband explores Tibet and captures Lhasa. Licensing laws for pubs and bars are introduced in Britain. The Rolls-Royce Company is founded in Britain. Anton Chechov writes The Cherry Orchard. Beatrix Potter publishes Peter Rabbit. The film The Great Train Robbery is the longest moving picture to-date at 12 minutes. J.M. Barrie’s Peter Pan is performed for the first time in London. Edward Elgar composes ‘Pomp and Circumstance’.

1905

1905

新芬党在都柏林成立。俄国爆发总罢工，革命失败；《十月宣言》中做出了一些有限的改革。德皇威廉二世访问丹吉尔，引发了与法国的危机。挪威脱离瑞典，选举哈康七世为国王。在克里特岛，希腊人反抗土耳其统治。日俄战争中，俄军在旅顺港投降；《朴茨茅斯条约》结束了这场造成10万人死亡的战争；俄国将满洲割让给日本。俄国发生严重饥荒；到1908年，有2000万人饿死。孟加拉的分割加剧了民族主义情绪。英属新几内亚成为澳大利亚的属地，并更名为巴布亚。中国废除了有着1300年历史的科举制度。伦敦开始运营公共汽车。毕加索从西班牙来到巴黎，开启了他的粉红时期。弗朗茨·莱哈尔创作了轻歌剧《风流寡妇》。阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦提出了狭义相对论。霓虹灯开始出现。印度发生地震，造成两万人死亡。拉斯维加斯建城。

Sinn Féin is founded in Dublin. General strike and a failed revolution in Russia; limited reforms are granted in the October Manifesto. Kaiser William II of Germany visits Tangier and provokes a crisis with France. Norway breaks away from Sweden and elects King Haakon VII. In Crete, the Greeks revolt against Turkish rule. In the Russo-Japanese War, the Russian army surrenders at Port Arthur; the Treaty of Portsmouth ends the war in which 100,000 die; Russia cedes Manchuria to Japan. There is severe famine in Russia; 20 million are starving by 1908. The partitioning of Bengal increases nationalist feelings. British New Guinea becomes a possession of Australia, and is named Papua. The 1,300-year-old civil service exam system in China is abolished. The first buses operate in London. Pablo Picasso arrives in Paris from Spain and begins his Pink Period. Franz Lehar writes his operetta, The Merry Widow. Albert Einstein formulates the special theory of relativity. Neon signs begin to appear. A total of 20,000 die in an earthquake in India. Las Vegas is founded.

1906

1906

维苏威火山爆发，对那不勒斯造成大范围破坏。

Mount Vesuvius erupts causing widespread damage to Naples.

英国自由党政府上台。俄国第一届国家杜马（代表机构）召开会议。波斯爆发自由主义革命。古巴在自由主义起义后被美国军队占领。首届法国大奖赛举行。克莱门斯·冯·皮尔凯提出“过敏”一词。英国第一艘现代战列舰“无畏号”下水。旧金山发生地震，造成约3000人死亡；香港发生海啸，造成10000人死亡。“SOS”成为国际通用的遇险信号。

A Liberal government comes to power in Britain. The first Russian Duma (representative body) meets. A liberal revolution takes place in Persia. Cuba is occupied by US forces following a liberal revolt. The first French Grand Prix motor race is held. Clemens von Pirquet introduces the term ‘allergy’. The first modern battleship, HMS Dreadnought, is launched in Britain. An earthquake kills around 3,000 in San Francisco, and 10,000 die in a tsunami in Hong Kong. SOS becomes the international signal for distress.

1907

1907

在第二次海牙和会上，德国反对军备限制。俄英协约和英法俄三国协约反对由德国、奥匈帝国和意大利组成的三国同盟。第二届和第三届大杜马会议在俄罗斯举行。英国和俄罗斯瓜分伊朗。内罗毕成为英属东非（今肯尼亚）的首都。金融家摩根大通阻止了美国银行挤兑。新西兰成为大英帝国的自治领。菲律宾举行首次选举。在英国，罗伯特·贝登堡创立了童子军运动。亨利·马蒂斯创造了“立体主义”一词，并在巴黎举办了第一次立体主义展览。E·M·福斯特创作了《看得见风景的房间》。肯尼斯·格雷姆出版了《柳林风声》。贝拉·巴托克创作了他的第一弦乐四重奏。胡佛吸尘器被发明出来。

Germany opposes arms limitation at the Second Hague Peace Conference. Entente Cordiale between Russia and Britain and Triple Entente between Britain, France and Russia opposes the Triple Alliance formed by Germany, Austro-Hungary and Italy. The Second and Third Dumas are held in Russia. Britain and Russia partition Iran. Nairobi becomes capital of British East Africa (now Kenya). A run on American banks is checked by financier J.P. Morgan. New Zealand becomes a dominion of the British Empire. The Philippines holds its first elections. In Britain, Robert Baden-Powell founds the Boy Scout movement. Henri Matisse invents the term ‘Cubism’ and the first Cubist exhibition is staged in Paris. E.M. Forster writes A Room with a View. Kenneth Graeme publishes The Wind in the Willows. Bela Bartok composes his String Quartet No. 1. The Hoover vacuum cleaner is invented.

1908

1908

克里特岛并入希腊。奥地利吞并波斯尼亚和黑塞哥维那。保加利亚宣布脱离土耳其独立，并拥立斐迪南一世为帝。葡萄牙国王卡洛斯一世遇刺身亡。土耳其爆发青年土耳其党革命。俄罗斯支持波斯成功发动反革命。德兰士瓦印度抗议运动领袖圣雄甘地获释。刚果自由邦更名为比属刚果。权倾朝野的中国皇太后慈禧太后逝世。通用汽车公司成立。伊莎多拉·邓肯成为广受欢迎的舞蹈表演艺术家。杰克·约翰逊成为拳击史上首位黑人重量级世界冠军。南非联邦成立。卡拉布里亚和西西里岛发生地震，造成15万人死亡，是欧洲历史上最强烈的地震。

Crete unifies with Greece. Austria annexes Bosnia and Herzegovina. Bulgaria declares independence from Turkey and declares Ferdinand I emperor. Carlos I of Portugal is assassinated. The Young Turk revolution takes place in Turkey. A successful counter-revolution in Persia is supported by Russia. Mahatma Gandhi, leader of the Indian protest movement in the Transvaal, is released from prison. Congo Free State becomes the Belgian Congo. The powerful Chinese Empress Dowager Tz’u His dies. The General Motors Corporation is founded. Isadora Duncan becomes a popular interpreter of dance. Jack Johnson becomes boxing’s first black heavyweight world champion. The Union of South Africa is created. An earthquake in Calabria and Sicily kills 150,000; the most violent earthquake ever in Europe.

1909

1909

亨利·福特开始采用流水线技术生产廉价汽车；最终生产了1500万辆T型福特汽车。

Henry Ford starts to produce cheap cars using assembly line technology; 15 million Model T Fords are eventually produced.

土耳其苏丹被推翻，其弟穆罕默德五世继位。胶木开始商业化生产。美国探险家罗伯特·皮里抵达北极。英国探险家欧内斯特·沙克尔顿发现磁南极。英国开始实行养老金制度。特拉维夫建城。路易·布莱里奥飞越英吉利海峡。

The Sultan of Turkey is overthrown and replaced by his brother, Muhammad V. Bakelite is manufactured commercially. US explorer Robert Peary reaches the North Pole. British explorer Ernest Shackleton finds the magnetic South Pole. Old age pensions are introduced in Britain. Tel Aviv is founded. Louis Bleriot flies across the English Channel.

1910

1910

乔治五世成为英国国王。葡萄牙成为共和国。黑山成为独立王国。南非成为大英帝国的自治领。日本吞并朝鲜。探戈舞在欧洲和美国流行起来。哈雷彗星被观测到。托马斯·爱迪生演示了有声电影。齐柏林飞艇首次飞行。伊戈尔·斯特拉文斯基的芭蕾舞剧《火鸟》由佳吉列夫的俄罗斯芭蕾舞团在巴黎首演。瓦西里·康定斯基发明了抽象绘画。

George V becomes king of Britain. Portugal becomes a republic. Montenegro becomes an independent kingdom. South Africa becomes a dominion of the British Empire. Japan annexes Korea. The tango becomes popular in Europe and the United States. Halley’s Comet is observed. Thomas Edison demonstrates talking motion pictures. The first Zeppelin airship flight takes place. Igor Stravinsky’s ballet, The Firebird, is danced for the first time by Diaghilev’s Ballets Russes in Paris. Wassily Kandinsky invents abstract painting.

1911

1911

阿加迪尔危机爆发，德国炮舰“豹”号驶入摩洛哥阿加迪尔港，加剧了德国和英国之间的紧张关系。意大利占领的黎波里后，与土耳其开战。墨西哥革命爆发，总统波菲里奥·迪亚斯被推翻。新西兰建立了全民军事训练体系。孙中山领导反抗满清的起义，建立了中华民国。挪威人罗尔德·阿蒙森成为第一个到达南极点的人。欧内斯特·卢瑟福发展出他的原子结构理论。《蒙娜丽莎》被盗，于1913年归还。施特劳斯的歌剧《玫瑰骑士》在德累斯顿首演。

The Agadir crisis, when the German gunship Panther entrers the port of Agadir in Morocco, heightens tension between Germany and Britain. Italy goes to war with Turkey after occupying Tripoli. The Mexican Revolution; President Porfirio Diaz is overthrown. Universal military training is established in New Zealand. Sun Yat-sen leads a rebellion against the Manchus and forms a Chinese republic. Norwegian Roald Amundsen, becomes the first person to reach the South Pole. Ernest Rutherford develops his atomic structure theory. The Mona Lisa is stolen; it is returned in 1913. Strauss’s Der Rosenkavalier premieres in Dresden.

1912

1912

第四届俄罗斯杜马。第一次巴尔干战争：保加利亚、希腊、黑山和塞尔维亚与土耳其交战。阿尔巴尼亚宣布脱离土耳其独立。法国在摩洛哥建立保护国。亚利桑那州和新墨西哥州成为美国的一个州。阿根廷实行普选制。南非非洲人国民大会成立。中国清朝灭亡；中华民国成立；国民党成立。日本大正时代开始。埃德温·布拉登伯格发明了制造玻璃纸的方法。吉姆·索普在斯德哥尔摩奥运会上表现出色。纽约中央车站启用。英国皇家飞行队（后来的英国皇家空军）成立。德国医疗传教士阿尔伯特·史怀泽在法属刚果兰巴雷内开设了一家医院。卡尔·荣格出版《无意识心理学》。英国邮轮泰坦尼克号沉没，1513人遇难。罗伯特·福尔肯·斯科特船长的南极探险失败，全员遇难。美国艺术家杰克逊·波洛克出生。马塞尔·杜尚创作了《下楼梯的裸女》。乔治·布拉克发明了绘画拼贴技法。

The Fourth Russian Duma. The First Balkan War: Bulgaria, Greece, Montenegro and Serbia fight Turkey. Albania declares independence from Turkey. A French protectorate is established in Morocco. Arizona and New Mexico become US states. Universal suffrage is introduced in Argentina. The founding of the African National Congress in South Africa. The end of the Qing dynasty in China; the Republic of China is established; the Kuomintang, the Chinese Nationalist Party, is founded. The beginning of the Taisho period in Japan. Edwin Bradenberger invents a process to manufacture cellophane. Jim Thorpe is the outstanding participant in the Stockholm Olympics. Grand Central station opens in New York. The Royal Flying Corps (later the Royal Air Force) is founded in Britain. Albert Schweizer, a German medical missionary, opens a hospital in Lambarene in the French Congo. Carl Jung publishes Psychology of the Unconscious. The British liner Titanic sinks with the loss of 1,513 people. Captain Robert Falcon Scott’s expedition to the South Pole fails; all of the party die. American artist Jackson Pollock is born. Marcel Duchamp paints Nude Descending a Staircase. Georges Braque invents collage in painting.

1913

1913

爱尔兰内战威胁加剧。青年土耳其党在土耳其发动政变。巴尔干国家赢得第一次巴尔干战争；第二次巴尔干战争爆发，塞尔维亚、希腊、罗马尼亚和土耳其与保加利亚交战。伍德罗·威尔逊就任美国总统。南非政府颁布法律，将87%的土地划为白人保留地；莫罕达斯·甘地因抗议被捕。中国承认外蒙古。D·H·劳伦斯创作《儿子与情人》 。托马斯·曼出版《威尼斯之死》。尼尔斯·玻尔提出原子结构理论。贝拉·希克发现白喉免疫测试方法。拉链开始流行。印度诗人泰戈尔荣获诺贝尔文学奖。纽约军械库展览将后印象主义和立体主义引入美国。斯特拉文斯基的歌剧《春之祭》由瓦斯拉夫·尼金斯基编舞，在巴黎引发骚乱。妇女参政论者艾米莉·戴维森在埃普索姆德比大赛上扑向国王的马匹身亡。第一幅纵横字谜画刊登在《纽约世界报》上。

The threat of civil war rises in Ireland. The Young Turks stage a coup in Turkey. The Balkan states win the First Balkan War; the Second Balkan War sets Serbia, Greece, Romania and Turkey against Bulgaria. Woodrow Wilson becomes president of the United States. The South African government introduces laws to reserve 87 per cent of land for whites; Mohandas Gandhi is arrested while protesting. China recognizes Outer Mongolia. D.H. Lawrence writes Sons and Lovers. Thomas Mann publishes Death in Venice. Niels Bohr formulates the theory of atomic structure. Bela Schick discovers the diphtheria immunity test. The zip fastener becomes popular. The Indian poet, Rabindranath Tagore is awarded the Nobel Prize for Literature. The Armory Show in New York introduces post-Impressionism and Cubism to America. Stravinsky’s The Rite of Spring, choreographed by Vaslav Nijinsky, causes a riot in Paris. Emily Davison, a suffragette, dies after throwing herself under the king’s horse at the Epsom Derby. The first crossword puzzle is published in the New York World.

1914

1914

第一次世界大战

World War I

奥地利大公弗朗茨·斐迪南被波斯尼亚学生加夫里洛·普林西普（左）刺杀，引发第一次世界大战，英国、法国、俄罗斯、意大利和美国与同盟国（德国、奥匈帝国和土耳其）对抗。7月28日，奥地利入侵塞尔维亚。

Archduke Franz Ferdinand of Austria is assassinated by Bosnian student, Gavrilo Princip (left), triggering the outbreak of World War I in which Britain, France, Russia, Italy and the United States face the Central Powers, Germany, Austria-Hungary and Turkey.28 July, Austria invades Serbia.

8月4日，德国入侵比利时。

4 August, Germany invades Belgium.

8月26日，俄军在坦能堡战役中被德军击败。

26 August, the Russians are defeated by Germany at the Battle of Tannenburg.

9月5日至9日，马恩河战役；德军向巴黎的推进被阻止。

5 to 9 September, the Battle of the Marne; the German advance on Paris is halted.

9月6日至15日，马祖里湖战役；俄军从东普鲁士撤退。

6 to 15 September, the Battle of the Masurian Lakes; Russia retreats from east Prussia.

10月30日至11月24日，伊普尔战役；德国试图抵达英吉利海峡港口的尝试失败。

30 October to 24 November, the Battle of Ypres; Germany fails in its attempts to reach the Channel ports.

《爱尔兰自治法案》允许爱尔兰设立独立的议会。尼日利亚南北统一。巴拿马运河开通。加拿大太平洋铁路竣工。新西兰占领西萨摩亚。拉尔夫·沃恩·威廉姆斯创作了《云雀高飞》。

The Irish Home Rule Act allows for a separate Parliament in Ireland. Northern and southern Nigeria are united. The Panama Canal is opened. The Grand Trunk Pacific Railway is completed in Canada. New Zealand occupies Western Samoa. Ralph Vaughan Williams composes ‘The Lark Ascending’.

1915

1915

1月5日，英国开始对德国实施海上封锁。

5 January, Britain begins a naval blockade of Germany.

1916 年 4 月，加里波利战役开始，持续到 1916 年 3 月 22 日；协约国军队未能控制达达尼尔海峡。

April, The Gallipoli Campaign begins, lasting until 22 March 1916; Allied forces fail to gain control of the Dardanelles.

2月18日，德国开始对英国实施潜艇封锁。

18 February, Germany begins a submarine blockade of Britain.

4月22日至5月25日，第二次伊普尔战役；德国首次使用毒气。

22 April to 25 May, The Second Battle of Ypres; the first use of poison gas by Germany.

5月7日，英国邮轮卢西塔尼亚号沉没，造成大量平民死亡。

7 May, the sinking of the British liner Lusitania, with many civilian deaths.

5月22日，意大利加入盟军。

22 May, Italy joins the Allied powers.

10月15日，保加利亚加入同盟国。

15 October, Bulgaria joins the Central Powers.

瑞士物理学家阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦发表了广义相对论。亚历山大·格雷厄姆·贝尔打出了第一个跨大西洋电话。日本提出了一系列威胁中国主权的要求。马塞尔·杜尚创作了第一批达达主义风格的作品。雨果·容克斯在德国制造出了第一架全金属战斗机。

The Swiss physicist Albert Einstein publishes the General Theory of Relativity. Alexander Graham Bell makes the first transatlantic telephone call. Japan makes a number of demands threatening China’s sovereignty. Marcel Duchamp paints the first works in a Dada style. The first all-metal fighter aircraft is built in Germany by Hugo Junkers.

1916

1916

2月21日至7月，凡尔登战役——惨重的损失和由此导致的僵局。

21 February to July, the Battle of Verdun – appalling losses and resulting stalemate.

5月31日，日德兰海战爆发，这是一场英国和德国之间的海战。

31 May, the Battle of Jutland, a naval battle between Britain and Germany.

6月4日，勃鲁西洛夫攻势，俄军进攻失败。

4 June, the Brusilov Offensive, a failed Russian attack.

7月1日至11月18日，索姆河战役；超过一百万人丧生，英国首次在战斗中使用坦克。

1 July to 18 November, the Battle of the Somme; more than one million killed and tanks used in battle for the first time by Britain.

爱尔兰复活节起义被镇压。英国实行夏令时。阿拉伯人在汉志地区爆发反抗奥斯曼土耳其人的起义；侯赛因自立为阿拉伯国王。布尔人领袖扬·史末资领导反德战争，从肯尼亚一路推进到坦桑尼亚（德属东非）。玛格丽特·桑格在美国开设了第一家计划生育诊所。美国以2500万美元购得荷属东印度群岛（维尔京群岛）。爵士乐风靡美国。伊波利托·伊里戈延当选阿根廷总统，推行了一系列改革。

The Easter Rising is suppressed in Ireland. Daylight-saving time is introduced in Britain. The beginning of Arab revolt against the Ottoman Turks in Hijaz; Hussein proclaims himself king of the Arabs. The Boer leader Jan Smuts leads an anti-German drive from Kenya into Tanzania (German East Africa). Margaret Sanger opens the first birth control clinic in the United States. The United States purchases the Dutch East Indies (the Virgin Islands) for $25 million. The jazz craze sweeps across the United States. Hipolito Irigoyen is elected president of Argentina, bringing extensive reforms.

1917

1917

3月11日，英国从土耳其手中夺取巴格达。

11 March, Britain takes Baghdad from Turkey.

4月6日，美国对德国宣战。

6 April, the United States declares war on Germany.

7月6日，T·E·劳伦斯（“阿拉伯的劳伦斯”）指挥阿拉伯人反抗土耳其的起义。

6 July, T.E. Lawrence (‘Lawrence of Arabia’) takes command of the Arab revolt against Turkey.

7月31日，第三次伊普尔战役（又称帕斯尚尔战役）以僵局告终。

31 July, the Third Battle of Ypres, also known as Passchendaele, ends in virtual stalemate.

10月24日，卡波雷托战役；意大利战败。

24 October, the Battle of Caporetto; the Italians lose.

12月9日，英国占领耶路撒冷。

9 December, Britain takes Jerusalem.

在十月革命中，弗拉基米尔·列宁领导的布尔什维克夺取了俄国政权。《贝尔福宣言》发表；英国宣布支持在巴勒斯坦建立犹太国。拉斯·塔法里（后来的海尔·塞拉西）成为埃塞俄比亚摄政王。波多黎各成为美国领土。墨西哥通过新宪法。巴西对德国宣战。孙中山在广州建立军政府，对抗北京政府。中国对德国和奥地利宣战。阿马代奥·莫迪利亚尼创作了《蹲伏的裸女》。西格蒙德·弗洛伊德出版了《精神分析导论》。

In the October Revolution, the Bolsheviks, led by Vladimir Lenin, seize power in Russia. The Balfour Declaration; Britain announces support for a Jewish state in Palestine. Ras Tafari (later, Haile Selassie) becomes regent of Ethiopia. Puerto Rico becomes a US territory. Mexico adopts a new constitution. Brazil declares war on Germany. Sun Yat-sen establishes a military government in Guangzhou in opposition to the Beijing government. China declares war on Germany and Austria. Amadeo Modigliani paints Crouching Female Nude. Sigmund Freud publishes Introductory Lectures to Psychoanalysis.

1918

1918

3月3日，俄罗斯退出战争。

3 March, Russia withdraws from the war.

7月15日至8月2日，第二次马恩河战役。

15 July to 2 August, the Second Battle of the Marne.

11月11日，德国签署停战协定，第一次世界大战结束。

11 November, Germany signs the Armistice and World War I ends.

8月8日，盟军进攻开始；德军撤退。

8 August, the beginning of the Allied offensive; the Germans retreat.

10月24日，意大利赢得维托里奥·维内托战役；奥匈帝国投降。

24 October, Italy wins the Battle of Vittorio Veneto; Austria-Hungary surrenders.

11月7日，德国爆发革命；威廉二世退位，共和国成立。

7 November, revolution in Germany; William II abdicates and a republic is declared.

俄国沙皇尼古拉二世及其家人遇害。俄罗斯采用格里历。1920年，费萨尔埃米尔宣布成立叙利亚国并登基。委内瑞拉油田开采。萨洛特女王成为汤加女王。一场持续数年的全球性流感大流行造成数百万人死亡。英国30岁以上女性获得选举权。西班牙画家胡安·米罗的作品首次展出。美国首次发行航空邮件。

The Russian Tsar Nicholas II and his family are murdered. Russia adopts the Gregorian calendar. Emir Faisal proclaims the Syrian state and becomes king in 1920. The Venezuelan oilfields are opened. Queen Salote becomes queen of Tonga. A worldwide influenza epidemic lasting several years, kills millions. Women over 30 are given the vote in Britain.The first exhibition of the work of Spanish painter Joan Miro. The first airmail postage is introduced in the United States.

1919

1919

新芬党在爱尔兰发动叛乱。巴黎和会召开，国际联盟成立。《凡尔赛条约》使德国失去阿尔萨斯-洛林及其殖民地，并需支付赔款。《圣日耳曼条约》终结了哈布斯堡王朝，捷克斯洛伐克、波兰、南斯拉夫和匈牙利获得独立。德国通过魏玛宪法；社会主义领袖罗莎·卢森堡遇刺身亡。贝尼托·墨索里尼在意大利创立法西斯运动。阿曼努拉成为阿富汗埃米尔。欧内斯特·卢瑟福首次成功分裂原子。在英国，阿斯特夫人成为英国首位女议员。沃尔特·格罗皮乌斯在德国创立包豪斯运动。马克斯·普朗克因提出量子理论而获得诺贝尔物理学奖。

Sinn Féin lead a rebellion in Ireland. The Peace Conference begins in Paris; the founding of the League of Nations. The Treaty of Versailles means Germany loses Alsace-Lorraine and its colonies and has to pay reparations. The Treaty of St Germain ends the Habsburg monarchy, and Czechoslovakia, Poland, Yugoslavia and Hungary gain independence. Germany adopts the Weimar Constitution; socialist leader Rosa Luxemburg is murdered. Benito Mussolini founds the Fascist movement in Italy. Amanullah becomes the Amir of Afghanistan. Ernest Rutherford splits the atom for the first time. In Britain, Lady Astor becomes the first female MP. Walter Gropius founds the Bauhaus movement in Germany. Max Planck wins the Nobel Prize for Physics for introducing quantum theory.

1920

1920

爱尔兰爆发内战；北爱尔兰接受自治法案。意大利和南斯拉夫签署《拉帕洛条约》。布尔什维克赢得俄国内战。俄国和波兰开战。由于土耳其在第一次世界大战中支持德国，被迫解散奥斯曼帝国。国际联盟第一次会议召开。巴勒斯坦在英国的监督下建立犹太国家。莫罕达斯·甘地成为印度独立运动的领袖。美国开始禁酒，禁酒令持续到1933年。美国妇女获得选举权。潘乔·比利亚向墨西哥当局投降。新西兰获得对萨摩亚的委任统治权。中国发生地震，造成20万人死亡。约翰·T·汤普森获得冲锋枪“汤姆逊冲锋枪”的专利。赫尔曼·罗萨克发明了墨迹测试法。作家格特鲁德·斯坦创造了“迷惘的一代”一词，用来形容战后在巴黎生活和工作的那些心灰意冷的流亡作家，如海明威、菲茨杰拉德、舍伍德·安德森等人。牛津大学开始招收女学生。海牙成为国际法院所在地。

Civil war breaks out in Ireland; Northern Ireland accepts the Home Rule Act. The Treaty of Rapallo is signed by Italy and Yugoslavia. The Bolsheviks win the Russian civil war. Russia and Poland go to war. Turkey is forced to dissolve the Ottoman Empire as a result of its support of Germany in World War I. The first meeting of the League of Nations takes place. Palestine is established as a Jewish state under British supervision. Mohandas Gandhi becomes leader of India’s struggle for independence. Prohibition against the sale of alcohol begins in the United States and lasts until 1933. Women are given the vote in the United States. Pancho Villa surrenders to the Mexican authorities. New Zealand is given a mandate over Samoa. An earthquake in China kills 200,000 people. John T. Thompson patents the sub-machine gun, the ‘Tommy gun’. Herman Rorsach develops the inkblot test. Writer Gertrude Stein coins the phrase ‘the lost generation’ to describe the disillusioned expatriot writers Hemingway, Fitzgerald, Sherwood Anderson and others living and working in Paris after the war. Oxford University enrols female students. The Hague becomes the home of the International Court of Justice.

1921

1921

希腊进攻土耳其，但战败。土耳其民族政府在安卡拉成立。《里加条约》结束了俄波战争。列宁在俄国推行新经济政策。阿卜杜勒·克里姆率领柏柏尔人和阿拉伯人在北非对抗欧洲人。印度第一届议会召开。英国、法国、日本和美国签署《太平洋条约》。澳大利亚获得对德属新几内亚的委任统治权。胡安·包蒂斯塔·萨维德拉总统开启了玻利维亚的进步政府时期。孙中山当选中国国家主席。蒙古成为世界第二个共产主义国家。鲁道夫·瓦伦蒂诺主演电影《酋长》。阿尔伯特·卡姆莱特和卡米尔·盖兰推广了卡介苗（BCG）结核病疫苗。玛丽·斯托普斯开设了英国第一家计划生育诊所。

Greece attacks Turkey but is defeated. A Turkish National Government is established in Ankara. The Treaty of Riga ends the Russo-Polish war. Lenin introduces the New Economic Policy in Russia. Abd-el-Krim leads the Berbers and Arabs against Europeans in North Africa. The meeting of the first Indian parliament takes place. Britain, France, Japan and the United States sign the Pacific Treaty. Australia is given a mandate over German New Guinea. President Juan Bautista Saavedra begins a period of progressive government in Bolivia. Sun Yat-sen is elected president of China. Mongolia becomes the world’s second communist state. Rudolf Valentino stars in the film The Sheik. Albert Camlette and Camille Guerin introduce the BCG tuberculosis vaccine. Marie Stopes opens Britain’s first birth control clinic.

英国广播公司（BBC）成立。

The British Broadcasting Company (BBC) is founded.

1922

1922

爱尔兰自由邦成立。墨索里尼进军罗马，建立法西斯政府。苏联在俄罗斯成立。土耳其苏丹被穆斯塔法·凯末尔废黜，凯末尔于次年当选总统。埃及在福阿德国王的统治下脱离英国独立。在印度，甘地因公民不服从运动被判处六年监禁。美国制造出第一台便携式收音机和第一台车载收音机。詹姆斯·乔伊斯的《尤利西斯》和T·S·艾略特的《荒原》出版，这两部作品是现代主义文学运动的代表作。A·E·豪斯曼出版《最后的诗篇》。P·G·伍德豪斯创作了《独一无二的吉夫斯》。毕加索开启了他的抽象时期。加拿大医生班廷、贝斯特和麦克劳德首次为糖尿病患者注射胰岛素。霍华德·卡特和卡那封伯爵在卢克索附近发现了图坦卡蒙陵墓。

The Irish Free State is founded. Mussolini marches on Rome and forms a Fascist government. The Union of Socialist Soviet Republics (USSR) is established in Russia. The sultan of Turkey is deposed by Mustafa Kemal who is elected president the following year. Egypt becomes independent from Britain under King Fuad. In India, Gandhi is sentenced to six years’ imprisonment for civil disobedience. The first portable radio and first car radio are made in the United States. James Joyce’s Ulysses and T.S. Eliot’s The Waste Land are published, two examples of the new literary movement, modernism. A.E. Housman publishes Last Poems. P.G. Wodehouse writes The Inimitable Jeeves. Picasso begins his Abstract Period. Canadian doctors Banting, Best and MacLoed administer the first insulin to diabetes sufferers. Tutankhamun’s tomb is discovered near Luxor by Howard Carter and the Earl of Carnarvon.

1923

1923

英国工党首次赢得大选；拉姆齐·麦克唐纳出任首相。法国和比利时军队占领德国鲁尔区，此前比利时未能支付赔款。德国国家社会主义党创始人阿道夫·希特勒推翻巴伐利亚政府的企图失败，被监禁。普里莫·德·里维拉将军成为西班牙独裁者，直至1930年。土耳其在穆斯塔法·凯末尔总统的领导下宣布成立共和国；安卡拉取代伊斯坦布尔成为首都。外约旦在阿米尔·阿卜杜拉的领导下获得独立。罗得西亚（今津巴布韦）成为英国的自治殖民地。墨西哥匪徒和革命家潘乔·比利亚被枪手击毙。阿根廷人恩里克·特里博斯基成为第一个从法国游过英吉利海峡到达英国的人。日本发生地震，东京和横滨市中心被摧毁，共造成12万人死亡。贝西·史密斯录制了她的第一首歌《伤心蓝调》。

The first victory for the British Labour Party at a general election; Ramsay MacDonald becomes prime minister. French and Belgian troops occupy the Ruhr Valley in Germany after the latter’s failure at reparations. Adolf Hitler, founder of the National Socialist Party in Germany, fails to overthrow the Bavarian government and is imprisoned. General Primo de Rivera becomes dictator in Spain, until 1930. Turkey is declared a republic under President Mustafa Kemal; Ankara replaces Istanbul as capital. Transjordan gains independence under the leadership of Amir Abdullah. Rhodesia (modern-day Zimbabwe) becomes a self-governing British colony. Mexican bandit and revolutionary Pancho Villa is killed by gunmen. The Argentinian Enrique Triboschi becomes the first person to swim the English Channel from France to England. A total of 120,000 die in an earthquake in Japan that destroys the centres of Tokyo and Yokohama. Bessie Smith records her first song, ‘Down-Hearted Blues’.

1924

1924

弗拉基米尔·列宁逝世，约瑟夫·斯大林继任。希腊和阿尔巴尼亚成为共和国。波斯国王被废黜，礼萨·沙阿继位。甘地因健康原因获释。美国给予古巴独立。孙中山领导的、包含共产党成员的政府在中国成立。杀虫剂首次被使用。印度爆发鼠疫，造成多达25000人死亡。首届冬季奥运会在法国霞慕尼举行；夏季奥运会在巴黎举行。乔治·格什温创作《蓝色狂想曲》。弗朗茨·卡夫卡因肺结核引发的饥饿而去世。乔治·马洛里和安德鲁·欧文在珠穆朗玛峰失踪。莫里斯·拉威尔的《波莱罗舞曲》在巴黎首演。

The death of Vladimir Lenin; Joseph Stalin succeeds him. Greece and Albania become republics. The shah of Persia is deposed; he is replaced by Reza Shah. Gandhi is released from prison on medical grounds. The United States grants independence to Cuba. A government led by Sun Yat-sen, and including Communists, is installed in China. Insecticides are used for the first time. Up to 25,000 die in a plague epidemic in India. The first Winter Olympic Games are held in Chamonix in France; the Summer Olympics are held in Paris. George Gerschwin composes ‘Rhapsody in Blue’. Franz Kafka dies of starvation brought on by tuberculosis. George Mallory and Andrew Irvine disappear on Mount Everest. Maurice Ravel’s Bolero opens in Paris.

1925

1925

欧洲主要强国签署的《洛迦诺协定》旨在维护和平与稳定。土耳其总统凯末尔·阿塔图尔克推行现代化；伊斯兰教被废除国教地位；佩戴土耳其毡帽被禁止。阿卜杜勒·克里姆在摩洛哥发动的阿拉伯起义被法国和西班牙镇压。伊本·沙特建立沙特阿拉伯。南非禁止黑人、印度人和混血儿从事技术性工作；南非荷兰语成为官方语言。F·斯科特·菲茨杰拉德出版《了不起的盖茨比》。弗朗茨·卡夫卡的《审判》在他去世后出版。首个超现实主义展览在巴黎举行。巴黎巴斯德研究所发现破伤风抗毒素。美国第一家汽车旅馆在加利福尼亚州开业。阿道夫·希特勒出版《我的奋斗》。巴黎装饰艺术博览会展现了装饰艺术运动的流行。挪威首都克里斯蒂安尼亚更名为奥斯陆。

The Locarno Agreements between the major European powers aim to maintain peace and stability. The modernization of Turkey by President Kemal Attaturk; Islam is abolished as the state religion; the wearing of the fez is banned. Abd-el-Krim’s Arab uprising in Morocco is quashed by the French and Spanish. Ibn Saud creates Saudi Arabia. Blacks, Indians and people of mixed race are prevented from taking skilled jobs in South Africa; Afrikaans becomes the official language. F. Scott Fitzgerald publishes The Great Gatsby. The Trial by Franz Kafka is published posthumously. The first Surrealist exhibition takes place in Paris. The Pasteur Institute in Paris discovers anti-tetanus serum. America’s first motel opens in California. Adolf Hitler publishes Mein Kampf. The Exposition des Arts Decoratifs in Paris demonstrates the popularity of the Art Deco movement. Norway’s capital Christiana is renamed Oslo.

1926

1926

约翰·洛吉·贝尔德发明了电视。

John Logie Baird invents television.

英国爆发总罢工，试图迫使政府采取行动，制止煤矿工人工资削减和恶劣的工作条件，但最终失败。墨索里尼完全控制了意大利。葡萄牙军队推翻了政府。德国加入国际联盟。黎巴嫩共和国成立。巴拿马和美国同意在战时共同保护巴拿马运河。堪培拉成为澳大利亚首都。裕仁天皇即位。T ·E·劳伦斯（阿拉伯的劳伦斯）出版了《智慧七柱》 。A·A·米尔恩出版了《小熊维尼》。印度妇女被允许竞选公职。罗伯特·戈达德在马萨诸塞州奥本发射了第一枚液态燃料火箭。

The General Strike in Britain; an unsuccessful attempt to force the government to act against wage reduction and poor conditions for coal miners. Mussolini takes complete control of Italy. In Portugal, the army overthrows the government. Germany is admitted to the League of Nations. The republic of Lebanon is proclaimed. Panama and the United States agree to protect the Panama Canal in wartime. Canberra becomes the Australian capital. Hirohito becomes emperor of Japan. The Seven Pillars of Wisdom is published by T.E. Lawrence (Lawrence of Arabia). A.A. Milne publishes Winnie the Pooh. Indian women are allowed to stand for public office. Robert Goddard launches the first liquid-fuelled rocket from Aubuurn, Massachusetts.

1927

1927

列昂·托洛茨基被苏联共产党开除。伊拉克发现石油。沙特阿拉伯获得独立。国民党领袖蒋介石清洗共产党，在南京建立政府；中国爆发内战。弗吉尼亚·伍尔夫出版《到灯塔去》 。马塞尔·普鲁斯特的《追忆似水年华》 （A la Recherche du Temps Perdu）在他去世后出版。铁肺被发明。伊万·彼得罗维奇·巴甫洛夫发表《条件反射》。英国爆发流感，每周造成1000人死亡。美国电影艺术与科学学院成立。查尔斯·林白完成首次单人跨大西洋飞行。中国发生地震，造成20万人死亡。有声电影《爵士歌手》的上映标志着无声电影时代的结束。比利时天文学家乔治·勒梅特提出宇宙大爆炸理论。

Leon Trotsky is expelled from the Soviet Communist Party. Iraq discovers oil. Saudi Arabia gains independence. Kuomintang leader Chiang Kai-shek purges the communists and establishes a government at Nanking; civil war breaks out in China. Virginia Woolf publishes To the Lighthouse. In Search of Lost Time (A la Recherche du Temps Perdu) by Marcel Proust, is published posthumously. The iron lung is invented. Ivan Petrovich Pavlov publishes Conditioned Reflexes. A flu epidemic in Britain kills 1,000 people a week. The Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences is founded. Charles Lindbergh makes the first solo transatlantic flight. A total of 200,000 die in an earthquake in China. The talking picture The Jazz Singer, marks the end of the silent film. Belgian astronomer Georges Le Maitre proposes the Big Bang theory for the creation of the universe.

1928

1928

法国开始在德法边境修建马奇诺防线。马耳他成为英国自治领。亚历山大·弗莱明发现了青霉素。埃及国王福阿德成为独裁者。日军杀害了满洲的军事统治者。裕仁天皇即位成为日本天皇。中国国民党军队攻占北京。澳大利亚皇家飞行医生服务队成立。乔治·伊士曼在纽约放映了第一部彩色电影。奥运会在阿姆斯特丹举行。米老鼠出现在第一部有声动画片《汽船威利》中。

The French begin to build the defensive Maginot Line on the German border. Malta becomes a British dominion. Alexander Fleming discovers penicillin. King Fuad becomes dictator of Egypt. Japanese troops murder the military ruler of Manchuria. Hirohito becomes emperor of Japan. Chinese nationalists capture Beijing. In Australia, the Royal Flying Doctor Service is inaugurated. George Eastman shows the first colour motion pictures in New York. The Olympic Games take place in Amsterdam. Mickey Mouse appears in Steamboat Willie, the first cartoon to have sound.

1929

1929

美国华尔街股市崩盘；大萧条重创全球经济。

The Wall Street Stock Exchange crashes in the United States; the Great Depression devastates the global economy.

梵蒂冈国成立。斯大林启动第一个五年计划。托洛茨基被驱逐出苏联。阿拉伯人和犹太人之间的第一次重大冲突在巴勒斯坦爆发。墨西哥革命制度党（PRI）开始实行一党专政，直至20世纪90年代末。理查德·伯德完成首次飞越南极的壮举。蒋介石将共产党军队驱赶到中国农村。威廉·福克纳出版《喧哗与骚动》。欧内斯特·海明威出版《永别了，武器》。纽约现代艺术博物馆（MoMA）开幕。帝国大厦开始动工。齐柏林飞艇用时20天4小时14分钟完成环球飞行。首届奥斯卡金像奖颁奖典礼举行。

The Vatican State is created. Stalin launches his first Five Year Plan. Trotsky is expelled from the USSR. The first major conflict between Arabs and Jews takes place in Palestine. The Partido Revolutionario Institutional (PRI) begins one party rule in Mexico which lasts until the late 1990s. Richard Byrd makes the first flight over the South Pole. Chiang Kai-shek drives the communists into rural China. William Faulkner publishes The Sound and the Fury. Ernest Hemingway publishes A Farewell to Arms. The Museum of Modern Art (MOMA) opens in New York. Construction starts on the Empire State Building. The Graf Zeppelin airship circumnavigates the globe in 20 days, 4 hours and 14 minutes. The first Academy Awards are presented.

1930

1930

纳粹党在德国大选中赢得107个席位。希腊和土耳其签署《安卡拉条约》。拉斯·塔法里加冕为埃塞俄比亚皇帝，取名海尔·塞拉西。南非白人女性获得选举权。英国政府与印度各党派举行首次圆桌会议；甘地要求印度独立。热图利奥·瓦加斯成为巴西总统，并于1937年掌握独裁权力。达希尔·哈米特出版小说《马耳他之鹰》。格兰特·伍德创作画作《美国哥特式》。业余天文学家克莱德·汤博发现冥王星。帝国大厦落成开放。悉尼海港大桥两部分连接完成。首届世界杯足球赛在乌拉圭举行。

The Nazis win 107 seats in the German elections. The Treaty of Ankara is signed between Greece and Turkey. Ras Tafari is crowned emperor of Ethiopia, taking the name Haile Selassie. White women are given the vote in South Africa. The first Round Table Conference between the British government and Indian parties is held; Gandhi demands Indian independence. Getulio Vargas becomes Brazilian president, assuming dictatorial powers in 1937. Dashiel Hammett publishes The Maltese Falcon. Grant Wood paints American Gothic. The planet Pluto is discovered by amateur astronomer Clyde Tombaugh. The Empire State Building opens. The two halves of the Sydney harbour bridge are joined. The first World Cup football tournament is played in Uruguay.

1931

1931

芝加哥黑帮老大阿尔·卡彭因逃税被判入狱。

Chicago gangster Al Capone is jailed for income tax evasion.

英国放弃金本位制。《威斯敏斯特法令》使大英帝国的自治领地实行自治。西班牙国王阿方索十三世退位后，西班牙宣布成立共和国。第一条横贯非洲的铁路建成，连接安哥拉和莫桑比克。日本占领中国东北的满洲省。毛泽东成为中华民国中央执行委员会主席。托尼·施密德和弗朗茨·施密德首次登顶瑞士的马特洪峰。耶和华见证人会成立。萨尔瓦多·达利创作了《记忆的永恒》。美国工程师卡尔·扬斯基发现了无线电波。

Britain abandons the gold standard. The Statute of Westminster makes dominions of the British Empire self-governing. Spain is declared a republic after King Alfonso XIII abdicates. The first trans-African railway is completed, from Angola to Mozambique. The Japanese occupy the Chinese province of Manchuria. Mao Zedong becomes chairman of the central executive committee of the Chinese Socialist Republic. Toni and Franz Schmid make the first ascent of the Matterhorn in Switzerland. The Jehovah’s Witnesses are founded. Salvador Dali paints Persistence of Memory. American engineer Karl Jansky discovers radio waves.

1932

1932

英国给予英联邦国家贸易优惠。安东尼奥·德·奥利维拉·萨拉查成为葡萄牙独裁者。斯大林在苏联启动第二个五年计划；苏联爆发毁灭性饥荒。印度的贱民获得选举权。民主党人富兰克林·罗斯福当选美国总统。巴拉圭和玻利维亚因查科地区爆发战争（直至1935年）。暹罗（泰国）的君主专制制度终结。奥尔德斯·赫胥黎创作《美丽新世界》。旧金山金门大桥开工建设。始建于1906年的荷兰须德海排水工程竣工。

Britain gives trading preference to the Commonwealth nations. Antonio de Oliveira Salazar becomes dictator of Portugal. Stalin launches the second Five Year Plan in the USSR; there is a devastating famine. The untouchables gain voting rights in India. Democrat Franklin D. Roosevelt becomes US president. Paraguay and Bolivia go to war (until 1935) over the Chaco region. Absolute monarchy ends in Siam (Thailand). Aldous Huxley writes Brave New World. Work begins on the Golden Gate Bridge in San Francisco. The Zuider Zee drainage project, begun in 1906 in Holland, is completed.

1933

1933

纳粹领袖阿道夫·希特勒被任命为德国总理；德国退出国际联盟；所有犹太人和非纳粹作家的书籍被焚毁；第一批集中营建成。在苏联，斯大林清洗共产党。英国承认伊拉克独立；加齐国王登基。查希尔·沙阿在其父被刺杀后成为阿富汗国王。美国废除禁酒令。罗斯福推行新政。在古巴，富尔亨西奥·巴蒂斯塔·萨尔迪瓦尔成为独裁者。秘鲁总统桑切斯·切罗遇刺身亡。澳大利亚控制了南极洲的大片区域。卡尔·荣格出版《心理学与宗教》。列昂·托洛茨基出版《俄国革命史》。尼斯湖水怪被发现。

Nazi leader Adolf Hitler is appointed German chancellor; Germany withdraws from the League of Nations; all books by Jewish and non-Nazi authors are burned; the first concentration camps are built. In Russia, Stalin purges the Communist Party. Britain recognizes Iraqi independence; King Ghazi takes the throne. Zahir Shah becomes king in Afghanistan after the assassination of his father. Prohibition ends in the United States. Roosevelt introduces the New Deal. In Cuba, Fulgencio Batista y Zaldivar becomes dictator. The Peruvian president Sanchez Cherro is assassinated. Australia takes control of a large area of Antarctica. Carl Jung publishes Psychology and Religion. Leon Trotsky publishes the History of the Russian Revolution. The Loch Ness Monster is sighted.

1934

1934

希特勒成为元首；他在“长刀之夜”清洗纳粹党；他在威尼斯会见了墨索里尼。奥地利总理被纳粹杀害。从伊拉克基尔库克到叙利亚的黎波里的英国输油管道开通。土耳其妇女获得选举权。英国殖民政府镇压了加纳的激进非洲批评人士。毛泽东和朱德领导的共产党人开始了穿越中国的长征。东道主意大利队赢得了第二届世界杯冠军。

Hitler becomes Führer; he purges the Nazi Party in ‘the night of the long knives’; he meets Mussolini in Venice. The Austrian chancellor is killed by Nazis. The British oil pipeline from Kirkuk (Iraq) to Tripoli (Syria) is opened. In Turkey, women get the vote. The British colonial government of Ghana suppresses radical African critics. The communists, led by Mao Zedong and Zhu De, begin the Long March through China. Hosts Italy win the second World Cup.

1935

1935

希特勒废除《凡尔赛条约》并开始重新武装。德国通过纽伦堡法案，开始迫害犹太人；强制兵役制开始实施。希腊恢复君主制。波斯更名为伊朗。英属印度各省自1937年起获得自治权。新西兰首届工党政府当选。乔治·格什温的歌剧《波吉与贝丝》在纽约首演。罗伯特·沃森-瓦特研制出用于探测飞机的雷达设备。莫斯科地铁开通运营。匿名戒酒互助会（Alcoholics Anonymous）在纽约成立。德国拳击手马克斯·施梅林击败美国拳击手乔·路易斯，赢得世界重量级拳王头衔。

Hitler renounces the Treaty of Versailles and starts to rearm. The persecution of the Jews begins in Germany with the Nuremberg Laws; compulsory military service is introduced. The monarchy is restored in Greece. Persia changes its name to Iran. The provinces of British India are granted autonomy and self-government from 1937. The first Labour government is elected in New Zealand. Porgy and Bess, an opera by George Gershwin, opens in New York. Robert Watson-Watt builds radar equipment to detect aircraft. The Moscow subway opens. Alcoholics Anonymous is founded in New York. German boxer Max Schmelling wins the world heavyweight title from the American Joe Louis.

1936

1936

英国国王爱德华八世退位迎娶离过两次婚的沃利斯·辛普森；乔治六世继位。德国入侵法比边境的莱茵兰地区，开始修建齐格菲防线。西班牙内战爆发（持续至1939年）。罗马-柏林轴心国成立。意大利入侵并吞并埃塞俄比亚。费萨尔王子在埃及掌权。法国给予叙利亚自治权。巴勒斯坦人发动反对犹太复国主义定居点的起义。美洲第一个法西斯政权在巴拉圭上台。《土著代表法》剥夺了南非黑人的政治平等权利。蒋介石对日宣战。中国红军长征在延安结束。美国胡佛水坝竣工。戴尔·卡耐基出版《人性的弱点》。玛格丽特·米切尔出版《飘》。约翰·斯坦贝克出版《愤怒的葡萄》。英国广播公司开播电视服务。令希特勒懊恼的是，美国黑人运动员杰西·欧文斯在柏林奥运会上赢得了四枚金牌。

Edward VIII, king of Britain, abdicates to marry double divorcee, Wallis Simpson; George VI becomes king. Germany invades the Rhineland region on the French–Belgian border and starts construction of the defensive Siegfried Line. The Spanish Civil War begins (until 1939). The Rome–Berlin Axis is established. Italy invades and annexes Ethiopia. Prince Faisal takes power in Egypt. The French grant Syria home rule. Palestinians begin the Great Revolt against Zionist settlement. The first fascist regime in the Americas comes to power in Paraguay. The Representation of Natives Act denies black South Africans political equality. Chiang Ki-shek declares war on Japan. The Long March of the Chinese Red Army ends in Yanan. The Hoover Dam is completed in the United States. Dale Carnegie publishes How to Win Friends and Influence People. Margaret Mitchell publishes Gone with the Wind. John Steinbeck publishes The Grapes of Wrath. The BBC launches a television service. To Hitler’s chagrin, the black American athlete Jesse Owens wins four gold medals at the Berlin Olympics.

1937

1937

美国建筑师弗兰克·劳埃德·赖特设计了流水别墅，这是20世纪建筑的杰作。

American architect Frank Lloyd Wright designs Falling Water, a masterpiece of 20th-century architecture.

英国组建了由内维尔·张伯伦领导的联合政府；英国对德国采取绥靖政策。埃蒙·德·瓦莱拉就任爱尔兰共和国总理。德国飞机轰炸了西班牙的格尔尼卡。犹太人和阿拉伯人在巴勒斯坦交战；巴勒斯坦皇家委员会倡导建立阿拉伯国家和犹太国家。伊拉克独裁者巴克尔·西德基·帕夏将军遇刺身亡。日本入侵中国；未宣战的战争持续到1945年；超过30万中国平民被屠杀；约8万名妇女遭到强奸；日军占领了北京、天津、南京、上海和杭州；南京国民党政府逃往中国西南地区。巴勃罗·毕加索创作了《格尔尼卡》。威廉·福克纳出版了《喧哗与骚动》。华莱士·H·卡罗瑟斯为杜邦公司在特拉华州申请了尼龙专利。弗兰克·惠特尔制造了第一台喷气式发动机。兴登堡号飞艇在试图停靠新泽西州时起火爆炸。阿梅莉亚·埃尔哈特在独自飞越太平洋时失踪。温莎公爵（原英国爱德华八世）与沃利斯·辛普森夫人结婚。

A coalition government headed by Neville Chamberlain is formed in Britain; Britain adopts a policy of appeasement towards Germany. Eamonn de Valera becomes prime minister of the Republic of Ireland. German planes bomb Guernica in Spain. Jews and Arabs fight in Palestine; a Royal Commission on Palestine advocates the formation of Arab and Jewish states. The Iraqi dictator General Bakr Sidki Pasha is assassinated. Japan invades China; undeclared war is waged until 1945; more than 300,000 Chinese civilians are slaughtered; around 80,000 women are raped; the Japanese seize Peking, Tientsin, Nanjing, Shanghai and Hangchow; the Kuomintang (Nationalist People’s Party) government in Nanjing flees to south-west China. Pablo Picasso paints Guernica. William Faulkner publishes The Sound and the Fury. Wallace H. Carothers patents nylon for the Dupont Company in Delaware. Frank Whittle builds the first jet engine. The airship Hindenberg bursts into flames while trying to dock at New Jersey. Amelia Earhart disappears on a solo flight across the Pacific. The Duke of Windsor (formerly Edward VIII of Britain) marries Mrs Wallis Simpson.

1938

1938

希特勒入侵并吞并奥地利。慕尼黑危机：法国和英国同意德国瓜分捷克斯洛伐克；11月9日夜间，纳粹在德国各地发动“水晶之夜”大屠杀，袭击犹太人的住所和商铺。日本在中国南京建立傀儡政权，并退出国际联盟。沙特阿拉伯发现石油。意大利在法国赢得1938年世界杯冠军。奥森·威尔斯的广播剧《世界大战》引发大规模恐慌。拉斯洛·比罗获得圆珠笔专利。

Hitler invades and annexes Austria. The Munich crisis: France and Britain agree to let Germany partition Czechoslovakia; Kristallnacht, a pogrom against the Jews in which the Nazis attack Jewish homes and businesses, takes place across Germany during the night of 9 November. The Japanese set up a puppet regime in Nanking in China and withdraw from the League of Nations. Oil is discovered in Saudi Arabia. Italy win the 1938 World Cup in France. Orson Welles’s War of the Worlds radio broadcast causes mass panic. László Bíró patents the ballpoint pen.

1939

1939

德国吞并捷克斯洛伐克；意大利入侵阿尔巴尼亚；德国入侵波兰；英国和法国对德国宣战；俄罗斯入侵波兰；波兰被德国和俄罗斯瓜分。

Germany annexes Czechoslovakia; Italy invades Albania; Germany invades Poland; Britain and France declare war on Germany. Russia invades Poland; Poland is partitioned between Germany and Russia.

在西班牙，弗朗哥将军领导的民族主义者攻占巴塞罗那；马德里的投降标志着西班牙内战的结束。苏芬战争爆发（俄罗斯于1940年获胜）。罗伯特·孟席斯就任澳大利亚总理。土耳其发生地震，造成45000人死亡。美国伊戈尔·西科斯基制造出第一架直升机。人类血液中的Rh因子被发现。美国出现了第一批尼龙丝袜。托洛茨基奉斯大林之命被刺杀。

In Spain, the nationalists under General Franco take Barcelona; the surrender of Madrid ends the Spanish Civil War. The Russo-Finnish War is being fought (Russia wins in 1940). Robert Menzies becomes Australian prime minister. An earthquake in Turkey kills 45,000. The first helicopter is built by Igor Sikorsky in the United States. The Rh factor in human blood is discovered. The first nylon stockings appear in the United States. Trotsky is assassinated on the orders of Stalin.

1940

1940

3月27日，海因里希·希姆莱开始建造奥斯维辛集中营。

27 March, Heinrich Himmler starts the construction of the Auschwitz concentration camp.

4月9日，德国入侵丹麦和挪威。

9 April, Germany invades Denmark and Norway.

4月30日，日本加入轴心国。

30 April, Japan joins the Axis powers.

5月10日，德国入侵比利时、荷兰和卢森堡。

10 May, Germany invades Belgium, The Netherlands and Luxemborg.

5月17日，德国入侵法国。

17 May, Germany invades France.

5月27日，英国军队从法国敦刻尔克撤退。

27 May, The British army is evacuated from Dunkirk, France.

6月10日，意大利向英国和法国宣战。

10 June, Italy declares war on Britain and France.

6月14日，德军占领巴黎，法国投降。

14 June, The Germans occupy Paris and France surrenders.

7月3日，英国皇家海军摧毁了法国舰队，以阻止其落入德国人手中。

3 July, The Royal Navy destroys the French fleet to stop it falling into German hands.

7月10日，英国赢得不列颠空战，这场空战胜利阻止了德国的入侵。

10 July, Britain wins the Battle of Britain, an air victory preventing invasion by Germany.

9月7日，希特勒对伦敦的轰炸开始。

7 September, Hitler’s bombing blitz of London starts.

10月28日，意大利入侵希腊。

28 October, Italy invades Greece.

11月15日，在华沙，35万犹太人被限制在隔都内。

15 November, in Warsaw, 350,000 Jews are confined to a ghetto.

12月9日，英国对西部沙漠的意大利军队发动进攻。

9 December, Britain launches an attack on Italian forces in the Western Desert.

英国科学家研制出雷达。罗斯福总统宣布美国在二战中保持中立。叙利亚成为维希法国的一部分。意大利轰炸巴勒斯坦。日本、德国和意大利签署军事和经济条约。

British scientists develop radar. President Roosevelt declares US neutrality in World War II. Syria becomes part of Vichy France. Italy bombs Palestine. Japan, Germany and Italy sign a military and economic pact.

法国发现了拉斯科洞穴。五岁的达赖喇嘛在西藏登基。出版书籍包括：欧内斯特·海明威的《丧钟为谁而鸣》 ；雷蒙德·钱德勒的《再见，吾爱》；托马斯·沃尔夫的《你不能再回家了》；埃德蒙·威尔逊的《前往芬兰车站》 ；卡尔·荣格的《人格的解析》；阿瑟·库斯勒的《正午的黑暗》。美国展示了第一台电子显微镜。

The Lascaux Caves are discovered in France. The five-year-old Dalai Lama is enthroned in Tibet. Books published: For Whom the Bell Tolls by Ernest Hemingway; Farewell, My Lovely by Raymond Chandler; You Can’t Go Home Again by Thomas Wolfe; To the Finland Station by Edmund Wilson; The Interpretation of Personality by Carl Jung; Darkness at Noon by Arthur Koestler. The first electron microscope is demonstrated in the United States.

1941

1941

2月14日，埃尔文·隆美尔的非洲军团登陆的黎波里。

14 February, Erwin Rommel’s Afrika Korps land in Tripoli.

4月13日，斯大林与日本签署中立条约。

13 April, Stalin signs a neutrality pact with Japan.

4月26日，德军进驻雅典。

26 April, German troops march into Athens.

6月22日，德国入侵苏联。

22 June, Germany invades the USSR.

5月20日，意属东非在亚的斯亚贝巴向英国投降。

20 May, Italian East Africa surrenders to the British at Addis Ababa.

7月13日，英国与苏联签署条约。

13 July, Britain signs a pact with the USSR.

7月27日，日军进入柬埔寨、泰国和越南，并占领菲律宾巴丹半岛。

27 July, Japanese troops move into Cambodia, Thailand and Vietnam and occupy Bataan in the Philippines.

9月1日，意大利和德国入侵埃及。

1 September, Italy and Germany invade Egypt.

9月8日，列宁格勒围城战开始；1944年1月，列宁格勒围城战解除。

8 September, the Siege of Leningrad begins; it is relieved in January 1944.

9月19日，英国和苏联军队占领伊朗首都德黑兰。

19 September, British and Soviet forces take Teheran in Iran.

10月17日，东条英机将军接管日本政府。

17 October, General Tojo takes over government of Japan.

12月8日，美国对轴心国宣战。英国对芬兰、匈牙利和罗马尼亚宣战。

8 December, The United States declares war on the Axis powers. Britain declares war on Finland, Hungary and Romania.

12月7日，日本炮击了位于夏威夷珍珠港的美国舰队。

7 December, Japan bombs the US fleet in Pearl Harbour, Hawaii.

12月11日，希特勒和墨索里尼向美国宣战。

11 December, Hitler and Mussolini declare war on the United States.

12月25日，香港向日本投降。

25 December, Hong Kong surrenders to Japan.

伊朗国王礼萨·沙阿被废黜。爱德华·霍珀创作了画作《夜鹰》。奥逊·威尔斯的《公民凯恩》成为年度最卖座的电影之一。诺埃尔·考沃德创作了戏剧《欢乐的精灵》。曼哈顿计划启动，开始原子能研究。钚被发现。汉斯·哈斯开发了水下摄影技术。英国飞行员艾米·约翰逊在飞机失事中丧生。

Reza Shah of Iran is deposed. Edward Hopper paints Nighthawks. Orson Welles’s Citizen Kane is among the biggest films of the year. Noel Coward writes the play Blithe Spirit. Atomic research begins on the Manhattan Project. Plutonium is discovered. Hans Haas develops underwater photography. British aviator Amy Johnson dies when her plane crashes.

1942

1942

1月2日，日本攻占马尼拉，随后又占领新加坡、仰光、曼德拉和菲律宾。

2 January, Japan captures Manila and goes on to take Singapore, Rangoon, Mandelay, and the Philippines.

1月20日，莱因哈德·海德里希公布了他消灭欧洲1100万犹太人的计划，即“最终解决方案”。

20 January, Reinhard Heydrich unveils his plan to eliminate 11 million Jews in Europe, the ‘final solution’.

2月1日，维德孔·吉斯林被任命为挪威傀儡首相。

1 February, Vidkun Quisling is appointed puppet prime minister in Norway.

3月26日，第一批犹太人被驱逐到奥斯维辛集中营。

26 March, the first deportation of Jews to Auschwitz.

3月28日，英国皇家空军开始轰炸德国军火工厂。

28 March, the RAF begins bombing German munitions factories.

4月18日，美国飞机轰炸东京。

18 April, United States aircraft bomb Tokyo.

5月8日，美军赢得珊瑚海海战。

8 May, the Americans win the Battle of the Coral Sea.

5月27日，托布鲁克被隆美尔的军队攻陷。

27 May, Tobruk falls to Rommel’s troops.

5月31日，盖世太保领导人海德里希被捷克游击队刺杀。

31 May, Gestapo leader Heydrich is assassinated by Czech partisans.

6月7日，日军经过激战后撤出中途岛。

7 June, the Japanese withdraw from Midway Island after heavy fighting.

6月29日，德军向斯大林格勒推进。

29 June, German forces advance on Stalingrad.

8月30日，隆美尔对埃及发动攻势。

30 August, Rommel launches an offensive in Egypt.

9月6日，德军在斯大林格勒战役中战败。

6 September, the Germans are defeated in the Battle of Stalingrad.

10月30日，阿拉曼战役；隆美尔率领的德军在埃及战败。

30 October, the Battle of El Alamein; the Germans under Rommel are defeated in Egypt.

11月7日，德军撤退到利比亚。

7 November, the Germans retreat into Libya.

在印度，甘地任命贾瓦哈拉尔·尼赫鲁为继任者。米尔登霍尔宝藏，一批罗马银器，在英国萨福克郡被发现。年度电影包括迪士尼的《小鹿斑比》。年度书籍包括：让-保罗·萨特的《苍蝇》 ；阿尔贝·加缪的《局外人》； T·S·艾略特的《四个四重奏》；G·M·特里维廉的《英国社会史》 。本杰明·布里顿创作了《安魂交响曲》。恩里科·费米实现了原子裂变。美国研制出了第一台自动计算机。德国容克斯公司的马克斯·穆勒研制出了涡轮螺旋桨发动机。乐施会成立。平·克劳斯贝录制了《白色圣诞节》。

In India, Gandhi appoints Jawaharlal Nehru as his successor. The Mildenhall Treasure, a hoard of Roman silverware, is found in Suffolk, England. Films of the year include Disney’s Bambi. Books – Les Mouches by Jean-Paul Sartre; L’Étranger by Albert Camus; The Four Quartets by T.S. Eliot; English Social History by G.M. Trevelyan. Benjamin Britten composes Sinfonia da Requiem. Enrico Fermi splits the atom. The first automatic computer is developed in the United States. The turboprop engine is developed by Max Müller of Junkers in Germany. Oxfam is founded. Bing Crosby records ‘White Christmas’.

1943

1943

1月14日，丘吉尔和罗斯福在卡萨布兰卡会面。

14 January, Churchill and Roosevelt meet at Casablanca.

1月18日，苏联军队在围困列宁格勒16个月后解除围困。

18 January, the Soviets break the siege of Leningrad after 16 months.

1月23日，盟军攻占的黎波里，这是轴心国在北非的最后一个据点。

23 January, the Allies take Tripoli, the last Axis stronghold in North Africa.

1月28日，希特勒下令动员德国全体16岁至65岁的人口。

28 January, Hitler orders the mobilization of the entire German population, from 16 to 65.

1月31日，德军在斯大林格勒投降。

31 January, The Germans surrender at Stalingrad.

2月9日，日本在所罗门群岛瓜达尔卡纳尔岛的抵抗结束。

9 February, Japanese resistance ends on Guadalcanal in the Solomon Islands.

4月14日，盟军攻占突尼斯。

14 April, the Allies take Tunis.

6月1日，法国抵抗运动领导人让·穆兰被盖世太保头目克劳斯·巴比逮捕。

1 June, French resistance leader Jean Moulin is arrested by Gestapo chief, Klaus Barbie.

7月1日，美国开始收复日本占领的太平洋岛屿。

1 July, the US begins to recapture Japanese-held islands in the Pacific.

7月13日，德军在库尔斯克战役中败给了俄军。

13 July, the Germans lose the Battle of Kursk to the Russians.

7月25日，墨索里尼下台。

25 July, Mussolini falls from power.

8月17日，西西里岛被盟军攻占。

17 August, Sicily falls to the Allies.

9月3日，意大利政府投降。

3 September, the Italian government surrenders.

10月13日，意大利对德国宣战。

13 October, Italy declares war on Germany.

11月11日，轴心国军队入侵维希法国。

11 November, the Axis forces launch an invasion of Vichy France.

11月26日，苏军突破了斯大林格勒的德军防线。

26 November, the Soviets break through German lines at Stalingrad.

凯恩斯战后经济复苏计划发表。阿图罗·罗森领导的军政府在阿根廷掌权。美国画家杰克逊·波洛克举办了他的首次个人画展。皮特·蒙德里安创作了《百老汇布吉伍吉》。马克·夏加尔创作了《杂耍艺人》。

The Keynes plan for postwar economic recovery is published. A military junta, under Arturo Rawson, takes power in Argentina. American painter Jackson Pollock stages his first exhibition. Piet Mondrian paints Broadway Boogie-Woogie. Marc Chagall paints The Juggler.

1944

1944

1月4日，希特勒下令征召10岁以上的儿童。

4 January, Hitler orders the mobilization of children over the age of ten.

1月19日，苏军击败了德军对列宁格勒的围攻。

19 January, the Soviets defeat the German siege of Leningrad.

2月3日，美国军舰炮击日本百里香岛。

3 February, US warships shell the Japanese island of Paramishu.

4月24日，日军撤离新几内亚。

24 April, the Japanese evacuate New Guinea.

6月4日，盟军进入罗马。

4 June, the Allies enter Rome.

6月6日，盟军在诺曼底登陆，开始了对欧洲的入侵，德军被迫撤退。

6 June, the Allies land in Normandy, beginning the invasion of Europe and the Germans are forced to retreat.

6月15日，美国飞机轰炸日本本土。

15 June, American planes bomb the Japanese mainland.

6月25日，德怀特·艾森豪威尔少将被任命为驻欧美军总司令。

25 June, Major General Dwight Eisenhower is put in command of US forces in Europe.

7月3日，明斯克陷落，这是德国在苏联的最后一个基地。

3 July, Minsk, the last German base in the USSR, falls.

7月20日，刺杀希特勒的阴谋失败了。

20 July, a plot to blow up Hitler fails.

7月31日，德军被赶入诺曼底。

31 July, the Germans are driven into Normandy.

9月2日，盟军解放巴黎和布鲁塞尔。

2 September, the Allies liberate Paris and Brussels.

9月8日，第一枚V-2导弹击中英国。

8 September, the first V-2 missile hits England.

9月11日，盟军登陆德国领土。

11 September, the Allies arrive on German soil.

10月3日，华沙的抵抗被德军镇压。

3 October, resistance in Warsaw is crushed by the Germans.

10月25日，日本海军在莱特湾海战中战败。

25 October, the Japanese navy is defeated at the Battle of Leyte Gulf.

12月16日，在比利时，阿登战役打响，这是德国的最后一次反击。

16 December, in Belgium, the start of the Battle of the Bulge, Germany’s final counter-attack.

黎巴嫩获得独​​立。犹太组织伊尔根在梅纳赫姆·贝京的领导下，宣布起义反抗英国在巴勒斯坦的统治。田纳西·威廉姆斯创作了《玻璃动物园》。阿伦·科普兰谱写了《阿巴拉契亚之春》。让·吉拉杜出版了《夏洛的疯女人》。亨利·马蒂斯创作了《白裙》。美国人奥斯瓦尔德·艾弗里发现了DNA。

Lebanon gains independence. The Jewish organization Irgun, under Menachem Begin, proclaims a revolt against British rule in Palestine. Tennessee Williams writes The Glass Menagerie. Aaron Copeland composes Appalachian Spring. Jean Giradoux publishes The Mad Woman of Chaillot. Henri Matisse paints The White Dress. DNA is discovered by American, Oswald Avery.

1945

1945

1月17日，俄罗斯占领华沙。

17 January, Russia captures Warsaw.

2月7日，丘吉尔、斯大林和罗斯福在雅尔塔会面，讨论战后安排。

7 Febuary, Churchill, Stalin and Roosevelt meet at Yalta to discuss post-war settlements.

3月7日，盟军入侵德国。德累斯顿遭到轰炸。

7 March, the Allies invade Germany. The bombing of Dresden.

4月，盟军解放了贝尔根-贝尔森、布痕瓦尔德和达豪集中营。

April, Allied troops liberate the concentration camps at Bergen-Belsen, Buchenwald and Dachau.

4月12日，罗斯福总统逝世；哈里·S·杜鲁门继任总统。

12 April, President Roosevelt dies; Harry S. Truman becomes president.

4月28日，墨索里尼被意大利游击队处决。

28 April, Mussolini is executed by Italian partisans.

4月30日，阿道夫·希特勒自杀身亡。

30 April, Adolf Hitler commits suicide.

5月7日，德国投降。

7 May, Germany surrenders.

5月8日，欧洲胜利日。

8 May, VE (Victory in Europe) Day.

7月16日，第一颗原子弹在新墨西哥州阿拉莫戈多引爆。

16 July, the first atomic bomb is detonated at Alamogordo, New Mexico.

7月/8月，召开波茨坦会议，讨论战后解决方案。

July/August, the Potsdam Conference is held to discuss postwar settlements.

8月6日和9日，第一批原子弹分别投向广岛和长崎。

6 and 9 August, the first atomic bombs are dropped on Hiroshima and Nagasaki.

8月14日，日本投降。第二次世界大战结束。

14 August, Japan surrenders. The end of World War II.

9月8日，美国和苏联瓜分朝鲜半岛。

8 September, the United States and USSR divide Korea.

9月14日，日本胜利日。

14 September, VJ (Victory in Japan) Day.

《联合国宪章》签署。阿拉伯联盟成立，旨在阻止建立犹太国。犹太旅升起犹太旗帜。印度国大党呼吁摆脱殖民统治。印度尼西亚共和国宣告成立。弗兰克·劳埃德·赖特设计了纽约古根海姆博物馆。乔治·奥威尔的《动物庄园》和伊夫林·沃的《故园风雨后》出版。普罗科菲耶夫的芭蕾舞剧《灰姑娘》在莫斯科首演。本杰明·布里顿的歌剧《彼得·格莱姆斯》在伦敦首演。长篇唱片问世。

The United Nations Charter is signed. The Arab League is founded to fight the creation of a Jewish state. The Jewish Brigade raises the Jewish flag. The Indian Congress Party calls for freedom from colonial rule. The republic of Indonesia is proclaimed. Frank Lloyd Wright designs the Guggenheim Museum in New York. Animal Farm by George Orwell and Brideshead Revisited by Evelyn Waugh are published. Prokoviev’s ballet Cinderella opens in Moscow. Benjamin Britten’s Peter Grimes premieres in London. The long-playing record is introduced.

1946

1946

国际联盟解散。挪威人特里格韦·赖伊成为联合国首任秘书长。巴黎和会开幕。纽伦堡审判纳粹战犯。意大利宣布成立共和国，妇女获得选举权。匈牙利共和国成立。英国和美国在柏林达成协议，合并各自占领区。丘吉尔警告说，共产主义欧洲和非共产主义欧洲之间将出现一道“铁幕”。约旦王国获得独立。伊拉克复兴党成立。印度和巴基斯坦成为英国的自治领。美国进行原子弹试验；美国和法国在太平洋岛屿上持续进行核试验引发众怒。胡安·庇隆当选阿根廷总统。胡志明领导的越南民族主义者在印度支那与法国作战。巴克敏斯特·富勒设计了戴马克西翁住宅。

The League of Nations is ended. Norwegian Trygve Lie becomes the first Secretary-General of the United Nations. The peace conference opens in Paris. The Nuremberg Trials of Nazi war criminals take place. A republic is declared in Italy; women get the vote. The Republic of Hungary is founded. Britain and America agree to the economic merger of their zones in Berlin. Churchill warns of an ‘Iron Curtain’ between communist and non-communist Europe. The kingdom of Jordan gains independence. The Baath Party is established in Iraq. India and Pakistan become separate British dominions. The United States tests an atomic bomb; continuing US and French nuclear testing on Pacific islands causes anger. Juan Peron is elected president of Argentina. The Vietnamese nationalists, led by Ho Chi Minh, fight the French in Indo-China. Buckminster Fuller designs the Dymaxion House.

1947

1947

盟军与意大利、罗马尼亚、匈牙利、保加利亚和芬兰签署和平条约。关于德国问题的会议未能达成协议。美国国务卿乔治·马歇尔提出马歇尔计划，一项援助欧洲的方案。巴勒斯坦被分割为阿拉伯国家和犹太国家；阿拉伯人拒绝接受分割。印度获得独立；印度教的印度和穆斯林的巴基斯坦成为两个独立的自治领。缅甸获得独立。在杜鲁门主义中，美国政府承诺援助任何抵抗共产主义的政府。田纳西·威廉姆斯创作了《欲望号街车》。《安妮日记》出版。温斯顿·丘吉尔发表了《风暴聚集》。阿尔弗雷德·金赛发表了《男性性行为》。死海古卷在库姆兰谷被发现。查克·耶格尔驾驶的美国X-1飞机突破了音障。贝尔实验室发明了晶体管。

The Allies sign peace treaties with Italy, Romania, Hungary, Bulgaria and Finland. A conference on Germany fails to reach agreement. US Secretary of State George Marshall introduces the Marshall Plan, an aid programme for Europe. Palestine is partitioned into Arab and Jewish states; Arabs reject the partition. India gains independence; Hindu India and Muslim Pakistan become two separate dominions. Burma gains independence. In the Truman Doctrine, the US government promises aid to any government resisting communism. Tennessee Williams writes A Streetcar Named Desire. The Diary of Ann Frank is published. Winston Churchill publishes The Gathering Storm. Alfred Kinsey publishes Sexual Behaviour in the Human Male. The Dead Sea Scrolls are discovered in Wadi Qumran. The American X-1 aircraft, piloted by Chuck Yeager, breaks the sound barrier. Bell Laboratories invent the transistor.

1948

1948

英国国民医疗服务体系（NHS）成立。苏联封锁西柏林；柏林空运持续为占领区提供物资，直至1949年。捷克斯洛伐克人民共和国成立。以色列建国；以色列与阿拉伯联盟爆发战争。圣雄甘地遇刺身亡。印度成为共和国。锡兰成为自治领。南非独立。中国爆发共产党与民族主义者之间的战争。朝鲜半岛分裂为南部的大韩民国和北部的朝鲜民主主义人民共和国。毛泽东在中国建立共产党政府；民族主义领导人逃往台湾（福尔摩沙）。缅甸联邦成为独立共和国。诺曼·梅勒出版《裸者与死者》。乔治·奥威尔出版《一九八四》。杰克逊·波洛克创作《构图一号》。世界基督教协会成立。

The National Health Service is introduced in Britain. The Soviet Union establishes a blockade of West Berlin; the Berlin airlift supplies the zone until 1949. A communist coup creates the People’s Republic of Czechoslovakia. The state of Israel is declared; war breaks out between Israel and the Arab League. Mahatma Gandhi is assassinated. India becomes a republic. Ceylon becomes a self-governing dominion. South Africa becomes independent. Communists and nationalists fight in China. Korea is divided into the Republic of Korea, in the south and the People’s Republic in the north. Mao Zedong establishes a Communist government in China; nationalist leaders flee to Taiwan (Formosa). The Union of Burma becomes an independent republic. Norman Mailer publishes The Naked and the Dead. George Orwell publishes Nineteen Eighty-Four. Jackson Pollock paints Composition No. 1. The World Council of Churches is founded.

1949

1949

英国承认爱尔兰共和国独立；面包和衣服配给制结束。柏林空运结束；德国分裂为东西两部分，即联邦德国（西德）和德意志民主共和国（东德）。苏联和其他共产主义国家成立了经互会（经济互助委员会）。十二名德国战犯被处以绞刑。西方国家成立了北大西洋公约组织（北约）。戴维·本-古里安成为新成立的以色列国总理；阿拉伯联盟与以色列之间的战争以停战告终；耶路撒冷被分割。种族隔离成为南非的官方政策。法国承认越南和柬埔寨。俄罗斯承认中华人民共和国。阿瑟·米勒创作了《推销员之死》。苏联科学家研制出原子弹。

Britain recognizes the independence of the Republic of Ireland; bread and clothes rationing ends. The Berlin airlift ends; Germany is split in two, the Federal Republic (West) and the German Democratic Republic (East). Comecon (the Council for Mutual Economic Assistance) is created by the Soviet Union and other communist countries. Twelve German war criminals are hung. The North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) is formed by Western nations. David Ben-Gurion becomes prime minister of the new state of Israel; war between the Arab League and Israel ends in a truce; Jerusalem is partitioned. Apartheid becomes official government policy in South Africa. France recognizes Vietnam and Cambodia. Russia recognizes the People’s Republic of China. Arthur Miller writes Death of a Salesman. Soviet scientists develop an atom bomb.

1950

1950

世界人口达到25亿。英国和埃及就苏丹和苏伊士运河问题发生争执。约瑟夫·麦卡锡领导了一项针对美国“非美（共产主义）活动”的调查。菲律宾获得独立。中国占领西藏。朝鲜战争爆发，交战双方为得到中国支持的朝鲜和得到联合国支持的韩国。中国发生旱灾和洪灾，造成一千万人死亡。第一张信用卡问世。

The population of the world is 2½ billion. Britain and Egypt argue over Sudan and the Suez Canal. Joseph McCarthy leads an inquiry into ‘un-American (communist) activities’ in the United States. The Philippines gain independence. China occupies Tibet. The Korean War begins between North Korea, with China’s support, and South Korea, supported by the forces of the United Nations. Ten million die in droughts and floods in China. The first credit card is introduced.

1951

1951

温斯顿·丘吉尔在英国组建了他的第一届和平时期政府。西德加入欧洲委员会。埃及退出苏伊士运河协议；英国军队占领运河区。约旦国王阿卜杜拉遇刺身亡。利比亚脱离意大利独立。马歇尔计划结束。日本在旧金山签署和平条约。中国占领西藏。爱达荷州首次利用原子能发电。唱片骑师艾伦·弗里德创造了“摇滚乐”一词。美国天文学家威廉·摩根宣布银河系呈螺旋状。

Winston Churchill forms his first peacetime government in Britain. West Germany is admitted to the Council of Europe. Egypt withdraws from the agreement on Suez; British troops occupy the Canal Zone. King Abdullah of Jordan is assassinated. Libya gains independence from Italy. The Marshall Plan ends. Japan signs a peace treaty at San Francisco. China occupies Tibet. Electric power is produced from atomic energy for the first time in Idaho. Disc jockey Alan Freed coins the term ‘rock ‘n’ roll’. William Morgan, an American astronomer, announces that the Milky Way is spiral-shaped.

1952

1952

伊丽莎白二世成为英国女王。

Elizabeth II becomes queen of the United Kingdom.

西德的占领结束。土耳其和希腊加入北约。茅茅运动（基库尤族部落的秘密组织）在肯尼亚开始对英国进行恐怖活动。在印度，贾瓦哈拉尔·尼赫鲁当选总理。盟军对日本的占领结束。乔纳斯·索尔克发现了脊髓灰质炎疫苗。特蕾莎修女在加尔各答开设了临终关怀院。英国的德哈维兰彗星飞机成为第一架涡轮喷气式客机。阿尔伯特·史怀泽获得诺贝尔和平奖。

The occupation of West Germany ends. Turkey and Greece join NATO. The Mau Mau (a secret organization of Kikuyu tribesmen) begin terrorist activities against the British in Kenya. In India, Jawaharlal Nehru is elected prime minister. The Allied occupation of Japan ends. Jonas Salk discovers polio vaccine. Mother Theresa opens her Home for Dying Destitutes in Calcutta. The British De Havilland Comet becomes the first turbojet passenger plane. Albert Schweizer wins the Nobel Peace Prize.

1953

1953

科学家、分子生物学家，美国人詹姆斯·沃森和英国人弗朗西斯·克里克，展示了他们的双螺旋DNA模型。

Scientists, molecular biologists, American James Watson and Englishman Francis Crick, demonstrate their double helix DNA model.

达格·哈马舍尔德就任联合国秘书长。约瑟夫·斯大林逝世；格奥尔基·马林科夫出任苏联最高领导人。在南斯拉夫，共产主义领导人铁托元帅就任总统。肯尼亚政治家乔莫·肯雅塔被指控参与茅茅运动并被监禁。德怀特·D·艾森豪威尔就任美国总统。埃及发生军事政变，君主制结束，共和国成立。在伊朗，中央情报局协助沙阿复辟。板门店条约结束了朝鲜战争。法国占领北越奠边府；越盟军队入侵老挝。柬埔寨脱离法国独立。美国科学家沃纳·冯·布劳恩和其他前纳粹科学家研制出第一枚中程弹道导弹——红石导弹。苏联试爆了第一颗氢弹。新西兰人埃德蒙·希拉里和夏尔巴人丹增成为首批登上珠穆朗玛峰的人。荷兰洪水造成2000人死亡。西蒙娜·德·波伏娃出版了具有里程碑意义的女权主义著作《第二性》。伊恩·弗莱明出版了他的第一部詹姆斯·邦德小说《皇家赌场》。据报道，吸烟会导致癌症。

Dag Hammarskjöld becomes United Nations Secretary-General. Joseph Stalin dies; Georgi Malenkov becomes Soviet premier. In Yugoslavia, communist leader, Marsahal Tito becomes president. Kenyan politician Jomo Kenyatta is accused of Mau Mau involvement and imprisoned. Dwight D. Eisenhower becomes president of the United States. A military coup ends the monarchy in Egypt; a republic is created. In Iran, the CIA helps in the restoration of the Shah to power. The Treaty of Panmunjon ends the Korean War. France occupies Dien Bien Phu in North Vietnam; Viet Minh forces invade Laos. Cambodia gains independence from France. The Redstone missile, the first intermediate range ballistic missile, is developed in the United States by Werner von Braun and other former Nazi scientists. The USSR tests its first hydrogen bomb. New Zealander Edmund Hillary and Sherpa Tensing become the first to climb Mount Everest. Flooding kills 2,000 in Holland. Simone de Beauvoir publishes the landmark feminist book, The Second Sex. Ian Fleming publishes his first James Bond novel, Casino Royale. Cigarette smoking is reported to cause cancer.

1954

1954

塞浦路斯和希腊因合并问题爆发冲突。阿尔及利亚爆发独立战争，争取摆脱法国的统治。加麦尔·阿卜杜勒·纳赛尔上校当选埃及总统。美国最高法院裁定公立学校种族隔离违宪。法国在奠边府战役中被越盟击败。日内瓦会议将越南分为北方（共产主义阵营）和南方（由英国和美国支持）。东南亚条约组织（SEATO）成立，旨在阻止共产主义在该地区的蔓延。美国首次推出彩色电视机。英国运动员罗杰·班尼斯特成为第一个在四分钟内跑完一英里的人。中国长江泛滥，造成四万人死亡，一千万人被迫撤离。美国下水“鹦鹉螺”号，这是世界上第一艘核动力潜艇。欧内斯特·海明威荣获诺贝尔文学奖。

Trouble flares up in Cyprus and Greece over their union. War for independence from France begins in Algeria. Colonel Gamal Abdul Nasser is elected Egyptian president. The US Supreme Court rules that segregation in public schools is unconstitutional. France is defeated by the Viet Minh at Dien Bien Phu. The Geneva Conference divides Vietnam into North (communist) and South (supported by Britain and the United States). The South East Asia Treaty Organization (SEATO) is created to prevent the spread of communism in the area. The first colour televisions are introduced in the United States. British athlete, Roger Bannister is the first person to run a mile in under four minutes. China’s Yangtze River floods, killing 40,000 and forcing 10 million to evacuate. The United States launches the Nautilus, the first nuclear-powered submarine. Ernest Hemingway is awarded the Nobel Prize for Literature.

1955

1955

温斯顿·丘吉尔辞去英国首相职务。华沙条约由共产主义国家签署。西德加入北约。希腊族塞浦路斯恐怖组织EOKA开始在塞浦路斯活动。以色列袭击埃及和叙利亚边境。苏丹第一次内战爆发。日内瓦会议讨论和平利用原子能。罗莎·帕克斯在阿拉巴马州蒙哥马利被捕，由此拉开了美国民权运动的序幕。阿根廷爆发武装叛乱和总罢工；总统胡安·庇隆流亡海外。英国开播商业电视。英国研制出原子钟。索尼研制出第一台袖珍晶体管收音机。

Winston Churchill resigns as prime minister in Britain. The Warsaw Pact is signed by the communist states. West Germany is admitted to NATO. The Greek Cypriot terrorist organization, EOKA, begins activities in Cyprus. Israel raids the borders of Egypt and Syria. The first Sudanese civil war begins. A conference at Geneva discusses the peaceful exploitation of atomic energy. The arrest of Rosa Parks in Montgomery, Alabama, launches the American Civil Rights movement. In Argentina, there is an armed rebellion and general strike; President Juan Peron goes into exile. Commercial television is launched in Britain. The British develop an atomic clock. Sony develops the first pocket-size transistor radio.

1956

1956

苏联最高领导人尼基塔·赫鲁晓夫谴责约瑟夫·斯大林。匈牙利爆发反俄起义，被苏联军队镇压。英国从苏伊士运河区撤军；纳赛尔总统将运河收归国有；以色列入侵埃及；英国和法国重新占领运河区；联合国派遣部队维持停火。法国承认摩洛哥和突尼斯独立。巴基斯坦成为伊斯兰共和国。艾森豪威尔总统在美国连任。猫王埃尔维斯·普雷斯利发行《伤心旅馆》，这是他170多首热门歌曲中的第一首。16岁的贝利签约巴西桑托斯足球俱乐部。美国影星格蕾丝·凯利嫁给摩纳哥亲王兰尼埃。第一种计算机语言FORTRAN被开发出来。

Soviet premier Nikita Kruschev denounces Joseph Stalin. An anti-Russian uprising in Hungary is quashed by the Russians. Britain withdraws its troops from the Suez Canal Zone; President Nasser nationalizes the canal; Israel invades Egypt; Britain and France reoccupy the Canal Zone; the United Nations sends in forces to police a ceasefire. France recognizes the independence of Morocco and Tunisia. Pakistan becomes an Islamic republic. President Eisenhower is re-elected in the United States. Elvis Presley releases Heartbreak Hotel, the first of more than 170 hit records. sixteen-year-old Pelé signs for the Santos football club in Brazil. American film star Grace Kelly marries Prince Rainier of Monaco. FORTRAN, the first computer language, is developed.

1957

1957

苏联发射了第一颗人造卫星“斯普特尼克一号”；一只名叫莱卡的狗成为第一个进入太空的生物。

The Soviet Union launches Sputnik I, the first artificial satellite; Laika, a dog, becomes the first living creature to travel into space.

《罗马条约》由多个欧洲国家签署，建立了欧洲经济共同体，即“共同市场”。加纳成为撒哈拉以南非洲第一个获得独立的国家。苏伊士运河重新开放。菲德尔·卡斯特罗领导古巴游击队反对独裁者富尔亨西奥·巴蒂斯塔。“爸爸医生”杜瓦利埃就任海地总统。天然蛋白质干扰素被发现。伦纳德·伯恩斯坦完成了音乐剧《西区故事》。

The Treaty of Rome is signed by a number of European nations, establishing the European Economic Community, the ‘Common Market’. Ghana becomes the first sub-Saharan African nation to obtain independence. The Suez Canal is reopened. Fidel Castro leads guerrilla activity in Cuba against the dictator Fulgencio Batista. ‘Papa Doc’ Duvalier becomes president of Haiti. The natural proteins, interferons, are discovered. Leonard Bernstein completes the musical West Side Story.

1958

1958

夏尔·戴高乐当选法兰西第五共和国首任总统。教皇约翰二十三世就任教皇，任期至1963年。埃及和叙利亚组成阿拉伯联合共和国（简称“阿拉伯联合共和国”），也门加入后，成为阿拉伯联合王国。阿卜杜勒·卡西姆领导伊拉克军事政变，费萨尔二世国王遇刺身亡，伊拉克宣布成立共和国。菲德尔·卡斯特罗在古巴发动革命。中国开始大跃进，迈向快速工业化。美国发射“探险者1号”探测器，太空竞赛拉开帷幕。天花和霍乱在东巴基斯坦造成超过7.5万人死亡。美国政府成立国家航空航天局（NASA），并启动水星载人航天计划。美国工程师杰克·基尔比发明集成电路，彻底改变了电子行业。巴西队在瑞典赢得世界杯冠军。埃尔维斯·普雷斯利应征入伍。

Charles de Gaule is elected first president of the French Fifth Republic. Pope John XXIII becomes pope until 1963. Egypt and Syria form the United Arab Republic (UAR); joined by Yemen, it becomes the United Arab States. Abdul Kassem leads a military revolt in Iraq; King Faisal II is assassinated and a republic is declared. Fidel Castro launches a revolution in Cuba. China begins the Great Leap Forward, a move towards rapid industrialization. The United States launches Explorer I and the space race begins. Smallpox and cholera kill more than 75,000 in East Pakistan. The US government creates the National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) and initiates the Mercury manned space programme. US engineer Jack Kilby invents the integrated circuit, revolutionizing the electronics industry. Brazil win the World Cup in Sweden. Elvis Presley is inducted into the US Army.

1959

1959

在比利时属刚果的利奥波德维尔，爆发了反对欧洲统治的暴动。阿拉伯激进组织法塔赫由亚西尔·阿拉法特在科威特创立。古巴巴蒂斯塔独裁政权被推翻；共产主义游击队领导人菲德尔·卡斯特罗成为古巴总理。西藏爆发反抗中国统治的起义；起义被镇压后，达赖喇嘛逃往印度。阿拉斯加和夏威夷成为美国的第49和第50个州。第一台商用复印机售出。日本皇太子明仁迎娶平民女子，这是1500年来首次发生此类事件。苏联“月球3号”探测器首次拍摄到月球背面。

Riots against European rule erupt in Leopoldville, in the Belgian Congo. The militant Arab organization al-Fatah is founded in Kuwait by Yasser Ararfat. The Batista dictatorship in Cuba is overthrown; communist guerrilla Fidel Castro becomes prime minister. Tibet revolts against Chinese rule; the Dalai Lama escapes to India as the revolt is crushed. Alaska and Hawaii become the 49th and 50th American states. The first commercial copier is sold. Crown Prince Akihito of Japan marries a commoner; the first time this has happened in 1,500 years. The Soviet spacecraft Luna 3 photographs the far side of the Moon for the first time.

1960

1960

世界人口超过30亿。爱尔兰共和军（IRA）开始对英国进行游击战。欧洲自由贸易联盟（EFTA）和中美洲共同市场成立。塞浦路斯在马卡里奥斯大主教总统的领导下成为独立共和国。列昂尼德·勃列日涅夫成为苏联总统。土耳其发生军事政变，恢复世俗主义。石油输出国组织（欧佩克）成立。16个非洲殖民地获得独立。刚果爆发内战。约翰·菲茨杰拉德·肯尼迪成为美国历史上最年轻的总统。一架美国侦察机在苏联领空被击落，引发U-2危机。所有对南极洲的领土主张均被放弃，南极洲被划为科学研究用地。连接五大湖和大西洋的圣劳伦斯航道竣工。前盖世太保头目阿道夫·艾希曼在南美洲被抓获。 1962年，他在以色列被处以绞刑。美国科学家研制出激光。心脏起搏器被研制出来。英国科学家发明了垂直起降喷气式飞机。在罗马奥运会上，埃塞俄比亚马拉松运动员阿贝贝·比基拉成为首位赢得奥运会田径金牌的非洲人。

The population of the world is more than three billion. The Irish Republican Army (IRA) begins a guerrilla campaign against the British.
