The European Free Trade Association (EFTA) and the Central American Common Market are formed. Cyprus becomes an independent republic under President Archbishop Makarios. Leonid Brezhnev becomes president of the Soviet Union. In Turkey, a military coup restores secularism. OPEC (Organization of Petrol Exporting Countries) is founded. Sixteen African colonies become independent. Civil war rages in the Congo. John Fitzgerald Kennedy becomes the youngest president of the United States. A United States reconnaissance plane is shot down over Soviet territory, initiating the U-2 crisis. All territorial claims on Antarctica are waived; it is reserved for scientific research. The St Lawrence Seaway, linking the Great Lakes and the Atlantic, is completed. Former Gestapo chief Adolf Eichmann is tracked down in South America; he is hanged in Israel in 1962. American scientists develop the laser. The heart pacemaker is developed. British scientists invent a vertical take-off jet. At the Rome Olympics, Ethiopian marathon runner Abebe Bikila is the first African to win an Olympic track and field gold medal.

1961

1961

东德修建柏林墙。英国开始申请加入欧洲经济共同体，但最终失败。猪湾流亡者入侵古巴，旨在推翻卡斯特罗政府，但行动失败。达格·哈马舍尔德因飞机失事去世后，吴丹接任联合国秘书长。叙利亚退出阿拉伯联合共和国。南非成为共和国并退出英联邦。女性口服避孕药上市。苏联宇航员尤里·加加林成为首位进入太空的人类。用于治疗妊娠反应的药物沙利度胺被发现会导致胎儿畸形。雷·克罗克从麦当劳兄弟手中收购了麦当劳快餐连锁店。

East Germany builds the Berlin Wall. Britain begins an unsuccessful application to join the European Economic Community. The Bay of Pigs exiles’ invasion of Cuba, aimed at overthrowing Castro’s government, fails. U Thant becomes secretary-general of the UN after Dag Hammarskjöld dies in a plane crash. Syria withdraws from the United Arab Republic. South Africa becomes a republic and withdraws from the Commonwealth. The female oral contraceptive pill comes onto the market. Soviet cosmonaut Yuri Gagarin becomes the first man in space. The morning sickness drug Thalidomide is discovered to cause birth defects. Ray Kroc buys the MacDonalds fast food chain from the MacDonald brothers.

1962

1962

美国艺术家安迪·沃霍尔创作了《坎贝尔汤罐头》系列画作。

US artist Andy Warhol paints Campbell’s Soup Tins.

古巴导弹危机：美国和苏联因苏联在古巴部署的导弹和轰炸机而发生对抗；苏联最终让步。第二次梵蒂冈大公会议对天主教会进行改革。马耳他宣布独立。阿尔及利亚脱离法国获得独立。也门在政变后分裂为南北两部分；北部为君主制国家，南部为共和国。牙买加宣布独立。纳尔逊·曼德拉因叛国罪在南非被捕入狱。印度和中国发生边境冲突。数万人游行至华盛顿特区，争取美国黑人的公民权利。西萨摩亚宣布独立。约翰·格伦成为首位绕地球轨道飞行的美国人。泰尔斯塔通信卫星发射升空，实现了美国和欧洲之间的首次电视直播。第一家沃尔玛超市开业。

The Cuban Missile Crisis: a confrontation between the United States and Russia over Russian missiles and bombers based in Cuba; the Soviet Union backs down. The Second Vatican Council introduces reforms to the Catholic Church. Malta becomes independent. Algeria gains independence from France. Yemen splits in two after a coup; the north is a monarchy, the south a republic. Jamaica becomes independent. Nelson Mandela is imprisoned for treason in South Africa. There are border clashes between India and China. Tens of thousands march on Washington DC to press for civil rights for black Americans. Western Samoa becomes independent. John Glen is the first American to orbit the Earth. The Telstar communications satellite is launched, providing the first live TV broadcasts between the United States and Europe. The first Wal-Mart store is opened.

1963

1963

美国总统约翰·F·肯尼迪被李·哈维·奥斯瓦尔德刺杀；林登·约翰逊继任总统。

US president John F. Kennedy is assassinated by Lee Harvey Oswald; Lyndon Johnson becomes president.

普罗富莫丑闻令英国政府震惊。法国否决了英国加入欧共体的提议。法国引爆了第一颗原子弹。保罗六世就任教皇。英国、美国和苏联签署了核试验禁令条约。苏联和美国之间开通了热线。马来西亚由马来亚、新加坡、北婆罗洲和沙捞越四个联邦组成（新加坡后来退出）。军事政变推翻了南越政府。非洲各国成立了非洲统一组织（非统组织）。麻疹疫苗研制成功。披头士乐队发行了他们的首张唱片，席卷英国，随后风靡全球。纽约举办了一场波普艺术展，展出了画家安迪·沃霍尔和贾斯珀·约翰斯的作品；美国波普艺术家罗伊·利希滕斯坦创作了《Whaam》。盒式磁带在荷兰研制成功。瓦伦蒂娜·捷列什科娃成为第一位进入太空的女性。荷兰天文学家马尔滕·施密特发现了第一个类星体。阿诺·彭齐亚斯和罗伯特·威尔逊发现了微弱的辐射，后来证实这是宇宙大爆炸的遗迹。马丁·路德·金在华盛顿特区发表了著名的“我有一个梦想”演讲。

The British government is shaken by the Profumo scandal. France vetoes British membership of the EEC. France detonates its first atomic bomb. Paul VI becomes pope. Britain, the United States and Russia sign a nuclear test ban treaty. A hotline is set up between the USSR and the United States. Malaysia is created from the federations of Malaya, Singapore, North Borneo and Sarawak (Singapore later withdraws). A military coup overthrows the government of South Vietnam. African states form the Organization of African Unity (OAU). The measles vaccine is developed. The Beatles release their first records, taking Britain and then the world by storm. An exhibition of pop art in New York features painters Andy Warhol and Jasper Johns; American pop artist Roy Lichtenstein paints Whaam. Cassette tapes are developed in the Netherlands. Valentina Tereshkova is the first woman in space. Dutch astronomer Maarten Schmidt discovers the first quasar. Arno Penzias and Robert Wilson discover faint radiation which turns out to be the remnants of the Big Bang. Martin Luther King delivers his ‘I have a dream’ speech in Washington DC.

1964

1964

尼基塔·赫鲁晓夫在苏联失去权力，列昂尼德·勃列日涅夫继任。希腊人和土耳其人在塞浦路斯交战，联合国部队被派往维持和平。巴勒斯坦解放组织成立，旨在团结巴勒斯坦难民。《民权法案》禁止美国联邦政府拨款和就业中的种族歧视。美国宣布支持南越对抗越共。巴西军方领导人夺取政权。印度尼西亚和马来西亚开战。中国试爆了第一颗原子弹。东京奥运会：这是第一届在亚洲举办的奥运会，也是第一届通过卫星向全球转播的奥运会。披头士乐队在美国艾德·沙利文秀上首次亮相。第一台家用录像机问世。卡修斯·克莱（穆罕默德·阿里）成为世界重量级拳王。鲍勃·迪伦凭借社会抗议歌曲使民谣音乐流行起来。

Nikita Kruschev loses power in the Soviet Union; Leonid Brezhnev succeeds him. Greeks and Turks fight in Cyprus; United Nations troops are sent in to maintain peace. The Palestine Liberation Organization is formed to unite Palestinian refugees. The Civil Rights Act bans racial discrimination in federal funding and employment in the United States. The United States declares support for the South Vietnamese against the Viet Cong. Military leaders seize power in Brazil. Indonesia and Malaysia go to war. China tests its first atomic bomb. The Tokyo Olympic Games: the first Olympics staged in Asia and the first event to be relayed to the world by satellite. The Beatles make their US debut on the Ed Sullivan Show. The first home videotape player is introduced. Cassius Clay (Muhammad Ali) becomes heavyweight champion of the world. Bob Dylan makes folk music popular with social protest songs.

1965

1965

美国开始轰炸北越，第一批美国海军陆战队员登陆南越。

The United States initiates bombing of North Vietnam and the first US marines land in South Vietnam.

印度和巴基斯坦因克什米尔问题爆发战争。在总理伊恩·史密斯的领导下，罗得西亚单方面宣布脱离英国独立；英国对罗得西亚实施经济制裁。加纳总统克瓦米·恩克鲁玛被军队推翻。约瑟夫·蒙博托上校在刚果夺取政权。新加坡脱离马来西亚并宣布独立。美国双子座计划将两名宇航员送入轨道。俄罗斯宇航员阿列克谢·列昂诺夫成为第一个在太空行走的人。水手4号探测器拍摄了第一张火星近距离照片。鲍勃·迪伦开始使用电声乐器。

India and Pakistan go to war over Kashmir. Under premier Ian Smith, Rhodesia makes a unilateral declaration of independence from Britain; Britain places economic sanctions on Rhodesia. Ghanaian president Kwame Nkrumah is toppled by the army. Colonel Joseph Mobutu seizes power in the Congo. Singapore breaks away from Malaysia and declares independence. The American Gemini space missions send two-man crews into orbit. Russian Alexei Leonov is the first man to ‘walk’ in space. Mariner 4 takes the first close-up pictures of Mars. Bob Dylan goes electric.

1966

1966

英迪拉·甘地就任印度总理。冈比亚脱离法国独立。博茨瓦纳和莱索托脱离英国独立。美国黑人穆斯林领袖马尔科姆·X遇刺身亡。南非总理亨德里克·弗沃德博士遇刺身亡，约翰·沃斯特继任。联合国对罗得西亚实施制裁。让-贝德尔·博卡萨接管中非共和国，于1972年宣布自己为终身总统，并于1977年称帝。中国爆发文化大革命（持续至1968年）；红卫兵成立；知识分子遭到清洗。印尼和马来西亚之间的战争结束。费迪南德·马科斯当选菲律宾总统。苏联将无人探测器“月球9号”送上月球。意大利北部发生洪水，艺术珍品受损。埃及阿布辛贝神庙和雕像被迁移，以防阿斯旺大坝水位上涨。东道主英格兰队赢得世界杯冠军。

Indira Gandhi becomes prime minister of India. Gambia gains independence from France. Bothswana and Lesotho gain independence from Britain. Black American Muslim leader Malcolm X is assassinated. South African premier Dr Hendrik Verwoerd is assassinated and succeeded by John Vorster. The United Nations imposes sanctions on Rhodesia. Jean-Bedel Bokassa takes over the Central African Republic, declaring himself president-for-life in 1972 and Emperor in 1977. The Cultural Revolution begins in China (until 1968); the Red Guards are formed; intellectuals are purged. The war between Indonesia and Malaysia ends. Ferdinand Marcos is elected president of the Philippines. The Soviet Union lands the unmanned Luna 9 spacecraft on the Moon. Floods damage art treasures in northern Italy. Temples and statues of Abu Simbel in Egypt are moved to protect them from the rising waters of the Aswan High Dam. Hosts, England win the World Cup.

1967

1967

法国第二次否决了英国加入欧共体的申请。乔治·帕帕多普洛斯上校在希腊发动军事政变并取得成功。在阿拉伯国家与以色列之间的六日战争中，以色列占领了西奈沙漠、耶路撒冷和约旦河西岸；联合国斡旋停火；苏伊士运河关闭至1975年。比夫拉脱离尼日利亚联邦，引发内战。切·格瓦拉在玻利维亚被杀。中国引爆了第一颗氢弹。克里斯蒂安·巴纳德医生在南非完成了世界上首例心脏移植手术。在美国，绿湾包装工队赢得了美式橄榄球历史上首届超级碗冠军。由于新型阿波罗飞船发生灾难性火灾，导致三名宇航员丧生，太空飞行暂停。第一台自动取款机在伦敦北部的一家巴克莱银行推出。爱尔兰天文学家乔斯林·贝尔发现了脉冲星，即超新星爆炸的遗迹。披头士乐队发行了《佩珀军士的孤独之心俱乐部乐队》。那是爱之夏；嬉皮士们听着迷幻音乐，并被鼓励“开启、融入、退出”。

France vetoes a British application to join the EEC for a second time. Colonel George Papadopoulos leads a successful military coup in Greece. In the Six Day War between Arabs and Israelis, Israel occupies the Sinai Desert, Jerusalem and the west bank of the Jordan; the United Nations brokers a ceasefire; the Suez Canal is closed until 1975. Biafra breaks away from the Nigerian Federation, leading to civil war. Che Guevara is killed in Bolivia. China detonates its first hydrogen bomb. Dr Christian Barnard performs the world’s first heart transplant operation in South Africa. In the United States, Green Bay win American football’s first Superbowl. Space flights are suspended after a disastrous fire on the new Apollo spacecraft kills three astronauts. The first ATM is launched at a Barclays bank in North London. Irish astronomer Jocelyn Bell discovers pulsars the remnants of supernova explosions. The Beatles release Sergeant Pepper’s Lonely Hearts Club Band. The summer of love; hippies listen to psychedelic music and are encouraged to ‘turn on, tune in and drop out’.

1968

1968

民权运动引发北爱尔兰危机。学生示威游行导致巴黎骚乱；大学和工厂被工人和学生占领。苏联军队入侵捷克斯洛伐克，以结束亚历山大·杜布切克政府的自由主义改革。复兴党在伊拉克上台执政。埃塞俄比亚内战爆发；北非萨赫勒地区遭遇长达六年的干旱，导致50万人死亡。伊朗发生地震，造成1.2万人死亡。在美国，民权领袖马丁·路德·金遇刺身亡。罗伯特·肯尼迪，即遇刺身亡的美国总统约翰·肯尼迪的弟弟，在竞选总统期间遇刺身亡。理查德·尼克松就任美国总统。越共在越南发动春节攻势；美国爆发大规模反战抗议；驻越美军人数达到48万人。教皇发表通谕，反对人工避孕。苏联核科学家安德烈·萨尔霍夫批评苏联极权主义。苏联作家亚历山大·索尔仁尼琴因政治异端被开除出苏联作家协会；次年，他荣获诺贝尔文学奖。弗兰克·博尔曼、詹姆斯·洛弗尔和威廉·安德斯乘坐阿波罗8号绕月飞行。

Civil rights riots result in crisis in Northern Ireland. Student demonstrations lead to riots in Paris; universities and factories are taken over by workers and students. Soviet forces invade Czechoslovakia to bring to an end the liberal reforms of the government of Alexander Dubcek. The Baath Party comes to power in Iraq. The Ethiopian civil war begins; 500,000 die in the North African Sahel region in a drought lasting six years. An earthquake in Iran kills 12,000. In America, civil rights leader Martin Luther King is assassinated. As he campaigns for the presidency, Robert Kennedy, brother of assassinated US president, John Kennedy, is assassinated. Richard Nixon becomes American president. The Viet Cong launch the Tet Offensive in Vietnam; major protests break out in the United States against the war; there are 480,000 US troops in Vietnam. The pope issues an encyclical against artificial contraception. Soviet nuclear scientist Andrei Sarkhov criticizes Soviet totalitarianism. Soviet writer Alexander Solzhenitsyn is expelled from the Soviet Writers’ Union for political heresy; next year he is awarded the Nobel Prize for Literature. Frank Borman, James Lovell and William Anders orbit the Moon in Apollo 8.

1969

1969

美国宇航员尼尔·阿姆斯特朗成为第一个登上月球的人。苏联实现了首次载人飞船对接。

The American astronaut Neil Armstrong becomes the first man to set foot on the Moon. The Soviet Union achieves the first docking of two manned spacecraft.

英国向北爱尔兰派兵。法国总统戴高乐辞职。美国总统尼克松与苏联举行战略武器限制谈判（SALT）。戈尔达·梅厄当选以色列第四任总理。穆阿迈尔·卡扎菲在利比亚夺取政权。英国赋予百慕大自治权。世界上第一架超音速飞机协和式飞机首飞。超过50万摇滚乐迷参加了在美国举办的伍德斯托克音乐节。

Britain sends troops into Northern Ireland. French president Charles de Gaule resigns. President Nixon engages in the SALT (Strategic Arms Limitation Talks) with the USSR. Golda Meir is elected Israel’s fourth prime minister. Muammar al-Qadaffi seizes power in Libya. Bermuda is granted self-government by Britain. Concorde, the world’s first supersonic aircraft, makes its maiden flight. More than 500,000 rock fans attend the Woodstock music festival in the United States.

1970

1970

世界人口超过35亿。约旦爆发内战。安瓦尔·萨达特就任埃及总统。比夫拉投降，尼日利亚内战结束。东巴基斯坦遭受飓风和洪水袭击，造成多达50万人死亡。红色高棉在柬埔寨掌权；美国入侵柬埔寨。汤加和斐济脱离英​​国独立。四名学生在俄亥俄州肯特州立大学抗议越南战争时被国民警卫队枪杀。微型计算机在美国开始研发。高级研究计划署网络（ARPANET）系统上线，成为互联网的前身。秘鲁发生洪水、地震和山体滑坡，造成5万至7万人死亡。贝利带领巴西队在墨西哥赢得第三座世界杯冠军奖杯。披头士乐队解散。

The population of the world is more than 3½ billion. Civil war breaks out in Jordan. Anwar Sadat becomes president of Egypt. Biafra surrenders, ending the Nigerian civil war. Up to 500,000 die in cyclones and floods in East Pakistan. Communist Khmer Rouge forces take power in Cambodia; the United States invades. Tonga and Fiji gain independence from Britain. Four students protesting against the Vietnam War are shot dead by National Guardsmen at Kent State University, Ohio. The development of micro-computers begins in the United States. The Advanced Research Projects Agency Network (ARPANET) system goes online, forerunner of the Internet. Between 50,000 and 70,000 die in floods, earthquakes and landslides in Peru. Pelé leads Brazil to their third World Cup victory, in Mexico. The Beatles break up.

1971

1971

伊朗国王举行盛大庆典，庆祝伊朗君主制延续2500周年。蒙博托将刚果共和国更名为扎伊尔。伊迪·阿明控制乌干达，实行残酷统治。东巴基斯坦在内战和印度干预后获得独立，成立孟加拉国。前总统胡安·庇隆结束流亡返回阿根廷。中国共产党加入联合国；台湾被逐出联合国。英国科学家研发出CT扫描和MRI技术。绿色和平组织成立。智利诗人巴勃罗·聂鲁达荣获诺贝尔文学奖。袖珍计算器问世。苏联发射“礼炮1号”空间站，这是世界上第一个载人空间站。中国发射了第一颗人造卫星。

The Shah of Iran celebrates 2,500 years of continuous Iranian monarchy with a lavish event. Mobutu renames the Republic of the Congo ‘Zaire’. Idi Amin takes control of Uganda and rules brutally. East Pakistan gains independence as Bangladesh after civil war and Indian intervention. Former president Juan Peron returns to Argentina from exile. Communist China joins the United Nations; Taiwan is expelled. British scientists develop the CT scan and MRI. Greenpeace is founded. Chilean poet Pablo Neruda wins the Nobel Prize for Literature. The pocket calculator is introduced. The USSR launches Salyut 1, the first manned space station. China launches its first satellite.

1972

1972

北爱尔兰伦敦德里发生“血腥星期日”事件；军队向民权游行者开火，造成 14 人死亡；英国接管直接统治权。

‘Bloody Sunday’ in Londonderry, Northern Ireland; troops fire on civil rights marchers, killing 14; Britain takes over direct rule.

在慕尼黑奥运会上，11名以色列运动员被阿拉伯“黑色九月”组织杀害。第一次苏丹内战结束，南苏丹获得自治权。锡兰更名为斯里兰卡共和国。美国飞机秘密轰炸柬埔寨。美国将冲绳归还日本。美国国会通过《平等机会法案》，以应对日益壮大的妇女运动。华盛顿特区警方在水门酒店民主党总部逮捕了五名男子，由此引发了水门事件。重达969.8克拉的“塞拉利昂之星”钻石被挖掘出来，这是迄今为止发现的最大钻石。在冰岛举行的一场充满政治意味的比赛中，美国棋手鲍比·菲舍尔击败苏联棋手鲍里斯·斯帕斯基，赢得世界国际象棋冠军。纽约世界贸易中心双子塔竣工，成为当时世界上最高的建筑。液晶显示器（LCD）在瑞士研制成功。美国游泳运动员马克·施皮茨在慕尼黑奥运会上获得创纪录的七枚金牌。

At the Munich Olympics, 11 Israeli athletes are killed by the Arab Black September organization. The first Sudanese civil war ends and southern Sudan is granted autonomy. Ceylon becomes the Republic of Sri Lanka. US planes secretly bomb Cambodia. The United States returns Okinawa to Japan. The US Congress passes the Equal Opportunity Act in response to the growing women’s movement. Washington DC police arrest five men inside the Democratic headquarters at the Watergate Hotel, beginning the Watergate scandal. The Star of Sierra Leone, the largest diamond ever found at 969.8 carats, is unearthed. In a politically charged match, American, Bobby Fischer wins the world chess title from Soviet Boris Spassky in Iceland. The World Trade Center twin towers in New York, the tallest structures in the world, are completed. The Liquid Crystal Display (LCD) is developed in Switzerland. American swimmer Mark Spitz wins a record seven gold medals at the Munich Olympics.

1973

1973

英国、爱尔兰和丹麦加入欧共体。阿拉伯产油国限制石油供应，导致世界经济危机。赎罪日战争爆发，以埃及和叙利亚为首的阿拉伯国家联盟进攻以色列；五周后达成停火协议。美国从越南撤军，并在巴黎签署和平协议。智利发生军事政变，推翻了马克思主义总统萨尔瓦多·阿连德。胡安·庇隆再次当选阿根廷总统。堕胎成为美国宪法赋予的权利。赛马“秘书处”赢得美国赛马三冠王。美国发射了天空实验室，一个轨道空间站。

Britain, Ireland and Denmark are admitted to the EEC. Arab oil-producing countries restrict oil supplies, leading to a world economic crisis. The Yom Kippur War a coalition of Arab states, led by Egypt and Syria, attacks Israel; a ceasefire is imposed after five weeks. The United States withdraws from Vietnam and a peace settlement is signed in Paris. A military coup in Chile overthrows the Marxist president, Salvador Allende. Juan Peron again becomes president of Argentina. Abortion becomes a US constitutional right. Secretariat wins horseracing’s Triple Crown in America. The United States launches Skylab, an orbiting space station.

1974

1974

爱尔兰共和军炸毁了伦敦塔和议会大厦。葡萄牙发生政变，结束了卡埃塔诺总统的独裁统治。希腊军政府辞职，举行选举。土耳其占领塞浦路斯首都尼科西亚，该岛被分割为希腊和土耳其两部分。叙利亚和以色列在戈兰高地达成停火协议。前葡萄牙殖民地几内亚比索、安哥拉和莫桑比克获得独立。尼日利亚成为非洲最大的石油生产国。革命马克思主义政权推翻了海尔·塞拉西，在埃塞俄比亚掌权，内战蔓延。巴哈马脱离英国获得独立。格林纳达宣布脱离英国独立。理查德·尼克松总统因水门事件被迫辞职，杰拉尔德·福特接任。非洲干旱威胁着数百万人的生命和生计；印度有3万人死于天花。芝加哥的西尔斯大厦成为当时世界上最高的建筑。印度引爆了一枚核装置，成为第六个进行核试验的国家。

The IRA bombs the Tower of London and Houses of Parliament. A coup in Portugal ends the dictatorship of President Caetano. The Greek military junta resigns; elections are held. The Turks occupy Nicosia on Cyprus; the island is partitioned into Greek and Turkish sections. Syria and Israel agree a ceasefire in the Golan Heights. Former Portuguese colonies Guinea-Bisseau, Angola and Mozambique gain independence. Nigeria becomes the leading oil producer in Africa. A revolutionary Marxist regime deposes Haile Selassie and takes power in Ethiopia; civil war spreads. The Bahamas are given independence from Britain. Grenada proclaims independence from Britain. President Richard Nixon is forced to resign because of the Watergate scandal; he is succeeded by Gerald Ford. Drought in Africa threatens the lives and livelihoods of millions; 30,000 die of smallpox in India. The Sears Tower in Chicago becomes the world’s tallest building. India detonates a nuclear device, the sixth nation to do so.

1975

1975

胡安·卡洛斯一世在佛朗哥44年的独裁统治后成为西班牙国王。黎巴嫩爆发穆斯林与基督徒之间的内战。南越向北越投降，越南战争结束。波尔布特的红色高棉在柬埔寨夺取政权；超过两百万柬埔寨人在“杀戮场”丧生。澳大利亚政治危机加剧，由英国君主任命的总督解散了民选政府。巴布亚新几内亚脱离澳大利亚独立。美苏首次太空合作。MITS Altair成为第一台桌面微型计算机。比尔·盖茨在美国创立微软公司。

King Juan Carlos I becomes king of Spain after 44 years of Franco’s dictatorship. Civil war breaks out in Lebanon between Muslims and Christians. South Vietnam surrenders to North Vietnam, ending the Vietnam War. Pol pot’s Khmer Rouge seize power in Cambodia; more than two million Cambodians die in the ‘killing fields’. Political crisis mounts in Australia as the governor-general, appointed by the British monarch, dismisses the elected government. Papua New Guinea gains independence from Australia. The first US–Soviet link-up in space takes place. The MITS Altair is the first desktop micro-computer. Bill Gates founds Microsoft in the United States.

1976

1976

《赫尔辛基人权公约》获得通过。吉米·卡特就任美国总统。1976年至1984年间，数千人在阿根廷的“肮脏战争”中失踪。非洲学童在南非索韦托发动起义，数百人被枪杀。安哥拉内战爆发，持续至1989年。在中国，周恩来和毛泽东逝世；“四人帮”垮台；华国锋就任中国总理。南北越统一。首次发出警告，称气雾剂中使用的氟碳化合物（CFCs）会破坏臭氧层。英国遭遇史上最严重的干旱。意大利、土耳其、中国、菲律宾、巴厘岛和危地马拉发生地震，造成约78万人死亡。美国圣公会批准女性担任牧师和主教。维京1号和2号探测器传回了第一批火星表面照片。军团病首次爆发于费城的一次会议上。菲利普·格拉斯完成了《海滩上的爱因斯坦》。

The Helsinki convention on human rights is adopted. Jimmy Carter becomes president of the United States. Between 1976 and 1984, thousands disappear in Argentina’s ‘dirty war’. African schoolchildren spark uprisings in Soweto in South Africa; hundreds are shot dead. The Angolan civil war begins, until 1989. In China, Zhou Enlai and Mao Zedong die; the fall of the ‘Gang of Four’; Hua Kuo-feng becomes Chinese premier. North and South Vietnam are united. The first warnings are issued that fluorocarbons (CFCs) used in aerosol sprays can damage the ozone layer. Britain suffers its worst-ever drought. Earthquakes in Italy, Turkey, China, the Philippines, Bali and Guatemala kill around 780,000 people. The Episcopal Church approves the ordination of women priests and bishops. Viking I and II transmit the first pictures from the surface of Mars. The first incidence of Legionnaire’s Disease occurs at a convention in Philadelphia. Philip Glass completes Einstein on the Beach.

1977

1977

电影《星球大战》引起了轰动。

The film Star Wars causes a sensation.

意大利宣布天主教不再是国教。240名捷克知识分子签署《七七宪章》，声明民主自由仍然遭到剥夺。以色列和埃及举行和平谈判。在巴基斯坦，穆罕默德·齐亚·哈克将军推翻了该国首位民选总理佐勒菲卡尔·阿里·布托。美国将巴拿马运河归还给巴拿马。猫王埃尔维斯·普雷斯利去世。朋克摇滚在英国引起轩然大波。首批苹果II型电脑上市销售。索马里隔离了最后一例天花病例。巴黎蓬皮杜艺术中心建成。

Italy announces that Catholicism is no longer the state religion. Two hundred and forty Czech intellectuals sign Charter 77 stating that democratic freedoms are still being denied. Peace negotiations take place between Israel and Egypt. In Pakistan, General Mohammed Zia ul-Haq overthrows Zulfiqar Ali Bhutto, the country’s first elected prime minister. The Panama Canal is returned to Panama by the United States. Elvis Presley dies. Punk Rock scandalizes England. The first Apple II computers go on sale. The last ever smallpox case is isolated in Somalia. The Pompidou Centre in Paris is built.

1978

1978

这一年出现了三位教宗：教宗若望保禄一世继任保禄六世，两个月后去世，若望保禄二世继任；若望保禄二世是波兰人，是450多年来首位非意大利籍教宗。阿富汗总统达乌德·汗在军事政变中遇害；努尔·穆罕默德·塔拉基继任。埃塞俄比亚对厄立特里亚发动进攻。美国主办埃及和以色列之间的戴维营峰会。美国同意与中国建立外交关系，断绝与台湾的关系。越南入侵柬埔寨，迫使红色高棉政权下台。世界上第一个“试管婴儿”在英国诞生。东道主阿根廷队赢得世界杯冠军。

A year of three popes: Pope John Paul I succeeds Paul VI and is replaced by Pope John Paul II when he dies two months later; John Paul II is Polish, the first non-Italian pope for over 450 years. Afghanistan president Daoud Khan is killed during a military coup; he is succeeded by Nur Mohammed Taraki. Ethiopia launches an offensive in Eritrea. The United States hosts the Camp David summit between Egypt and Israel. The United States agrees to diplomatic relations with China, ending those with Taiwan. Vietnam invades Cambodia and forces out the Khmer Rouge. The first ‘test tube baby’ is born, in England. Hosts Argentina win the World Cup.

1979

1979

英国选举玛格丽特·撒切尔为首位女首相；她开始将国有企业私有化。

Britain elects its first female prime minister, Margaret Thatcher; she begins privatizing state-owned companies.

蒙巴顿勋爵死于爱尔兰共和军炸弹袭击。欧洲议会举行首次直接选举。伊朗国王在骚乱和政治压力下流亡；流亡的宗教领袖霍梅尼返回伊朗，并为伊朗制定了伊斯兰宪法。长达十年的两伊战争爆发。苏联军队进入阿富汗。以色列和埃及在华盛顿签署和平条约。萨达姆·侯赛因就任伊拉克总统，并赢得美国的支持。伊迪·阿明逃离乌干达。中非帝​​国皇帝博卡萨在法国支持的政变中被推翻。罗得西亚在内部和解协议下举行选举；游击战仍在继续；英国控制了该国。桑地诺民族解放阵线在尼加拉瓜夺取政权。中国入侵越南。宾夕法尼亚州三里岛核电站险些发生核灾难。索尼随身听问世。特蕾莎修女荣获诺贝尔和平奖。 Sugar Hill Gang 录制了第一首商业说唱热门歌曲《Rapper's Delight》。

Lord Mountbatten is killed by an IRA bomb. The first direct elections to the European Parliament are held. The shah of Iran goes into exile after riots and political pressure; the exiled religious leader, Ayatollah Khomeini, returns and adopts an Islamic constitution for Iran. The ten-year Iran–Iraq war begins. Russian forces move into Afghanistan. A peace treaty is signed in Washington between Israel and Egypt. Sadam Hussein becomes president of Iraq and wins US support. Idi Amin flees from Uganda. Emperor Bokassa of the Central African Empire is overthrown in a French-backed coup. Elections are held in Rhodesia under an internal settlement; guerrilla warfare continues; Britain takes control of the country. The communist Sandinistas seize power in Nicaragua. China invades Vietnam. Nuclear catastrophe is narrowly averted at the Three Mile Island nuclear plant in Pennsylvania. The Sony Walkman is introduced. Mother Theresa is awarded the Nobel Peace Prize. The Sugar Hill Gang record the first commercial rap hit, Rapper’s Delight.

1980

1980

世界人口接近45亿。社会主义者弗朗索瓦·密特朗当选法国总统。南斯拉夫总统铁托逝世。波兰成立独立工会“团结工会”。英迪拉·甘地获释后重返政坛。罗得西亚独立，更名为津巴布韦，由罗伯特·穆加贝领导。前电影明星罗纳德·里根当选美国总统。萨尔瓦多爆发内战。在中国，邓小平巩固了其作为共产党领导人的地位，改善了中西方关系，并发展了社会主义市场经济理念。美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）成为首个24小时新闻电视台。美国圣海伦斯火山爆发。科学家发现了艾滋病病毒。日本成为世界最大的汽车生产国。50个国家抵制莫斯科奥运会，以抗议苏联入侵阿富汗。旅行者1号探测器传回了壮观的土星照片。前披头士乐队成员约翰·列侬被一名狂热粉丝枪杀。

The population of the world is almost 4½ billion. The socialist François Mitterand becomes president of France. President Tito of Yugoslavia dies. The independent trade union Solidarity is formed in Poland. Indira Gandhi returns to power after being imprisoned. Rhodesia becomes independent as Zimbabwe, under Robert Mugabe. Former film star Ronald Reagan is elected president of the United States. Civil war breaks out in El Salvador. In China, Deng Xiaoping consolidates his position as leader of the Communist Party, improving relations with the West and developing the concept of a socialist market economy. CNN becomes the first 24-hour news television station. The Mount St Helens volcano erupts in the United States. Scientists identify the AIDS virus. Japan becomes the world’s largest car manufacturer. The Moscow Olympics are boycotted by 50 countries, protesting at the Soviet invasion of Afghanistan. The Voyager I space probe transmits spectacular pictures of Saturn. Former Beatle, John Lennon is shot to death by an obsessed fan.

1981

1981

威尔士亲王查尔斯与戴安娜·斯宾塞小姐结婚。教皇约翰·保罗二世被土耳其人穆罕默德·阿里·阿加枪击，但幸存下来。波兰总理约瑟夫·平科夫斯基辞职，由沃伊切赫·雅鲁泽尔斯基将军接任。埃及总统萨达特遇刺身亡。锡克教徒开始争取旁遮普邦独立。以色列吞并戈兰高地。约翰·欣克利在华盛顿试图刺杀美国总统里根。毛泽东的第四任妻子江琴（毛夫人）在中国被判处死刑，后被改判，但她最终自杀身亡。MTV电视台开播。美国航天飞机哥伦比亚号完成首飞。世界上速度最快的列车TGV在法国开始运行。比尔·盖茨为IBM公司设计了MS-DOS操作系统。

Charles, Prince of Wales, marries Lady Diana Spencer. Pope John Paul II is shot by a Turk, Mehmet Ali Agca, but survives. The Polish prime minister Józef Pinkowski resigns; he is replaced by General Wojciech Jaruzelski. Egyptian president Sadat is assassinated. The Sikhs begin fighting for Punjabi independence. Israel annexes the Golan Heights. John Hinckley tries to assassinate President Reagan in Washington. Jiang Qin, ‘Madam Mao’, Mao Zedong’s fourth wife, is sentenced to death in China; the sentence is later commuted, but she commits suicide. MTV is launched. The US space shuttle Columbia makes its maiden flight. The world’s fastest train, the TGV, begins to run in France. Bill Gates devises MS-DOS for IBM.

1982

1982

迈克尔·杰克逊录制了《Thriller》，这是有史以来最畅销的专辑。

Michael Jackson records Thriller, the biggest-selling album ever.

马岛战争爆发；阿根廷占领马岛；英国特遣部队夺回马岛。红色旅在意大利发动恐怖袭击。赫尔穆特·科尔接替赫尔穆特·施密特出任德国总理。在苏联，前克格勃负责人尤里·安德罗波夫接替已故的列昂尼德·勃列日涅夫，成为中共中央总书记。以色列军队入侵黎巴嫩，驱逐巴勒斯坦解放组织；黎巴嫩基督教民兵在西贝鲁特的萨布拉和沙蒂拉难民营杀害数百名巴勒斯坦人。黎巴嫩真主党成立，这是一个政治和军事组织。墨西哥无力偿还外债，引发国际金融危机。哥伦比亚作家加西亚·马尔克斯荣获诺贝尔文学奖。意大利在西班牙赢得世界杯冠军。

The Falklands War; Argentina occupies the Falkland Islands; a British task force recaptures them. The Red Brigade carries out terrorist activities in Italy. Helmut Kohl replaces Helmut Schmidt as chancellor of Germany. In the Soviet Union, former KGB head Yuri Andropov becomes general secretary of the Communist Party’s Central Committee, succeeding the late Leonid Brezhnev.Israeli forces invade Lebanon to drive out the PLO; Lebanese Christian Militia kill hundreds of Palestinians in the Sabra and Chatila refugee camps in West Beirut. Hezbollah, a political and military organization, is founded in Lebanon. Mexico fails to repay foreign loans, provoking an international financial crisis. Colombian author Gabriel Garcia Marquez is awarded the Nobel Prize for Literature. Italy win the World Cup in Spain.

1983

1983

玛格丽特·撒切尔在英国大选中以压倒性优势获胜。爱尔兰共和军继续在英国开展恐怖活动。美国驻贝鲁特大使馆发生炸弹袭击，造成200多名海军陆战队员死亡；美国从黎巴嫩撤军。以色列签署协议从黎巴嫩撤军。非洲各国采纳国际货币基金组织（IMF）的经济管理方案。第二次苏丹内战爆发，穆斯林与非穆斯林交战，造成超过150万人死亡。泰米尔猛虎组织开始为少数族裔泰米尔人争取建立独立国家的斗争。阿根廷在七年军政府统治后举行民主选举。格林纳达总理莫里斯·毕晓普和其他40人在军事政变中被处决。菲律宾反对派领导人小贝尼尼奥·阿基诺在结束流亡返回马尼拉时遇刺身亡。中国人口达到10亿。纳粹战犯克劳斯·巴比在玻利维亚被捕。比约恩·博格赢得第五个温布尔登网球公开赛冠军，并宣布退役。英国开始强制要求使用安全带。微软Word首次发布。美国“先驱者10号”航天器成为首个飞出太阳系的人造物体。

Margaret Thatcher wins by a landslide in a general election in Britain. The IRA continues terrorist activities in Britain. More than 200 marines die when a bomb is detonated at the US embassy in Beirut; America withdraws from Lebanon. Israel signs an agreement to withdraw from Lebanon. African countries adopt IMF (International Monetary Fund) plans for managing their economies. More than 1½ million people die in the second Sudanese civil war between Muslims and non-Muslims. Tamil Tiger rebels begin their fight for a separate state for the minority Tamils. Democratic elections take place in Argentina after seven years of military rule. Maurice Bishop, the prime minister of Grenada, and 40 others are executed in a military coup. Benigno Aquino Jr., Philippine opposition leader, is assassinated in Manila as he returns from exile. The population of China reaches a billion. Nazi war criminal Klaus Barbie is arrested in Bolivia. Bjorn Borg wins his fifth consecutive Wimbledon championship and retires from tennis. Seatbelts become compulsory in Britain. Microsoft Word is first released. Pioneer 10, an American spacecraft, becomes the first man-made object to travel beyond the solar system.

1984

1984

临时爱尔兰共和军（PIRA）试图在布莱顿大酒店引爆炸弹刺杀英国内阁成员。英国爆发了持续一年的矿工罢工。康斯坦丁·契尔年科成为苏联共产党中央委员会总书记。印度军队袭击了阿姆利则的锡克教金庙；印度总理英迪拉·甘地被锡克教徒刺杀；拉吉夫·甘地成为印度总理。文莱苏丹国获得独立。上沃尔特更名为布基纳法索。埃塞俄比亚爆发饥荒。新西兰被宣布为无核区。首批商用CD播放器问世。印度博帕尔联合碳化物工厂发生有毒气体泄漏事故，造成2500人死亡，并对无数其他人造成持久影响。罗纳德·里根再次当选美国总统。马尼拉有50万人举行示威游行，反对费迪南德·马科斯政府。苏联和其他共产主义国家抵制洛杉矶奥运会。苹果公司推出Macintosh电脑，这是第一台带有图形界面的个人电脑。首批商用CD播放器问世。南非基督教协进会总书记德斯蒙德·图图主教荣获诺贝尔和平奖。

The Provisional Irish Republican Army (PIRA) tries to assassinate the British Cabinet with a bomb in the Grand Hotel in Brighton. The year-long miners’ strike begins in Britain. Konstantin Chernenko becomes general secretary of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union. Indian troops attack the Sikh Golden Temple at Amritsar; Indian prime minister, Indira Gandhi is assassinated by Sikhs; Rajiv Gandhi becomes prime minister of India. The sultanate of Brunei gains independence. Upper Volta becomes Burkina Faso. Famine begins in Ethiopia. New Zealand is declared a nuclear-free zone. The first commercial CD players are introduced. A leak of toxic gas from a Union Carbide plant in Bhopal in India kills 2,500 and leaves lasting effects on countless others. Ronald Reagan is re-elected president of the United States. Half a million people in Manila demonstrate against the government of Ferdinand Marcos. The Soviet Union and other communist countries boycott the Los Angeles Olympics. Apple introduces the Macintosh, the first PC with a graphical interface. The first commercial CD players are introduced. Bishop Desmund Tutu, general secretary of the South African Council of Churches, wins the Nobel Peace Prize.

1985

1985

在宾夕法尼亚州费城和伦敦举行的 Live Aid 演唱会为埃塞俄比亚的饥荒救济筹集了超过 5000 万英镑。

The Live Aid pop concerts in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and London raise over £50 million for famine relief in Ethiopia.

米哈伊尔·戈尔巴乔夫当选苏联共产党最高领导人，并推行改革。南非取消了种族通婚禁令。日本推出了CD-ROM（只读光盘）。澳大利亚诞生了第一个冷冻胚胎婴儿。英国拨出了第一个手机电话（由喜剧演员厄尼·怀斯拨打给沃达丰）。孟加拉国热带风暴造成1万人死亡；墨西哥城地震造成9000人死亡；哥伦比亚内华达·德·鲁伊斯火山爆发造成23000人死亡。微软发布了Windows操作系统的第一个版本。英国科学家亚历克·杰弗里斯开发了基因指纹识别技术。

Mikhail Gorbachev is elected Soviet party leader and introduces reforms. South Africa ends its ban on interracial marriages. In Japan, the CD-ROM (Compact Disk Read-Only Memory) is introduced. In Australia, the first child is born from a frozen embryo. The first British cellphone call is made (by comedian Ernie Wise, to Vodafone). A total of 10,000 die in tropical storms in Bangladesh; 9,000 die in an earthquake in Mexico City; 23,000 die when the Nevada del Ruiz volcano erupts in Colombia. Microsoft releases the first version of its Windows operating system. British scientist Alec Jeffreys develops genetic fingerprinting.

1986

1986

西班牙和葡萄牙加入欧洲共同体。南非在150万黑人举行全国性罢工后宣布进入紧急状态。美国战机轰炸利比亚，以报复利比亚的恐怖活动。约韦里·穆塞韦尼在经过五年的解放斗争后成为乌干达总统。让-克洛德·杜瓦利埃总统逃离海地；他的家族统治海地长达28年。菲律宾总统马科斯因其选举胜利受到质疑而逃亡；科拉松·阿基诺继任总统。《拉罗汤加条约》设立了南太平洋无核区。喀麦隆尼奥斯火山湖喷发的有毒气体造成2000人死亡。《牛津英语词典》 （Se至Z）的最终增补本出版，距离第一版出版已过去一个多世纪。挑战者号航天飞机在升空后不久爆炸，机上七名宇航员全部遇难，其中包括首位乘坐航天飞机的平民乘客。苏联发射了和平号空间站。基辅的切尔诺贝利核电站发生了世界上最严重的核事故，其放射性尘埃几乎影响了整个欧洲。英国记者约翰·麦卡锡在贝鲁特被绑架，于1991年获释。阿根廷在墨西哥赢得世界杯冠军。

Spain and Portugal join the European Community. A state of emergency is declared in South Africa after a general strike by 1.5 million blacks. US warplanes bomb Libya in retaliation for Libyan terrorist activity. Yoweri Museveni becomes president of Uganda after a five-year liberation struggle. President Jean-Claude Duvalier flees Haiti; his family have ruled for 28 years. President Marcos of the Philippines flees after doubts about his election victory; Corazon Aquino becomes president. The Treaty of Rarotonga sets up a South Pacific Nuclear-Free Zone. Toxic gas from the volcanic Lake Nyos in Cameroon kills 2,000. The final supplement of the Oxford English Dictionary (Se to Z) is published, more than a century after the first edition. The space shuttle Challenger explodes not long after take-off, killing all seven crew members, including the first civilian spaceship passenger. The Soviet Union launches the Mir space station. The Chernobyl power station in Kiev is the source of the world’s worst nuclear accident with fallout affecting almost all of Europe. British journalist John McCarthy is kidnapped in Beirut; he is released in 1991. Argentina win the World Cup in Mexico.

1987

1987

地球人口达到50亿。玛格丽特·撒切尔在英国赢得第三次大选。10月19日，黑色星期一，全球股市暴跌。苏联领导人戈尔巴乔夫宣布其“公开性”（glasnost）和“改革”（perestroika）政策。苏联军队开始从阿富汗撤军。巴勒斯坦人起义（Intifada）爆发，起义对象为以色列。文森特·梵高的《鸢尾花》以4900万美元的价格成为世界上最昂贵的画作。坎特伯雷大主教的特使特里·韦特在贝鲁特被绑架，并于1991年获释。《辛普森一家》在电视上首播。美国进行了首例心肺移植手术。纳粹战犯鲁道夫·赫斯被发现死于施潘道监狱的牢房中，他自二战以来一直被关押在那里。连接法国和英国的英吉利海峡隧道开始动工。

The population of the earth is five billion. Margaret Thatcher wins her third general election in the United Kingdom. On Black Monday, 19 October, stockmarkets around the world plummet. Soviet leader Gorbachev announces his policies of glasnost (openness) and perestroika (reconstruction). Soviet forces begin a withdrawal from Afghanistan. The Palestinian Intifada uprising against Israel begins. Vincent Van Gogh’s Irises becomes the world’s most expensive painting at $49 million. Terry Waite, special envoy of the Archbishop of Canterbury, is kidnapped in Beirut; he is released in 1991. The Simpsons debuts on television. The first heart–lung transplant takes place in the United States. Nazi war criminal Rudolf Hess is found dead in his cell in Spandau Prison where he had been incarcerated since the World War II. Work begins on the Channel Tunnel linking France and England.

1988

1988

一架泛美航空波音747客机在苏格兰洛克比上空爆炸，造成270人死亡；人们认为叙利亚支持的恐怖分子对此负责。

A Pan Am Boeing 747 is blown up over Lockerbie, Scotland, killing 270 people; Syrian-backed terrorists are thought responsible.

科索沃的阿尔巴尼亚族人举行示威游行，要求脱离塞尔维亚独立。两伊战争达成停火协议，据估计已有100万人丧生。伊拉克政府军对库尔德城镇哈拉布贾发动毒气袭击。贝娜齐尔·布托成为首位领导伊斯兰国家的女性。乔治·H·W·布什就任美国总统。百忧解上市。可卡因开始流行。亚美尼亚发生地震，造成8万人死亡。伦敦环球剧院遗址重见天日。奥运会在韩国首尔举行。巴西工会和环保活动家奇科·门德斯被反对他的牧场主暗杀。

Ethnic Albanians in Kosovo demonstrate for independence from Serbia. A ceasefire comes into being in the Iran–Iraq War; an estimated one million lives have been lost. The Iraqi government forces carry out a poison gas attack on the Kurdish town of Halabja. Benazir Bhutto becomes the first woman to lead an Islamic nation. George H.W. Bush becomes president of the United States. Prozac becomes available. The drug Crack cocaine gains popularity. A total of 80,000 die in an earthquake in Armenia. The original Globe Theatre is uncovered in London. The Olympic Games are held in Seoul, South Korea. Brazilian union and environmental activist Chico Mendes is assassinated by ranchers opposed to him.

1989

1989

反共革命席卷中欧和东欧。东德共产党政府辞职；柏林墙被拆除。波兰共产党承认团结工会合法化；团结工会赢得选举。罗马尼亚的抗议者推翻了总统尼古拉·齐奥塞斯库，并处决了他和他的妻子。剧作家瓦茨拉夫·哈维尔成为新成立的非共产主义捷克斯洛伐克的总统。巴基斯坦重新加入英联邦，此前它于1972年退出该联邦。赞比亚和其他一些国家通过民主选举实现了政府更迭。美国入侵巴拿马，推翻了其统治者诺列加将军。巴拉圭发生军事政变，推翻了自1954年以来一直掌权的阿尔弗雷多·斯特罗斯纳。智利举行了16年来的首次自由选举。弗雷德里克·威廉·德克勒克接替彼得·威廉·博塔成为南非总统。在中国北京天安门广场爆发了大规模的民主示威游行；最终以屠杀告终。日本昭和时代结束，裕仁天皇驾崩；明仁天皇即位。越南军队撤出柬埔寨。缅甸在军事政变后更名为缅甸联邦；反对派领导人昂山素季被软禁。埃克森·瓦尔迪兹号油轮造成世界历史上最大规模的漏油事故（1100万加仑）。天空电视台在欧洲开播。针对英印裔作家萨尔曼·鲁西迪的《撒旦诗篇》发布了追杀令。

Anti-communist revolutions take place all over Central and Eastern Europe. East Germany’s communist government resigns; the Berlin Wall is dismantled. The Communist Party in Poland legalizes the Solidarity union; Solidarity wins the election. Protesters in Romania overthrow President Nicolae Ceauçescu and execute him and his wife. Playwright Vaclav Havel becomes president of the newly non-communist Czechoslovakia. Pakistan rejoins the British Commonwealth from which it withdrew in 1972. Zambia and other countries see changes of government by democratic election. The United States invades Panama and deposes its ruler, General Noriega. A military coup in Paraguay overthrows Alfredo Stroessner who has been in power since 1954. Chile holds its first free election in 16 years. F.W. de Klerk succeeds P.W. Botha as president in South Africa. Mass demonstrations for democracy take place in Tiananmen Square in Beijing, China; they end in massacre. The Showa period in Japan ends with the death of Emperor Hirohito; Akihito becomes Emperor. Vietnamese troops withdraw from Cambodia. Burma is renamed Myanmar after a military coup; opposition leader Aung San Suu Kyi is placed under house arrest. The tanker Exxon Valdez causes the world’s biggest oil spill (11 million gallons). Sky Television is launched in Europe. A Fatwah is announced on Anglo-Indian author Salman Rushdie, for writing The Satanic Verses.

1990

1990

纳尔逊·曼德拉从南非监狱获释；种族隔离制度的瓦解进程开始。

Nelson Mandela is freed from prison in South Africa; the process of dismantling apartheid begins.

世界人口达到52.5亿。伦敦爆发骚乱，抗议玛格丽特·撒切尔的“人头税”。东西德统一，赫尔穆特·科尔出任总理。斯洛博丹·米洛绍维奇就任塞尔维亚总统。团结工会领导人莱赫·瓦文萨当选波兰总统。黎巴嫩内战期间，叙利亚军队入侵黎巴嫩，推翻了米歇尔·奥恩将军的政府。伊拉克入侵科威特；美国及其盟国向海湾地区派遣军队，海湾战争爆发。桑地诺民族解放阵线在尼加拉瓜大选中落败。纳米比亚获得独立。哈勃太空望远镜投入使用。文森特·梵高的《加歇医生肖像》以8250万美元的价格成为世界上最昂贵的画作。西德队在意大利赢得世界杯冠军。

The population of the world is 5¼ billion. Riots break out in London against Margaret Thatcher’s poll tax. East and West Germany are unified as one nation; Helmut Kohl becomes chancellor. Slobodan Milošovi´c becomes president of Serbia. Solidarity’s leader Lech Walesa is elected president of Poland. In the Lebanese Civil War, Syrian military forces invade Lebanon and oust General Michel Aoun’s government. Iraq invades Kuwait; the United States and allies send forces to the Gulf region and the Gulf War begins. The Sandinistas are defeated in elections in Nicaragua. Namibia gains independence. The Hubble Space Telescope comes into operation. Vincent Van Gogh’s Portrait of Dr Gachet becomes the world’s most expensive painting at $82.5 million. West Germany win the World Cup in Italy.

1991

1991

约翰·梅杰接替玛格丽特·撒切尔成为英国首相。苏联解体；戈尔巴乔夫辞职；鲍里斯·叶利钦在俄罗斯掌权；波罗的海三国宣布脱离苏联独立；华沙条约组织解散；苏联于12月9日不复存在。盟军解放科威特。拉吉夫·甘地在印度遇刺身亡。孟加拉国遭遇飓风袭击，造成20万人死亡；随后吉大港三角洲的风暴潮又造成15万人死亡。萨尔瓦多长达十年的内战结束。南非废除种族隔离制度；纳尔逊·曼德拉成为南非首位黑人总统。蒂姆·伯纳斯-李推出万维网。在黎巴嫩被扣押近五年的北爱尔兰作家布莱恩·基南获释。

John Major replaces Margaret Thatcher as prime minister in Britain. The break-up of the Soviet Union; the resignation of Gorbachev; Boris Yeltsin takes power in Russia; the Baltic states declare independence from the Soviet Union; the Warsaw Pact is dissolved; the USSR ceases to exist on 9 December. Allied forces liberate Kuwait. Rajiv Gandhi is assassinated in India. A cyclone in Bangladesh kills 200,000; a later storm surge in the Chittagong Delta kills another 150,000. The decade-long civil war in El Salvador comes to an end. Apartheid is dismantled in South Africa; Nelson Mandela becomes its first black president. Tim Berners-Lee launches the World Wide Web. Northern Irish writer Brian Keenan, held hostage for nearly five years in Lebanon, is released.

1992

1992

约翰·梅杰意外赢得英国大选。黑色星期三，英镑和意大利里拉被迫退出欧洲汇率机制；英国财政部估计损失高达34亿英镑。《马斯特里赫特条约》签署，创建了欧盟。南斯拉夫解体，爆发血腥内战；联合国维和部队进驻；斯洛文尼亚和克罗地亚获得独立。阿尔及利亚总统穆罕默德·布迪亚夫被保镖刺杀；该国动荡不安直至2002年。比尔·克林顿击败时任总统乔治·布什和独立候选人罗斯·佩罗，当选美国总统。萨尔瓦多内战持续12年后结束。台湾解除对中国大陆的贸易和社会联系禁令。布特罗斯·布特罗斯·加利就任联合国秘书长。巴塞罗那奥运会举行。英国查尔斯王子和戴安娜王妃宣布分居。英国女王将 922 年描述为“恐怖之年”。

John Major unexpectedly wins the general election in Britain. Black Wednesday; the pound and the Italian lira are forced out of the European Exchange Rate Mechanism; the British Treasury estimates the cost to be £3.4 billion. The Maastricht Treaty, creating the European Union, is signed. Yugoslavia breaks up and erupts into bloody civil war; a UN peacekeeping force is sent in; Slovenia and Croatia gain independence. A bodyguard assassinates President Muhammad Boudiaf of Algeria; the country experiences turmoil until 2002. Bill Clinton defeats the incumbent, George Bush, and independent, Ross Perot, to become president of the United States. The civil war in El Salvador ends after 12 years. Taiwan suspends the ban on trade and social links with China. Boutros Boutros Ghali becomes Secretary-General of the United Nations. The Olympic Games are held in Barcelona. Prince Charles and Princess Diana of Britain announce they are to separate; the British Queen describes 1992 as an Annus Horribilis.

1993

1993

艾滋病成为美国25至44岁男性最大的杀手。

AIDS becomes the biggest killer of US men aged 25 to 44.

两名儿童在英国沃灵顿因爱尔兰共和军炸弹爆炸身亡。捷克斯洛伐克分裂为捷克共和国和斯洛伐克共和国。巴勒斯坦领导人亚西尔·阿拉法特和以色列总理拉宾在美国签署和平协议；阿拉法特成立巴勒斯坦民族权力机构，管辖加沙和杰里科。厄立特里亚（位于埃塞俄比亚北部）脱离埃塞俄比亚。19名美军士兵在索马里摩加迪沙与当地民兵的激烈战斗中阵亡。斯里兰卡总统拉纳辛哈·普雷马达萨被泰米尔猛虎组织自杀式炸弹袭击者刺杀身亡。为报复美国前总统乔治·布什访问科威特期间遭遇的暗杀未遂事件，美国向位于巴格达曼苏尔区的伊拉克情报总部发射巡航导弹。朝鲜拒绝进入其核设施，并退出《不扩散核武器条约》。纽约世界贸易中心发生恐怖袭击，造成6人死亡。印度地震致1万人死亡。

Two children die when an IRA bomb explodes in Warrington, England. Czechoslovakia splits into the Czech and Slovak Rebublics. Palestinian leader, Yasser Arafat, and Israeli prime minister, Rabin, sign a peace agreement in the United States; Arafat forms the Palestine National Authority to govern Gaza and Jericho. Eritrea (in north Ethiopia) breaks away from Ethiopia. Nineteen American soldiers die in a major battle with local militia in Mogadishu in Somalia. President Ranasinghe Premadasa of Sri Lanka is assassinated by a Tamil Tiger suicide bomber. America launches a cruise missile attack on Iraqi intelligence headquarters in the Al-Mansur District of Baghdad, in response to the attempted assassination of former US president George Bush during a visit to Kuwait. North Korea refuses access to nuclear sites and withdraws from the Nuclear Non-proliferation Treaty. A terrorist bomb goes off in the World Trade Center in New York, killing six. 10,000 die in an earthquake in India.

1994

1994

在爱尔兰，临时爱尔兰共和军宣布停止军事行动。波斯尼亚塞族军队的一枚迫击炮弹在萨拉热窝的一个市场造成68名平民死亡。俄罗斯镇压了车臣叛乱。美国总统比尔·克林顿和俄罗斯总统鲍里斯·叶利钦签署了《克里姆林宫协议》，停止了预先设定的、瞄准两国目标的核导弹发射。约旦和以色列签署了结束两国冲突的条约。非洲人国民大会（非国大）赢得了南非历史上首次多种族选举。在卢旺达内战中，共有50万图西族人被胡图族武装分子杀害。以色列总理伊扎克·拉宾遇刺身亡；本雅明·内塔尼亚胡继任总理，并终止了以巴和平协议。越南恢复了与美国的外交关系。金正日接替其父成为朝鲜领导人。世界贸易组织成立，旨在促进全球经济发展。连接英国和法国的英法海底隧道开通。英国建立了世界上第一个基于DNA的犯罪数据库。在线拍卖网站eBay成立。体育传奇人物O·J·辛普森因谋杀罪受审，并于1995年被判无罪。赛车手艾尔顿·塞纳在圣马力诺大奖赛中发生事故身亡。巴西队在美国赢得世界杯冠军。

In Ireland, the Provisional IRA announces a cessation of military operations. A Bosnian Serb army mortar shell kills 68 civilians in a Sarajevo market. A Chechnyan revolt is crushed by Russia. US president Bill Clinton and Russian president Boris Yeltsin sign the Kremlin Accords, stopping the preprogrammed aiming of nuclear missiles towards each country’s targets. Jordan and Israel sign a treaty ending conflict between the two countries. The African National Congress (ANC) wins the first multi-racial election ever held in South Africa. A total of 500,000 Tutsi are killed by Hutu gangs in civil war in Rwanda. Itzhak Rabin, prime minister of Israel, is assassinated; Benjamin Netanyahu becomes prime minister and brings the Israeli–Palestinian accord to an end. Vietnam restores diplomatic relations with the United States. Kim Jong Il replaces his father as leader in North Korea. The World Trade Organization is created to promote global economic development. The Channel Tunnel, linking Britain and France, is opened. Britain creates the world’s first DNA-based crime database. Online auction site eBay is founded. Sports legend, O.J. Simpson, is tried for murder and is acquitted in 1995. Racing driver Ayrton Senna is killed in an accident at the San Marino Grand Prix. Brazil win the World Cup in the United States.

1995

1995

雅克·希拉克就任法国总统。北约轰炸波斯尼亚境内的塞尔维亚军队阵地。21名波斯尼亚塞族指挥官被控犯有种族灭绝罪和反人类罪；波斯尼亚和平协议达成。在伊拉克，萨达姆·侯赛因继续阻挠搜寻大规模杀伤性武器。巴林银行因经纪人尼克·里森在东京证券交易所损失14亿美元而倒闭。美国俄克拉荷马城一座联邦大楼发生爆炸，造成168人死亡。博斯曼法案在足球界生效，允许球员在合同到期后自由转会。

Jacques Chirac becomes president of France. NATO bombs Serbian troop positions in Bosnia. Twenty-one Bosnian Serb commanders are charged with genocide and crimes against humanity; a peace agreement for Bosnia is reached. In Iraq, Saddam Hussein continues to hinder searches for weapons of mass destruction. Barings Bank collapses after broker Nick Leeson loses $1.4 billion on the Tokyo Stock Exchange. A bomb is exploded in a federal building in Oklahoma City, United States, killing 168 people. The Bosman Ruling is introduced in football, allowing footballers to move freely at the end of their contracts.

1996

1996

互联网搜索引擎谷歌正式上线。

Internet seach engine Google is launched.

爱尔兰共和军停火协议因伦敦金丝雀码头的炸弹袭击而终止；与新芬党的和平谈判于6月开始。鲍里斯·叶利钦与车臣达成停火协议。塔利班在阿富汗夺取政权并实施严格的伊斯兰教法。奥萨马·本·拉登被驱逐出苏丹，前往阿富汗。伊拉克主要的生物战剂生产设施哈卡姆在联合国特别委员会（UNSCOM）的监督下被摧毁。亚西尔·阿拉法特在巴勒斯坦首次选举中当选总统。以色列对真主党发动大规模攻势。比尔·克林顿再次当选美国总统。美国对伊拉克发动“沙漠风暴”行动。疯牛病爆发导致英国禁止牛肉出口。日本首批DVD播放机问世。吉隆坡双子塔成为世界最高建筑。Java编程语言的第一个版本发布。托马斯·汉密尔顿在苏格兰邓布兰的一所学校枪杀了16名儿童。奥运会在美国亚特兰大举行。查尔斯和戴安娜离婚。爵士歌手艾拉·菲茨杰拉德去世。

The IRA ceasefire is ended by a bomb in Canary Wharf in London; peace talks with Sinn Féin begin in June. Boris Yeltsin negotiates a ceasefire with the Chechnyans. The Taliban seize power in Afghanistan and impose strict Islamic law. Osama Bin Laden is expelled from Sudan and moves to Afghanistan. Al-Hakam, Iraq’s main production facility of biological warfare agents, is destroyed under the supervision of the United Nations Special Commission (UNSCOM). Yasser Arafat is voted president in the first Palestinian elections. Israel launches a major offensive against Hezbollah. Bill Clinton is re-elected as president of the United States. The US launches Operation Desert Strike against Iraq. An outbreak of mad cow disease leads to a ban on exports of beef from the UK. In Japan, the first DVD players are released. The Petronas Towers in Kuala Lumpur become the world’s tallest buildings. The first version of Java programming language is released. Sixteen children are killed by Thomas Hamilton in a school at Dunblane in Scotland. The Olympic Games take place in Atlanta in the United States. Charles and Diana divorce. Jazz singer Ella Fitzgerald dies.

1997

1997

威尔士王妃戴安娜在巴黎的一场车祸中丧生；超过十亿人观看了她的葬礼。

Diana, Princess of Wales dies in a car crash in Paris; more than a billion people watch her funeral.

工党的托尼·布莱尔就任英国首相。威尔士和苏格兰投票赞成设立各自的议会。俄罗斯和车臣签署和平条约。以色列将希伯伦归还巴勒斯坦，这是以色列控制的最后一个西岸城市。伊拉克宣布将开始击落联合国特委会的监控设备。扎伊尔更名为刚果民主共和国；总统蒙博托逃亡。香港回归中国。中华人民共和国最后一位主要革命家邓小平逝世。柬埔寨人民党的洪森发动政变推翻了诺罗敦·拉那烈。英国科学家克隆了一只成年绵羊，并将其命名为多莉。海尔-博普彗星近日点近地球，导致39名“天堂之门”邪教成员自杀。J·K·罗琳出版了她的第一部《哈利·波特》系列小说，开启了出版业的辉煌。切·格瓦拉的遗骸被运回古巴安葬。设计师詹尼·范思哲在佛罗里达州被枪杀。特蕾莎修女逝世。香港扑杀所有鸡只，试图阻止致命流感病毒的传播。伟哥成为美国史上销售速度最快的药物。泰格·伍兹成为赢得美国大师赛最年轻的选手。

Labour’s Tony Blair becomes British prime minister. Wales and Scotland vote in favour of having their own parliaments. Russia and Chechnya sign a peace treaty. Israel hands Hebron back to the Palestinians, the last West Bank city it controlled. Iraq says it will begin shooting down UNSCOM surveillance. Zaire becomes the Democratic Republic of the Congo; President Mobutu flees. Hong Kong reverts to Chinese rule. Deng Xiaoping, the last of the People’s Republic of China’s major revolutionaries, dies. Hun Sen of the Cambodian People’s Party overthrows Norodom Ranariddh in a coup. British scientists clone an adult sheep; they name her Dolly. The comet Hale-Bopp makes its closest approach to Earth, inspiring 39 Heaven’s Gate cult members to commit suicide. J.K. Rowling publishes the first of her Harry Potter books, launching a publishing phenomenon. Che Guevara’s remains are returned to Cuba for burial. Designer Gianni Versace is shot to death in Florida. Mother Theresa dies. Hong Kong kills all chickens in an attempt to stop the spread of a deadly influenza strain. Viagra becomes the fastest-selling drug of all time in the United States. Tiger Woods becomes the youngest person to win the Masters golf tournament.

1998

1998

英国和爱尔兰政府以及北爱尔兰大多数政党签署了《贝尔法斯特协议》；北爱尔兰奥马爆炸案造成29人死亡。北约对南斯拉夫发动空袭；米洛舍维奇总统奉命从科索沃撤军。伊拉克阻止联合国武器核查人员进行搜查；联合国秘书长科菲·安南斡旋达成协议，避免战争爆发。印度和巴基斯坦开始进行核武器试验。美国总统比尔·克林顿因莫妮卡·莱温斯基事件遭到弹劾。乌戈·查韦斯就任委内瑞拉总统。在南非，真相与和解委员会谴责冲突双方犯下暴行。东南亚爆发经济危机。苏哈托总统在担任印尼总统32年后辞职。厄尔尼诺现象被认为是造成干旱和酷暑的原因。东道主法国队赢得世界杯冠军。智利前总统奥古斯托·皮诺切特将军在英国接受治疗期间被软禁。欧洲人权法院在斯特拉斯堡成立。国际空间站开始建造。歌手弗兰克·辛纳屈因心脏病去世，享年82岁。

The Belfast Agreement is signed between the British and Irish governments and most Northern Irish political parties; the Omagh bombing in Northern Ireland kills 29. NATO launches air strikes against Yugoslavia; President Milošovi ´c is ordered to withdraw troops from Kosovo. Iraq stops UN weapons inspectors from conducting searches; Kofi Annan, UN secretary-general brokers a deal that prevents war. India and Pakistan begin testing nuclear weapons. Impeachment proceedings begin against US president Bill Clinton for the Monica Lewinsky affair. Hugo Chavez becomes Venezuelan president. In South Africa, the Truth and Reconciliation Commission condemns both sides for committing atrocities. An economic crisis strikes South East Asia. President Suharto resigns after 32 years as president of Indonesia. The ocean-atmospheric phenomenon, El Niño, is blamed for droughts and scorching temperatures. Hosts France win the World Cup. Former Chilean president, General Augusto Pinochet, is placed under house arrest during medical treatment in the UK. The European Court of Human Rights is instituted in Strasbourg. Construction of the International Space Station begins. Singer Frank Sinatra, dies of a heart attack, aged 82.

1999

1999

苏格兰和威尔士议会举行首次会议。欧元正式发行。南斯拉夫与北约之间的战争爆发，持续到六月。匈牙利、波兰和捷克共和国加入北约。俄罗斯入侵车臣。穆罕默德六世成为摩洛哥国王。约旦国王侯赛因去世，其子阿卜杜拉二世继位。埃胡德·巴拉克成为以色列总理。尼日利亚结束军人统治。佩尔韦兹·穆沙拉夫将军在巴基斯坦发动不流血军事政变夺取政权。美国总统克林顿的弹劾案失败。巴拿马运河归巴拿马控制。澳大利亚投票决定保留女王为国家元首。葡萄牙将澳门归还中国。东帝汶投票决定脱离印度尼西亚独立。MySpace.com网站上线。科罗拉多州发生科伦拜恩校园枪击案。BBC主持人吉尔·丹多被枪杀。欧洲和亚洲观测到日全食。土耳其发生地震，造成17000人死亡。随着千禧年的临近，世界对计算机的千年虫问题过度担忧。

The first meetings take place of the Scottish and Welsh parliaments. The Euro currency is introduced. War breaks out between Yugoslavia and NATO until June. Hungary, Poland and the Czech Republic join NATO. Russia invades Chechnya. Mohammed VI becomes king of Morocco. King Hussein of Jordan dies; his son Abdullah II ascends the throne. Ehud Barak becomes prime minister of Israel. Military rule ends in Nigeria. General Pervez Musharraf seizes power in Pakistan in a bloodless military coup. The impeachment of US President Clinton fails. The Panama Canal comes under Panamanian control. Australia votes to keep the Queen as head of state. Portugal hands Macau over to China. East Timor votes for independence from Indonesia. MySpace.com is launched. The Columbine massacre takes place in Colorado. BBC presenter Jill Dando is shot dead. A total solar eclipse is viewed in Europe and Asia. An earthquake kills 17,000 in Turkey. The world worries unduly about Y2K date-handling problems on computers as the millennium approaches.

2000

2000

世界庆祝千禧年之际，世界人口已达六十亿。英国爆发了燃油抗议活动。弗拉基米尔·普京当选俄罗斯总统。南斯拉夫总统斯洛博丹·米洛绍维奇被迫下台。克罗地亚总统斯捷潘·梅西奇当选。在经历了多年的杀戮和恐怖活动后，阿尔及利亚的伊斯兰救世阵线解散。恐怖组织基地组织召开峰会。巴沙尔·阿萨德在全民公投中成为叙利亚领导人。印度议会遭到恐怖分子袭击后，印巴两国险些爆发战争。在亚丁，美国海军“科尔”号驱逐舰遭到自杀式炸弹袭击，造成17人死亡。大约在同一时期，艾滋病在非洲蔓延；在一些国家，近40%的人口感染了艾滋病毒。乔治·W·布什在历史上最接近的总统选举中当选美国总统；由于选票争议，选举结果被推迟了一个月公布。比森特·福克斯当选墨西哥总统，成为自1929年以来首位来自非革命制度党（PRI）的总统。阿尔韦托·藤森被解除秘鲁总统职务。森喜朗就任日本首相。“互联网泡沫”破灭，许多企业倒闭。英国医生哈罗德·希普曼因涉嫌杀害365人而被判处终身监禁。汉斯·布利克斯就任联合国监测、核查和视察委员会（监核会）主席。悉尼奥运会举行。一架协和式超音速客机在巴黎坠毁，机上100名乘客全部遇难。

As the world celebrates the millennium, its population has risen to six billion. There are fuel protests in Britain. Vladimir Putin is elected president of Russia. Yugoslav president Slobodan Milošovi´c is forced from office. In Croatia, Stjepan Mesic is elected president. After years of killing and terror, the Islamic Salvation Front disbands in Algeria. Terrorist organization al-Qaeda holds a summit. Bashar al-Assad becomes Syria’s leader in a national referendum. India and Pakistan come close to war after the Indian parliament is attacked by terrorists. In Aden the USS Cole is damaged by suicide bombers, killing 17. Around this time, AIDS becomes an epidemic in Africa; in some countries, almost 40 per cent of the population is HIV-positive. George W Bush becomes president of the United States in the closest election ever; the result is delayed for a month because of disputed votes. Vincente Fox becomes Mexican president, the first president from a party other than the PRI since 1929. Alberto Fujimori is sacked as president of Peru. Yoshiro Mori becomes prime minister of Japan. The ‘dotcom boom’ goes bust and many businesses go under. British doctor Harold Shipman is sentenced to life in prison, suspected of having killed 365 people. Hans Blix becomes president of the United Nations Monitoring, Verification and Inspection Commission (UNMOVIC). The Olympics are held in Sydney. A Concorde supersonic jet crashes in Paris, killing all 100 passengers.

2001

2001

9·11事件：基地组织恐怖分子劫持的飞机撞向纽约世界贸易中心和华盛顿五角大楼，造成近3000人死亡。美国推翻了阿富汗塔利班政权。

9/11: planes hijacked by al-Qaeda terrorists are crashed into the World Trade Center in New York and the Pentagon in Washington DC, killing nearly 3,000 people. The United States brings down the Taliban government of Afghanistan.

在英国，托尼·布莱尔领导的工党赢得大选。英国爆发口蹄疫。传媒大亨西尔维奥·贝卢斯科尼第二次出任意大利总理。斯洛博丹·米洛绍维奇投降，接受战争罪审判。阿里埃勒·沙龙当选以色列总理；以色列与巴勒斯坦之间的暴力冲突加剧。英国和美国对伊拉克国防网络进行轰炸。佩尔韦兹·穆沙拉夫就任巴基斯坦总统。在印度古吉拉特邦，超过2万人死于地震。小泉纯一郎就任日本首相。格洛丽亚·马卡帕加尔·阿罗约就任菲律宾总统。约翰·霍华德再次当选澳大利亚总理。苹果公司发布iPod。安然公司申请破产。印度成为继中国之后第二个人口超过10亿的国家。

In Britain, Tony Blair’s Labour Party win the general election. Foot and Mouth breaks out in Britain. Media magnate Silvio Berlusconi becomes prime minister of Italy for the second time. Slobodan Milošovi´c surrenders to be tried for war crimes. Ariel Sharon is elected prime minister of Israel; violence with Palestinians worsens. Britain and the United States make bombing raids on the Iraqi defence network. Pervez Musharraf becomes president of Pakistan. In Gujurat in India, more than 20,000 die in an earthquake. Junichiro Koizumi becomes prime minister of Japan. Gloria Macapagal-Arroyo becomes president of the Philippines. John Howard is re-elected prime minister in Australia. Apple releases the iPod. Enron files for bankruptcy. India becomes the second country, after China, to have one billion inhabitants.

2002

2002

欧盟推出欧元，成为其众多成员国的新货币。雅克·希拉克继续担任法国总统。瑞士加入联合国。前南斯拉夫总统斯洛博丹·米洛舍维奇的审判在海牙开庭。以色列入侵加沙地带和约旦河西岸，并在其约旦河西岸定居点周围修建了一道巨大的隔离墙。印度和巴基斯坦继续就克什米尔问题发生争端，核战争的威胁迫在眉睫。斯里兰卡开始停火。刚果民主共和国尼拉贡戈火山爆发，导致40万人流离失所。美国国会授权总统在认为必要和适当的情况下动用美国武装部队对伊拉克采取行动。联合国安理会通过第1441号决议，迫使萨达姆·侯赛因解除武装，否则将面临“严重后果”；伊拉克同意接受决议条款。朝鲜承认一直在寻求发展核能力。恐怖分子炸毁巴厘岛两家夜总会，造成202人死亡。东帝汶宣布独立。世界最高桥梁米洛高架桥正式通车。南极洲巨大的拉森冰架开始崩解。伊丽莎白王太后逝世，享年101岁。巴西队在韩日世界杯上夺冠。洪水席卷中欧，造成大范围破坏。

The European Union launches the Euro, the new currency of many of its member states. Jacqes Chirac retains the French presidency. Switzerland joins the United Nations. The trial of former Yugoslav President Slobodan Milošovi´c opens in The Hague. Israel invades the Gaza Strip and West Bank; it builds a huge wall around its West Bank settlements. India and Pakistan continue their dispute over Kashmir and nuclear war is threatened. A ceasefire begins in Sri Lanka. 400,000 people are displaced by the eruption of Mount Nyiragongo in the Democratic Republic of the Congo. The United States Congress authorizes the president to use the United States Armed Forces as he deems necessary and appropriate, against Iraq. The United Nations Security Council approves Resolution 1441, forcing Saddam Hussein to disarm or face ‘serious consequences’; Iraq agrees to its terms. North Korea admits to have been pursuing nuclear capability. Terrorists blow up two nightclubs in Bali, killing 202. East Timor becomes independent. The Millau Viaduct, the world’s tallest bridge, is opened. The huge Larsen Ice Shelf in Antarctica begins to disintegrate. Queen Elizabeth the Queen Mother dies aged 101. Brazil win the World Cup in South Korea and Japan. Floods cause widespread damage in central Europe.

2003

2003

美国领导的联军入侵伊拉克；萨达姆·侯赛因被俘，他的儿子们被杀，但人们认为那里存在的大规模杀伤性武器却没有被找到。

A coalition led by the United States invades Iraq; Saddam Hussein is captured and his sons are killed, but the weapons of mass destruction thought to be there are not found.

格鲁吉亚玫瑰革命成功；爱德华·谢瓦德纳尔泽辞职。以色列轰炸叙利亚。联合国维和部队被派往利比里亚。苏丹达尔富尔地区爆发种族和宗教冲突。人类基因组计划完成，该计划旨在识别和绘制人类DNA中的所有基因图谱。哥伦比亚号航天飞机爆炸，机上七名宇航员全部遇难。胡锦涛就任中国国家主席。中国发射了首次载人航天任务。SARS病毒从中国传播开来；最早发现该病毒的卡洛·乌尔巴尼医生死于该疾病。美国中央情报局泄密丑闻始于《华盛顿邮报》刊登特工瓦莱丽·普莱姆的名字。前联合国武器核查员大卫·凯利自杀身亡；他的死引发了赫顿调查。欧洲遭遇热浪；巴黎475人死于高温。演员阿诺德·施瓦辛格就任加利福尼亚州州长。中国发射了首次载人航天任务。协和式飞机完成了最后一次商业飞行。迈克尔·杰克逊因猥亵儿童被捕。英格兰队赢得橄榄球世界杯。利比亚人阿里·穆罕默德·迈格拉希被判犯有1988年苏格兰洛克比空难（泛美航空103号航班）的罪行。伊朗东南部巴姆发生地震，造成超过4万人死亡。

The Georgian Rose Revolution succeeds; Eduard Shevadnardze resigns. Israel bombs Syria. A UN peacekeeping force is sent to Liberia. Ethnic and religious turmoil erupts in Sudan’s Darfur region. The Human Genome Project, identifying and mapping all the genes in human DNA, is completed. The Columbia space shuttle blows up, killing all seven of its crew. Hu Jintao becomes president of China. China launches its first manned space mission. The SARS virus spreads from China; Doctor Carlo Urbani, who first identified it, dies of the disease. The CIA leak scandal begins in the United States when agent Valerie Plame’s name is released in the Washington Post. David Kelly, former UN weapons inspector, commits suicide; his death leads to the Hutton enquiry. There is a heatwave in Europe; 475 people die in Paris. Actor Arnold Schwarzenegger becomes governor of California. China launches its first manned space mission. Concorde makes its last commercial flight. Michael Jackson is arrested for child molestation. England win the Rugby World Cup. Libyan Al Ali Mohmed Al Megrahi, is convicted of bombing Pan Am Flight 103 over Lockerbie in Scotland in 1988. More than 40,000 die in an earthquake in Bam in the south-east of Iran.

2004

2004

《建立欧洲第一部宪法的条约和最后文件》在罗马签署。马德里高峰时段列车爆炸，造成190人死亡。弗拉基米尔·普京再次当选俄罗斯总统。乌克兰大选结果被宣布无效；举行新的选举，反对派候选人维克托·尤先科获胜。俄罗斯车臣叛军占领一所学校；300多名成人和儿童丧生。伊拉克阿布格莱布监狱的战俘被曝遭到美军酷刑。在伊拉克，美国领导的联军将主权移交给临时政府。联合国安理会呼吁所有外国军队撤出黎巴嫩。哈米德·卡尔扎伊当选阿富汗总统。乔治·W·布什再次当选美国总统；康多莉扎·赖斯出任国务卿。海地爆发叛乱，让-贝特朗·阿里斯蒂德下台。诺罗敦·西哈莫尼王子成为柬埔寨国王。历史上最严重的自然灾害之一——海啸袭击印度尼西亚和南亚，造成30万人死亡。台北101大楼成为世界最高建筑。干旱和蝗灾威胁着西非萨赫勒地区数百万人的生命。哈罗德·希普曼被发现吊死在牢房中。赫顿调查委员会宣布英国政府无罪，但批评了英国广播公司（BBC）在戴维·凯利之死事件中所扮演的角色。北约成员国增加，保加利亚、爱沙尼亚、拉脱维亚、立陶宛、罗马尼亚、斯洛伐克和斯洛文尼亚加入。美国前总统、电影明星罗纳德·里根逝世，享年93岁。奥运会在雅典举行。爱德华·蒙克的画作《呐喊》在奥斯陆被盗。一级方程式赛车手迈克尔·舒马赫赢得创纪录的第七个世界冠军。新的苏格兰议会大厦落成启用。在北爱尔兰，武装劫匪从北爱尔兰银行总部抢走了超过 2200 万英镑。

The Treaty and Final Act establishing the first European Constitution is signed in Rome. Explosions on rush-hour trains in Madrid kill 190 people. Vladimir Putin is re-elected Russian president. The Ukrainian election result is annulled; a new election is held and won by opposition candidate, Viktor Yuschenko. Chechnyan rebels seize a school in Russia; more than 300 adults and children are killed. It emerges that POWs in the Abu Ghraib prison in Iraq have been tortured by their US captors. In Iraq, sovereignty is transferred by the US-led coalition to an Interim government. The UN Security Council calls for the removal of all foreign troops from Lebanon. Hamid Karzai is elected president in Afghanistan. George W. Bush is re-elected president in the United States; Condoleeza Rice becomes secretary of state. A rebellion in Haiti replaces Jean-Bertrand Aristide as president. Prince Norodom Sihamoni becomes king of Cambodia. In one of the worst natural disasters in history, a tsunami kills 300,000 in Indonesia and South Asia. Taipei 101 becomes the world’s tallest building. Drought and locusts threaten the lives of millions in West Africa’s Sahel region. Harold Shipman is found hanged in his cell. The Hutton enquiry exonerates the British government, but criticizes the part played by the BBC in the death of David Kelly. NATO membership is increased with the addition of Bulgaria, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Romania, Slovakia and Slovenia. Former film star and US president, Ronald Reagan dies, aged 93. The Olympic Games take place in Athens. Edvard Munch’s The Scream is stolen in Oslo. Formula One driver Michael Schumacher,wins a record seventh world championship. The new Scottish parliament building is opened. In Northern Ireland, armed robbers steal over £22 million from the headquarters of the Northern Bank.

2005

2005

与基地组织有关联的自杀式炸弹袭击者在伦敦公共交通系统制造了四起爆炸，造成 52 人死亡；14 天后，另一起袭击未遂。

Suicide bombers linked to al-Qaeda kill 52 people in four explosions on London’s public transport system; another attack fails 14 days later.

世界人口接近65亿。在英国，托尼·布莱尔领导的工党以微弱优势再次当选。临时爱尔兰共和军正式宣布结束自1969年以来持续不断的武装斗争。巴黎爆发大规模骚乱，不满的青年群体中爆发骚乱；12天后，希拉克总统宣布进入紧急状态。荷兰和法国举行全民公投，否决了欧洲宪法。基督教民主党人安格拉·默克尔就任德国总理。教皇约翰·保罗二世逝世；四百万哀悼者前往梵蒂冈；德国枢机主教约瑟夫·拉辛格继任教皇本笃十六世。摩纳哥亲王兰尼埃三世逝世；阿尔贝二世继位。亚西尔·阿拉法特去世后，马哈茂德·阿巴斯就任巴勒斯坦权力机构主席。黎巴嫩总理拉菲克·哈里里遭自杀式炸弹袭击身亡。叙利亚在驻扎黎巴嫩29年后，撤出了最后一批军队。伊拉克举行了50多年来的首次自由选举。爆炸和抗议活动持续不断；萨达姆·侯赛因受审。沙特阿拉伯国王法赫德继位，其同父异母兄弟阿卜杜拉继位。乍得向苏丹宣战。卡特里娜飓风袭击美国墨西哥湾沿岸，造成美国历史上最严重的国家灾难之一。厄瓜多尔宣布进入紧急状态；总统逃亡。朝鲜宣布拥有核武器。美国自行车运动员兰斯·阿姆斯特朗史无前例地连续第七次赢得环法自行车赛冠军。一个与基地组织有关联的组织在巴厘岛制造爆炸，造成26人死亡。《京都议定书》在没有美国和澳大利亚支持的情况下生效。在英国，查尔斯王子与卡米拉·帕克·鲍尔斯结婚。迈克尔·杰克逊被判无罪，所有猥亵儿童的指控均不成立。“消除贫困”运动在全球各地举行了8场现场演唱会；在苏格兰格伦伊格尔斯举行的八国集团峰会期间爆发了暴力示威活动。英格兰队赢得灰烬杯板球赛。克什米尔地震造成8万人死亡；爪哇岛地震造成6000人死亡。泰国军方宣布罢免总理他信·西那瓦。朝鲜进行核试验。法国完成首例人脸移植手术。

The population of the world is almost 6½ billion. In Britain, Tony Blair’s Labour Party is re-elected with a reduced majority. The Provisional IRA formally orders an end to its armed campaign, ongoing since 1969. Widespread rioting breaks out among disaffected youths in Paris; President Chirac declares a state of emergency after 12 days. Dutch and French referendums reject the European Constitution. Christian Democrat Angela Merkel becomes chancellor of Germany. Pope John Paul II dies; four million mourners travel to the Vatican; German Cardinal Joseph Ratzinger becomes Benedict XVI. Prince Rainier III of Monaco dies; Albert II succeeds him. Mahmoud Abbas becomes president of the Palestinian Authority following the death of Yasser Arafat. Rafik Hariri, the prime minister of Lebanon, is killed by a suicide bomber. Syria withdraws the last of its troops from Lebanon after 29 years. Iraq holds its first free elections in more than 50 years; bombings and protests continue; Saddam Hussein’s trial begins. King Fahd of Saudi Arabia is succeeded by his half-brother Abdullah. Chad declares war on Sudan. Hurricane Katrina strikes the US Gulf Coast creating one of the worst national disasters in American history. A state of emergency is declared in Ecuador; the president flees. North Korea announces that it possesses nuclear weapons. US cyclist Lance Armstrong wins an unprecedented seventh consecutive Tour de France cycle race. An al-Qaeda-linked organization kills 26 people in explosions on Bali. The Kyoto Protocol on climate change comes into effect without the support of the United States or Australia. In Britain, Prince Charles marries Camilla Parker Bowles. Michael Jackson is acquitted of all child molestation charges. Live 8 concerts in support of Make Poverty History take place across the world; violent demonstrations take place at the G8 conference in Gleneagles in Scotland. England wins the Ashes. 80,000 die in an earthquake in Kashmir; 6,000 die in an earthquake in Java. In Thailand, the army announces the removal of Prime Minister Thaksin Shinawatra from power. North Korea tests a nuclear device. The first human face transplant is carried out in France.

2006

2006

前俄罗斯克格勃特工亚历山大·利特维年科在伦敦一家寿司店因钋-210中毒身亡。

Alexander Litvinenko, a former Russian KGB agent, dies from being poisoned with Polonium-210 in a London sushi bar.

罗马诺·普罗迪在意大利大选中险胜西尔维奥·贝卢斯科尼。埃塔宣布永久停火，停止其争取巴斯克地区脱离西班牙独立的运动。前南斯拉夫总统斯洛博丹·米洛绍维奇在海牙的牢房中被发现死亡。黑山宣布独立；塞尔维亚和黑山解体。以色列总理阿里埃勒·沙龙突发严重中风；埃胡德·奥尔默特接任总理。以色列入侵黎巴嫩；真主党向以色列宣战。哈马斯在巴勒斯坦立法委员会选举中赢得多数席位。萨达姆·侯赛因在巴格达被处决；伊拉克境内持续发生爆炸袭击和抗议活动，反对占领。埃塞俄比亚入侵索马里。乌干达总统约韦里·穆塞韦尼赢得连任，引发坎帕拉骚乱。美国国防部长唐纳德·拉姆斯菲尔德辞职。菲德尔·卡斯特罗在接受手术前，暂时将古巴权力移交给他的弟弟劳尔。朝鲜试射至少七枚导弹。韩国人潘基文就任联合国秘书长。随着禽流感病例增多，世界各国开始防范疫情爆发。意大利队在德国赢得世界杯冠军。美国自行车运动员弗洛伊德·兰迪斯赢得环法自行车赛冠军，但药检呈阳性。

Romano Prodi narrowly defeats Silvio Berlusconi in the Italian general election. ETA declares a permanent ceasefire in its campaign for Basque independence from Spain. Former Yugoslav president Slobodan Milošovi´c is found dead in his cell in The Hague. Montenegro declares independence; Serbia and Montenegro is dissolved. Israeli premier Ariel Sharon suffers a massive stroke; Ehud Olmert takes power. Israel invades Lebanon; Hezbollah declares war against Israel. Hamas wins a majority in elections to the Palestinian Legislative Council. Saddam Hussein is executed in Baghdad; bombings and protests against occupations continue in Iraq. Ethiopia invades Somalia. President Yoweri Museveni wins his second re-election in Uganda, leading to riots in Kampala. US Defence Secretary Donald Rumsfeld, resigns. Fidel Castro temporarily passes power in Cuba to his brother, Raul, prior to surgery. North Korea tests at least seven missiles. South Korean Ban Ki-moon becomes secretary-general of the United Nations. The world prepares for an avian flu epidemic as more human cases occur. Italy wins the World Cup in Germany. American cyclist Floyd Landis win the Tour de France, but fails a drugs test.

2007

2007

美国总统乔治·W·布什宣布向伊拉克增派21500名士兵的计划；轰炸仍在继续。

US President George W. Bush announces a plan to send 21,500 additional troops to Iraq; bombings continue.

英国首相托尼·布莱尔因“以荣誉换取报酬”调查接受质询。阿尔斯特民主统一党领袖伊恩·佩斯利与新芬党主席格里·亚当斯历史性握手。保加利亚和罗马尼亚加入欧盟。由于俄白能源争端升级，俄罗斯切断了对波兰、德国和乌克兰的石油供应；三天后恢复供应。基地组织在阿尔及利亚首都阿尔及尔引爆炸弹，造成33人死亡。伊拉克前情报局长、萨达姆·侯赛因的同父异母兄弟巴尔赞·易卜拉欣·提克里提和前革命法院首席法官阿瓦德·哈米德·班达尔在伊拉克被处决。伊朗革命卫队在伊朗-伊拉克争议水域俘虏英国皇家海军人员，并将其扣押12天。在索马里，伊斯兰法院联盟的武装人员逃往肯尼亚。朝鲜同意放弃核计划以换取石油。美国弗吉尼亚理工大学枪击案：学生赵承熙枪击案，造成32人死亡。俄罗斯前总统叶利钦因心脏衰竭去世，享年76岁。戈登·布朗接替托尼·布莱尔出任英国首相。

British prime minister Tony Blair is questioned in the Cash for Honours investigation. Ulster Democratic Unionist leader, Ian Paisley, exchanges a historic handshake with Sinn Féin president, Gerry Adams. Bulgaria and Romania join the European Union. Russian oil supplies to Poland, Germany, and Ukraine are cut as the Russia–Belarus energy dispute escalates; they are restored after three days. Al-Qaeda kills 33 people with two bombs in the Algerian capital, Algiers. Barzan Ibrahim al-Tikriti, former Iraqi intelligence chief and half-brother of Saddam Hussein, and Awad Hamed al-Bandar, former chief judge of the Revolutionary Court, are executed in Iraq. Iran’s Revolutionary Guard hold Royal Navy personnel for 12 days after capturing them in disputed Iran–Iraq waters. In Somalia, fighters of the Islamic Courts Union flee to Kenya. North Korea agrees to give up its nuclear programme in exchange for oil. Student Cho Seung-hui shoots 32 dead at Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University in the United States. Former Russian president Boris Yeltsin dies of heart failure, aged 76. Gordon Brown succeeds Tony Blair as British prime minister.
